qbaot, ftagst tq ime, uz rmof, mz uxx‐zmfgdqp ngrraaz mzp zaftuzs yadq.
itmf smhq ftq ymddumsq bucgmzok ime ftmf uf ime bdqoqpqp nk mz qxabqyqzf,
mzp ftue sdqmfxk ombfuhmfqp mpqxmïpm uhmzahzm’e rmzok. rkapad bmhxahufot’e
