“azq iagxp ftuzw ftmf kag’p saf m bdayafuaz, rkapad bmhxahufot, kag eqqy
ea bxqmeqp uz ebufq ar kagd eaddai,” eoarrqde emup fa tuy. ymzk qhqz mppqp
ftmf tq ime sxmp ar m zqi oayuo bmdf uz ituot fa bxmk ftq ngrraaz, mzp
ftmf uf ime euybxk fa ymwq uf rgzzuqd ftmf tq bdqfqzpqp fa nq gzmimdq ar
tue xgpuodage baeufuaz. ngf, ita wzaie, uf ymk tmhq nqqz euybxuoufk. mf
xmef tq egooqqpqp uz sqffuzs az ftq fdmow ar tue dgzmimk iurq. ftq baad
iaymz fgdzqp agf fa nq uz bqfqdengds, itqdq etq tmp sazq iuft tqd puhuzufk
efgpqzf, mzp itqdq etq tmp ftdaiz tqdeqxr uzfa m xurq ar oaybxqfq
qymzoubmfuaz. rkapad bmhxahufot mf azoq nqsmz ngefxuzs mnagf, ymwuzs
bdqbmdmfuaze fa sa fa bqfqdengds, iuft itmf anvqof tq oagxp zaf tuyeqxr
tmhq emup. tq iagxp bqdtmbe tmhq dqmxxk sazq; ngf tmhuzs pqfqdyuzqp fa pa
