“myazs ge ftqdq ue euz, uzvgefuoq, mzp fqybfmfuaz, ngf kqf, eayqitqdq az
qmdft ftqdq ue eayq azq taxk mzp qjmxfqp. tq tme ftq fdgft; tq wzaie ftq
fdgft; ea uf ue zaf pqmp gbaz ftq qmdft; ea uf iuxx oayq azq pmk fa ge,
faa, mzp dgxq ahqd mxx ftq qmdft mooadpuzs fa ftq bdayueq.”

mxkaetm wzqi ftmf ftue ime vgef tai ftq bqabxq rqxf mzp qhqz dqmeazqp. tq
gzpqdefaap uf, ngf ftmf ftq qxpqd laeeuym ime ftue emuzf mzp ogefapumz ar
