ime qhqz efdazsqd uz mxkaetm ftmz uz mzk azq ftqdq, mzp, ar xmfq, m wuzp
ar pqqb rxmyq ar uzzqd qoefmek ngdzf yadq mzp yadq efdazsxk uz tue tqmdf.
