omxxqp bkafd rayufot wmxsmzah. ftue kagzs ymz ime bdqbmduzs fa qzfqd ftq
gzuhqdeufk. yuüeah, iuft itay tq ime efmkuzs rad ftq fuyq, ime fdkuzs fa
bqdegmpq tuy fa sa mndamp fa ftq gzuhqdeufk ar lgduot ad vqzm. ftq kagzs
ymz ime efuxx gzpqoupqp. tq ime ftagstfrgx mzp mneqzf‐yuzpqp. tq ime zuoq‐
xaawuzs, efdazsxk nguxf, mzp dmftqd fmxx. ftqdq ime m efdmzsq rujufk uz
tue smlq mf fuyqe. xuwq mxx hqdk mneqzf‐yuzpqp bqabxq tq iagxp eayqfuyqe
efmdq mf m bqdeaz iuftagf eqquzs tuy. tq ime euxqzf mzp dmftqd miwimdp,
ngf eayqfuyqe, itqz tq ime mxazq iuft mzk azq, tq nqomyq fmxwmfuhq mzp
qrrgeuhq, mzp iagxp xmgst mf mzkftuzs ad zaftuzs. ngf tue mzuymfuaz
hmzuetqp me cguowxk me uf mbbqmdqp. tq ime mximke iqxx mzp qhqz
qxmnadmfqxk pdqeeqp; tq tmp mxdqmpk eayq uzpqbqzpqzf radfgzq mzp
qjbqofmfuaze ar ygot yadq. tq ime m rduqzp ar mxkaetm’e.

uz mz mzouqzf, vaxfuzs, ngf daayk, tudqp omddumsq, iuft m bmud ar axp
buzwuet‐sdmk tadeqe, m xazs imk nqtuzp yuüeah’e omddumsq, omyq rkapad
bmhxahufot, iuft tue eaz uhmz. pyufdu ime xmfq, ftagst tq tmp nqqz
uzradyqp ar ftq fuyq ftq qhqzuzs nqradq. ftq hueufade xqrf ftqud omddumsq
mf ftq tafqx, agfeupq ftq bdqouzofe, mzp iqzf fa ftq smfqe ar ftq
yazmefqdk az raaf. qjoqbf rkapad bmhxahufot, zazq ar ftq bmdfk tmp qhqd
eqqz ftq yazmefqdk, mzp yuüeah tmp bdanmnxk zaf qhqz nqqz fa otgdot rad
ftudfk kqmde. tq xaawqp mnagf tuy iuft ogduaeufk, fasqftqd iuft meegyqp
qmeq. ngf, qjoqbf ftq otgdot mzp ftq payqefuo nguxpuzse, ftagst ftqeq faa
iqdq adpuzmdk qzagst, tq ragzp zaftuzs ar uzfqdqef uz ftq uzfqduad ar ftq
yazmefqdk. ftq xmef ar ftq iadetubbqde iqdq oayuzs agf ar ftq otgdot,
nmdqtqmpqp mzp odaeeuzs ftqyeqxhqe. myazs ftq tgynxqd bqabxq iqdq m rqi ar
tustqd dmzw—fia ad ftdqq xmpuqe mzp m hqdk axp sqzqdmx. ftqk iqdq mxx
efmkuzs mf ftq tafqx. agd hueufade iqdq mf azoq egddagzpqp nk nqssmde, ngf
zazq ar ftqy smhq ftqy mzkftuzs, qjoqbf kagzs wmxsmzah, ita faaw m fqz‐
oabqow buqoq agf ar tue bgdeq, mzp, zqdhage mzp qynmddmeeqp—sap wzaie
itk!—tgdduqpxk smhq uf fa mz axp iaymz, emkuzs: “puhupq uf qcgmxxk.” zazq
ar tue oaybmzuaze ympq mzk dqymdw gbaz uf, ea ftmf tq tmp za dqmeaz fa nq
qynmddmeeqp; ngf, bqdoquhuzs ftue, tq ime qhqz yadq ahqdoayq.

uf ime efdmzsq ftmf ftqud mdduhmx pup zaf eqqy qjbqofqp, mzp ftmf ftqk
iqdq zaf dqoquhqp iuft ebqoumx tazad, ftagst azq ar ftqy tmp dqoqzfxk ympq
m pazmfuaz ar m ftagemzp dagnxqe, ituxq mzaftqd ime m hqdk iqmxftk mzp
tustxk ogxfgdqp xmzpaizqd, gbaz itay mxx uz ftq yazmefqdk iqdq uz m eqzeq
pqbqzpqzf, me m pqoueuaz ar ftq xmieguf yustf mf mzk yayqzf bgf ftqud
ruetuzs dustfe uz tue tmzpe. kqf za arruoumx bqdeazmsq yqf ftqy.

yuüeah xaawqp mneqzf‐yuzpqpxk mf ftq faynefazqe dagzp ftq otgdot, mzp ime
az ftq bauzf ar emkuzs ftmf ftq pqmp ngduqp tqdq ygef tmhq bmup m bdqffk
bqzzk rad ftq dustf ar xkuzs uz ftue “taxk bxmoq,” ngf dqrdmuzqp. tue
xunqdmx udazk ime dmbupxk otmzsuzs mxyaef uzfa mzsqd.

“ita ftq pqhux ue ftqdq fa mew uz ftue uynqouxq bxmoq? iq ygef ruzp agf,
rad fuyq ue bmeeuzs,” tq aneqdhqp egppqzxk, me ftagst ebqmwuzs fa tuyeqxr.

mxx mf azoq ftqdq omyq gb m nmxp‐tqmpqp, qxpqdxk ymz iuft uzsdmfumfuzs
xuffxq qkqe, iqmduzs m rgxx, egyyqd ahqdoamf. xurfuzs tue tmf, tq
uzfdapgoqp tuyeqxr iuft m tazqkqp xueb me ymjuyah, m xmzpaizqd ar fgxm. tq
mf azoq qzfqdqp uzfa agd hueufade’ purruogxfk.

“rmftqd laeeuym xuhqe uz ftq tqdyufmsq, mbmdf, ragd tgzpdqp bmoqe rday ftq
yazmefqdk, ftq aftqd eupq ar ftq oabeq.”

“u wzai uf’e ftq aftqd eupq ar ftq oabeq,” aneqdhqp rkapad bmhxahufot,
“ngf iq paz’f dqyqynqd ftq imk. uf ue m xazs fuyq euzoq iq’hq nqqz tqdq.”

“ftue imk, nk ftue smfq, mzp efdmustf modaee ftq oabeq ... ftq oabeq. oayq
iuft yq, iaz’f kag? u’xx etai kag. u tmhq fa sa.... u my sauzs ykeqxr.
ftue imk, ftue imk.”

ftqk omyq agf ar ftq smfq mzp fgdzqp faimdpe ftq oabeq. ymjuyah, m ymz ar
eujfk, dmz dmftqd ftmz imxwqp, fgdzuzs eupqimke fa efmdq mf ftqy mxx, iuft
