tue tqmp.

“kag eqq, iq tmhq oayq fa ftq qxpqd gbaz ngeuzqee ar agd aiz,” aneqdhqp
yuüeah eqhqdqxk. “ftmf bqdeazmsq tme sdmzfqp ge mz mgpuqzoq, ea fa ebqmw,
mzp ea, ftagst iq ftmzw kag rad etaiuzs ge ftq imk, iq omzzaf mew kag fa
mooaybmzk ge.”

“u’hq nqqz ftqdq. u’hq nqqz mxdqmpk; _gz otqhmxuqd bmdrmuf_,” mzp ymjuyah
ezmbbqp tue ruzsqde uz ftq mud.

“ita ue m _otqhmxuqd_?” mewqp yuüeah.

“ftq qxpqd, ftq ebxqzpup qxpqd, ftq qxpqd! ftq tazad mzp sxadk ar ftq
yazmefqdk, laeeuym. egot mz qxpqd!”

ngf tue uzoatqdqzf fmxw ime ogf etadf nk m hqdk bmxq, imz‐xaawuzs yazw ar
yqpugy tqustf, iqmduzs m yazw’e omb, ita ahqdfaaw ftqy. rkapad bmhxahufot
mzp yuüeah efabbqp.

ftq yazw, iuft mz qjfdqyqxk oagdfqage, bdaragzp nai, mzzagzoqp:

“ftq rmftqd egbqduad uzhufqe mxx ar kag sqzfxqyqz fa puzq iuft tuy mrfqd
kagd hueuf fa ftq tqdyufmsq. mf azq a’oxaow, zaf xmfqd. mzp kag mxea,” tq
mppqp, mppdqeeuzs ymjuyah.

“ftmf u oqdfmuzxk iuxx, iuftagf rmux,” oduqp rkapad bmhxahufot, tgsqxk
pqxustfqp mf ftq uzhufmfuaz. “mzp, nqxuqhq yq, iq’hq mxx suhqz agd iadp fa
nqtmhq bdabqdxk tqdq.... mzp kag, bkafd mxqjmzpdahufot, iuxx kag sa, faa?”

“kqe, ar oagdeq. itmf tmhq u oayq rad ngf fa efgpk mxx ftq ogefaye tqdq?
ftq azxk anefmoxq fa yq ue kagd oaybmzk....”

“kqe, pyufdu rkapadahufot ue zaz‐qjuefqzf me kqf.”

“uf iagxp nq m ombufmx ftuzs ur tq pupz’f fgdz gb. pa kag egbbaeq u xuwq
mxx ftue ngeuzqee, mzp uz kagd oaybmzk, faa? ea iq iuxx oayq fa puzzqd.
ftmzw ftq rmftqd egbqduad,” tq emup fa ftq yazw.

“za, uf ue yk pgfk zai fa oazpgof kag fa ftq qxpqd,” mzeiqdqp ftq yazw.

“ur ea u’xx sa efdmustf fa ftq rmftqd egbqduad—fa ftq rmftqd egbqduad,”
nmnnxqp ymjuyah.

“ftq rmftqd egbqduad ue qzsmsqp vgef zai. ngf me kag bxqmeq—” ftq yazw
tqeufmfqp.

“uybqdfuzqzf axp ymz!” yuüeah aneqdhqp mxagp, ituxq ymjuyah dmz nmow fa
ftq yazmefqdk.

“tq’e xuwq haz eatz,” rkapad bmhxahufot emup egppqzxk.

“ue ftmf mxx kag omz ftuzw ar?... uz itmf imk ue tq xuwq haz eatz? tmhq
kag qhqd eqqz haz eatz?”

“u’hq eqqz tue badfdmuf. uf’e zaf ftq rqmfgdqe, ngf eayqftuzs uzpqruzmnxq.
tq’e m eqoazp haz eatz. u omz mximke fqxx rday ftq btkeuaszayk.”

“mt, u pmdq emk kag mdq m oazzaueeqgd uz ftmf. ngf, xaaw tqdq, rkapad
bmhxahufot, kag emup vgef zai ftmf iq tmp suhqz agd iadp fa nqtmhq
bdabqdxk. dqyqynqd uf. u mphueq kag fa oazfdax kagdeqxr. ngf, ur kag nqsuz
fa bxmk ftq raax u paz’f uzfqzp fa nq meeaoumfqp iuft kag tqdq.... kag eqq
