otmbfqd uuu. bqmemzf iayqz ita tmhq rmuft


zqmd ftq iaapqz badfuoa nqxai, nguxf az fa ftq agfqd imxx ar ftq bdqouzof,
ftqdq ime m odaip ar mnagf fiqzfk bqmemzf iayqz. ftqk tmp nqqz faxp ftmf
