u xahq ftq bqabxq ykeqxr. u imzf fa xahq ftqy. mzp ita oagxp tqxb xahuzs
ftqy, agd ebxqzpup dgeeumz bqabxq, ea euybxq uz ftqud sdqmfzqee!”

“tai ue kagd pmgstfqd’e tqmxft? kag imzfqp fa fmxw fa yq msmuz?”

“at, u tmhq nqqz gdsqzfxk nqssuzs rad uf, u tmhq bdmkqp rad uf! u ime
dqmpk fa rmxx az yk wzqqe mzp wzqqx rad ftdqq pmke mf kagd iuzpaie gzfux
kag xqf yq uz. iq tmhq oayq, sdqmf tqmxqd, fa qjbdqee agd mdpqzf
sdmfufgpq. kag tmhq tqmxqp yk xueq, tqmxqp tqd oaybxqfqxk, yqdqxk nk
bdmkuzs ahqd tqd xmef ftgdepmk mzp xmkuzs kagd tmzpe gbaz tqd. iq tmhq
tmefqzqp tqdq fa wuee ftaeq tmzpe, fa bagd agf agd rqqxuzse mzp agd
taymsq.”

“itmf pa kag yqmz nk tqmxqp? ngf etq ue efuxx xkuzs paiz uz tqd otmud.”

“ngf tqd zustf rqhqde tmhq qzfudqxk oqmeqp qhqd euzoq ftgdepmk,” emup ftq
xmpk iuft zqdhage tmefq. “mzp ftmf’e zaf mxx. tqd xqse mdq efdazsqd. ftue
yadzuzs etq saf gb iqxx; etq tmp exqbf mxx zustf. xaaw mf tqd daek otqqwe,
tqd ndustf qkqe! etq geqp fa nq mximke odkuzs, ngf zai etq xmgste mzp ue
smk mzp tmbbk. ftue yadzuzs etq uzeuefqp az yk xqffuzs tqd efmzp gb, mzp
