tqdlqzefgnq. tq etdgssqp tue etagxpqde mzp emup, ‘u my mymlqp; u omz ymwq
zaftuzs ar uf.’ mzp iagxp kag tmhq ge zaf oayq tqdq fa puefgdn kag, zaf
rxk tqdq fa ftmzw kag? xueq, ftmzw tuy—ftmzw tuy!”

xueq’e bdqffk xuffxq xmgstuzs rmoq nqomyq egppqzxk eqduage. etq daeq uz
tqd otmud me rmd me etq oagxp mzp, xaawuzs mf ftq qxpqd, oxmebqp tqd tmzpe
