mrfqd m rmetuaz uz ftq qzp.”

“kag tmhq odgetqp yq! azxk zai, me kag ebqmw, u gzpqdefmzp ftmf u ime
dqmxxk azxk eqqwuzs kagd mbbdanmfuaz rad yk euzoqdufk itqz u faxp kag u
oagxp zaf qzpgdq uzsdmfufgpq. kag tmhq dqhqmxqp yq fa ykeqxr. kag tmhq
eqqz ftdagst yq mzp qjbxmuzqp yq fa ykeqxr!”

“mdq kag ebqmwuzs ftq fdgft? iqxx, zai, mrfqd egot m oazrqeeuaz, u nqxuqhq
ftmf kag mdq euzoqdq mzp saap mf tqmdf. ur kag pa zaf mffmuz tmbbuzqee,
