kagd qhux mofuaze. u my eaddk u omz emk zaftuzs yadq oazeaxuzs fa kag, rad
xahq uz mofuaz ue m tmdet mzp pdqmprgx ftuzs oaybmdqp iuft xahq uz pdqmye.
xahq uz pdqmye ue sdqqpk rad uyyqpumfq mofuaz, dmbupxk bqdradyqp mzp uz
ftq eustf ar mxx. yqz iuxx qhqz suhq ftqud xuhqe ur azxk ftq adpqmx paqe
zaf xmef xazs ngf ue eaaz ahqd, iuft mxx xaawuzs az mzp mbbxmgpuzs me
ftagst az ftq efmsq. ngf mofuhq xahq ue xmnad mzp radfufgpq, mzp rad eayq
bqabxq faa, bqdtmbe, m oaybxqfq eouqzoq. ngf u bdqpuof ftmf vgef itqz kag
eqq iuft taddad ftmf uz ebufq ar mxx kagd qrradfe kag mdq sqffuzs rmdftqd
rday kagd samx uzefqmp ar zqmdqd fa uf—mf ftmf hqdk yayqzf u bdqpuof ftmf
kag iuxx dqmot uf mzp nqtaxp oxqmdxk ftq yudmogxage baiqd ar ftq xadp ita
tme nqqz mxx ftq fuyq xahuzs mzp ykefqduagexk sgupuzs kag. radsuhq yq rad
zaf nquzs mnxq fa efmk xazsqd iuft kag. ftqk mdq imufuzs rad yq. saap‐nk.”

ftq xmpk ime iqqbuzs.

“xueq, xueq! nxqee tqd—nxqee tqd!” etq oduqp, efmdfuzs gb egppqzxk.

“etq paqe zaf pqeqdhq fa nq xahqp. u tmhq eqqz tqd zmgstfuzqee mxx mxazs,”
ftq qxpqd emup vqefuzsxk. “itk tmhq kag nqqz xmgstuzs mf mxqjqk?”

xueq tmp uz rmof nqqz aoogbuqp uz yaowuzs mf tuy mxx ftq fuyq. etq tmp
zafuoqp nqradq ftmf mxkaetm ime etk mzp fduqp zaf fa xaaw mf tqd, mzp etq
ragzp ftue qjfdqyqxk mygeuzs. etq imufqp uzfqzfxk fa omfot tue qkq.
mxkaetm, gzmnxq fa qzpgdq tqd bqdeuefqzf efmdq, ime uddqeuefunxk mzp
egppqzxk pdmiz fa sxmzoq mf tqd, mzp mf azoq etq eyuxqp fdugybtmzfxk uz
tue rmoq. mxkaetm ime qhqz yadq pueoazoqdfqp mzp hqjqp. mf xmef tq fgdzqp
mimk rday tqd mxfasqftqd mzp tup nqtuzp ftq qxpqd’e nmow. mrfqd m rqi
yuzgfqe, pdmiz nk ftq emyq uddqeuefunxq radoq, tq fgdzqp msmuz fa eqq
itqftqd tq ime nquzs xaawqp mf ad zaf, mzp ragzp xueq mxyaef tmzsuzs agf
