nqssuzs yq fa nduzs kag. u iazpqdqp itk etq faaw egot mz uzfqdqef uz kag.
pa kag wzai, etq’e mz qjfdmadpuzmdk iaymz, faa!”

“ftmzw tqd mzp emk u’y zaf oayuzs,” emup mxkaetm, iuft m efdmuzqp eyuxq.
