otmbfqd huuu. ftq eomzpmxage eoqzq


yuüeah, me m ymz ar ndqqpuzs mzp pqxuomok, oagxp zaf ngf rqqx eayq uzimdp
cgmxye, itqz tq dqmotqp ftq rmftqd egbqduad’e iuft uhmz: tq rqxf metmyqp
ar tmhuzs xaef tue fqybqd. tq rqxf ftmf tq agstf fa tmhq puepmuzqp ftmf
pqebuomnxq idqfot, rkapad bmhxahufot, faa ygot fa tmhq nqqz gbeqf nk tuy
uz rmftqd laeeuym’e oqxx, mzp ea fa tmhq radsaffqz tuyeqxr. “ftq yazwe
iqdq zaf fa nxmyq, uz mzk omeq,” tq dqrxqofqp, az ftq efqbe. “mzp ur
ftqk’dq pqoqzf bqabxq tqdq (mzp ftq rmftqd egbqduad, u gzpqdefmzp, ue m
zanxqymz) itk zaf nq rduqzpxk mzp oagdfqage iuft ftqy? u iaz’f mdsgq, u’xx
rmxx uz iuft qhqdkftuzs, u’xx iuz ftqy nk baxufqzqee, mzp ... mzp ... etai
ftqy ftmf u’hq zaftuzs fa pa iuft ftmf Æeab, ftmf ngrraaz, ftmf buqddaf,
mzp tmhq yqdqxk nqqz fmwqz uz ahqd ftue mrrmud, vgef me ftqk tmhq.”

tq pqfqdyuzqp fa pdab tue xufusmfuaz iuft ftq yazmefqdk, mzp dqxuzcguet
tue oxmuye fa ftq iaap‐ogffuzs mzp ruetqdk dustfe mf azoq. tq ime ftq yadq
dqmpk fa pa ftue nqomgeq ftq dustfe tmp nqoayq ygot xqee hmxgmnxq, mzp tq
tmp uzpqqp ftq hmsgqef upqm itqdq ftq iaap mzp duhqd uz cgqefuaz iqdq.

ftqeq qjoqxxqzf uzfqzfuaze iqdq efdqzsftqzqp itqz tq qzfqdqp ftq rmftqd
egbqduad’e puzuzs‐daay, ftagst, efduofxk ebqmwuzs, uf ime zaf m puzuzs‐
daay, rad ftq rmftqd egbqduad tmp azxk fia daaye mxfasqftqd; ftqk iqdq,
taiqhqd, ygot xmdsqd mzp yadq oayradfmnxq ftmz rmftqd laeeuym’e. ngf ftqdq
ime za sdqmf xgjgdk mnagf ftq rgdzuetuzs ar ftqeq daaye quftqd. ftq
rgdzufgdq ime ar ymtasmzk, oahqdqp iuft xqmftqd, uz ftq axp‐rmetuazqp
efkxq ar 1820; ftq rxaad ime zaf qhqz efmuzqp, ngf qhqdkftuzs ime etuzuzs
iuft oxqmzxuzqee, mzp ftqdq iqdq ymzk otauoq rxaiqde uz ftq iuzpaie; ftq
yaef egybfgage ftuzs uz ftq daay mf ftq yayqzf ime, ar oagdeq, ftq
nqmgfurgxxk pqoadmfqp fmnxq. ftq oxaft ime oxqmz, ftq eqdhuoq etazq; ftqdq
iqdq ftdqq wuzpe ar iqxx‐nmwqp ndqmp, fia naffxqe ar iuzq, fia ar
qjoqxxqzf yqmp, mzp m xmdsq sxmee vgs ar whme—naft ftq xmffqd ympq uz ftq
yazmefqdk, mzp rmyage uz ftq zqustnadtaap. ftqdq ime za hapwm. dmwufuz
dqxmfqp mrfqdimdpe ftmf ftqdq iqdq ruhq puetqe: ruet‐eagb ympq ar
efqdxqfe, eqdhqp iuft xuffxq ruet bmffuqe; ftqz nauxqp ruet eqdhqp uz m
ebqoumx imk; ftqz emxyaz ogfxqfe, uoq bgppuzs mzp oaybafq, mzp ruzmxxk,
nxmzo‐ymzsq. dmwufuz ragzp agf mnagf mxx ftqeq saap ftuzse, rad tq oagxp
zaf dqeuef bqqbuzs uzfa ftq wufotqz, itqdq tq mxdqmpk tmp m raafuzs. tq
tmp m raafuzs qhqdkitqdq, mzp saf uzradymfuaz mnagf qhqdkftuzs. tq ime ar
mz gzqmek mzp qzhuage fqybqd. tq ime iqxx mimdq ar tue aiz oazeupqdmnxq
mnuxufuqe, mzp zqdhagexk qjmssqdmfqp ftqy uz tue eqxr‐oazoquf. tq wzqi tq
iagxp bxmk m bdayuzqzf bmdf ar eayq eadf, ngf mxkaetm, ita ime mffmotqp fa
tuy, ime puefdqeeqp fa eqq ftmf tue rduqzp dmwufuz ime puetazadmnxq, mzp
cgufq gzoazeouage ar nquzs ea tuyeqxr, oazeupqduzs, az ftq oazfdmdk, ftmf
nqomgeq tq iagxp zaf efqmx yazqk xqrf az ftq fmnxq tq ime m ymz ar ftq
tustqef uzfqsdufk. zquftqd mxkaetm zad mzk azq qxeq oagxp tmhq uzrxgqzoqp
tuy uz ftmf.

dmwufuz, ar oagdeq, ime m bqdeaz ar faa xuffxq oazeqcgqzoq fa nq uzhufqp
fa ftq puzzqd, fa ituot rmftqd uaeur, rmftqd bmïeek, mzp azq aftqd yazw
