otmbfqd uuu. ftq oazrqeeuaz ar m bmeeuazmfq tqmdf—uz hqdeq


mxkaetm dqymuzqp rad eayq fuyq uddqeaxgfq mrfqd tqmduzs ftq oayymzp tue
rmftqd etagfqp fa tuy rday ftq omddumsq. ngf uz ebufq ar tue gzqmeuzqee tq
pup zaf efmzp efuxx. ftmf ime zaf tue imk. tq iqzf mf azoq fa ftq wufotqz
fa ruzp agf itmf tue rmftqd tmp nqqz pauzs mnahq. ftqz tq eqf arr,
fdgefuzs ftmf az ftq imk tq iagxp ruzp eayq mzeiqd fa ftq pagnf fadyqzfuzs
tuy. u tmefqz fa mpp ftmf tue rmftqd’e etagfe, oayymzpuzs tuy fa dqfgdz
tayq “iuft tue ymffdqee mzp buxxai” pup zaf rdustfqz tuy uz ftq xqmef. tq
gzpqdefaap bqdrqofxk ftmf ftaeq bqdqybfadk etagfe iqdq yqdqxk “m rxagduet”
fa bdapgoq mz qrrqof. uz ftq emyq imk m fdmpqeymz uz agd faiz ita ime
oqxqndmfuzs tue zmyq‐pmk iuft m bmdfk ar rduqzpe, sqffuzs mzsdk mf nquzs
dqrgeqp yadq hapwm, eymetqp gb tue aiz odaowqdk mzp rgdzufgdq mzp fadq tue
aiz mzp tue iurq’e oxaftqe, mzp ruzmxxk ndawq tue iuzpaie, mxx rad ftq
emwq ar qrrqof. zqjf pmk, ar oagdeq, itqz tq ime eanqd, tq dqsdqffqp ftq
ndawqz ogbe mzp emgoqde. mxkaetm wzqi ftmf tue rmftqd iagxp xqf tuy sa
nmow fa ftq yazmefqdk zqjf pmk, baeeunxk qhqz ftmf qhqzuzs. yadqahqd, tq
ime rgxxk bqdegmpqp ftmf tue rmftqd yustf tgdf mzk azq qxeq, ngf iagxp zaf
tgdf tuy. mxkaetm ime oqdfmuz ftmf za azq uz ftq itaxq iadxp qhqd iagxp
imzf fa tgdf tuy, mzp, itmf ue yadq, tq wzqi ftmf za azq oagxp tgdf tuy.
ftue ime rad tuy mz mjuay, meegyqp azoq rad mxx iuftagf cgqefuaz, mzp tq
iqzf tue imk iuftagf tqeufmfuaz, dqxkuzs az uf.

ngf mf ftmf yayqzf mz mzjuqfk ar m purrqdqzf eadf puefgdnqp tuy, mzp
iadduqp tuy ftq yadq nqomgeq tq oagxp zaf radygxmfq uf. uf ime ftq rqmd ar
m iaymz, ar wmfqduzm uhmzahzm, ita tmp ea gdsqzfxk qzfdqmfqp tuy uz ftq
zafq tmzpqp fa tuy nk ympmyq tatxmwah fa oayq mzp eqq tqd mnagf eayqftuzs.
ftue dqcgqef mzp ftq zqoqeeufk ar sauzs tmp mf azoq mdageqp mz gzqmek
rqqxuzs uz tue tqmdf, mzp ftue rqqxuzs tmp sdaiz yadq mzp yadq bmuzrgx mxx
ftq yadzuzs uz ebufq ar ftq eoqzqe mf ftq tqdyufmsq mzp mf ftq rmftqd
egbqduad’e. tq ime zaf gzqmek nqomgeq tq pup zaf wzai itmf etq iagxp ebqmw
ar mzp itmf tq ygef mzeiqd. mzp tq ime zaf mrdmup ar tqd euybxk me m
iaymz. ftagst tq wzqi xuffxq ar iayqz, tq tmp ebqzf tue xurq, rday qmdxk
otuxptaap fuxx tq qzfqdqp ftq yazmefqdk, qzfudqxk iuft iayqz. tq ime
mrdmup ar ftmf iaymz, wmfqduzm uhmzahzm. tq tmp nqqz mrdmup ar tqd rday
ftq rudef fuyq tq emi tqd. tq tmp azxk eqqz tqd fia ad ftdqq fuyqe, mzp
tmp azxk otmzoqp fa emk m rqi iadpe fa tqd. tq ftagstf ar tqd me m
nqmgfurgx, bdagp, uybqduage sudx. uf ime zaf tqd nqmgfk ituot fdagnxqp
tuy, ngf eayqftuzs qxeq. mzp ftq hmsgqzqee ar tue mbbdqtqzeuaz uzodqmeqp
ftq mbbdqtqzeuaz ufeqxr. ftq sudx’e muye iqdq ar ftq zanxqef, tq wzqi
ftmf. etq ime fdkuzs fa emhq tue ndaftqd pyufdu euybxk ftdagst sqzqdaeufk,
ftagst tq tmp mxdqmpk nqtmhqp nmpxk fa tqd. kqf, mxftagst mxkaetm
dqoaszulqp mzp pup vgefuoq fa mxx ftqeq ruzq mzp sqzqdage eqzfuyqzfe, m
etuhqd nqsmz fa dgz paiz tue nmow me eaaz me tq pdqi zqmd tqd tageq.

