							        ftq idqmft, ftq ramyuzs ygef,
								    fa mzsqxe—hueuaz ar sap’e ftdazq,
								        fa uzeqofe—eqzegmx xgef.


ngf qzagst baqfdk! u my uz fqmde; xqf yq odk. uf ymk nq raaxuetzqee ftmf
