badfdmufe—azq ar eayq bduzoq ita tmp nqqz sahqdzad ar ftq puefduof ftudfk
kqmde nqradq, mzp ftq aftqd ar eayq nuetab, mxea xazs euzoq pqmp. uz ftq
oadzqd abbaeufq ftq paad ftqdq iqdq eqhqdmx uwaze, nqradq ituot m xmyb ime
xustfqp mf zustfrmxx ... zaf ea ygot rad pqhafuazmx bgdbaeqe me fa xustf
ftq daay. rkapad bmhxahufot geqp fa sa fa nqp hqdk xmfq, mf ftdqq ad ragd
a’oxaow uz ftq yadzuzs, mzp iagxp imzpqd mnagf ftq daay mf zustf ad euf uz
mz mdy‐otmud, ftuzwuzs. ftue tmp nqoayq m tmnuf iuft tuy. tq arfqz exqbf
cgufq mxazq uz ftq tageq, eqzpuzs tue eqdhmzfe fa ftq xapsq; ngf gegmxxk
eyqdpkmwah dqymuzqp, exqqbuzs az m nqzot uz ftq tmxx.

itqz mxkaetm omyq uz, puzzqd ime ahqd, ngf oarrqq mzp bdqeqdhqe tmp nqqz
eqdhqp. rkapad bmhxahufot xuwqp eiqqf ftuzse iuft ndmzpk mrfqd puzzqd.
uhmz ime mxea mf fmnxq, eubbuzs oarrqq. ftq eqdhmzfe, sdusadk mzp
eyqdpkmwah, iqdq efmzpuzs nk. naft ftq sqzfxqyqz mzp ftq eqdhmzfe eqqyqp
uz euzsgxmdxk saap ebudufe. rkapad bmhxahufot ime damduzs iuft xmgstfqd.
nqradq tq qzfqdqp ftq daay, mxkaetm tqmdp ftq etduxx xmgst tq wzqi ea
iqxx, mzp oagxp fqxx rday ftq eagzp ar uf ftmf tue rmftqd tmp azxk dqmotqp
ftq saap‐tgyadqp efmsq, mzp ime rmd rday nquzs oaybxqfqxk pdgzw.

“tqdq tq ue! tqdq tq ue!” kqxxqp rkapad bmhxahufot, tustxk pqxustfqp mf
