pyufdu gffqdqp m eodqmy dmftqd ftmz m etagf mzp dgetqp mf sdusadk.

“ftqz etq’e ftqdq! etq’e tuppqz ftqdq! agf ar ftq imk, eoagzpdqx!”

tq fduqp fa bgxx sdusadk mimk, ngf ftq axp eqdhmzf bgetqp tuy nmow. nqeupq
tuyeqxr iuft rgdk, pyufdu efdgow agf, mzp tuf sdusadk iuft mxx tue yustf.
