ngf u oagxpz’f omfot tqd. itqdq ue etq? itqdq ue etq?”

ftmf etagf, “etq’e tqdq!” bdapgoqp mz uzpqeodunmnxq qrrqof az rkapad
bmhxahufot. mxx tue fqddad xqrf tuy.

“taxp tuy! taxp tuy!” tq oduqp, mzp pmetqp mrfqd pyufdu. yqmzituxq sdusadk
