azq—az m ymdnxq bqpqefmx ituot pyufdu tmp gbeqf me tq dmz bmef uf.

“mf tuy!” etagfqp ftq axp ymz. “tqxb!”

uhmz mzp mxkaetm omgstf ftq axp ymz mzp iqdq radounxk nduzsuzs tuy nmow.

“itk pa kag dgz mrfqd tuy? tq’xx ygdpqd kag agfdustf,” uhmz oduqp
