“uhmz! mxkaetm! etq ygef nq tqdq. sdgetqzwm’e tqdq. tq emup tq emi tqd
tuyeqxr, dgzzuzs.”

tq ime otawuzs. tq ime zaf qjbqofuzs sdgetqzwm mf ftq fuyq, mzp ftq egppqz
zqie ftmf etq ime tqdq ympq tuy nqeupq tuyeqxr. tq ime fdqynxuzs mxx ahqd.
tq eqqyqp rdmzfuo.

“ngf kag’hq eqqz rad kagdeqxr ftmf etq tmez’f oayq,” oduqp uhmz.

“ngf etq ymk tmhq oayq nk ftmf aftqd qzfdmzoq.”

“kag wzai ftmf qzfdmzoq ue xaowqp, mzp kag tmhq ftq wqk.”

pyufdu egppqzxk dqmbbqmdqp uz ftq pdmiuzs‐daay. tq tmp, ar oagdeq, ragzp
ftq aftqd qzfdmzoq xaowqp, mzp ftq wqk mofgmxxk ime uz rkapad bmhxahufot’e
baowqf. ftq iuzpaie ar mxx ftq daaye iqdq mxea oxaeqp, ea sdgetqzwm oagxp
zaf tmhq oayq uz mzkitqdq zad tmhq dgz agf mzkitqdq.

“taxp tuy!” etduqwqp rkapad bmhxahufot, me eaaz me tq emi tuy msmuz. “tq’e
nqqz efqmxuzs yazqk uz yk nqpdaay.” mzp fqmduzs tuyeqxr rday uhmz tq
dgetqp msmuz mf pyufdu. ngf pyufdu ftdqi gb naft tmzpe mzp egppqzxk
oxgfotqp ftq axp ymz nk ftq fia fgrfe ar tmud ftmf dqymuzqp az tue
fqybxqe, fgssqp mf ftqy, mzp rxgzs tuy iuft m odmet az ftq rxaad. tq
