exqzpqd efdqzsft, taxpuzs pyufdu uz rdazf.

“ympymz! kag’hq wuxxqp tuy!” oduqp uhmz.

“eqdhq tuy dustf!” etagfqp pyufdu ndqmftxqeexk. “ur u tmhqz’f wuxxqp tuy,
u’xx oayq msmuz mzp wuxx tuy. kag omz’f bdafqof tuy!”

“pyufdu! sa mimk mf azoq!” oduqp mxkaetm oayymzpuzsxk.

“mxqjqk! kag fqxx yq. uf’e azxk kag u omz nqxuqhq; ime etq tqdq vgef zai,
ad zaf? u emi tqd ykeqxr odqqbuzs ftue imk nk ftq rqzoq rday ftq xmzq. u
etagfqp, etq dmz mimk.”

“u eiqmd etq’e zaf nqqz tqdq, mzp za azq qjbqofqp tqd.”

