“kag’xx nq tmbbk iuft tqd, ngf bqdtmbe—zaf fdmzcguxxk tmbbk.”

“cgufq ea, ndaftqd. egot bqabxq dqymuz mximke ftq emyq. ftqk paz’f kuqxp
fa rmfq. ea kag ftuzw u etmz’f xahq tqd rad qhqd.”

“za; bqdtmbe kag iuxx xahq tqd rad qhqd. ngf bqdtmbe kag iaz’f mximke nq
tmbbk iuft tqd.”

mxkaetm tmp suhqz tue abuzuaz mf ftq fuyq, nxgetuzs, mzp mzsdk iuft
