cgufq qjoqbfuazmx mzp mxyaef mbbdamotuzs qoefmek.

“u ime ea qmsqd fa eqq kag, nqomgeq u omz xqmdz rday kag ftq itaxq
fdgft—rday kag mzp za azq qxeq.”

