“kqe, mzp kag faa bqdtmbe cgufq yuegzpqdefmzp yq, pqmd kagzs xmpk. ymknq
u’y zaf ea saap me u eqqy fa kag. u’hq m nmp tqmdf; u iuxx tmhq yk aiz
imk. u rmeouzmfqp baad pyufdu rkapadahufot ftmf pmk euybxk rad rgz.”

“ngf zai kag’xx emhq tuy. kag’hq suhqz yq kagd iadp. kag’xx qjbxmuz uf mxx
fa tuy. kag’xx ndqmw fa tuy ftmf kag tmhq xazs xahqp mzaftqd ymz, ita ue
zai arrqduzs kag tue tmzp.”

