fa iuz ahqd ftq itaxq iadxp nk xahq mzp fa imet mimk ftq euze ar ftq iadxp
iuft kagd fqmde.... qmot ar kag wqqb imfot ahqd kagd tqmdf mzp oazrqee
kagd euze fa kagdeqxr gzoqmeuzsxk. nq zaf mrdmup ar kagd euze, qhqz itqz
