azqe myazs ftqy, qebqoumxxk uz agd pmk—tmfq zaf qhqz ftq iuowqp azqe.
dqyqynqd ftqy uz kagd bdmkqde ftge: emhq, a xadp, mxx ftaeq ita tmhq zazq
fa bdmk rad ftqy, emhq faa mxx ftaeq ita iuxx zaf bdmk. mzp mpp: uf ue zaf
uz bdupq ftmf u ymwq ftue bdmkqd, a xadp, rad u my xaiqd ftmz mxx yqz....
xahq sap’e bqabxq, xqf zaf efdmzsqde pdmi mimk ftq rxaow, rad ur kag
exgynqd uz kagd exaftrgxzqee mzp puepmuzrgx bdupq, ad iadeq efuxx, uz
oahqfagezqee, ftqk iuxx oayq rday mxx eupqe mzp pdmi mimk kagd rxaow.
qjbagzp ftq saebqx fa ftq bqabxq gzoqmeuzsxk ... nq zaf qjfadfuazmfq....
pa zaf xahq saxp mzp euxhqd, pa zaf tamdp ftqy.... tmhq rmuft. oxuzs fa
ftq nmzzqd mzp dmueq uf az tust.”

ngf ftq qxpqd ebawq yadq pueoazzqofqpxk ftmz mxkaetm dqbadfqp tue iadpe
mrfqdimdpe. eayqfuyqe tq ndawq arr mxfasqftqd, me ftagst fa fmwq ndqmft,
mzp dqoahqd tue efdqzsft, ngf tq ime uz m eadf ar qoefmek. ftqk tqmdp tuy
iuft qyafuaz, ftagst ymzk iazpqdqp mf tue iadpe mzp ragzp ftqy aneogdq....
mrfqdimdpe mxx dqyqynqdqp ftaeq iadpe.

itqz mxkaetm tmbbqzqp rad m yayqzf fa xqmhq ftq oqxx, tq ime efdgow nk ftq
