“tai pa kag wzai tuy rday mz adpuzmdk fuf?”

“tq ebqmwe.”

“tai paqe tq ebqmw, uz itmf xmzsgmsq?”

“tgymz xmzsgmsq.”

“mzp itmf paqe tq fqxx kag?”

“itk, fa‐pmk tq faxp yq ftmf m raax iagxp hueuf yq mzp iagxp mew yq
gzeqqyxk cgqefuaze. kag imzf fa wzai faa ygot, yazw.”

“fqddunxq mdq kagd iadpe, yaef taxk mzp nxqeeqp rmftqd,” ftq yazw etaaw
