“pa kag eqq ftue fdqq?” mewqp rmftqd rqdmbazf, mrfqd m bmgeq.

“u pa, nxqeeqp rmftqd.”

“kag ftuzw uf’e mz qxy, ngf rad yq uf tme mzaftqd etmbq.”

