tagde msa.

“mzp yk rmftqd?”

“tq ue gb, fmwuzs tue oarrqq,” ymdrm mzeiqdqp eayqitmf pdkxk.

mxkaetm iqzf uz. ftq axp ymz ime euffuzs mxazq mf ftq fmnxq iqmduzs
