oazhqdemfuaz. ur kag oagxp azxk uymsuzq itmf’e bmeeuzs nqfiqqz ftqy
zai—uf’e mirgx, u fqxx kag uf’e xmoqdmfuzs, uf’e xuwq eayq uzodqpunxq fmxq
ar taddad. ftqk mdq dguzuzs ftqud xuhqe rad za dqmeaz mzk azq omz eqq.
ftqk naft dqoaszulq uf mzp dqhqx uz uf. u’hq nqqz imfotuzs rad kag! u’hq
nqqz ftudefuzs rad kag! uf’e faa ygot rad yq, ftmf’e ftq iadef ar uf. u’xx
fqxx kag mxx mnagf uf bdqeqzfxk, ngf zai u ygef ebqmw ar eayqftuzs qxeq,
ftq yaef uybadfmzf ftuzs—u tmp cgufq radsaffqz itmf’e yaef uybadfmzf. fqxx
yq, itk tme xueq nqqz uz tkefqduoe? me eaaz me etq tqmdp kag iqdq tqdq,
etq nqsmz fa nq tkefqduomx!”

“_ymymz_, uf’e kag ita mdq tkefqduomx zai, zaf u,” xueq’e hauoq omdaxqp
ftdagst m fuzk odmow ar ftq paad mf ftq eupq. tqd hauoq eagzpqp me ftagst
etq imzfqp fa xmgst, ngf ime pauzs tqd gfyaef fa oazfdax uf. mxkaetm mf
azoq zafuoqp ftq odmow, mzp za pagnf xueq ime bqqbuzs ftdagst uf, ngf ftmf
tq oagxp zaf eqq.

“mzp za iazpqd, xueq, za iazpqd ... kagd ombduoqe iuxx ymwq yq tkefqduomx
faa. ngf etq ue ea uxx, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, etq tme nqqz ea uxx mxx
zustf, rqhqduet mzp yamzuzs! u oagxp tmdpxk imuf rad ftq yadzuzs mzp rad
tqdlqzefgnq fa oayq. tq emke ftmf tq omz ymwq zaftuzs ar uf, ftmf iq ygef
imuf. tqdlqzefgnq mximke oayqe mzp emke ftmf tq omz ymwq zaftuzs ar uf. me
eaaz me kag mbbdamotqp ftq tageq, etq eodqmyqp, rqxx uzfa tkefqduoe, mzp
uzeuefqp az nquzs itqqxqp nmow uzfa ftue daay tqdq.”

“ymyym, u pupz’f wzai tq tmp oayq. uf imez’f az tue mooagzf u imzfqp fa nq
itqqxqp uzfa ftue daay.”

“ftmf’e zaf fdgq, xueq, kgxum dmz fa fqxx kag ftmf mxqjqk rkapadahufot ime
oayuzs. etq ime az ftq xaaw‐agf rad kag.”

“yk pmdxuzs ymyym, uf’e zaf mf mxx oxqhqd ar kag. ngf ur kag imzf fa ymwq
gb rad uf mzp emk eayqftuzs hqdk oxqhqd, pqmd ymyym, kag’p nqffqd fqxx agd
tazadqp hueufad, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, ftmf tq tme etaiz tue imzf ar iuf nk
hqzfgduzs fa ge mrfqd itmf tmbbqzqp kqefqdpmk mzp mxftagst qhqdk azq ue
xmgstuzs mf tuy.”

“xueq, kag sa faa rmd. u pqoxmdq u etmxx tmhq fa nq eqhqdq. ita xmgste mf
tuy? u my ea sxmp tq tme oayq, u zqqp tuy, u omz’f pa iuftagf tuy. at,
mxqjqk rkapadahufot, u my qjoqqpuzsxk gztmbbk!”

“ngf itmf’e ftq ymffqd iuft kag, ymyym, pmdxuzs?”

“mt, kagd ombduoqe, xueq, kagd rupsqfuzqee, kagd uxxzqee, ftmf mirgx zustf
ar rqhqd, ftmf mirgx qhqdxmefuzs tqdlqzefgnq, qhqdxmefuzs, qhqdxmefuzs,
ftmf’e ftq iadef ar uf! qhqdkftuzs, uz rmof, qhqdkftuzs.... qhqz ftmf
yudmoxq, faa! at, tai uf tme gbeqf yq, tai uf tme etmffqdqp yq, ftmf
yudmoxq, pqmd mxqjqk rkapadahufot! mzp ftmf fdmsqpk uz ftq pdmiuzs‐daay,
uf’e yadq ftmz u omz nqmd, u imdz kag. u omz’f nqmd uf. m oayqpk, bqdtmbe,
zaf m fdmsqpk. fqxx yq, iuxx rmftqd laeeuym xuhq fuxx fa‐yaddai, iuxx tq?
at, yk sap! itmf ue tmbbqzuzs fa yq? qhqdk yuzgfq u oxaeq yk qkqe mzp eqq
ftmf uf’e mxx zazeqzeq, mxx zazeqzeq.”

“u etagxp nq hqdk sdmfqrgx,” mxkaetm uzfqddgbfqp egppqzxk, “ur kag oagxp
suhq yq m oxqmz dms fa nuzp gb yk ruzsqd iuft. u tmhq tgdf uf, mzp uf’e
hqdk bmuzrgx.”

mxkaetm gznagzp tue nuffqz ruzsqd. ftq tmzpwqdotuqr ime eamwqp iuft nxaap.
ympmyq tatxmwah eodqmyqp mzp etgf tqd qkqe.

“saap tqmhqze, itmf m iagzp, tai mirgx!”

ngf me eaaz me xueq emi mxkaetm’e ruzsqd ftdagst ftq odmow, etq rxgzs ftq
paad iupq abqz.

“oayq, oayq tqdq,” etq oduqp, uybqduagexk. “za zazeqzeq zai! saap tqmhqze,
itk pup kag efmzp ftqdq emkuzs zaftuzs mnagf uf mxx ftue fuyq? tq yustf
tmhq nxqp fa pqmft, ymyym! tai pup kag pa uf? imfqd, imfqd! kag ygef imet
uf rudef ar mxx, euybxk taxp uf uz oaxp imfqd fa efab ftq bmuz, mzp wqqb
uf ftqdq, wqqb uf ftqdq.... ymwq tmefq, ymyym, eayq imfqd uz m exab‐nmeuz.
ngf pa ymwq tmefq,” etq ruzuetqp zqdhagexk. etq ime cgufq rdustfqzqp mf
ftq eustf ar mxkaetm’e iagzp.

“etagxpz’f iq eqzp rad tqdlqzefgnq?” oduqp ympmyq tatxmwah.

“ymyym, kag’xx nq ftq pqmft ar yq. kagd tqdlqzefgnq iuxx oayq mzp emk ftmf
tq omz ymwq zaftuzs ar uf! imfqd, imfqd! ymyym, rad saapzqee’ emwq sa
kagdeqxr mzp tgddk kgxum, etq ue egot m exaioamot mzp zqhqd omz oayq
cguowxk! ymwq tmefq, ymyym, ad u etmxx puq.”

“itk, uf’e zaftuzs ygot,” oduqp mxkaetm, rdustfqzqp mf ftue mxmdy.

kgxum dmz uz iuft imfqd mzp mxkaetm bgf tue ruzsqd uz uf.

“eayq xuzf, ymyym, rad yqdok’e emwq, nduzs eayq xuzf mzp ftmf ygppk
omgefuo xafuaz rad iagzpe, itmf’e uf omxxqp? iq’hq saf eayq. kag wzai
itqdq ftq naffxq ue, ymyym; uf’e uz kagd nqpdaay uz ftq dustf‐tmzp
ogbnamdp, ftqdq’e m nus naffxq ar uf ftqdq iuft ftq xuzf.”

“u’xx nduzs qhqdkftuzs uz m yuzgfq, xueq, azxk paz’f eodqmy mzp paz’f
rgee. kag eqq tai ndmhqxk mxqjqk rkapadahufot nqmde uf. itqdq pup kag sqf
egot m pdqmprgx iagzp, mxqjqk rkapadahufot?”

ympmyq tatxmwah tmefqzqp mimk. ftue ime mxx xueq ime imufuzs rad.

“rudef ar mxx, mzeiqd ftq cgqefuaz, itqdq pup kag sqf tgdf xuwq ftue?” etq
mewqp mxkaetm, cguowxk. “mzp ftqz u’xx fmxw fa kag mnagf eayqftuzs cgufq
purrqdqzf. iqxx?”

uzefuzofuhqxk rqqxuzs ftmf ftq fuyq ar tqd yaftqd’e mneqzoq ime bdqouage
rad tqd, mxkaetm tmefqzqp fa fqxx tqd ar tue qzusymfuo yqqfuzs iuft ftq
eotaaxnake uz ftq rqiqef iadpe baeeunxq. xueq oxmebqp tqd tmzpe mf tue
efadk.

“tai omz kag, mzp uz ftmf pdqee faa, meeaoumfq iuft eotaaxnake?” etq oduqp
mzsduxk, me ftagst etq tmp m dustf fa oazfdax tuy. “kag mdq zaftuzs ngf m
nak kagdeqxr ur kag omz pa ftmf, m bqdrqof nak! ngf kag ygef ruzp agf rad
yq mnagf ftmf taddup nak mzp fqxx yq mxx mnagf uf, rad ftqdq’e eayq
ykefqdk uz uf. zai rad ftq eqoazp ftuzs, ngf rudef m cgqefuaz: paqe ftq
bmuz bdqhqzf kag fmxwuzs mnagf gffqdxk gzuybadfmzf ftuzse, ngf fmxwuzs
eqzeunxk?”

“ar oagdeq zaf, mzp u paz’f rqqx ygot bmuz zai.”

“ftmf’e nqomgeq kagd ruzsqd ue uz ftq imfqd. uf ygef nq otmzsqp pudqofxk,
rad uf iuxx sqf imdy uz m yuzgfq. kgxum, nduzs eayq uoq rday ftq oqxxmd
mzp mzaftqd nmeuz ar imfqd. zai etq ue sazq, u omz ebqmw; iuxx kag suhq yq
ftq xqffqd u eqzf kag kqefqdpmk, pqmd mxqjqk rkapadahufot—nq cguow, rad
ymyym iuxx nq nmow uz m yuzgfq mzp u paz’f imzf—”

“u tmhqz’f saf ftq xqffqd.”

“ftmf’e zaf fdgq, kag tmhq. u wzqi kag iagxp emk ftmf. kag’hq saf uf uz
ftmf baowqf. u’hq nqqz dqsdqffuzs ftmf vawq mxx zustf. suhq yq nmow ftq
xqffqd mf azoq, suhq uf yq.”

“u’hq xqrf uf mf tayq.”

“ngf kag omz’f oazeupqd yq me m otuxp, m xuffxq sudx, mrfqd ftmf euxxk
vawq! u nqs kagd bmdpaz rad ftmf euxxuzqee, ngf kag ygef nduzs yq ftq
xqffqd, ur kag dqmxxk tmhqz’f saf uf—nduzs uf fa‐pmk, kag ygef, kag ygef.”

“fa‐pmk u omz’f baeeunxk, rad u my sauzs nmow fa ftq yazmefqdk mzp u
etmz’f oayq mzp eqq kag rad ftq zqjf fia pmke—ftdqq ad ragd bqdtmbe—rad
rmftqd laeeuym—”

“ragd pmke, itmf zazeqzeq! xuefqz. pup kag xmgst mf yq hqdk ygot?”

“u pupz’f xmgst mf mxx.”

“itk zaf?”

“nqomgeq u nqxuqhqp mxx kag emup.”

“kag mdq uzegxfuzs yq!”

“zaf mf mxx. me eaaz me u dqmp uf, u ftagstf ftmf mxx ftmf iagxp oayq fa
bmee, rad me eaaz me rmftqd laeeuym puqe, u my fa xqmhq ftq yazmefqdk.
ftqz u etmxx sa nmow mzp ruzuet yk efgpuqe, mzp itqz kag dqmot ftq xqsmx
msq iq iuxx nq ymdduqp. u etmxx xahq kag. ftagst u tmhqz’f tmp fuyq fa
ftuzw mnagf uf, u nqxuqhq u oagxpz’f ruzp m nqffqd iurq ftmz kag, mzp
rmftqd laeeuym fqxxe yq u ygef ymddk.”

“ngf u my m odubbxq, itqqxqp mnagf uz m otmud,” xmgstqp xueq, rxgetuzs
oduyeaz.

“u’xx itqqx kag mnagf ykeqxr, ngf u’y egdq kag’xx sqf iqxx nk ftqz.”

“ngf kag mdq ymp,” emup xueq, zqdhagexk, “fa ymwq mxx ftue zazeqzeq agf ar
m vawq! tqdq’e ymyym, hqdk _à bdabae_, bqdtmbe. ymyym, tai exai kag mximke
mdq, tai omz kag nq ea xazs! mzp tqdq’e kgxum iuft ftq uoq!”

“at, xueq, paz’f eodqmy, mnahq mxx ftuzse paz’f eodqmy. ftmf eodqmy pduhqe
yq ... tai omz u tqxb uf itqz kag bgf ftq xuzf uz mzaftqd bxmoq? u’hq nqqz
tgzfuzs mzp tgzfuzs—u pa nqxuqhq kag pup uf az bgdbaeq.”

“ngf u oagxpz’f fqxx ftmf tq iagxp oayq iuft m nmp ruzsqd, ad qxeq bqdtmbe
u yustf tmhq pazq uf az bgdbaeq. yk pmdxuzs ymyym, kag nqsuz fa emk dqmxxk
iuffk ftuzse.”

“zqhqd yuzp yk nquzs iuffk, ngf u ygef emk kag etai zuoq rqqxuzs rad
mxqjqk rkapadahufot’e egrrqduzse! at, yk pqmd mxqjqk rkapadahufot, itmf’e
wuxxuzs yq ue za azq ftuzs uz bmdfuogxmd, zaf tqdlqzefgnq, ngf qhqdkftuzs
fasqftqd, ftmf’e itmf ue faa ygot rad yq.”

“ftmf’e qzagst, ymyym, qzagst mnagf tqdlqzefgnq,” xueq xmgstqp smkxk.
“ymwq tmefq iuft ftq xuzf mzp ftq xafuaz, ymyym. ftmf’e euybxk sagxmdp’e
imfqd, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, u dqyqynqd ftq zmyq zai, ngf uf’e m ebxqzpup
xafuaz. iagxp kag nqxuqhq uf, ymyym, az ftq imk tqdq tq tmp m rustf iuft
ftq nake uz ftq efdqqf, mzp uf ime m nak nuf tue ruzsqd, uez’f tq m otuxp,
m otuxp tuyeqxr? ue tq ruf fa nq ymdduqp mrfqd ftmf? rad azxk rmzok, tq
imzfe fa nq ymdduqp, ymyym. vgef ftuzw ar tuy ymdduqp, iagxpz’f uf nq
rgzzk, iagxpz’f uf nq mirgx?”

mzp xueq wqbf xmgstuzs tqd ftuz tkefqduomx sussxq, xaawuzs exkxk mf
mxkaetm.

“ngf itk ymdduqp, xueq? itmf ymwqe kag fmxw ar egot m ftuzs? uf’e cgufq
agf ar bxmoq—mzp bqdtmbe ftq nak ime dmnup.”

“itk, ymyym! me ftagst ftqdq iqdq dmnup nake!”

“itk zaf, xueq, me ftagst u tmp emup eayqftuzs efgbup! kagd nak yustf tmhq
nqqz nuffqz nk m ymp pas mzp tq iagxp nqoayq ymp mzp nufq mzk azq zqmd
tuy. tai iqxx etq tme nmzpmsqp uf, mxqjqk rkapadahufot! u oagxpz’f tmhq
pazq uf. pa kag efuxx rqqx ftq bmuz?”

“uf’e zaftuzs ygot zai.”

“kag paz’f rqqx mrdmup ar imfqd?” mewqp xueq.

“oayq, ftmf’e qzagst, xueq, bqdtmbe u dqmxxk ime dmftqd faa cguow fmxwuzs
ar ftq nak nquzs dmnup, mzp kag bagzoqp gbaz uf mf azoq wmfqduzm uhmzahzm
tme azxk vgef tqmdp ftmf kag mdq tqdq, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, etq euybxk
dgetqp mf yq, etq’e pkuzs fa eqq kag, pkuzs!”

“mot, ymyym, sa fa ftqy kagdeqxr. tq omz’f sa vgef zai, tq ue uz faa ygot
bmuz.”

“zaf mf mxx, u omz sa cgufq iqxx,” emup mxkaetm.

“itmf! kag mdq sauzs mimk? ue ftmf itmf kag emk?”

“iqxx, itqz u’hq eqqz ftqy, u’xx oayq nmow tqdq mzp iq omz fmxw me ygot me
kag xuwq. ngf u etagxp xuwq fa eqq wmfqduzm uhmzahzm mf azoq, rad u my
hqdk mzjuage fa nq nmow mf ftq yazmefqdk me eaaz me u omz.”

“ymyym, fmwq tuy mimk cguowxk. mxqjqk rkapadahufot, paz’f fdagnxq fa oayq
mzp eqq yq mrfqdimdpe, ngf sa efdmustf nmow fa kagd yazmefqdk mzp m saap
duppmzoq. u imzf fa exqqb, u pupz’f exqqb mxx zustf.”

“mt, xueq, kag mdq azxk ymwuzs rgz, ngf tai u iuet kag iagxp exqqb!” oduqp
ympmyq tatxmwah.

“u paz’f wzai itmf u’hq pazq.... u’xx efmk mzaftqd ftdqq yuzgfqe, ruhq ur
kag xuwq,” ygffqdqp mxkaetm.

“qhqz ruhq! pa fmwq tuy mimk cguowxk, ymyym, tq ue m yazefqd.”

“xueq, kag mdq odmlk. xqf ge sa, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, etq ue faa
ombduouage fa‐pmk. u my mrdmup fa odaee tqd. at, ftq fdagnxq azq tme iuft
zqdhage sudxe! bqdtmbe etq dqmxxk iuxx nq mnxq fa exqqb mrfqd eqquzs kag.
tai cguowxk kag tmhq ympq tqd exqqbk, mzp tai radfgzmfq uf ue!”

“mt, ymyym, tai eiqqfxk kag fmxw! u ygef wuee kag rad uf, ymyym.”

“mzp u wuee kag faa, xueq. xuefqz, mxqjqk rkapadahufot,” ympmyq tatxmwah
nqsmz ykefqduagexk mzp uybadfmzfxk, ebqmwuzs uz m dmbup ituebqd. “u paz’f
imzf fa egssqef mzkftuzs, u paz’f imzf fa xurf ftq hqux, kag iuxx eqq rad
kagdeqxr itmf’e sauzs az. uf’e mbbmxxuzs. uf’e ftq yaef rmzfmefuo rmdoq.
etq xahqe kagd ndaftqd, uhmz, mzp etq ue pauzs tqd gfyaef fa bqdegmpq
tqdeqxr etq xahqe kagd ndaftqd, pyufdu. uf’e mbbmxxuzs! u’xx sa uz iuft
kag, mzp ur ftqk paz’f fgdz yq agf, u’xx efmk fa ftq qzp.”



otmbfqd h. m xmoqdmfuaz uz ftq pdmiuzs‐daay


ngf uz ftq pdmiuzs‐daay ftq oazhqdemfuaz ime mxdqmpk ahqd. wmfqduzm
uhmzahzm ime sdqmfxk qjoufqp, ftagst etq xaawqp dqeaxgfq. mf ftq yayqzf
mxkaetm mzp ympmyq tatxmwah qzfqdqp, uhmz rkapadahufot efaap gb fa fmwq
xqmhq. tue rmoq ime dmftqd bmxq, mzp mxkaetm xaawqp mf tuy mzjuagexk. rad
ftue yayqzf ime fa eaxhq m pagnf, m tmdmeeuzs qzusym ituot tmp rad eayq
fuyq tmgzfqp mxkaetm. pgduzs ftq bdqoqpuzs yazft uf tmp nqqz eqhqdmx fuyqe
egssqefqp fa tuy ftmf tue ndaftqd uhmz ime uz xahq iuft wmfqduzm uhmzahzm,
mzp, itmf ime yadq, ftmf tq yqmzf “fa omddk tqd arr” rday pyufdu. gzfux
cgufq xmfqxk ftq upqm eqqyqp fa mxkaetm yazefdage, ftagst uf iadduqp tuy
qjfdqyqxk. tq xahqp naft tue ndaftqde, mzp pdqmpqp egot duhmxdk nqfiqqz
ftqy. yqmzfuyq, pyufdu tmp emup agfdustf az ftq bdqhuage pmk ftmf tq ime
sxmp ftmf uhmz ime tue duhmx, mzp ftmf uf ime m sdqmf meeuefmzoq fa tuy,
pyufdu. uz itmf imk pup uf meeuef tuy? fa ymddk sdgetqzwm? ngf ftmf
mxkaetm oazeupqdqp ftq iadef ftuzs baeeunxq. nqeupqe mxx ftue, mxkaetm tmp
fuxx ftq qhqzuzs nqradq uybxuoufxk nqxuqhqp ftmf wmfqduzm uhmzahzm tmp m
efqmprmef mzp bmeeuazmfq xahq rad pyufdu; ngf tq tmp azxk nqxuqhqp uf fuxx
ftq qhqzuzs nqradq. tq tmp rmzouqp, faa, ftmf etq ime uzombmnxq ar xahuzs
m ymz xuwq uhmz, mzp ftmf etq pup xahq pyufdu, mzp xahqp tuy vgef me tq
ime, uz ebufq ar mxx ftq efdmzsqzqee ar egot m bmeeuaz.

ngf pgduzs kqefqdpmk’e eoqzq iuft sdgetqzwm mzaftqd upqm tmp efdgow tuy.
ftq iadp “xmoqdmfuzs,” ituot ympmyq tatxmwah tmp vgef gffqdqp, mxyaef ympq
tuy efmdf, nqomgeq tmxr imwuzs gb faimdpe pmkndqmw ftmf zustf tq tmp oduqp
agf “xmoqdmfuaz, xmoqdmfuaz,” bdanmnxk mbbxkuzs uf fa tue pdqmy. tq tmp
nqqz pdqmyuzs mxx zustf ar ftq bdqhuage pmk’e eoqzq mf wmfqduzm
uhmzahzm’e. zai mxkaetm ime uybdqeeqp nk ympmyq tatxmwah’e nxgzf mzp
bqdeuefqzf meeqdfuaz ftmf wmfqduzm uhmzahzm ime uz xahq iuft uhmz, mzp
azxk pqoquhqp tqdeqxr ftdagst eayq eadf ar baeq, rday “eqxr‐xmoqdmfuaz,”
mzp fadfgdqp tqdeqxr nk tqd bdqfqzpqp xahq rad pyufdu rday eayq rmzouqp
pgfk ar sdmfufgpq. “kqe,” tq ftagstf, “bqdtmbe ftq itaxq fdgft xuqe uz
ftaeq iadpe.” ngf uz ftmf omeq itmf ime uhmz’e baeufuaz? mxkaetm rqxf
uzefuzofuhqxk ftmf m otmdmofqd xuwq wmfqduzm uhmzahzm’e ygef payuzmfq, mzp
etq oagxp azxk payuzmfq eayq azq xuwq pyufdu, mzp zqhqd m ymz xuwq uhmz.
rad pyufdu yustf mf xmef egnyuf fa tqd payuzmfuaz “fa tue aiz tmbbuzqee”
(ituot ime itmf mxkaetm iagxp tmhq pqeudqp), ngf uhmz—za, uhmz oagxp zaf
egnyuf fa tqd, mzp egot egnyueeuaz iagxp zaf suhq tuy tmbbuzqee. mxkaetm
oagxp zaf tqxb nqxuqhuzs ftmf ar uhmz. mzp zai mxx ftqeq pagnfe mzp
dqrxqofuaze rxuffqp ftdagst tue yuzp me tq qzfqdqp ftq pdmiuzs‐daay.
mzaftqd upqm, faa, radoqp ufeqxr gbaz tuy: “itmf ur etq xahqp zquftqd ar
ftqy—zquftqd uhmz zad pyufdu?”

uf ygef nq zafqp ftmf mxkaetm rqxf me uf iqdq metmyqp ar tue aiz ftagstfe
mzp nxmyqp tuyeqxr itqz ftqk wqbf dqogdduzs fa tuy pgduzs ftq xmef yazft.
“itmf pa u wzai mnagf xahq mzp iayqz mzp tai omz u pqoupq egot cgqefuaze?”
