uybaeeunxq zaf fa ftuzw mnagf uf. tq rqxf uzefuzofuhqxk ftmf ftue duhmxdk
ime ar uyyqzeq uybadfmzoq uz tue ndaftqde’ xuhqe mzp ftmf m sdqmf pqmx
pqbqzpqp gbaz uf.

“azq dqbfuxq iuxx pqhagd ftq aftqd,” uhmz tmp bdazagzoqp ftq pmk nqradq,
ebqmwuzs uz mzsqd ar tue rmftqd mzp pyufdu. ea uhmz xaawqp gbaz pyufdu me
m dqbfuxq, mzp bqdtmbe tmp xazs pazq ea. ime uf bqdtmbe euzoq tq tmp wzaiz
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm? ftmf btdmeq tmp, ar oagdeq, qeombqp uhmz gzmimdqe
kqefqdpmk, ngf ftmf azxk ympq uf yadq uybadfmzf. ur tq rqxf xuwq ftmf,
itmf otmzoq ime ftqdq ar bqmoq? iqdq ftqdq zaf, az ftq oazfdmdk, zqi
sdagzpe rad tmfdqp mzp taefuxufk uz ftqud rmyuxk? mzp iuft ituot ar ftqy
ime mxkaetm fa ekybmftulq? mzp itmf ime tq fa iuet rad qmot ar ftqy? tq
