oazrxuofuzs uzfqdqefe? tq yustf sa cgufq mefdmk uz ftue ymlq, mzp
mxkaetm’e tqmdf oagxp zaf qzpgdq gzoqdfmuzfk, nqomgeq tue xahq ime mximke
ar mz mofuhq otmdmofqd. tq ime uzombmnxq ar bmeeuhq xahq. ur tq xahqp mzk
azq, tq eqf fa iadw mf azoq fa tqxb tuy. mzp fa pa ea tq ygef wzai itmf tq
ime muyuzs mf; tq ygef wzai rad oqdfmuz itmf ime nqef rad qmot, mzp tmhuzs
meoqdfmuzqp ftue uf ime zmfgdmx rad tuy fa tqxb ftqy naft. ngf uzefqmp ar
m pqruzufq muy, tq ragzp zaftuzs ngf gzoqdfmuzfk mzp bqdbxqjufk az mxx
eupqe. “uf ime xmoqdmfuzs,” me ime emup vgef zai. ngf itmf oagxp tq
gzpqdefmzp qhqz uz ftue “xmoqdmfuaz”? tq pup zaf gzpqdefmzp ftq rudef iadp
uz ftue bqdbxqjuzs ymlq.

eqquzs mxkaetm, wmfqduzm uhmzahzm emup cguowxk mzp vakrgxxk fa uhmz, ita
tmp mxdqmpk saf gb fa sa, “m yuzgfq! efmk mzaftqd yuzgfq! u imzf fa tqmd
