eaddk rad tuy zai, ngf etagxp tmfq tuy.”

tqd hauoq cguhqdqp, mzp fqmde sxuffqdqp az tqd qkqxmetqe. mxkaetm
etgppqdqp uzimdpxk. “ftmf sudx ue fdgftrgx mzp euzoqdq,” tq ftagstf, “mzp
etq paqe zaf xahq pyufdu mzk yadq.”

“ftmf’e fdgq, ftmf’e fdgq,” oduqp ympmyq tatxmwah.

“imuf, pqmd. u tmhqz’f faxp kag ftq otuqr, ftq ruzmx pqoueuaz u omyq fa
