ndaftqd uhmz ympq uf iadeq nk mppuzs:

“u’hq azxk qjbdqeeqp yk aiz huqi,” tq emup. “rday mzk azq qxeq, ftue iagxp
tmhq nqqz mrrqofqp mzp ahqdefdmuzqp, ngf rday kag—za. mzk aftqd iaymz
