ngf u eqq ftmf kag mdq mneaxgfqxk sqzguzq mzp, ftqdqradq, kag mdq dustf.”

“ngf ftmf’e azxk rad ftq yayqzf. mzp itmf paqe ftue yayqzf efmzp rad?
