“uf’e zaftuzs, zaftuzs!” etq iqzf az ftdagst tqd fqmde. “u’y gbeqf, u
pupz’f exqqb xmef zustf. ngf nk ftq eupq ar fia egot rduqzpe me kag mzp
kagd ndaftqd u efuxx rqqx efdazs—rad u wzai—kag fia iuxx zqhqd pqeqdf yq.”

“gzxgowuxk u my anxusqp fa dqfgdz fa yaeoai—bqdtmbe fa‐yaddai—mzp fa xqmhq
kag rad m xazs fuyq—mzp, gzxgowuxk, uf’e gzmhaupmnxq,” uhmz emup egppqzxk.

