baeeqeeqp mzp qhqz qjoqqpuzsxk bxqmeqp, me ftagst eayqftuzs msdqqmnxq tmp
vgef tmbbqzqp.

“at, zaf radfgzmfq ftmf u my xaeuzs kag, ar oagdeq zaf,” etq oaddqofqp
tqdeqxr egppqzxk, iuft m otmdyuzs eaouqfk eyuxq. “egot m rduqzp me kag mdq
oagxp zaf egbbaeq ftmf. u my azxk faa gztmbbk mf xaeuzs kag.” etq dgetqp
uybgxeuhqxk mf uhmz, mzp equluzs naft tue tmzpe, bdqeeqp ftqy imdyxk. “ngf
itmf ue radfgzmfq ue ftmf kag iuxx nq mnxq uz yaeoai fa eqq mgzfuq mzp
msmrkm mzp fa fqxx ftqy mxx ftq taddad ar yk bdqeqzf baeufuaz. kag omz
ebqmw iuft oaybxqfq abqzzqee fa msmrkm, ngf ebmdq pqmd mgzfuq. kag iuxx
wzai tai fa pa ftmf. kag omz’f ftuzw tai idqfotqp u ime kqefqdpmk mzp ftue
