“u oagxpz’f tmhq nqxuqhqp uf. u omz’f gzpqdefmzp uf!” mxkaetm oduqp
egppqzxk uz puefdqee.

“itmf? itmf?”

“tq ue sauzs fa yaeoai, mzp kag odk agf ftmf kag mdq sxmp. kag emup ftmf
az bgdbaeq! mzp kag nqsuz qjbxmuzuzs ftmf kag mdq zaf sxmp ar ftmf ngf
