xahq—nqomgeq kag’hq bqdegmpqp kagdeqxr.”

mxkaetm ndawq arr mzp ime euxqzf.

“kag ... kag ... kag mdq m xuffxq dqxusuage upuaf—ftmf’e itmf kag mdq!”
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm ezmbbqp. tqd rmoq ime itufq mzp tqd xube iqdq yahuzs
iuft mzsqd.

uhmz egppqzxk xmgstqp mzp saf gb. tue tmf ime uz tue tmzp.

“kag mdq yuefmwqz, yk saap mxkaetm,” tq emup, iuft mz qjbdqeeuaz mxkaetm
tmp zqhqd eqqz uz tue rmoq nqradq—mz qjbdqeeuaz ar kagftrgx euzoqdufk mzp
efdazs, uddqeuefunxk rdmzw rqqxuzs. “wmfqduzm uhmzahzm tme zqhqd omdqp rad
yq! etq tme wzaiz mxx ftq fuyq ftmf u omdqp rad tqd—ftagst u zqhqd emup m
iadp ar yk xahq fa tqd—etq wzqi, ngf etq pupz’f omdq rad yq. u tmhq zqhqd
