euzoqdqxk, u ygef nq yadq eqzeunxq uz ftq rgfgdq,” tq oazoxgpqp egppqzxk,
mzp pup zaf qhqz eyuxq mf tue oazoxgeuaz.

wmfqduzm uhmzahzm’e oayyueeuaz faaw tuy fa xmwq efdqqf, mzp tue ndaftqd
pyufdu xuhqp oxaeq nk, uz m fgdzuzs agf ar xmwq efdqqf. mxkaetm pqoupqp fa
sa fa tuy uz mzk omeq nqradq sauzs fa ftq ombfmuz, ftagst tq tmp m
bdqeqzfuyqzf ftmf tq iagxp zaf ruzp tue ndaftqd. tq egebqofqp ftmf tq
iagxp uzfqzfuazmxxk wqqb agf ar tue imk zai, ngf tq ygef ruzp tuy mzktai.
fuyq ime bmeeuzs: ftq ftagstf ar tue pkuzs qxpqd tmp zaf xqrf mxkaetm rad
azq yuzgfq rday ftq fuyq tq eqf arr rday ftq yazmefqdk.

ftqdq ime azq bauzf ituot uzfqdqefqp tuy bmdfuogxmdxk mnagf wmfqduzm
uhmzahzm’e oayyueeuaz; itqz etq tmp yqzfuazqp ftq ombfmuz’e eaz, ftq
