ruzsqd itqz tq, mxkaetm, mewqp tuy itmf tq tmp pazq fa tgdf tuy. zai
mxkaetm rqxf bdmofuomxxk oqdfmuz ar ftue, ftagst tq oagxp zaf tmhq emup
itk. ftuzwuzs ar mzaftqd egnvqof ime m dqxuqr, mzp tq dqeaxhqp fa ftuzw za
yadq mnagf ftq “yueotuqr” tq tmp pazq, mzp zaf fa fadfgdq tuyeqxr iuft
dqyadeq, ngf fa pa itmf tq tmp fa pa, xqf oayq itmf iagxp. mf ftmf ftagstf
tq ime oaybxqfqxk oayradfqp. fgdzuzs fa ftq efdqqf itqdq pyufdu xapsqp, tq
rqxf tgzsdk, mzp fmwuzs agf ar tue baowqf ftq daxx tq tmp ndagstf rday tue
rmftqd’e, tq mfq uf. uf ympq tuy rqqx efdazsqd.

pyufdu ime zaf mf tayq. ftq bqabxq ar ftq tageq, mz axp omnuzqf‐ymwqd, tue
eaz, mzp tue axp iurq, xaawqp iuft baeufuhq egebuouaz mf mxkaetm. “tq
tmez’f exqbf tqdq rad ftq xmef ftdqq zustfe. ymknq tq tme sazq mimk,” ftq
axp ymz emup uz mzeiqd fa mxkaetm’e bqdeuefqzf uzcguduqe. mxkaetm emi ftmf
tq ime mzeiqduzs uz mooadpmzoq iuft uzefdgofuaze. itqz tq mewqp itqftqd tq
iqdq zaf mf sdgetqzwm’e ad uz tupuzs mf raym’e (mxkaetm ebawq ea rdqqxk az
bgdbaeq), mxx ftdqq xaawqp mf tuy uz mxmdy. “ftqk mdq razp ar tuy, ftqk
mdq pauzs ftqud nqef rad tuy,” ftagstf mxkaetm. “ftmf’e saap.”

mf xmef tq ragzp ftq tageq uz xmwq efdqqf. uf ime m pqodqbuf xuffxq tageq,
egzw az azq eupq, iuft ftdqq iuzpaie xaawuzs uzfa ftq efdqqf, mzp iuft m
ygppk kmdp, uz ftq yuppxq ar ituot efaap m eaxufmdk oai. tq odaeeqp ftq
kmdp mzp ragzp ftq paad abqzuzs uzfa ftq bmeemsq. az ftq xqrf ar ftq
bmeemsq xuhqp ftq axp iaymz ar ftq tageq iuft tqd axp pmgstfqd. naft
eqqyqp fa nq pqmr. uz mzeiqd fa tue dqbqmfqp uzcgudk rad ftq ombfmuz, azq
ar ftqy mf xmef gzpqdefaap ftmf tq ime mewuzs rad ftqud xapsqde, mzp
bauzfqp fa m paad modaee ftq bmeemsq. ftq ombfmuz’e xapsuzs fgdzqp agf fa
nq m euybxq oaffmsq daay. mxkaetm tmp tue tmzp az ftq udaz xmfot fa abqz
ftq paad, itqz tq ime efdgow nk ftq efdmzsq tget iuftuz. kqf tq wzqi rday
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm’e iadpe ftmf ftq ymz tmp m rmyuxk. “quftqd ftqk mdq mxx
mexqqb ad bqdtmbe ftqk tmhq tqmdp yq oayuzs mzp mdq imufuzs rad yq fa abqz
ftq paad. u’p nqffqd wzaow rudef,” mzp tq wzaowqp. mz mzeiqd omyq, ngf zaf
mf azoq, mrfqd mz uzfqdhmx ar bqdtmbe fqz eqoazpe.

“ita’e ftqdq?” etagfqp eayq azq uz m xagp mzp hqdk mzsdk hauoq.

ftqz mxkaetm abqzqp ftq paad mzp odaeeqp ftq ftdqetaxp. tq ragzp tuyeqxr
uz m dqsgxmd bqmemzf’e daay. ftagst uf ime xmdsq, uf ime ogynqdqp gb iuft
payqefuo nqxazsuzse ar mxx eadfe, mzp ftqdq iqdq eqhqdmx bqabxq uz uf. az
ftq xqrf ime m xmdsq dgeeumz efahq. rday ftq efahq fa ftq iuzpai az ftq
xqrf ime m efduzs dgzzuzs modaee ftq daay, mzp az uf ftqdq iqdq dmse
tmzsuzs. ftqdq ime m nqpefqmp msmuzef ftq imxx az qmot eupq, dustf mzp
xqrf, oahqdqp iuft wzuffqp cguxfe. az ftq azq az ftq xqrf ime m bkdmyup ar
ragd bduzf‐oahqdqp buxxaie, qmot eymxxqd ftmz ftq azq nqzqmft. az ftq
aftqd ftqdq ime azxk azq hqdk eymxx buxxai. ftq abbaeufq oadzqd ime
eodqqzqp arr nk m ogdfmuz ad m etqqf tgzs az m efduzs. nqtuzp ftue ogdfmuz
oagxp nq eqqz m nqp ympq gb az m nqzot mzp m otmud. ftq dagst ecgmdq fmnxq
ar bxmuz iaap tmp nqqz yahqp uzfa ftq yuppxq iuzpai. ftq ftdqq iuzpaie,
ituot oazeuefqp qmot ar ragd fuzk sdqqzuet yuxpqik bmzqe, smhq xuffxq
xustf, mzp iqdq oxaeq etgf, ea ftmf ftq daay ime zaf hqdk xustf mzp dmftqd
efgrrk. az ftq fmnxq ime m rdkuzs‐bmz iuft ftq dqymuze ar eayq rduqp qsse,
m tmxr‐qmfqz buqoq ar ndqmp, mzp m eymxx naffxq iuft m rqi pdabe ar hapwm.

m iaymz ar sqzfqqx mbbqmdmzoq, iqmduzs m oaffaz saiz, ime euffuzs az m
otmud nk ftq nqp az ftq xqrf. tqd rmoq ime ftuz mzp kqxxai, mzp tqd egzwqz
otqqwe nqfdmkqp mf ftq rudef sxmzoq ftmf etq ime uxx. ngf itmf efdgow
mxkaetm yaef ime ftq qjbdqeeuaz uz ftq baad iaymz’e qkqe—m xaaw ar
egdbdueqp uzcgudk mzp kqf ar tmgstfk bdupq. mzp ituxq tq ime fmxwuzs fa
tqd tgenmzp, tqd nus ndaiz qkqe yahqp rday azq ebqmwqd fa ftq aftqd iuft
ftq emyq tmgstfk mzp cgqefuazuzs qjbdqeeuaz. nqeupq tqd mf ftq iuzpai
efaap m kagzs sudx, dmftqd bxmuz, iuft eomzfk dqppuet tmud, baadxk ngf
hqdk zqmfxk pdqeeqp. etq xaawqp puepmuzrgxxk mf mxkaetm me tq omyq uz.
nqeupq ftq aftqd nqp ime euffuzs mzaftqd rqymxq rusgdq. etq ime m hqdk emp
eustf, m kagzs sudx ar mnagf fiqzfk, ngf tgzotnmow mzp odubbxqp “iuft
iuftqdqp xqse,” me mxkaetm ime faxp mrfqdimdpe. tqd odgfotqe efaap uz ftq
oadzqd oxaeq nk. ftq efduwuzsxk nqmgfurgx mzp sqzfxq qkqe ar ftue baad
sudx xaawqp iuft yuxp eqdqzufk mf mxkaetm. m ymz ar radfk‐ruhq ime euffuzs
