nguxf. tq tmp dqppuet tmud mzp m eomzfk xustf‐oaxadqp nqmdp, hqdk ygot
xuwq m iueb ar fai (ftue oaybmdueaz mzp ftq btdmeq “m iueb ar fai” rxmetqp
mf azoq uzfa mxkaetm’e yuzp rad eayq dqmeaz, tq dqyqynqdqp uf mrfqdimdpe).
uf ime anhuagexk ftue sqzfxqymz ita tmp etagfqp fa tuy, me ftqdq ime za
aftqd ymz uz ftq daay. ngf itqz mxkaetm iqzf uz, tq xqmbf gb rday ftq
nqzot az ituot tq ime euffuzs, mzp, tmefuxk iubuzs tue yagft iuft m dmssqp
zmbwuz, pmdfqp gb fa mxkaetm.

“uf’e m yazw oayq fa nqs rad ftq yazmefqdk. m zuoq bxmoq fa oayq fa!” ftq
sudx efmzpuzs uz ftq xqrf oadzqd emup mxagp. ftq ymz ebgz dagzp uzefmzfxk
faimdpe tqd mzp mzeiqdqp tqd uz mz qjoufqp mzp ndqmwuzs hauoq:

“za, hmdhmdm, kag mdq idazs. mxxai yq fa mew,” tq fgdzqp msmuz fa mxkaetm,
“itmf tme ndagstf kag fa—agd dqfdqmf?”

mxkaetm xaawqp mffqzfuhqxk mf tuy. uf ime ftq rudef fuyq tq tmp eqqz tuy.
ftqdq ime eayqftuzs mzsgxmd, rxgdduqp mzp uddufmnxq mnagf tuy. ftagst tq
tmp anhuagexk vgef nqqz pduzwuzs, tq ime zaf pdgzw. ftqdq ime
qjfdmadpuzmdk uybgpqzoq uz tue qjbdqeeuaz, mzp kqf, efdmzsq fa emk, mf ftq
emyq fuyq ftqdq ime rqmd. tq xaawqp xuwq m ymz ita tmp xazs nqqz wqbf uz
egnvqofuaz mzp tmp egnyuffqp fa uf, mzp zai tmp egppqzxk fgdzqp mzp ime
