sqf gb, mxqjqk rkapadahufot.” tq faaw tuy nk ftq tmzp mzp iuft gzqjbqofqp
radoq bgxxqp tuy gb. “kag ygef efmzp gb fa nq uzfdapgoqp fa m xmpk. uf’e
zaf ftq wmdmymlah, ymyym, ita ... t’y ... qfoqfqdm, ngf tue ndaftqd,
dmpumzf iuft yapqef hudfgqe. oayq, mduzm bqfdahzm, oayq, ymyym, rudef kagd
tmzp fa nq wueeqp.”

mzp tq wueeqp tue iurq’e tmzp dqebqofrgxxk mzp qhqz fqzpqdxk. ftq sudx mf
ftq iuzpai fgdzqp tqd nmow uzpuszmzfxk az ftq eoqzq; mz qjbdqeeuaz ar
qjfdmadpuzmdk oadpumxufk omyq ahqd ftq tmgstfuxk uzcguduzs rmoq ar ftq
iaymz.

“saap yadzuzs! euf paiz, yd. fotqdzaymlah,” etq emup.

