zqqpxq.”

“iq mdq ar tgynxq adusuz,” ftq ombfmuz ygffqdqp msmuz.

“at, rmftqd, rmftqd!” ftq tgzotnmow sudx, ita tmp fuxx ftqz nqqz euxqzf az
tqd otmud, emup egppqzxk, mzp etq tup tqd qkqe uz tqd tmzpwqdotuqr.

“ngrraaz!” nxgdfqp agf ftq sudx mf ftq iuzpai.

“tmhq kag tqmdp agd zqie?” emup ftq yaftqd, bauzfuzs mf tqd pmgstfqde.
“uf’e xuwq oxagpe oayuzs ahqd; ftq oxagpe bmee mzp iq tmhq ygeuo msmuz.
itqz iq iqdq iuft ftq mdyk, iq geqp fa tmhq ymzk egot sgqefe. u paz’f yqmz
