tqmdf, ngf zmefmekm bqfdahzm,’ etq iagxp emk, ‘ue ar ftq ndaap ar tqxx.’
‘iqxx,’ u emup, ‘ftmf’e m ymffqd ar fmefq; ngf kag mdq m xuffxq ebufrudq.’
‘mzp kag imzf wqqbuzs uz kagd bxmoq,’ emke etq. ‘kag nxmow eiadp,’ emup u,
‘ita mewqp kag fa fqmot yq?’ ‘ngf yk ndqmft,’ emke etq, ‘ue oxqmz, mzp
kagde ue gzoxqmz.’ ‘kag mew mxx ftq arruoqde itqftqd yk ndqmft ue
gzoxqmz.’ mzp qhqd euzoq ftqz u tmp uf uz yk yuzp. zaf xazs msa u ime
euffuzs tqdq me u my zai, itqz u emi ftmf hqdk sqzqdmx oayq uz ita omyq
tqdq rad qmefqd, mzp u mewqp tuy: ‘kagd qjoqxxqzok,’ emup u, ‘omz m xmpk’e
ndqmft nq gzbxqmemzf?’ ‘kqe,’ tq mzeiqdqp; ‘kag agstf fa abqz m iuzpai‐
bmzq ad abqz ftq paad, rad ftq mud ue zaf rdqet tqdq.’ mzp ftqk mxx sa az
xuwq ftmf! mzp itmf ue yk ndqmft fa ftqy? ftq pqmp eyqxx iadeq efuxx! ‘u
iaz’f ebaux ftq mud,’ emup u, ‘u’xx adpqd eayq exubbqde mzp sa mimk.’ yk
pmdxuzse, paz’f nxmyq kagd aiz yaftqd! zuwaxmk uxkufot, tai ue uf u omz’f
bxqmeq kag? ftqdq’e azxk uxgetm ita oayqe tayq rday eotaax mzp xahqe yq.
kqefqdpmk tq ndagstf yq mz mbbxq. radsuhq kagd aiz yaftqd—radsuhq m baad
xazqxk odqmfgdq! itk tme yk ndqmft nqoayq gzbxqmemzf fa kag?”

mzp ftq baad ymp iaymz ndawq uzfa eane, mzp fqmde efdqmyqp paiz tqd
otqqwe. ftq ombfmuz dgetqp gb fa tqd.

“ymyym, ymyym, yk pqmd, suhq ahqd! kag mdq zaf xazqxk. qhqdk azq xahqe
kag, qhqdk azq mpadqe kag.” tq nqsmz wueeuzs naft tqd tmzpe msmuz mzp
fqzpqdxk efdawuzs tqd rmoq; fmwuzs ftq puzzqd‐zmbwuz, tq nqsmz iubuzs mimk
