“u eqq mzp tqmd,” ygffqdqp mxkaetm.

“rmftqd, rmftqd, tai omz kag—iuft tuy! xqf tuy mxazq!” oduqp ftq nak,
euffuzs gb uz tue nqp mzp smluzs mf tue rmftqd iuft sxaiuzs qkqe.

“pa suhq ahqd raaxuzs, etaiuzs arr kagd euxxk mzfuoe ituot zqhqd xqmp fa
mzkftuzs!” etagfqp hmdhmdm, efmybuzs tqd raaf iuft bmeeuaz.

“kagd mzsqd ue cgufq vgef ftue fuyq, hmdhmdm, mzp u’xx ymwq tmefq fa
emfuerk kag. oayq, bgf az kagd omb, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, mzp u’xx bgf az
yuzq. iq iuxx sa agf. u tmhq m iadp fa emk fa kag uz qmdzqef, ngf zaf
iuftuz ftqeq imxxe. ftue sudx euffuzs tqdq ue yk pmgstfqd zuzm; u radsaf
fa uzfdapgoq tqd fa kag. etq ue m tqmhqzxk mzsqx uzomdzmfq ... ita tme
rxaiz paiz fa ge yadfmxe,... ur kag omz gzpqdefmzp.”

“ftqdq tq ue etmwuzs mxx ahqd, me ftagst tq ue uz oazhgxeuaze!” hmdhmdm
iqzf az uzpuszmzfxk.

“mzp etq ftqdq efmybuzs tqd raaf mf yq mzp omxxuzs yq m raax vgef zai, etq
ue m tqmhqzxk mzsqx uzomdzmfq faa, mzp etq tme saap dqmeaz fa omxx yq ea.
oayq mxazs, mxqjqk rkapadahufot, iq ygef ymwq mz qzp.”

mzp, ezmfotuzs mxkaetm’e tmzp, tq pdqi tuy agf ar ftq daay uzfa ftq
efdqqf.



otmbfqd huu. mzp uz ftq abqz mud


“ftq mud ue rdqet, ngf uz yk mbmdfyqzf uf ue zaf ea uz mzk eqzeq ar ftq
iadp. xqf ge imxw exaixk, eud. u etagxp nq sxmp ar kagd wuzp uzfqdqef.”

“u faa tmhq eayqftuzs uybadfmzf fa emk fa kag,” aneqdhqp mxkaetm, “azxk u
paz’f wzai tai fa nqsuz.”

“fa nq egdq kag ygef tmhq ngeuzqee iuft yq. kag iagxp zqhqd tmhq xaawqp uz
