qjbxmuz fa kag uz ftqdq, ngf tqdq u iuxx pqeodunq ftmf eoqzq fa kag. yk
fai ime ftuowqd m iqqw msa—u yqmz yk nqmdp. ftmf’e ftq zuowzmyq ftqk suhq
fa yk nqmdp, ftq eotaaxnake yaef ar mxx. iqxx, kagd ndaftqd pyufdu
rkapadahufot ime bgxxuzs yq nk yk nqmdp, u’p pazq zaftuzs, tq ime uz m
faiqduzs dmsq mzp tmbbqzqp fa oayq gbaz yq. tq pdmssqp yq agf ar ftq
fmhqdz uzfa ftq ymdwqf‐bxmoq; mf ftmf yayqzf ftq nake iqdq oayuzs agf ar
eotaax, mzp iuft ftqy uxgetm. me eaaz me tq emi yq uz egot m efmfq tq
dgetqp gb fa yq. ‘rmftqd,’ tq oduqp, ‘rmftqd!’ tq omgstf taxp ar yq,
