oxgfotqp mf ftmf tmzp, ftmf hqdk tmzp, uz tue xuffxq tmzpe mzp wueeqp
uf.... u dqyqynqd tue xuffxq rmoq mf ftmf yayqzf, u tmhqz’f radsaffqz uf
mzp u zqhqd etmxx!”

