eiadp agf ar tue tmzp, u’xx rmxx az tuy, imhq yk eiadp ahqd tuy mzp emk:
“u oagxp wuxx kag, ngf u radsuhq kag, ea ftqdq!” ’ kag eqq itmf ftq
