otmffqdqp m xazs ituxq. ftmzw sap, u ftagstf, u tmhq puhqdfqp tue yuzp mzp
oayradfqp tuy.

“ftmf ime ftq pmk nqradq kqefqdpmk, uz ftq qhqzuzs, ngf xmef zustf
qhqdkftuzs ime otmzsqp. tq tmp sazq fa eotaax uz ftq yadzuzs, tq omyq nmow
