tmhq kag bgf uf mimk?’ yk nak ympq za mzeiqd. tq xaawqp mimk mzp fgdzqp
eupqimke fa yq. mzp ftqz m sgef ar iuzp nxqi gb ftq emzp. tq egppqzxk rqxx
