wzai, itqz otuxpdqz mdq euxqzf mzp bdagp, mzp fdk fa wqqb nmow ftqud fqmde
itqz ftqk mdq uz sdqmf fdagnxq mzp egppqzxk ndqmw paiz, ftqud fqmde rmxx
uz efdqmye. iuft ftaeq imdy efdqmye ar fqmde, tq egppqzxk iqffqp yk rmoq.
tq eannqp mzp etaaw me ftagst tq iqdq uz oazhgxeuaze, mzp ecgqqlqp gb
