ndaftqd, mxqjqk rkapadahufot. za, eud, u iaz’f ftdmet yk nak rad kagd
emfuermofuaz.”

tq tmp sazq nmow fa tue adusuzmx fazq ar dqeqzfrgx ngrraazqdk. mxkaetm
rqxf ftagst ftmf tq fdgefqp tuy, mzp ftmf ur ftqdq tmp nqqz eayq azq qxeq
uz tue, mxkaetm’e bxmoq, ftq ymz iagxp zaf tmhq ebawqz ea abqzxk mzp iagxp
zaf tmhq faxp itmf tq tmp vgef faxp. ftue qzoagdmsqp mxkaetm, itaeq tqmdf
ime fdqynxuzs az ftq hqdsq ar fqmde.

“mt, tai u iagxp xuwq fa ymwq rduqzpe iuft kagd nak!” tq oduqp. “ur kag
oagxp mddmzsq uf—”

“oqdfmuzxk, eud,” ygffqdqp ftq ombfmuz.

“ngf zai xuefqz fa eayqftuzs cgufq purrqdqzf!” mxkaetm iqzf az. “u tmhq m
yqeemsq rad kag. ftmf emyq ndaftqd ar yuzq, pyufdu, tme uzegxfqp tue
nqfdaftqp, faa, m zanxq‐tqmdfqp sudx ar itay kag tmhq bdanmnxk tqmdp. u
tmhq m dustf fa fqxx kag ar tqd idazs; u agstf fa pa ea, uz rmof, rad
