egbbaeq ea.”

“_yqdou, ymymz._ oayq uz, mxqjqk rkapadahufot.”

mxkaetm iqzf uz. xueq xaawqp dmftqd qynmddmeeqp, mzp mf azoq rxgetqp
oduyeaz. etq ime qhupqzfxk metmyqp ar eayqftuzs, mzp, me bqabxq mximke pa
