“ftq rmof ue u pupz’f suhq uf fa tuy, mzp uf’e m xazs efadk,” mzeiqdqp
mxkaetm, me ftagst tq, faa, oagxp ftuzw ar zaftuzs ngf tue dqsdqf mf
