dqmp eayqitqdq ar vatz ftq yqdourgx, m emuzf, ftmf itqz m tgzsdk, rdalqz
nqssmd omyq fa tuy, tq faaw tuy uzfa tue nqp, tqxp tuy uz tue mdye, mzp
