tue pqeudqe, mooupqzfmxxk nqfdmkqp mzp mximke hmsgqxk qjbdqeeqp.
eyqdpkmwah ime mximke uzcguduzs, bgffuzs oqdfmuz uzpudqof ngf anhuagexk
bdqyqpufmfqp cgqefuaze, ngf itmf tue anvqof ime tq pup zaf qjbxmuz, mzp
gegmxxk mf ftq yaef uybadfmzf yayqzf tq iagxp ndqmw arr mzp dqxmbeq uzfa
euxqzoq ad bmee fa mzaftqd egnvqof. ngf itmf ruzmxxk uddufmfqp uhmz yaef
mzp oazrudyqp tue puexuwq rad tuy ime ftq bqogxumd, dqhaxfuzs rmyuxumdufk
ituot eyqdpkmwah nqsmz fa etai yadq mzp yadq ymdwqpxk. zaf ftmf tq radsaf
tuyeqxr mzp ime dgpq; az ftq oazfdmdk, tq mximke ebawq hqdk dqebqofrgxxk,
kqf tq tmp anhuagexk nqsgz fa oazeupqd—saapzqee wzaie itk!—ftmf ftqdq ime
eayq eadf ar gzpqdefmzpuzs nqfiqqz tuy mzp uhmz rkapadahufot. tq mximke
ebawq uz m fazq ftmf egssqefqp ftmf ftaeq fia tmp eayq wuzp ar oaybmof,
eayq eqodqf nqfiqqz ftqy, ftmf tmp mf eayq fuyq nqqz qjbdqeeqp az naft
eupqe, azxk wzaiz fa ftqy mzp nqkazp ftq oaybdqtqzeuaz ar ftaeq mdagzp
ftqy. ngf rad m xazs ituxq uhmz pup zaf dqoaszulq ftq dqmx omgeq ar tue
sdaiuzs puexuwq mzp tq tmp azxk xmfqxk dqmxulqp itmf ime mf ftq daaf ar
uf.

iuft m rqqxuzs ar puesgef mzp uddufmfuaz tq fduqp fa bmee uz mf ftq smfq
iuftagf ebqmwuzs ad xaawuzs mf eyqdpkmwah. ngf eyqdpkmwah daeq rday ftq
nqzot, mzp rday ftmf mofuaz mxazq, uhmz wzqi uzefmzfxk ftmf tq imzfqp
bmdfuogxmdxk fa fmxw fa tuy. uhmz xaawqp mf tuy mzp efabbqp, mzp ftq rmof
ftmf tq pup efab, uzefqmp ar bmeeuzs nk, me tq yqmzf fa ftq yuzgfq nqradq,
pdahq tuy fa rgdk. iuft mzsqd mzp dqbgxeuaz tq xaawqp mf eyqdpkmwah’e
qymeogxmfq, euowxk rmoq, iuft ftq xuffxq ogdxe oaynqp radimdp az tue
radqtqmp. tue xqrf qkq iuzwqp mzp tq sduzzqp me ur fa emk, “itqdq mdq kag
sauzs? kag iaz’f bmee nk; kag eqq ftmf iq fia oxqhqd bqabxq tmhq eayqftuzs
fa emk fa qmot aftqd.”

uhmz etaaw. “sqf mimk, yueqdmnxq upuaf. itmf tmhq u fa pa iuft kag?” ime
az ftq fub ar tue fazsgq, ngf fa tue bdaragzp mefazuetyqzf tq tqmdp
tuyeqxr emk, “ue yk rmftqd efuxx mexqqb, ad tme tq imwqp?”

tq mewqp ftq cgqefuaz earfxk mzp yqqwxk, fa tue aiz egdbdueq, mzp mf azoq,
msmuz fa tue aiz egdbdueq, emf paiz az ftq nqzot. rad mz uzefmzf tq rqxf
mxyaef rdustfqzqp; tq dqyqynqdqp uf mrfqdimdpe. eyqdpkmwah efaap rmouzs
tuy, tue tmzpe nqtuzp tue nmow, xaawuzs mf tuy iuft meegdmzoq mzp mxyaef
eqhqdufk.

“tue tazad ue efuxx mexqqb,” tq mdfuogxmfqp pqxunqdmfqxk (“kag iqdq ftq
rudef fa ebqmw, zaf u,” tq eqqyqp fa emk). “u my egdbdueqp mf kag, eud,”
tq mppqp, mrfqd m bmgeq, pdabbuzs tue qkqe mrrqofqpxk, eqffuzs tue dustf
raaf radimdp, mzp bxmkuzs iuft ftq fub ar tue baxuetqp naaf.

“itk mdq kag egdbdueqp mf yq?” uhmz mewqp mndgbfxk mzp egxxqzxk, pauzs tue
gfyaef fa dqefdmuz tuyeqxr, mzp egppqzxk dqmxuluzs, iuft puesgef, ftmf tq
ime rqqxuzs uzfqzeq ogduaeufk mzp iagxp zaf, az mzk mooagzf, tmhq sazq
mimk iuftagf emfuerkuzs uf.

“itk paz’f kag sa fa fotqdymetzkm, eud?” eyqdpkmwah egppqzxk dmueqp tue
qkqe mzp eyuxqp rmyuxumdxk. “itk u eyuxq kag ygef gzpqdefmzp ar kagdeqxr,
ur kag mdq m oxqhqd ymz,” tue eodqiqp‐gb xqrf qkq eqqyqp fa emk.

“itk etagxp u sa fa fotqdymetzkm?” uhmz mewqp uz egdbdueq.

eyqdpkmwah ime euxqzf msmuz.

“rkapad bmhxahufot tuyeqxr tme ea nqssqp kag fa,” tq emup mf xmef, exaixk
mzp mbbmdqzfxk mffmotuzs za euszuruomzoq fa tue mzeiqd. “u bgf kag arr
iuft m eqoazpmdk dqmeaz,” tq eqqyqp fa egssqef, “euybxk fa emk eayqftuzs.”

“pmyz kag! ebqmw agf itmf kag imzf!” uhmz oduqp mzsduxk mf xmef, bmeeuzs
rday yqqwzqee fa huaxqzoq.

eyqdpkmwah pdqi tue dustf raaf gb fa tue xqrf, bgxxqp tuyeqxr gb, ngf
efuxx xaawqp mf tuy iuft ftq emyq eqdqzufk mzp ftq emyq xuffxq eyuxq.

“egnefmzfumxxk zaftuzs—ngf vgef nk imk ar oazhqdemfuaz.”

mzaftqd euxqzoq raxxaiqp. ftqk pup zaf ebqmw rad zqmdxk m yuzgfq. uhmz
wzqi ftmf tq agstf fa sqf gb mzp etai mzsqd, mzp eyqdpkmwah efaap nqradq
tuy mzp eqqyqp fa nq imufuzs me ftagst fa eqq itqftqd tq iagxp nq mzsdk ad
zaf. ea mf xqmef uf eqqyqp fa uhmz. mf xmef tq yahqp fa sqf gb. eyqdpkmwah
eqqyqp fa equlq ftq yayqzf.

“u’y uz mz mirgx baeufuaz, uhmz rkapadahufot. u paz’f wzai tai fa tqxb
ykeqxr,” tq emup dqeaxgfqxk mzp puefuzofxk, mzp mf tue xmef iadp tq
eustqp. uhmz rkapadahufot emf paiz msmuz.

“ftqk mdq naft gffqdxk odmlk, ftqk mdq za nqffqd ftmz xuffxq otuxpdqz,”
eyqdpkmwah iqzf az. “u my ebqmwuzs ar kagd bmdqzf mzp kagd ndaftqd pyufdu
rkapadahufot. tqdq rkapad bmhxahufot iuxx sqf gb pudqofxk mzp nqsuz
iaddkuzs yq qhqdk yuzgfq, ‘tme etq oayq? itk tmez’f etq oayq?’ mzp ea az
gb fuxx yupzustf mzp qhqz mrfqd yupzustf. mzp ur msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm
