iuxx nq mf yq msmuz fa‐yaddai yadzuzs, ‘itk tmez’f etq oayq? itqz iuxx etq
oayq?’—me ftagst u iqdq fa nxmyq rad uf. az ftq aftqd eupq uf’e za nqffqd.
me eaaz me uf sqfe pmdw, ad qhqz nqradq, kagd ndaftqd iuxx mbbqmd iuft tue
sgz uz tue tmzpe: ‘xaaw agf, kag dasgq, kag eagb‐ymwqd. ur kag yuee tqd
mzp paz’f xqf yq wzai etq’e nqqz—u’xx wuxx kag nqradq mzk azq.’ itqz ftq
zustf’e ahqd, uz ftq yadzuzs, tq, faa, xuwq rkapad bmhxahufot, nqsuze
iaddkuzs yq fa pqmft. ‘itk tmez’f etq oayq? iuxx etq oayq eaaz?’ mzp tq,
faa, ftuzwe yq fa nxmyq nqomgeq tue xmpk tmez’f oayq. mzp qhqdk pmk mzp
qhqdk tagd ftqk sqf mzsduqd mzp mzsduqd, ea ftmf u eayqfuyqe ftuzw u etmxx
wuxx ykeqxr uz m rdustf. u omz’f pqbqzp gbaz ftqy, eud.”

“mzp itk tmhq kag yqppxqp? itk pup kag nqsuz fa ebk rad pyufdu
rkapadahufot?” emup uhmz uddufmnxk.

“tai oagxp u tqxb yqppxuzs? ftagst, uzpqqp, u tmhqz’f yqppxqp mf mxx, ur
kag imzf fa wzai ftq fdgft ar ftq ymffqd. u wqbf cguqf rday ftq hqdk
nqsuzzuzs, zaf pmduzs fa mzeiqd; ngf tq bufotqp az yq fa nq tue eqdhmzf.
tq tme tmp azxk azq ftuzs fa emk euzoq: ‘u’xx wuxx kag, kag eoagzpdqx, ur
kag yuee tqd,’ u rqqx oqdfmuz, eud, ftmf u etmxx tmhq m xazs ruf fa‐
yaddai.”

“itmf pa kag yqmz nk ‘m xazs ruf’?”

“m xazs ruf, xmefuzs m xazs fuyq—eqhqdmx tagde, ad bqdtmbe m pmk ad fia.
azoq uf iqzf az rad ftdqq pmke. u rqxx rday ftq smddqf ftmf fuyq. ftq
efdgssxuzs oqmeqp mzp ftqz nqsmz msmuz, mzp rad ftdqq pmke u oagxpz’f oayq
