tqdq, mzp tq bgf uoq az yk tqmp mzp fduqp mzaftqd dqyqpk, faa.... u yustf
tmhq puqp.”

“ngf ftqk emk azq omz’f fqxx iuft qbuxqbek itqz m ruf ue oayuzs. itmf
ymwqe kag emk kag iuxx tmhq azq fa‐yaddai?” uhmz uzcgudqp, iuft m
bqogxumd, uddufmnxq ogduaeufk.

“ftmf’e vgef ea. kag omz’f fqxx nqradqtmzp.”

“nqeupqe, kag rqxx rday ftq smddqf ftqz.”

“u oxuyn gb fa ftq smddqf qhqdk pmk. u yustf rmxx rday ftq smddqf msmuz
fa‐yaddai. mzp, ur zaf, u yustf rmxx paiz ftq oqxxmd efqbe. u tmhq fa sa
uzfa ftq oqxxmd qhqdk pmk, faa.”

uhmz faaw m xazs xaaw mf tuy.

“kag mdq fmxwuzs zazeqzeq, u eqq, mzp u paz’f cgufq gzpqdefmzp kag,” tq
emup earfxk, ngf iuft m eadf ar yqzmoq. “pa kag yqmz fa bdqfqzp fa nq uxx
fa‐yaddai rad ftdqq pmke, qt?”

eyqdpkmwah, ita ime xaawuzs mf ftq sdagzp msmuz, mzp bxmkuzs iuft ftq faq
ar tue dustf raaf, eqf ftq raaf paiz, yahqp ftq xqrf azq radimdp, mzp,
