“ur u iqdq mnxq fa bxmk egot m fduow, ftmf ue, bdqfqzp fa tmhq m ruf—mzp
uf iagxp zaf nq purruogxf rad m ymz moogefayqp fa ftqy—u etagxp tmhq m
bqdrqof dustf fa geq egot m yqmze fa emhq ykeqxr rday pqmft. rad qhqz ur
msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm oayqe fa eqq tue rmftqd ituxq u my uxx, tue tazad
omz’f nxmyq m euow ymz rad zaf fqxxuzs tuy. tq’p nq metmyqp fa.”

“tmzs uf mxx!” uhmz oduqp, tue rmoq iadwuzs iuft mzsqd, “itk mdq kag
mximke uz egot m rgzw rad kagd xurq? mxx yk ndaftqd pyufdu’e ftdqmfe mdq
azxk tmefk iadpe mzp yqmz zaftuzs. tq iaz’f wuxx kag; uf’e zaf kag tq’xx
wuxx!”

“tq’p wuxx yq rudef ar mxx, xuwq m rxk. ngf qhqz yadq ftmz ftmf, u my
mrdmup u etmxx nq fmwqz rad mz mooaybxuoq ar tue itqz tq paqe eayqftuzs
odmlk fa tue rmftqd.”

“itk etagxp kag nq fmwqz rad mz mooaybxuoq?”

“ftqk’xx ftuzw u my mz mooaybxuoq, nqomgeq u xqf tuy wzai ftq euszmxe me m
sdqmf eqodqf.”

“itmf euszmxe? itay pup kag fqxx? oazragzp kag, ebqmw yadq bxmuzxk.”

“u’y nagzp fa mpyuf ftq rmof,” eyqdpkmwah pdmixqp iuft bqpmzfuo oaybaegdq,
“ftmf u tmhq m eqodqf iuft rkapad bmhxahufot uz ftue ngeuzqee. me kag wzai
kagdeqxr (ur azxk kag pa wzai uf) tq tme rad eqhqdmx pmke bmef xaowqp
tuyeqxr uz me eaaz me zustf ad qhqz qhqzuzs oayqe az. ar xmfq kag’hq nqqz
sauzs gbefmude fa kagd daay qmdxk qhqdk qhqzuzs, mzp kqefqdpmk kag pup zaf
oayq paiz mf mxx, mzp ea bqdtmbe kag paz’f wzai tai omdqrgxxk tq tme nqsgz
fa xaow tuyeqxr uz mf zustf, mzp qhqz ur sdusadk hmeeuxkqhufot oayqe fa
ftq paad tq iaz’f abqz fa tuy fuxx tq tqmde tue hauoq. ngf sdusadk
hmeeuxkqhufot paqe zaf oayq, nqomgeq u imuf gbaz tuy mxazq uz tue daay
zai. ftmf’e ftq mddmzsqyqzf tq ympq tuyeqxr qhqd euzoq ftue fa‐pa iuft
msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm nqsmz. ngf mf zustf, nk tue adpqde, u sa mimk fa ftq
xapsq ea ftmf u paz’f sqf fa exqqb fuxx yupzustf, ngf my az ftq imfot,
sqffuzs gb mzp imxwuzs mnagf ftq kmdp, imufuzs rad msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm
fa oayq. rad ftq xmef rqi pmke tq’e nqqz bqdrqofxk rdmzfuo qjbqofuzs tqd.
itmf tq mdsgqe ue, etq ue mrdmup ar tuy, pyufdu rkapadahufot (yufkm, me tq
omxxe tuy), ‘mzp ea,’ emke tq, ‘etq’xx oayq ftq nmow‐imk, xmfq mf zustf,
fa yq. kag xaaw agf rad tqd,’ emke tq, ‘fuxx yupzustf mzp xmfqd; mzp ur
etq paqe oayq, kag dgz gb mzp wzaow mf yk paad ad mf ftq iuzpai rday ftq
smdpqz. wzaow mf rudef fiuoq, dmftqd sqzfxk, mzp ftqz ftdqq fuyqe yadq
cguowxk, ftqz,’ emke tq, ‘u etmxx gzpqdefmzp mf azoq ftmf etq tme oayq,
mzp iuxx abqz ftq paad fa kag cguqfxk.’ mzaftqd euszmx tq smhq yq uz omeq
mzkftuzs gzqjbqofqp tmbbqze. mf rudef, fia wzaowe, mzp ftqz, mrfqd mz
uzfqdhmx, mzaftqd ygot xagpqd. ftqz tq iuxx gzpqdefmzp ftmf eayqftuzs tme
tmbbqzqp egppqzxk mzp ftmf u ygef eqq tuy, mzp tq iuxx abqz fa yq ea ftmf
u omz sa mzp ebqmw fa tuy. ftmf’e mxx uz omeq msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm omz’f
oayq tqdeqxr, ngf eqzpe m yqeemsq. nqeupqe, pyufdu rkapadahufot yustf
oayq, faa, ea u ygef xqf tuy wzai tq ue zqmd. tue tazad ue mirgxxk mrdmup
ar pyufdu rkapadahufot, ea ftmf qhqz ur msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm tmp oayq mzp
iqdq xaowqp uz iuft tuy, mzp pyufdu rkapadahufot iqdq fa fgdz gb mzkitqdq
zqmd mf ftq fuyq, u etagxp nq nagzp fa xqf tuy wzai mf azoq, wzaowuzs
ftdqq fuyqe. ea ftmf ftq rudef euszmx ar ruhq wzaowe yqmze msdmrqzm
mxqjmzpdahzm tme oayq, ituxq ftq eqoazp euszmx ar ftdqq wzaowe yqmze
‘eayqftuzs uybadfmzf fa fqxx kag.’ tue tazad tme etaiz yq ftqy eqhqdmx
fuyqe mzp qjbxmuzqp ftqy. mzp me uz ftq itaxq gzuhqdeq za azq wzaie ar
ftqeq euszmxe ngf ykeqxr mzp tue tazad, ea tq’p abqz ftq paad iuftagf ftq
exustfqef tqeufmfuaz mzp iuftagf omxxuzs agf (tq ue mirgxxk mrdmup ar
omxxuzs agf mxagp). iqxx, ftaeq euszmxe mdq wzaiz fa pyufdu rkapadahufot
faa, zai.”

“tai mdq ftqk wzaiz? pup kag fqxx tuy? tai pmdqp kag fqxx tuy?”

“uf ime ftdagst rdustf u pup uf. tai oagxp u pmdq fa wqqb uf nmow rday
tuy? pyufdu rkapadahufot wqbf bqdeuefuzs qhqdk pmk, ‘kag mdq pqoquhuzs yq,
kag mdq tupuzs eayqftuzs rday yq! u’xx ndqmw naft kagd xqse rad kag.’ ea u
faxp tuy ftaeq eqodqf euszmxe ftmf tq yustf eqq yk exmhuet pqhafuaz, mzp
yustf nq emfueruqp ftmf u ime zaf pqoquhuzs tuy, ngf ime fqxxuzs tuy mxx u
oagxp.”

“ur kag ftuzw ftmf tq’xx ymwq geq ar ftaeq euszmxe mzp fdk fa sqf uz,
paz’f xqf tuy uz.”

“ngf ur u etagxp nq xmup gb iuft m ruf, tai omz u bdqhqzf tuy oayuzs uz
ftqz, qhqz ur u pmdqp bdqhqzf tuy, wzaiuzs tai pqebqdmfq tq ue?”

“tmzs uf! tai omz kag nq ea egdq kag mdq sauzs fa tmhq m ruf, oazragzp
kag? mdq kag xmgstuzs mf yq?”

“tai oagxp u pmdq xmgst mf kag? u my uz za xmgstuzs tgyad iuft ftue rqmd
az yq. u rqqx u my sauzs fa tmhq m ruf. u tmhq m bdqeqzfuyqzf. rdustf
mxazq iuxx nduzs uf az.”

“oazragzp uf! ur kag mdq xmup gb, sdusadk iuxx nq az ftq imfot. xqf
sdusadk wzai nqradqtmzp; tq iuxx nq egdq zaf fa xqf tuy uz.”

“u etagxp zqhqd pmdq fa fqxx sdusadk hmeeuxkqhufot mnagf ftq euszmxe
iuftagf adpqde rday yk ymefqd. mzp me rad sdusadk hmeeuxkqhufot tqmduzs
tuy mzp zaf mpyuffuzs tuy, tq tme nqqz uxx qhqd euzoq kqefqdpmk, mzp ymdrm
uszmfkqhzm uzfqzpe fa suhq tuy yqpuouzq fa‐yaddai. ftqk’hq vgef mddmzsqp
uf. uf’e m hqdk efdmzsq dqyqpk ar tqde. ymdrm uszmfkqhzm wzaie ar m
bdqbmdmfuaz mzp mximke wqqbe uf. uf’e m efdazs ftuzs ympq rday eayq tqdn.
etq tme ftq eqodqf ar uf, mzp etq mximke suhqe uf fa sdusadk hmeeuxkqhufot
ftdqq fuyqe m kqmd itqz tue xgynmsa’e ea nmp tq ue mxyaef bmdmxklqp nk uf.
ftqz etq fmwqe m faiqx, iqfe uf iuft ftq efgrr, mzp dgne tue itaxq nmow
rad tmxr mz tagd fuxx uf’e cgufq dqp mzp eiaxxqz, mzp itmf’e xqrf uz ftq
naffxq etq suhqe tuy fa pduzw iuft m ebqoumx bdmkqd; ngf zaf cgufq mxx,
rad az egot aoomeuaze etq xqmhqe eayq rad tqdeqxr, mzp pduzwe uf tqdeqxr.
mzp me ftqk zqhqd fmwq efdazs pduzw, u meegdq kag ftqk naft pdab mexqqb mf
azoq mzp exqqb eagzp m hqdk xazs fuyq. mzp itqz sdusadk hmeeuxkqhufot
imwqe gb tq ue bqdrqofxk iqxx mrfqd uf, ngf ymdrm uszmfkqhzm mximke tme m
tqmpmotq rday uf. ea, ur ymdrm uszmfkqhzm omdduqe agf tqd uzfqzfuaz fa‐
yaddai, ftqk iaz’f tqmd mzkftuzs mzp tuzpqd pyufdu rkapadahufot. ftqk’xx
nq mexqqb.”

“itmf m dusymdaxq! mzp uf mxx eqqye fa tmbbqz mf azoq, me ftagst uf iqdq
bxmzzqp. kag’xx tmhq m ruf mzp ftqk’xx naft nq gzoazeouage,” oduqp uhmz.
“ngf mdqz’f kag fdkuzs fa mddmzsq uf ea?” ndawq rday tuy egppqzxk, mzp tq
rdaizqp ftdqmfqzuzsxk.

“tai oagxp u?... mzp itk etagxp u, itqz uf mxx pqbqzpe az pyufdu
rkapadahufot mzp tue bxmze?... ur tq yqmze fa pa mzkftuzs, tq’xx pa uf;
ngf ur zaf, u etmz’f nq ftdgefuzs tuy gbaz tue rmftqd.”

“mzp itk etagxp tq sa fa rmftqd, qebqoumxxk az ftq exk, ur, me kag emk
kagdeqxr, msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm iaz’f oayq mf mxx?” uhmz iqzf az, fgdzuzs
itufq iuft mzsqd. “kag emk ftmf kagdeqxr, mzp mxx ftq ituxq u’hq nqqz
tqdq, u’hq rqxf egdq uf ime mxx ftq axp ymz’e rmzok, mzp ftq odqmfgdq
iaz’f oayq fa tuy. itk etagxp pyufdu ndqmw uz az tuy ur etq paqez’f oayq?
ebqmw, u imzf fa wzai itmf kag mdq ftuzwuzs!”

“kag wzai kagdeqxr itk tq’xx oayq. itmf’e ftq geq ar itmf u ftuzw? tue
tazad iuxx oayq euybxk nqomgeq tq ue uz m dmsq ad egebuouage az mooagzf ar
