“iqxx, kag idufq fa ftq bduqef; tq’xx ymwq ftq nmdsmuz.”

“tq omz’f pa uf. tq tme za qkq rad ngeuzqee. tq ue m bqdrqof fdqmegdq, u’p
suhq tuy fiqzfk ftagemzp fa fmwq omdq ar rad yq iuftagf m dqoqubf; ngf tq
