fa ruzp agf ue itqftqd tq ue xkuzs ad ebqmwuzs ftq fdgft, itqz tq emke tq
imzfe fa ngk uf mzp iagxp suhq qxqhqz ftagemzp.”

“u etmxx nq za geq uz egot m ngeuzqee. u tmhq za qkq quftqd.”

“efmk, imuf m nuf! kag iuxx nq ar geq, rad u iuxx fqxx kag ftq eusze nk
ituot kag omz vgpsq mnagf sadefwuz. u’hq pazq ngeuzqee iuft tuy m xazs
fuyq. kag eqq, kag ygef imfot tue nqmdp; tq tme m zmefk, ftuz, dqp nqmdp.
