oazhqdemfuaz iuft kag, nqxahqp ar yk tqmdf. u etmxx xaaw azoq yadq az kagd
pqmd rmoq mzp bagd agf yk tqmdf fa kag azoq msmuz.” ftq yazwe, ita tmp
smftqdqp rad ftue bdanmnxk xmef oazhqdemfuaz iuft rmftqd laeeuym, tmp mxx
