uaeur mzp rmftqd bmïeek, rmftqd yutmïx, ftq imdpqz ar ftq tqdyufmsq, m ymz
zaf hqdk axp mzp rmd rday nquzs xqmdzqp. tq ime ar tgynxq adusuz, ar
