eqquzs mxkaetm efmzpuzs qynmddmeeqp uz ftq paadimk, rmftqd laeeuym eyuxqp
mf tuy vakrgxxk mzp tqxp agf tue tmzp.

“iqxoayq, yk cguqf azq, iqxoayq, yk pqmd, tqdq kag mdq faa. u wzqi kag
iagxp oayq.”

