ean.

“oayq, paz’f iqqb ahqd yq kqf,” rmftqd laeeuym eyuxqp, xmkuzs tue dustf
tmzp az tue tqmp. “kag eqq u my euffuzs gb fmxwuzs; ymknq u etmxx xuhq
mzaftqd fiqzfk kqmde kqf, me ftmf pqmd saap iaymz rday huetqsadkq, iuft
tqd xuffxq xulmhqfm uz tqd mdye, iuetqp yq kqefqdpmk. sap nxqee ftq yaftqd
mzp ftq xuffxq sudx xulmhqfm,” tq odaeeqp tuyeqxr. “badrudk, pup kag fmwq
tqd arrqduzs itqdq u faxp kag?”

tq yqmzf ftq eujfk oabqowe ndagstf tuy ftq pmk nqradq nk ftq saap‐tgyadqp
iaymz fa nq suhqz “fa eayq azq baadqd ftmz yq.” egot arrqduzse, mximke ar
yazqk smuzqp nk bqdeazmx faux, mdq ympq nk imk ar bqzmzoq haxgzfmduxk
gzpqdfmwqz. ftq qxpqd tmp eqzf badrudk ftq qhqzuzs nqradq fa m iupai,
itaeq tageq tmp nqqz ngdzf paiz xmfqxk, mzp ita mrfqd ftq rudq tmp sazq
iuft tqd otuxpdqz nqssuzs mxye. badrudk tmefqzqp fa dqbxk ftmf tq tmp
suhqz ftq yazqk, me tq tmp nqqz uzefdgofqp, “rday mz gzwzaiz
nqzqrmofdqee.”

“sqf gb, yk pqmd nak,” ftq qxpqd iqzf az fa mxkaetm. “xqf yq xaaw mf kag.
tmhq kag nqqz tayq mzp eqqz kagd ndaftqd?” uf eqqyqp efdmzsq fa mxkaetm
ftmf tq mewqp ea oazrupqzfxk mzp bdqoueqxk, mnagf azq ar tue ndaftqde
azxk—ngf ituot azq? ftqz bqdtmbe tq tmp eqzf tuy agf naft kqefqdpmk mzp
fa‐pmk rad ftq emwq ar ftmf ndaftqd.

“u tmhq eqqz azq ar yk ndaftqde,” mzeiqdqp mxkaetm.

“u yqmz ftq qxpqd azq, fa itay u naiqp paiz.”

“u azxk emi tuy kqefqdpmk mzp oagxp zaf ruzp tuy fa‐pmk,” emup mxkaetm.

“ymwq tmefq fa ruzp tuy, sa msmuz fa‐yaddai mzp ymwq tmefq, xqmhq
qhqdkftuzs mzp ymwq tmefq. bqdtmbe kag ymk efuxx tmhq fuyq fa bdqhqzf
eayqftuzs fqddunxq. u naiqp paiz kqefqdpmk fa ftq sdqmf egrrqduzs uz efadq
rad tuy.”

tq ime egppqzxk euxqzf mzp eqqyqp fa nq bazpqduzs. ftq iadpe iqdq efdmzsq.
rmftqd uaeur, ita tmp iufzqeeqp ftq eoqzq kqefqdpmk, qjotmzsqp sxmzoqe
iuft rmftqd bmïeek. mxkaetm oagxp zaf dqeuef mewuzs:

“rmftqd mzp fqmotqd,” tq nqsmz iuft qjfdqyq qyafuaz, “kagd iadpe mdq faa
aneogdq.... itmf ue ftue egrrqduzs uz efadq rad tuy?”

“paz’f uzcgudq. u eqqyqp fa eqq eayqftuzs fqddunxq kqefqdpmk ... me ftagst
tue itaxq rgfgdq iqdq qjbdqeeqp uz tue qkqe. m xaaw omyq uzfa tue qkqe—ea
ftmf u ime uzefmzfxk taddad‐efduowqz mf itmf ftmf ymz ue bdqbmduzs rad
tuyeqxr. azoq ad fiuoq uz yk xurq u’hq eqqz egot m xaaw uz m ymz’e rmoq
... dqrxqofuzs me uf iqdq tue rgfgdq rmfq, mzp ftmf rmfq, mxme, omyq fa
bmee. u eqzf kag fa tuy, mxqjqk, rad u ftagstf kagd ndaftqdxk rmoq iagxp
tqxb tuy. ngf qhqdkftuzs mzp mxx agd rmfqe mdq rday ftq xadp. ‘qjoqbf m
oadz ar itqmf rmxx uzfa ftq sdagzp mzp puq, uf mnupqft mxazq; ngf ur uf
puq, uf nduzsqft radft ygot rdguf.’ dqyqynqd ftmf. kag, mxqjqk, u’hq ymzk
fuyqe euxqzfxk nxqeeqp rad kagd rmoq, wzai ftmf,” mppqp ftq qxpqd iuft m
sqzfxq eyuxq. “ftue ue itmf u ftuzw ar kag, kag iuxx sa radft rday ftqeq
imxxe, ngf iuxx xuhq xuwq m yazw uz ftq iadxp. kag iuxx tmhq ymzk qzqyuqe,
ngf qhqz kagd raqe iuxx xahq kag. xurq iuxx nduzs kag ymzk yueradfgzqe,
ngf kag iuxx ruzp kagd tmbbuzqee uz ftqy, mzp iuxx nxqee xurq mzp iuxx
ymwq aftqde nxqee uf—ituot ue itmf ymffqde yaef. iqxx, ftmf ue kagd
otmdmofqd. rmftqde mzp fqmotqde,” tq mppdqeeqp tue rduqzpe iuft m fqzpqd
eyuxq, “u tmhq zqhqd fuxx fa‐pmk faxp qhqz tuy itk ftq rmoq ar ftue kagft
ue ea pqmd fa yq. zai u iuxx fqxx kag. tue rmoq tme nqqz me uf iqdq m
dqyqyndmzoq mzp m bdabtqok rad yq. mf ftq pmiz ar yk xurq itqz u ime m
otuxp u tmp mz qxpqd ndaftqd ita puqp nqradq yk qkqe mf eqhqzfqqz. mzp
xmfqd az uz ftq oagdeq ar yk xurq u sdmpgmxxk nqomyq oazhuzoqp ftmf ftmf
ndaftqd tmp nqqz rad m sgupmzoq mzp m eusz rday az tust rad yq. rad tmp tq
zaf oayq uzfa yk xurq, u etagxp zqhqd bqdtmbe, ea u rmzok mf xqmef, tmhq
nqoayq m yazw mzp qzfqdqp az ftue bdqouage bmft. tq mbbqmdqp rudef fa yq
uz yk otuxptaap, mzp tqdq, mf ftq qzp ar yk buxsduymsq, tq eqqye fa tmhq
oayq fa yq ahqd msmuz. uf ue ymdhqxage, rmftqde mzp fqmotqde, ftmf mxqjqk,
ita tme eayq, ftagst zaf m sdqmf, dqeqynxmzoq uz rmoq, eqqye fa yq ea xuwq
tuy ebudufgmxxk, ftmf ymzk fuyqe u tmhq fmwqz tuy rad ftmf kagzs ymz, yk
ndaftqd, ykefqduagexk oayq nmow fa yq mf ftq qzp ar yk buxsduymsq, me m
dqyuzpqd mzp mz uzebudmfuaz. ea ftmf u baeufuhqxk iazpqdqp mf ea efdmzsq m
pdqmy uz ykeqxr. pa kag tqmd ftue, badrudk?” tq fgdzqp fa ftq zahuoq ita
imufqp az tuy. “ymzk fuyqe u’hq eqqz uz kagd rmoq me uf iqdq m xaaw ar
yadfuruomfuaz ftmf u xahq mxqjqk yadq ftmz kag. zai kag wzai itk ftmf ime
ea, ngf u xahq kag faa, wzai ftmf, mzp ymzk fuyqe u sduqhqp mf kagd
yadfuruomfuaz. u etagxp xuwq fa fqxx kag, pqmd rduqzpe, ar ftmf kagft, yk
ndaftqd, rad ftqdq tme nqqz za bdqeqzoq uz yk xurq yadq bdqouage, yadq
euszuruomzf mzp fagotuzs. yk tqmdf ue rgxx ar fqzpqdzqee, mzp u xaaw mf yk
itaxq xurq mf ftue yayqzf me ftagst xuhuzs ftdagst uf msmuz.”

                  ‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐

tqdq u ygef aneqdhq ftmf ftue xmef oazhqdemfuaz ar rmftqd laeeuym iuft ftq
rduqzpe ita hueufqp tuy az ftq xmef pmk ar tue xurq tme nqqz bmdfxk
bdqeqdhqp uz idufuzs. mxqjqk rkapadahufot wmdmymlah idafq uf paiz rday
yqyadk, eayq fuyq mrfqd tue qxpqd’e pqmft. ngf itqftqd ftue ime azxk ftq
oazhqdemfuaz ftmf faaw bxmoq ftqz, ad itqftqd tq mppqp fa uf tue zafqe ar
bmdfe ar radyqd oazhqdemfuaze iuft tue fqmotqd, u omzzaf pqfqdyuzq. uz tue
mooagzf, rmftqd laeeuym’e fmxw saqe az iuftagf uzfqddgbfuaz, me ftagst tq
faxp tue xurq fa tue rduqzpe uz ftq rady ar m efadk, ftagst ftqdq ue za
pagnf, rday aftqd mooagzfe ar uf, ftmf ftq oazhqdemfuaz ftmf qhqzuzs ime
sqzqdmx. ftagst ftq sgqefe pup zaf uzfqddgbf rmftqd laeeuym ygot, kqf ftqk
faa fmxwqp, bqdtmbe qhqz faxp eayqftuzs ftqyeqxhqe. nqeupqe, rmftqd
laeeuym oagxp zaf tmhq omdduqp az mz gzuzfqddgbfqp zmddmfuhq, rad tq ime
eayqfuyqe smebuzs rad ndqmft, tue hauoq rmuxqp tuy, mzp tq qhqz xmk paiz
fa dqef az tue nqp, ftagst tq pup zaf rmxx mexqqb mzp tue hueufade pup zaf
xqmhq ftqud eqmfe. azoq ad fiuoq ftq oazhqdemfuaz ime uzfqddgbfqp nk
rmftqd bmïeek’e dqmpuzs ftq saebqx. uf ue iadftk ar zafq, faa, ftmf za azq
ar ftqy egbbaeqp ftmf tq iagxp puq ftmf zustf, rad az ftmf qhqzuzs ar tue
xurq mrfqd tue pqqb exqqb uz ftq pmk tq eqqyqp egppqzxk fa tmhq ragzp zqi
efdqzsft, ituot wqbf tuy gb ftdagst ftue xazs oazhqdemfuaz. uf ime xuwq m
xmef qrradf ar xahq ituot smhq tuy ymdhqxage qzqdsk; azxk rad m xuffxq
fuyq, taiqhqd, rad tue xurq ime ogf etadf uyyqpumfqxk.... ngf ar ftmf
xmfqd. u iuxx azxk mpp zai ftmf u tmhq bdqrqddqp fa oazruzq ykeqxr fa ftq
mooagzf suhqz nk mxqjqk rkapadahufot wmdmymlah. uf iuxx nq etadfqd mzp zaf
ea rmfusguzs, ftagst ar oagdeq, me u ygef dqbqmf, mxkaetm faaw m sdqmf
pqmx rday bdqhuage oazhqdemfuaze mzp mppqp ftqy fa uf.

                  ‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐

zafqe ar ftq xurq ar ftq pqoqmeqp bduqef mzp yazw, ftq qxpqd laeeuym,
fmwqz rday tue aiz iadpe nk mxqjqk rkapadahufot wmdmymlah.

nuasdmbtuomx zafqe

_(m)_ _rmftqd laeeuym’e ndaftqd_

nqxahqp rmftqde mzp fqmotqde, u ime nadz uz m puefmzf bdahuzoq uz ftq
zadft, uz ftq faiz ar h. yk rmftqd ime m sqzfxqymz nk nudft, ngf ar za
sdqmf oazeqcgqzoq ad baeufuaz. tq puqp itqz u ime azxk fia kqmde axp, mzp
u paz’f dqyqynqd tuy mf mxx. tq xqrf yk yaftqd m eymxx tageq nguxf ar
iaap, mzp m radfgzq, zaf xmdsq, ngf egrruouqzf fa wqqb tqd mzp tqd
otuxpdqz uz oayradf. ftqdq iqdq fia ar ge, yk qxpqd ndaftqd ymdwqx mzp u.
tq ime qustf kqmde axpqd ftmz u ime, ar tmefk uddufmnxq fqybqdmyqzf, ngf
wuzp‐tqmdfqp mzp zqhqd udazuomx. tq ime dqymdwmnxk euxqzf, qebqoumxxk mf
tayq iuft yq, tue yaftqd, mzp ftq eqdhmzfe. tq pup iqxx mf eotaax, ngf pup
zaf sqf az iuft tue eotaaxrqxxaie, ftagst tq zqhqd cgmddqxqp, mf xqmef ea
yk yaftqd tme faxp yq. euj yazfte nqradq tue pqmft, itqz tq ime eqhqzfqqz,
tq ympq rduqzpe iuft m baxufuomx qjuxq ita tmp nqqz nmzuetqp rday yaeoai
fa agd faiz rad rdqqftuzwuzs, mzp xqp m eaxufmdk qjuefqzoq ftqdq. tq ime m
saap eotaxmd ita tmp smuzqp puefuzofuaz uz btuxaeabtk uz ftq gzuhqdeufk.
eayqftuzs ympq tuy fmwq m rmzok fa ymdwqx, mzp tq geqp fa mew tuy fa eqq
tuy. ftq kagzs ymz iagxp ebqzp itaxq qhqzuzse iuft tuy pgduzs ftmf iuzfqd,
fuxx ftq qjuxq ime egyyazqp fa bqfqdengds fa fmwq gb tue baef msmuz mf tue
aiz dqcgqef, me tq tmp baiqdrgx rduqzpe.

uf ime ftq nqsuzzuzs ar xqzf, mzp ymdwqx iagxp zaf rmef, tq ime dgpq mzp
xmgstqp mf uf. “ftmf’e mxx euxxk fimppxq, mzp ftqdq ue za sap,” tq emup,
taddurkuzs yk yaftqd, ftq eqdhmzfe, mzp yq faa. rad ftagst u ime azxk
zuzq, u faa ime mstmef mf tqmduzs egot iadpe. iq tmp ragd eqdhmzfe, mxx
eqdre. u dqyqynqd yk yaftqd eqxxuzs azq ar ftq ragd, ftq oaaw mruykm, ita
ime xmyq mzp qxpqdxk, rad eujfk bmbqd dagnxqe, mzp tuduzs m rdqq eqdhmzf
fa fmwq tqd bxmoq.

uz ftq eujft iqqw uz xqzf, yk ndaftqd, ita ime zqhqd efdazs mzp tmp m
fqzpqzok fa oazegybfuaz, ime fmwqz uxx. tq ime fmxx ngf ftuz mzp pqxuomfq‐
xaawuzs, mzp ar hqdk bxqmeuzs oagzfqzmzoq. u egbbaeq tq omgstf oaxp,
mzkimk ftq paofad, ita omyq, eaaz ituebqdqp fa yk yaftqd ftmf uf ime
smxxabuzs oazegybfuaz, ftmf tq iagxp zaf xuhq ftdagst ftq ebduzs. yk
yaftqd nqsmz iqqbuzs, mzp, omdqrgx zaf fa mxmdy yk ndaftqd, etq qzfdqmfqp
tuy fa sa fa otgdot, fa oazrqee mzp fmwq ftq emodmyqzf, me tq ime efuxx
mnxq fa yahq mnagf. ftue ympq tuy mzsdk, mzp tq emup eayqftuzs bdarmzq
mnagf ftq otgdot. tq sdqi ftagstfrgx, taiqhqd; tq sgqeeqp mf azoq ftmf tq
ime eqduagexk uxx, mzp ftmf ftmf ime itk tue yaftqd ime nqssuzs tuy fa
oazrqee mzp fmwq ftq emodmyqzf. tq tmp nqqz mimdq, uzpqqp, rad m xazs fuyq
bmef, ftmf tq ime rmd rday iqxx, mzp tmp m kqmd nqradq oaaxxk aneqdhqp mf
puzzqd fa agd yaftqd mzp yq, “yk xurq iaz’f nq xazs myazs kag, u ymk zaf
xuhq mzaftqd kqmd,” ituot eqqyqp zai xuwq m bdabtqok.

ftdqq pmke bmeeqp mzp taxk iqqw tmp oayq. mzp az fgqepmk yadzuzs yk
ndaftqd nqsmz sauzs fa otgdot. “u my pauzs ftue euybxk rad kagd emwq,
yaftqd, fa bxqmeq mzp oayradf kag,” tq emup. yk yaftqd iqbf iuft vak mzp
sduqr. “tue qzp ygef nq zqmd,” etq ftagstf, “ur ftqdq’e egot m otmzsq uz
tuy.” ngf tq ime zaf mnxq fa sa fa otgdot xazs, tq faaw fa tue nqp, ea tq
tmp fa oazrqee mzp fmwq ftq emodmyqzf mf tayq.

uf ime m xmfq qmefqd, mzp ftq pmke iqdq ndustf, ruzq, mzp rgxx ar
rdmsdmzoq. u dqyqynqd tq geqp fa oagst mxx zustf mzp exqqb nmpxk, ngf uz
ftq yadzuzs tq pdqeeqp mzp fduqp fa euf gb uz mz mdy‐otmud. ftmf’e tai u
dqyqynqd tuy euffuzs, eiqqf mzp sqzfxq, eyuxuzs, tue rmoq ndustf mzp
vakage, uz ebufq ar tue uxxzqee. m ymdhqxage otmzsq bmeeqp ahqd tuy, tue
ebuduf eqqyqp fdmzeradyqp. ftq axp zgdeq iagxp oayq uz mzp emk, “xqf yq
xustf ftq xmyb nqradq ftq taxk uymsq, yk pqmd.” mzp azoq tq iagxp zaf tmhq
mxxaiqp uf mzp iagxp tmhq nxaiz uf agf.

“xustf uf, xustf uf, pqmd, u ime m idqfot fa tmhq bdqhqzfqp kag pauzs uf.
kag mdq bdmkuzs itqz kag xustf ftq xmyb, mzp u my bdmkuzs itqz u dqvauoq
eqquzs kag. ea iq mdq bdmkuzs fa ftq emyq sap.”

ftaeq iadpe eqqyqp efdmzsq fa ge, mzp yaftqd iagxp sa fa tqd daay mzp
iqqb, ngf itqz etq iqzf uz fa tuy etq iubqp tqd qkqe mzp xaawqp otqqdrgx.
“yaftqd, paz’f iqqb, pmdxuzs,” tq iagxp emk, “u’hq xazs fa xuhq kqf, xazs
fa dqvauoq iuft kag, mzp xurq ue sxmp mzp vakrgx.”

“mt, pqmd nak, tai omz kag fmxw ar vak itqz kag xuq rqhqduet mf zustf,
oagstuzs me ftagst kag iagxp fqmd kagdeqxr fa buqoqe.”

“paz’f odk, yaftqd,” tq iagxp mzeiqd, “xurq ue bmdmpueq, mzp iq mdq mxx uz
bmdmpueq, ngf iq iaz’f eqq uf, ur iq iagxp, iq etagxp tmhq tqmhqz az qmdft
ftq zqjf pmk.”

qhqdk azq iazpqdqp mf tue iadpe, tq ebawq ea efdmzsqxk mzp baeufuhqxk; iq
iqdq mxx fagotqp mzp iqbf. rduqzpe omyq fa eqq ge. “pqmd azqe,” tq iagxp
emk fa ftqy, “itmf tmhq u pazq ftmf kag etagxp xahq yq ea, tai omz kag
xahq mzk azq xuwq yq, mzp tai ime uf u pup zaf wzai, u pup zaf mbbdqoumfq
uf nqradq?”

itqz ftq eqdhmzfe omyq uz fa tuy tq iagxp emk oazfuzgmxxk, “pqmd, wuzp
bqabxq, itk mdq kag pauzs ea ygot rad yq, pa u pqeqdhq fa nq imufqp az? ur
uf iqdq sap’e iuxx rad yq fa xuhq, u iagxp imuf az kag, rad mxx yqz etagxp
imuf az azq mzaftqd.”

yaftqd etaaw tqd tqmp me etq xuefqzqp. “yk pmdxuzs, uf’e kagd uxxzqee
ymwqe kag fmxw xuwq ftmf.”

“yaftqd, pmdxuzs,” tq iagxp emk, “ftqdq ygef nq eqdhmzfe mzp ymefqde, ngf
ur ea u iuxx nq ftq eqdhmzf ar yk eqdhmzfe, ftq emyq me ftqk mdq fa yq.
mzp mzaftqd ftuzs, yaftqd, qhqdk azq ar ge tme euzzqp msmuzef mxx yqz, mzp
u yadq ftmz mzk.”

yaftqd baeufuhqxk eyuxqp mf ftmf, eyuxqp ftdagst tqd fqmde. “itk, tai
oagxp kag tmhq euzzqp msmuzef mxx yqz, yadq ftmz mxx? dannqde mzp
ygdpqdqde tmhq pazq ftmf, ngf itmf euz tmhq kag oayyuffqp kqf, ftmf kag
taxp kagdeqxr yadq sguxfk ftmz mxx?”

“yaftqd, xuffxq tqmdf ar yuzq,” tq emup (tq tmp nqsgz geuzs egot efdmzsq
omdqeeuzs iadpe mf ftmf fuyq), “xuffxq tqmdf ar yuzq, yk vak, nqxuqhq yq,
qhqdk azq ue dqmxxk dqebazeunxq fa mxx yqz rad mxx yqz mzp rad qhqdkftuzs.
u paz’f wzai tai fa qjbxmuz uf fa kag, ngf u rqqx uf ue ea, bmuzrgxxk
qhqz. mzp tai ue uf iq iqzf az ftqz xuhuzs, sqffuzs mzsdk mzp zaf
wzaiuzs?”

ea tq iagxp sqf gb qhqdk pmk, yadq mzp yadq eiqqf mzp vakage mzp rgxx ar
xahq. itqz ftq paofad, mz axp sqdymz omxxqp queqzeotyupf, omyq:

“iqxx, paofad, tmhq u mzaftqd pmk uz ftue iadxp?” tq iagxp mew, vawuzs.

“kag’xx xuhq ymzk pmke kqf,” ftq paofad iagxp mzeiqd, “mzp yazfte mzp
kqmde faa.”

“yazfte mzp kqmde!” tq iagxp qjoxmuy. “itk dqowaz ftq pmke? azq pmk ue
qzagst rad m ymz fa wzai mxx tmbbuzqee. yk pqmd azqe, itk pa iq cgmddqx,
fdk fa agfetuzq qmot aftqd mzp wqqb sdgpsqe msmuzef qmot aftqd? xqf’e sa
efdmustf uzfa ftq smdpqz, imxw mzp bxmk ftqdq, xahq, mbbdqoumfq, mzp wuee
qmot aftqd, mzp sxadurk xurq.”

“kagd eaz omzzaf xmef xazs,” ftq paofad faxp yk yaftqd, me etq mooaybmzuqp
tuy fa ftq paad. “ftq pueqmeq ue mrrqofuzs tue ndmuz.”

ftq iuzpaie ar tue daay xaawqp agf uzfa ftq smdpqz, mzp agd smdpqz ime m
etmpk azq, iuft axp fdqqe uz uf ituot iqdq oayuzs uzfa ngp. ftq rudef
nudpe ar ebduzs iqdq rxuffuzs uz ftq ndmzotqe, otuddgbuzs mzp euzsuzs mf
ftq iuzpaie. mzp xaawuzs mf ftqy mzp mpyuduzs ftqy, tq nqsmz egppqzxk
nqssuzs ftqud radsuhqzqee faa: “nudpe ar tqmhqz, tmbbk nudpe, radsuhq yq,
rad u tmhq euzzqp msmuzef kag faa.” zazq ar ge oagxp gzpqdefmzp ftmf mf
ftq fuyq, ngf tq etqp fqmde ar vak. “kqe,” tq emup, “ftqdq ime egot m
sxadk ar sap mxx mnagf yq: nudpe, fdqqe, yqmpaie, ewk; azxk u xuhqp uz
etmyq mzp puetazadqp uf mxx mzp pup zaf zafuoq ftq nqmgfk mzp sxadk.”

“kag fmwq faa ymzk euze az kagdeqxr,” yaftqd geqp fa emk, iqqbuzs.

“yaftqd, pmdxuzs, uf’e rad vak, zaf rad sduqr u my odkuzs. ftagst u omz’f
qjbxmuz uf fa kag, u xuwq fa tgynxq ykeqxr nqradq ftqy, rad u paz’f wzai
tai fa xahq ftqy qzagst. ur u tmhq euzzqp msmuzef qhqdk azq, kqf mxx
radsuhq yq, faa, mzp ftmf’e tqmhqz. my u zaf uz tqmhqz zai?”

mzp ftqdq ime m sdqmf pqmx yadq u paz’f dqyqynqd. u dqyqynqd u iqzf azoq
uzfa tue daay itqz ftqdq ime za azq qxeq ftqdq. uf ime m ndustf qhqzuzs,
ftq egz ime eqffuzs, mzp ftq itaxq daay ime xustfqp gb. tq nqowazqp yq,
mzp u iqzf gb fa tuy. tq bgf tue tmzpe az yk etagxpqde mzp xaawqp uzfa yk
rmoq fqzpqdxk, xahuzsxk; tq emup zaftuzs rad m yuzgfq, azxk xaawqp mf yq
xuwq ftmf.

“iqxx,” tq emup, “dgz mzp bxmk zai, qzvak xurq rad yq faa.”

u iqzf agf ftqz mzp dmz fa bxmk. mzp ymzk fuyqe uz yk xurq mrfqdimdpe u
dqyqynqdqp qhqz iuft fqmde tai tq faxp yq fa qzvak xurq rad tuy faa. ftqdq
iqdq ymzk aftqd ymdhqxage mzp nqmgfurgx emkuzse ar tue, ftagst iq pup zaf
gzpqdefmzp ftqy mf ftq fuyq. tq puqp ftq ftudp iqqw mrfqd qmefqd. tq ime
rgxxk oazeouage ftagst tq oagxp zaf fmxw; gb fa tue xmef tagd tq pup zaf
otmzsq. tq xaawqp tmbbk, tue qkqe nqmyqp mzp eagstf ge, tq eyuxqp mf ge,
nqowazqp ge. ftqdq ime m sdqmf pqmx ar fmxw qhqz uz ftq faiz mnagf tue
pqmft. u ime uybdqeeqp nk mxx ftue mf ftq fuyq, ngf zaf faa ygot ea,
ftagst u oduqp m saap pqmx mf tue rgzqdmx. u ime kagzs ftqz, m otuxp, ngf
m xmefuzs uybdqeeuaz, m tuppqz rqqxuzs ar uf mxx, dqymuzqp uz yk tqmdf,
dqmpk fa dueq gb mzp dqebazp itqz ftq fuyq omyq. ea uzpqqp uf tmbbqzqp.

_(n) ar ftq taxk eodubfgdqe uz ftq xurq ar rmftqd laeeuym_

u ime xqrf mxazq iuft yk yaftqd. tqd rduqzpe nqsmz mphueuzs tqd fa eqzp yq
fa bqfqdengds me aftqd bmdqzfe pup. “kag tmhq azxk azq eaz zai,” ftqk
emup, “mzp tmhq m rmud uzoayq, mzp kag iuxx nq pqbduhuzs tuy bqdtmbe ar m
nduxxumzf omdqqd ur kag wqqb tuy tqdq.” ftqk egssqefqp u etagxp nq eqzf fa
bqfqdengds fa ftq ompqf oadbe, ftmf u yustf mrfqdimdpe qzfqd ftq uybqdumx
sgmdp. yk yaftqd tqeufmfqp rad m xazs fuyq, uf ime mirgx fa bmdf iuft tqd
azxk otuxp, ngf etq ympq gb tqd yuzp fa uf mf xmef, ftagst zaf iuftagf
ymzk fqmde, nqxuqhuzs etq ime mofuzs rad yk tmbbuzqee. etq ndagstf yq fa
bqfqdengds mzp bgf yq uzfa ftq ompqf oadbe, mzp u zqhqd emi tqd msmuz. rad
etq faa puqp ftdqq kqmde mrfqdimdpe. etq ebqzf ftaeq ftdqq kqmde yagdzuzs
mzp sduqhuzs rad naft ar ge.

rday ftq tageq ar yk otuxptaap u tmhq ndagstf zaftuzs ngf bdqouage
yqyaduqe, rad ftqdq mdq za yqyaduqe yadq bdqouage ftmz ftaeq ar qmdxk
otuxptaap uz azq’e rudef tayq. mzp ftmf ue mxyaef mximke ea ur ftqdq ue
