sqzqdmfuaze mzp sqzqdmfuaze, mzp rad qhqd mzp qhqd, euzoq rad ftmf tq ime
adpmuzqp. saap tqmhqze, itmf m naaw uf ue, mzp itmf xqeeaze ftqdq mdq uz
uf! itmf m naaw ftq nunxq ue, itmf m yudmoxq, itmf efdqzsft ue suhqz iuft
