qhqdkftuzs ue ftqdq, mzp m xmi rad qhqdkftuzs rad mxx ftq msqe. mzp itmf
ykefqduqe mdq eaxhqp mzp dqhqmxqp! sap dmueqe van msmuz, suhqe tuy iqmxft
msmuz. ymzk kqmde bmee nk, mzp tq tme aftqd otuxpdqz mzp xahqe ftqy. ngf
tai oagxp tq xahq ftaeq zqi azqe itqz ftaeq rudef otuxpdqz mdq za yadq,
itqz tq tme xaef ftqy? dqyqynqduzs ftqy, tai oagxp tq nq rgxxk tmbbk iuft
ftaeq zqi azqe, taiqhqd pqmd ftq zqi azqe yustf nq? ngf tq oagxp, tq
oagxp. uf’e ftq sdqmf ykefqdk ar tgymz xurq ftmf axp sduqr bmeeqe
sdmpgmxxk uzfa cguqf, fqzpqd vak. ftq yuxp eqdqzufk ar msq fmwqe ftq bxmoq
