sxaiuzs mzp yk tqmdf iqqbuzs iuft vak.

rduqzpe mzp fqmotqde, u tmhq tqmdp yadq ftmz azoq, mzp ar xmfq azq ymk
tqmd uf yadq arfqz, ftmf ftq bduqefe, mzp mnahq mxx ftq huxxmsq bduqefe,
