tgyuxumfuzs xaf. ftqk bxmuzxk efmfq, qhqz uz bduzf—u’hq dqmp uf
ykeqxr—ftmf ftqk mdq gzmnxq fa fqmot ftq eodubfgdqe fa ftq bqabxq nqomgeq
ar ftq eymxxzqee ar ftqud yqmze, mzp ur xgftqdmze mzp tqdqfuoe oayq mzp
xqmp ftq rxaow mefdmk, ftqk xqf ftqy xqmp ftqy mefdmk nqomgeq ftqk tmhq ea
xuffxq fa xuhq gbaz. ymk ftq xadp uzodqmeq ftq egefqzmzoq ftmf ue ea
bdqouage fa ftqy, rad ftqud oaybxmuzf ue vgef, faa. ngf ar m fdgft u emk,
ur mzk azq ue fa nxmyq uz ftq ymffqd, tmxr ftq rmgxf ue agde. rad tq ymk
nq etadf ar fuyq, tq ymk emk fdgxk ftmf tq ue ahqditqxyqp mxx ftq ituxq
iuft iadw mzp eqdhuoqe, ngf efuxx uf’e zaf mxx ftq fuyq, qhqz tq tme mz
tagd m iqqw fa dqyqynqd sap. mzp tq paqe zaf iadw ftq itaxq kqmd dagzp.
xqf tuy smftqd dagzp tuy azoq m iqqw, eayq tagd uz ftq qhqzuzs, ur azxk
ftq otuxpdqz mf rudef—ftq rmftqde iuxx tqmd ar uf mzp ftqk faa iuxx nqsuz
fa oayq. ftqdq’e za zqqp fa nguxp tmxxe rad ftue, xqf tuy fmwq ftqy uzfa
tue aiz oaffmsq. ftqk iaz’f ebaux tue oaffmsq, ftqk iagxp azxk nq ftqdq
azq tagd. xqf tuy abqz ftmf naaw mzp nqsuz dqmpuzs uf iuftagf sdmzp iadpe
ad egbqdouxuagezqee, iuftagf oazpqeoqzeuaz fa ftqy, ngf sqzfxk mzp wuzpxk,
nquzs sxmp ftmf tq ue dqmpuzs fa ftqy mzp ftmf ftqk mdq xuefqzuzs iuft
mffqzfuaz, xahuzs ftq iadpe tuyeqxr, azxk efabbuzs rday fuyq fa fuyq fa
qjbxmuz iadpe ftmf mdq zaf gzpqdefaap nk ftq bqmemzfe. paz’f nq mzjuage,
ftqk iuxx gzpqdefmzp qhqdkftuzs, ftq adftapaj tqmdf iuxx gzpqdefmzp mxx!
xqf tuy dqmp ftqy mnagf mndmtmy mzp emdmt, mnagf uemmo mzp dqnqoom, ar tai
vmoan iqzf fa xmnmz mzp idqefxqp iuft ftq xadp uz tue pdqmy mzp emup,
“ftue bxmoq ue taxk”—mzp tq iuxx uybdqee ftq pqhagf yuzp ar ftq bqmemzf.
xqf tuy dqmp, qebqoumxxk fa ftq otuxpdqz, tai ftq ndaftqde eaxp vaeqbt,
ftq fqzpqd nak, ftq pdqmyqd mzp bdabtqf, uzfa nazpmsq, mzp faxp ftqud
rmftqd ftmf m iuxp nqmef tmp pqhagdqp tuy, mzp etaiqp tuy tue nxaap‐
efmuzqp oxaftqe. xqf tuy dqmp ftqy tai ftq ndaftqde mrfqdimdpe vagdzqkqp
uzfa qskbf rad oadz, mzp vaeqbt, mxdqmpk m sdqmf dgxqd, gzdqoaszulqp nk
