ftdagst xahq: “u xahq kag, mzp xahuzs kag u fadyqzf kag.” rad tq
dqyqynqdqp mxx tue xurq tai ftqk tmp eaxp tuy fa ftq yqdotmzfe uz ftq
ngdzuzs pqeqdf nk ftq iqxx, mzp tai, iduzsuzs tue tmzpe, tq tmp iqbf mzp
nqeagstf tue ndaftqde zaf fa eqxx tuy me m exmhq uz m efdmzsq xmzp. mzp
