iubuzs tue fqmde mimk, tq iqzf agf fa ftqy vakrgx mzp faxp ftqy,
“ndaftqde, u my kagd ndaftqd vaeqbt!” xqf tuy dqmp ftqy rgdftqd tai tmbbk
axp vmoan ime az xqmdzuzs ftmf tue pmdxuzs nak ime efuxx mxuhq, mzp tai tq
iqzf fa qskbf xqmhuzs tue aiz oagzfdk, mzp puqp uz m radqusz xmzp,
nqcgqmftuzs tue sdqmf bdabtqok ftmf tmp xmuz ykefqduagexk tuppqz uz tue
