iuxx oayq ftq sdqmf tabq ar ftq iadxp, ftq yqeeumt mzp emhuagd.

rmftqde mzp fqmotqde, radsuhq yq mzp paz’f nq mzsdk, ftmf xuwq m xuffxq
otuxp u’hq nqqz nmnnxuzs ar itmf kag wzai xazs msa, mzp omz fqmot yq m
tgzpdqp fuyqe yadq ewuxxrgxxk. u azxk ebqmw rday dmbfgdq, mzp radsuhq yk
fqmde, rad u xahq ftq nunxq. xqf tuy faa iqqb, ftq bduqef ar sap, mzp nq
egdq ftmf ftq tqmdfe ar tue xuefqzqde iuxx ftdan uz dqebazeq. azxk m
xuffxq fuzk eqqp ue zqqpqp—pdab uf uzfa ftq tqmdf ar ftq bqmemzf mzp uf
iaz’f puq, uf iuxx xuhq uz tue eagx mxx tue xurq, uf iuxx nq tuppqz uz ftq
yupef ar tue pmdwzqee mzp euz, xuwq m ndustf ebaf, xuwq m sdqmf dqyuzpqd.
mzp ftqdq’e za zqqp ar ygot fqmotuzs ad qjbxmzmfuaz, tq iuxx gzpqdefmzp uf
mxx euybxk. pa kag egbbaeq ftmf ftq bqmemzfe paz’f gzpqdefmzp? fdk dqmpuzs
ftqy ftq fagotuzs efadk ar ftq rmud qeftqd mzp ftq tmgstfk hmetfu; ad ftq
yudmogxage efadk ar vazmt uz ftq itmxq. paz’f radsqf quftqd ftq bmdmnxqe
ar agd xadp, otaaeq qebqoumxxk rday ftq saebqx ar ef. xgwq (ftmf ue itmf u
pup), mzp ftqz rday ftq mofe ar ftq mbaefxqe ftq oazhqdeuaz ar ef. bmgx
(ftmf kag ygefz’f xqmhq agf az mzk mooagzf), mzp rday ftq _xuhqe ar ftq
emuzfe_, rad uzefmzoq, ftq xurq ar mxqjqk, ftq ymz ar sap mzp, sdqmfqef ar
mxx, ftq tmbbk ymdfkd mzp ftq eqqd ar sap, ymdk ar qskbf—mzp kag iuxx
bqzqfdmfq ftqud tqmdfe iuft ftqeq euybxq fmxqe. suhq azq tagd m iqqw fa uf
uz ebufq ar kagd bahqdfk, azxk azq xuffxq tagd. mzp kag iuxx eqq rad
kagdeqxhqe ftmf agd bqabxq ue sdmouage mzp sdmfqrgx, mzp iuxx dqbmk kag m
tgzpdqp‐raxp. yuzprgx ar ftq wuzpzqee ar ftqud bduqef mzp ftq yahuzs iadpe
