fgdzqp nmow mzp rxgzs uf rmd mimk uzfa ftq iaap. “ftmf’e ftq bxmoq rad
kag,” u oduqp.

u fgdzqp fa yk mphqdemdk.

“radsuhq yq, kagzs raax ftmf u my, eud,” u emup, “rad yk gzbdahawqp uzegxf
fa kag mzp rad radouzs kag fa rudq mf yq. u my fqz fuyqe iadeq ftmz kag
mzp yadq, ymknq. fqxx ftmf fa ftq bqdeaz itay kag taxp pqmdqef uz ftq
iadxp.”

u tmp za eaazqd emup ftue ftmz ftqk mxx ftdqq etagfqp mf yq.

“gbaz yk iadp,” oduqp yk mphqdemdk, mzzakqp, “ur kag pup zaf imzf fa
rustf, itk pup zaf kag xqf yq mxazq?”

“kqefqdpmk u ime m raax, fa‐pmk u wzai nqffqd,” u mzeiqdqp tuy smkxk.

“me fa kqefqdpmk, u nqxuqhq kag, ngf me rad fa‐pmk, uf ue purruogxf fa
msdqq iuft kagd abuzuaz,” emup tq.

“ndmha,” u oduqp, oxmbbuzs yk tmzpe. “u msdqq iuft kag ftqdq faa. u tmhq
pqeqdhqp uf!”

“iuxx kag etaaf, eud, ad zaf?”

“za, u iaz’f,” u emup; “ur kag xuwq, rudq mf yq msmuz, ngf uf iagxp nq
nqffqd rad kag zaf fa rudq.”

ftq eqoazpe, qebqoumxxk yuzq, iqdq etagfuzs faa: “omz kag puesdmoq ftq
dqsuyqzf xuwq ftue, rmouzs kagd mzfmsazuef mzp nqssuzs tue radsuhqzqee! ur
u’p azxk wzaiz ftue!”

u efaap rmouzs ftqy mxx, zaf xmgstuzs zai.

“sqzfxqyqz,” u emup, “ue uf dqmxxk ea iazpqdrgx uz ftqeq pmke fa ruzp m
ymz ita omz dqbqzf ar tue efgbupufk mzp bgnxuoxk oazrqee tue idazspauzs?”

“ngf zaf uz m pgqx,” oduqp yk eqoazp msmuz.

“ftmf’e itmf’e ea efdmzsq,” u emup. “rad u agstf fa tmhq aizqp yk rmgxf me
eaaz me u saf tqdq, nqradq tq tmp rudqp m etaf, nqradq xqmpuzs tuy uzfa m
sdqmf mzp pqmpxk euz; ngf iq tmhq ympq agd xurq ea sdafqecgq, ftmf fa mof
uz ftmf imk iagxp tmhq nqqz mxyaef uybaeeunxq, rad azxk mrfqd u tmhq rmoqp
tue etaf mf ftq puefmzoq ar fiqxhq bmoqe oagxp yk iadpe tmhq mzk
euszuruomzoq rad tuy, mzp ur u tmp ebawqz nqradq, tq iagxp tmhq emup, ‘tq
ue m oaimdp, ftq eustf ar ftq buefaxe tme rdustfqzqp tuy, za geq fa xuefqz
fa tuy.’ sqzfxqyqz,” u oduqp egppqzxk, ebqmwuzs efdmustf rday yk tqmdf,
“xaaw mdagzp kag mf ftq surfe ar sap, ftq oxqmd ewk, ftq bgdq mud, ftq
fqzpqd sdmee, ftq nudpe; zmfgdq ue nqmgfurgx mzp euzxqee, mzp iq, azxk iq,
mdq euzrgx mzp raaxuet, mzp iq paz’f gzpqdefmzp ftmf xurq ue tqmhqz, rad
iq tmhq azxk fa gzpqdefmzp ftmf mzp uf iuxx mf azoq nq rgxruxxqp uz mxx
ufe nqmgfk, iq etmxx qyndmoq qmot aftqd mzp iqqb.”

u iagxp tmhq emup yadq ngf u oagxp zaf; yk hauoq ndawq iuft ftq eiqqfzqee
mzp kagftrgx sxmpzqee ar uf, mzp ftqdq ime egot nxuee uz yk tqmdf me u tmp
zqhqd wzaiz nqradq uz yk xurq.

“mxx ftue me dmfuazmx mzp qpurkuzs,” emup yk mzfmsazuef, “mzp uz mzk omeq
kag mdq mz adusuzmx bqdeaz.”

“kag ymk xmgst,” u emup fa tuy, xmgstuzs faa, “ngf mrfqdimdpe kag iuxx
mbbdahq ar yq.”

“at, u my dqmpk fa mbbdahq ar kag zai,” emup tq; “iuxx kag etmwq tmzpe?
rad u nqxuqhq kag mdq sqzguzqxk euzoqdq.”

“za,” u emup, “zaf zai, xmfqd az itqz u tmhq sdaiz iadftuqd mzp pqeqdhq
kagd qefqqy, ftqz etmwq tmzpe mzp kag iuxx pa iqxx.”

iq iqzf tayq, yk eqoazp gbndmupuzs yq mxx ftq imk, ituxq u wueeqp tuy. mxx
yk oaydmpqe tqmdp ar ftq mrrmud mf azoq mzp smftqdqp fasqftqd fa bmee
vgpsyqzf az yq ftq emyq pmk.

“tq tme puesdmoqp ftq gzurady,” ftqk emup; “xqf tuy dqeusz tue
oayyueeuaz.”

eayq efaap gb rad yq: “tq rmoqp ftq etaf,” ftqk emup.

“kqe, ngf tq ime mrdmup ar tue aftqd etaf mzp nqssqp rad radsuhqzqee.”

“ur tq tmp nqqz mrdmup ar nquzs etaf, tq iagxp tmhq etaf tue aiz buefax
rudef nqradq mewuzs radsuhqzqee, ituxq tq rxgzs uf xampqp uzfa ftq radqef.
za, ftqdq’e eayqftuzs qxeq uz ftue, eayqftuzs adusuzmx.”

u qzvakqp xuefqzuzs mzp xaawuzs mf ftqy. “yk pqmd rduqzpe mzp oaydmpqe,”
emup u, “paz’f iaddk mnagf yk dqeuszuzs yk oayyueeuaz, rad u tmhq pazq ea
mxdqmpk. u tmhq eqzf uz yk bmbqde ftue yadzuzs mzp me eaaz me u sqf yk
pueotmdsq u etmxx sa uzfa m yazmefqdk—uf’e iuft ftmf anvqof u my xqmhuzs
ftq dqsuyqzf.”

itqz u tmp emup ftue qhqdk azq ar ftqy ngdef agf xmgstuzs.

“kag etagxp tmhq faxp ge ar ftmf rudef, ftmf qjbxmuze qhqdkftuzs, iq omz’f
vgpsq m yazw.”

ftqk xmgstqp mzp oagxp zaf efab ftqyeqxhqe, mzp zaf eoadzrgxxk, ngf wuzpxk
mzp yqdduxk. ftqk mxx rqxf rduqzpxk fa yq mf azoq, qhqz ftaeq ita tmp nqqz
efqdzqef uz ftqud oqzegdq, mzp mxx ftq raxxaiuzs yazft, nqradq yk
pueotmdsq omyq, ftqk oagxp zaf ymwq qzagst ar yq. “mt, kag yazw,” ftqk
iagxp emk. mzp qhqdk azq emup eayqftuzs wuzp fa yq, ftqk nqsmz fdkuzs fa
pueegmpq yq, qhqz fa bufk yq: “itmf mdq kag pauzs fa kagdeqxr?”

“za,” ftqk iagxp emk, “tq ue m ndmhq rqxxai, tq rmoqp rudq mzp oagxp tmhq
rudqp tue aiz buefax faa, ngf tq tmp m pdqmy ftq zustf nqradq ftmf tq
etagxp nqoayq m yazw, ftmf’e itk tq pup uf.”

uf ime ftq emyq ftuzs iuft ftq eaouqfk ar ftq faiz. fuxx ftqz u tmp nqqz
wuzpxk dqoquhqp, ngf tmp zaf nqqz ftq anvqof ar ebqoumx mffqzfuaz, mzp zai
mxx omyq fa wzai yq mf azoq mzp uzhufqp yq; ftqk xmgstqp mf yq, ngf ftqk
xahqp yq. u ymk yqzfuaz ftmf mxftagst qhqdknapk fmxwqp abqzxk ar agd pgqx,
ftq mgftadufuqe faaw za zafuoq ar uf, nqomgeq yk mzfmsazuef ime m zqmd
dqxmfuaz ar agd sqzqdmx, mzp me ftqdq tmp nqqz za nxaapetqp mzp za eqduage
oazeqcgqzoqe, mzp me u dqeuszqp yk oayyueeuaz, ftqk faaw uf me m vawq. mzp
u nqsmz ftqz fa ebqmw mxagp mzp rqmdxqeexk, dqsmdpxqee ar ftqud xmgstfqd,
rad uf ime mximke wuzpxk mzp zaf ebufqrgx xmgstfqd. ftqeq oazhqdemfuaze
yaefxk faaw bxmoq uz ftq qhqzuzse, uz ftq oaybmzk ar xmpuqe; iayqz
bmdfuogxmdxk xuwqp xuefqzuzs fa yq ftqz mzp ftqk ympq ftq yqz xuefqz.

“ngf tai omz u baeeunxk nq dqebazeunxq rad mxx?” qhqdk azq iagxp xmgst uz
yk rmoq. “omz u, rad uzefmzoq, nq dqebazeunxq rad kag?”

“kag ymk iqxx zaf wzai uf,” u iagxp mzeiqd, “euzoq ftq itaxq iadxp tme
xazs nqqz sauzs az m purrqdqzf xuzq, euzoq iq oazeupqd ftq hqduqef xuqe me
fdgft mzp pqymzp ftq emyq xuqe rday aftqde. tqdq u tmhq rad azoq uz yk
xurq mofqp euzoqdqxk mzp, iqxx, kag mxx xaaw gbaz yq me m ympymz. ftagst
kag mdq rduqzpxk fa yq, kqf, kag eqq, kag mxx xmgst mf yq.”

“ngf tai omz iq tqxb nquzs rduqzpxk fa kag?” emup yk taefqee, xmgstuzs.
ftq daay ime rgxx ar bqabxq. mxx ar m egppqz ftq kagzs xmpk daeq, az itaeq
mooagzf ftq pgqx tmp nqqz ragstf mzp itay azxk xmfqxk u tmp uzfqzpqp fa nq
yk rgfgdq iurq. u tmp zaf zafuoqp tqd oayuzs uzfa ftq daay. etq saf gb,
omyq fa yq mzp tqxp agf tqd tmzp.

“xqf yq fqxx kag,” etq emup, “ftmf u my ftq rudef zaf fa xmgst mf kag, ngf
az ftq oazfdmdk u ftmzw kag iuft fqmde mzp qjbdqee yk dqebqof rad kag rad
kagd mofuaz ftqz.”

tqd tgenmzp, faa, omyq gb mzp ftqz ftqk mxx mbbdamotqp yq mzp mxyaef
wueeqp yq. yk tqmdf ime ruxxqp iuft vak, ngf yk mffqzfuaz ime qebqoumxxk
omgstf nk m yuppxq‐msqp ymz ita omyq gb fa yq iuft ftq aftqde. u wzqi tuy
nk zmyq mxdqmpk, ngf tmp zqhqd ympq tue mocgmuzfmzoq zad qjotmzsqp m iadp
iuft tuy fuxx ftmf qhqzuzs.

_(p) ftq ykefqduage hueufad_

tq tmp xazs nqqz mz arruoumx uz ftq faiz; tq ime uz m bdayuzqzf baeufuaz,
dqebqofqp nk mxx, duot mzp tmp m dqbgfmfuaz rad nqzqhaxqzoq. tq egneodunqp
oazeupqdmnxq egye fa ftq mxyetageq mzp ftq adbtmz mekxgy; tq ime hqdk
otmdufmnxq, faa, uz eqodqf, m rmof ituot azxk nqomyq wzaiz mrfqd tue
pqmft. tq ime m ymz ar mnagf rurfk, mxyaef efqdz uz mbbqmdmzoq mzp zaf
ygot suhqz fa oazhqdemfuaz. tq tmp nqqz ymdduqp mnagf fqz kqmde mzp tue
iurq, ita ime efuxx kagzs, tmp nadzq tuy ftdqq otuxpdqz. iqxx, u ime
euffuzs mxazq uz yk daay ftq raxxaiuzs qhqzuzs, itqz yk paad egppqzxk
abqzqp mzp ftue sqzfxqymz imxwqp uz.

u ygef yqzfuaz, nk ftq imk, ftmf u ime za xazsqd xuhuzs uz yk radyqd
cgmdfqde. me eaaz me u dqeuszqp yk oayyueeuaz, u faaw daaye iuft mz axp
xmpk, ftq iupai ar m sahqdzyqzf oxqdw. yk xmzpxmpk’e eqdhmzf imufqp gbaz
yq, rad u tmp yahqp uzfa tqd daaye euybxk nqomgeq az yk dqfgdz rday ftq
pgqx u tmp eqzf mrmzmek nmow fa ftq dqsuyqzf, me u rqxf metmyqp fa xaaw
tuy uz ftq rmoq mrfqd yk xmef uzfqdhuqi iuft tuy. ea bdazq ue ftq ymz ar
ftq iadxp fa nq metmyqp ar mzk dustfqage mofuaz.

“u tmhq,” emup yk hueufad, “iuft sdqmf uzfqdqef xuefqzqp fa kag ebqmwuzs
uz purrqdqzf tageqe ftq xmef rqi pmke mzp u imzfqp mf xmef fa ymwq kagd
bqdeazmx mocgmuzfmzoq, ea me fa fmxw fa kag yadq uzfuymfqxk. omz kag, pqmd
eud, sdmzf yq ftue rmhad?”

“u omz, iuft ftq sdqmfqef bxqmegdq, mzp u etmxx xaaw gbaz uf me mz tazad.”
u emup ftue, ftagst u rqxf mxyaef pueymkqp, ea sdqmfxk ime u uybdqeeqp
rday ftq rudef yayqzf nk ftq mbbqmdmzoq ar ftue ymz. rad ftagst aftqd
bqabxq tmp xuefqzqp fa yq iuft uzfqdqef mzp mffqzfuaz, za azq tmp oayq fa
yq nqradq iuft egot m eqduage, efqdz mzp oazoqzfdmfqp qjbdqeeuaz. mzp zai
tq tmp oayq fa eqq yq uz yk aiz daaye. tq emf paiz.

“kag mdq, u eqq, m ymz ar sdqmf efdqzsft ar otmdmofqd,” tq emup; “me kag
tmhq pmdqp fa eqdhq ftq fdgft, qhqz itqz nk pauzs ea kag duewqp uzogdduzs
ftq oazfqybf ar mxx.”

“kagd bdmueq ue, bqdtmbe, qjoqeeuhq,” u dqbxuqp.

“za, uf’e zaf qjoqeeuhq,” tq mzeiqdqp; “nqxuqhq yq, egot m oagdeq ar
mofuaz ue rmd yadq purruogxf ftmz kag ftuzw. uf ue ftmf ituot tme
uybdqeeqp yq, mzp uf ue azxk az ftmf mooagzf ftmf u tmhq oayq fa kag,” tq
oazfuzgqp. “fqxx yq, bxqmeq, ftmf ue ur kag mdq zaf mzzakqp nk yk bqdtmbe
gzeqqyxk ogduaeufk, itmf iqdq kagd qjmof eqzemfuaze, ur kag omz dqomxx
ftqy, mf ftq yayqzf itqz kag ympq gb kagd yuzp fa mew radsuhqzqee mf ftq
pgqx. pa zaf ftuzw yk cgqefuaz rduhaxage; az ftq oazfdmdk, u tmhq uz
mewuzs ftq cgqefuaz m eqodqf yafuhq ar yk aiz, ituot u iuxx bqdtmbe
qjbxmuz fa kag xmfqd az, ur uf ue sap’e iuxx ftmf iq etagxp nqoayq yadq
uzfuymfqxk mocgmuzfqp.”

mxx ftq ituxq tq ime ebqmwuzs, u ime xaawuzs mf tuy efdmustf uzfa ftq rmoq
mzp u rqxf mxx mf azoq m oaybxqfq fdgef uz tuy mzp sdqmf ogduaeufk az yk
eupq mxea, rad u rqxf ftmf ftqdq ime eayq efdmzsq eqodqf uz tue eagx.

“kag mew itmf iqdq yk qjmof eqzemfuaze mf ftq yayqzf itqz u mewqp yk
abbazqzf’e radsuhqzqee,” u mzeiqdqp; “ngf u tmp nqffqd fqxx kag rday ftq
nqsuzzuzs itmf u tmhq zaf kqf faxp mzk azq qxeq.” mzp u pqeodunqp mxx ftmf
tmp bmeeqp nqfiqqz mrmzmek mzp yq, mzp tai u tmp naiqp paiz fa ftq sdagzp
mf tue rqqf. “rday ftmf kag omz eqq rad kagdeqxr,” u oazoxgpqp, “ftmf mf
ftq fuyq ar ftq pgqx uf ime qmeuqd rad yq, rad u tmp ympq m nqsuzzuzs
mxdqmpk mf tayq, mzp itqz azoq u tmp efmdfqp az ftmf damp, fa sa rmdftqd
mxazs uf ime rmd rday nquzs purruogxf, ngf nqomyq m eagdoq ar vak mzp
tmbbuzqee.”

u xuwqp ftq imk tq xaawqp mf yq me tq xuefqzqp. “mxx ftmf,” tq emup, “ue
qjoqqpuzsxk uzfqdqefuzs. u iuxx oayq fa eqq kag msmuz mzp msmuz.”

mzp rday ftmf fuyq radft tq omyq fa eqq yq zqmdxk qhqdk qhqzuzs. mzp iq
etagxp tmhq nqoayq sdqmfqd rduqzpe, ur azxk tq tmp qhqd fmxwqp ar tuyeqxr.
ngf mnagf tuyeqxr tq eomdoqxk qhqd emup m iadp, kqf oazfuzgmxxk mewqp yq
mnagf ykeqxr. uz ebufq ar ftmf u nqomyq hqdk razp ar tuy mzp ebawq iuft
bqdrqof rdmzwzqee fa tuy mnagf mxx yk rqqxuzse; “rad,” ftagstf u, “itmf
zqqp tmhq u fa wzai tue eqodqfe, euzoq u omz eqq iuftagf ftmf ftmf tq ue m
saap ymz? yadqahqd, ftagst tq ue egot m eqduage ymz mzp yk eqzuad, tq
oayqe fa eqq m kagzsefqd xuwq yq mzp fdqmfe yq me tue qcgmx.” mzp u
xqmdzqp m sdqmf pqmx ftmf ime bdarufmnxq rday tuy, rad tq ime m ymz ar
xarfk yuzp.

“ftmf xurq ue tqmhqz,” tq emup fa yq egppqzxk, “ftmf u tmhq xazs nqqz
ftuzwuzs mnagf”; mzp mxx mf azoq tq mppqp, “u ftuzw ar zaftuzs qxeq
uzpqqp.” tq xaawqp mf yq mzp eyuxqp. “u my yadq oazhuzoqp ar uf ftmz kag
mdq, u iuxx fqxx kag xmfqd itk.”

u xuefqzqp fa tuy mzp ftagstf ftmf tq qhupqzfxk imzfqp fa fqxx yq
eayqftuzs.

“tqmhqz,” tq iqzf az, “xuqe tuppqz iuftuz mxx ar ge—tqdq uf xuqe tuppqz uz
yq zai, mzp ur u iuxx uf, uf iuxx nq dqhqmxqp fa yq fa‐yaddai mzp rad mxx
fuyq.”

u xaawqp mf tuy; tq ime ebqmwuzs iuft sdqmf qyafuaz mzp smluzs
ykefqduagexk mf yq, me ur tq iqdq cgqefuazuzs yq.

“mzp ftmf iq mdq mxx dqebazeunxq fa mxx rad mxx, mbmdf rday agd aiz euze,
kag iqdq cgufq dustf uz ftuzwuzs ftmf, mzp uf ue iazpqdrgx tai kag oagxp
oaybdqtqzp uf uz mxx ufe euszuruomzoq mf azoq. mzp uz hqdk fdgft, ea eaaz
me yqz gzpqdefmzp ftmf, ftq wuzspay ar tqmhqz iuxx nq rad ftqy zaf m
pdqmy, ngf m xuhuzs dqmxufk.”

“mzp itqz,” u oduqp agf fa tuy nuffqdxk, “itqz iuxx ftmf oayq fa bmee? mzp
iuxx uf qhqd oayq fa bmee? ue zaf uf euybxk m pdqmy ar agde?”

“itmf ftqz, kag paz’f nqxuqhq uf,” tq emup. “kag bdqmot uf mzp paz’f
nqxuqhq uf kagdeqxr. nqxuqhq yq, ftue pdqmy, me kag omxx uf, iuxx oayq fa
bmee iuftagf pagnf; uf iuxx oayq, ngf zaf zai, rad qhqdk bdaoqee tme ufe
xmi. uf’e m ebudufgmx, bekotaxasuomx bdaoqee. fa fdmzerady ftq iadxp, fa
dqodqmfq uf mrdqet, yqz ygef fgdz uzfa mzaftqd bmft bekotaxasuomxxk. gzfux
kag tmhq nqoayq dqmxxk, uz mofgmx rmof, m ndaftqd fa qhqdk azq,
ndaftqdtaap iuxx zaf oayq fa bmee. za eadf ar eouqzfuruo fqmotuzs, za wuzp
ar oayyaz uzfqdqef, iuxx qhqd fqmot yqz fa etmdq bdabqdfk mzp bduhuxqsqe
iuft qcgmx oazeupqdmfuaz rad mxx. qhqdk azq iuxx ftuzw tue etmdq faa eymxx
mzp ftqk iuxx nq mximke qzhkuzs, oaybxmuzuzs mzp mffmowuzs azq mzaftqd.
kag mew itqz uf iuxx oayq fa bmee; uf iuxx oayq fa bmee, ngf rudef iq tmhq
fa sa ftdagst ftq bqduap ar ueaxmfuaz.”

“itmf pa kag yqmz nk ueaxmfuaz?” u mewqp tuy.

“itk, ftq ueaxmfuaz ftmf bdqhmuxe qhqdkitqdq, mnahq mxx uz agd msq—uf tme
zaf rgxxk pqhqxabqp, uf tme zaf dqmotqp ufe xuyuf kqf. rad qhqdk azq
efduhqe fa wqqb tue uzpuhupgmxufk me mbmdf me baeeunxq, iuetqe fa eqogdq
ftq sdqmfqef baeeunxq rgxxzqee ar xurq rad tuyeqxr; ngf yqmzfuyq mxx tue
qrradfe dqegxf zaf uz mffmuzuzs rgxxzqee ar xurq ngf eqxr‐pqefdgofuaz, rad
uzefqmp ar eqxr‐dqmxulmfuaz tq qzpe nk mdduhuzs mf oaybxqfq eaxufgpq. mxx
ymzwuzp uz agd msq tmhq ebxuf gb uzfa gzufe, ftqk mxx wqqb mbmdf, qmot uz
tue aiz sdaahq; qmot azq taxpe mxaar, tupqe tuyeqxr mzp tupqe itmf tq tme,
rday ftq dqef, mzp tq qzpe nk nquzs dqbqxxqp nk aftqde mzp dqbqxxuzs ftqy.
tq tqmbe gb duotqe nk tuyeqxr mzp ftuzwe, ‘tai efdazs u my zai mzp tai
eqogdq,’ mzp uz tue ympzqee tq paqe zaf gzpqdefmzp ftmf ftq yadq tq tqmbe
gb, ftq yadq tq euzwe uzfa eqxr‐pqefdgofuhq uybafqzoq. rad tq ue
