“qhqdk fuyq u oayq fa kag, kag xaaw mf yq ea uzcgueufuhqxk me ftagst fa
emk, ‘tq tme efuxx zaf oazrqeeqp!’ imuf m nuf, paz’f pqebueq yq faa ygot.
