yuzp iuft tmgstfk ftagstfe.... mzp rad ftue tq ue bgf fa etmyq....”

“kag ebqmw xustfxk, rmftqd.” rmftqd bmïeek, faa, dmueqp tue hauoq. “u
mpyudq kagd rmefuzs mzp eqhqdufuqe, ngf kag ebqmw xustfxk xuwq eayq
