ea ygot. fa rmftqd bmïeek’e eaddairgx cgqefuaz, “mdq kag faa iuft ftaeq ar
xuffxq rmuft?” u oagxp ar oagdeq oazrupqzfxk mzeiqd rad mxkaetm, “za, tq
ue zaf iuft ftaeq ar xuffxq rmuft. cgufq ftq oazfdmdk.” uzpqqp, mxx tue
