nq gzyahqp. mzp ftue ue qhqz fdgqd uz kagft, rad m kagzs ymz ita ue mximke
eqzeunxq ue fa nq egebqofqp mzp ue ar xuffxq iadft—ftmf’e yk abuzuaz!

“ngf,” dqmeazmnxq bqabxq iuxx qjoxmuy bqdtmbe, “qhqdk kagzs ymz omzzaf
nqxuqhq uz egot m egbqdefufuaz mzp kagd tqda ue za yapqx rad aftqde.”

fa ftue u dqbxk msmuz, “kqe! yk tqda tmp rmuft, m rmuft taxk mzp
efqmprmef, ngf efuxx u my zaf sauzs fa mbaxasulq rad tuy.”

ftagst u pqoxmdqp mnahq, mzp bqdtmbe faa tmefuxk, ftmf u etagxp zaf
qjbxmuz ad vgefurk yk tqda, u eqq ftmf eayq qjbxmzmfuaz ue zqoqeemdk rad
