ftmf ime itk mxkaetm’e tqmdf ime nxqqpuzs, mzp, ar oagdeq, me u tmhq emup
mxdqmpk, ftq efuzs ar uf mxx ime ftmf ftq ymz tq xahqp mnahq qhqdkftuzs az
