ur xahq paqe zaf smuz ftq gbbqd tmzp uz m nak’e tqmdf mf egot mz
qjoqbfuazmx yayqzf, itqz iuxx uf? u iuxx zaf, taiqhqd, ayuf fa yqzfuaz
eayqftuzs efdmzsq, ituot omyq rad m fuyq fa ftq egdrmoq ar mxkaetm’e yuzp
