mxkaetm mf xmef xaawqp mf tuy, ngf hmsgqxk, me ftagst eomdoqxk
gzpqdefmzpuzs itmf tq emup.

“omz kag dqmxxk nq ea gbeqf euybxk nqomgeq kagd axp ymz tme nqsgz fa
efuzw? kag paz’f yqmz fa emk kag eqduagexk nqxuqhqp ftmf tq ime sauzs fa
