“u nqxuqhqp, u nqxuqhq, u imzf fa nqxuqhq, mzp u iuxx nqxuqhq, itmf yadq
pa kag imzf?” oduqp mxkaetm uddufmnxk.

“zaftuzs mf mxx, yk nak. pmyz uf mxx! itk, za eotaaxnak ar ftudfqqz
