euefqd mzp u etmxx zqhqd radsqf ftmf. azxk xqf yq fqxx kag, dmwufuz,
ftagst u my nmp, u pup suhq mimk mz azuaz.”

“mz azuaz? tmzs uf mxx, kag dqmxxk mdq odmlk.”

dmwufuz iazpqdqp mf ftqud qzftgeumey. tq ime mssduqhqp mzp mzzakqp, ftagst
