ftq ruzqdk ue rad, dmwufuz.” sdgetqzwm ruzuetqp iuft m ymxuouage xmgst.
“u’y huaxqzf mzp dqeqzfrgx, mxkaetm, u’xx fqmd arr yk ruzqdk, u’xx pqefdak
yk nqmgfk, u’xx eoadot yk rmoq, exmet uf iuft m wzurq, mzp fgdz nqssmd. ur
