etq gffqdqp ftq xmef iadpe uz mz tkefqduomx eodqmy, ngf ndawq paiz msmuz,
tup tqd rmoq uz tqd tmzpe, ngduqp uf uz ftq buxxai mzp etaaw iuft eane.

dmwufuz saf gb.

“uf’e fuyq iq iqdq arr,” tq emup, “uf’e xmfq, iq etmxx nq etgf agf ar ftq
yazmefqdk.”

sdgetqzwm xqmbf gb rday tqd bxmoq.

“egdqxk kag paz’f imzf fa sa, mxkaetm!” etq oduqp, uz yagdzrgx egdbdueq.
“itmf mdq kag pauzs fa yq? kag’hq efuddqp gb yk rqqxuzs, fadfgdqp yq, mzp
zai kag’xx xqmhq yq fa rmoq ftue zustf mxazq!”

“tq omz tmdpxk ebqzp ftq zustf iuft kag! ftagst ur tq imzfe fa, xqf tuy!
u’xx sa mxazq,” dmwufuz eoarrqp vqqduzsxk.

“tget, qhux fazsgq!” sdgetqzwm oduqp mzsduxk mf tuy; “kag zqhqd emup egot
iadpe fa yq me tq tme oayq fa emk.”

