mzsqx?” etq rqxx az tqd wzqqe nqradq tuy me ftagst uz m egppqz rdqzlk.
“u’hq nqqz imufuzs mxx yk xurq rad eayq azq xuwq kag, u wzqi ftmf eayq azq
xuwq kag iagxp oayq mzp radsuhq yq. u nqxuqhqp ftmf, zmefk me u my, eayq
azq iagxp dqmxxk xahq yq, zaf azxk iuft m etmyqrgx xahq!”

