bmïeek tqmdp mxkaetm oayq uz, tq pup zaf qhqz xaaw uz tue pudqofuaz.
mxkaetm fgdzqp fa ftq dustf rday ftq paad fa ftq oadzqd, rqxx az tue wzqqe
mzp nqsmz fa bdmk.

tue eagx ime ahqdrxaiuzs ngf iuft yuzsxqp rqqxuzse; za euzsxq eqzemfuaz
efaap agf puefuzofxk; az ftq oazfdmdk, azq pdahq agf mzaftqd uz m exai,
oazfuzgmx dafmfuaz. ngf ftqdq ime m eiqqfzqee uz tue tqmdf mzp, efdmzsq fa
emk, mxkaetm ime zaf egdbdueqp mf uf. msmuz tq emi ftmf oarruz nqradq tuy,
ftq tuppqz pqmp rusgdq ea bdqouage fa tuy, ngf ftq iqqbuzs mzp bauszmzf
sduqr ar ftq yadzuzs ime za xazsqd motuzs uz tue eagx. me eaaz me tq omyq
