ime sxaiuzs uz tue yuzp mzp uz tue tqmdf. ftq azq iuzpai ar ftq oqxx ime
abqz, ftq mud ime rdqet mzp oaax. “ea ftq eyqxx ygef tmhq nqoayq efdazsqd,
