rqi tagde nqradq, za xazsqd ympq tuy rqqx yueqdmnxq ad uzpuszmzf. tq nqsmz
cguqfxk bdmkuzs, ngf tq eaaz rqxf ftmf tq ime bdmkuzs mxyaef yqotmzuomxxk.
rdmsyqzfe ar ftagstf rxamfqp ftdagst tue eagx, rxmetqp xuwq efmde mzp iqzf
agf msmuz mf azoq, fa nq egooqqpqp nk aftqde. ngf kqf ftqdq ime dquszuzs
uz tue eagx m eqzeq ar ftq itaxqzqee ar ftuzse—eayqftuzs efqmprmef mzp
oayradfuzs—mzp tq ime mimdq ar uf tuyeqxr. eayqfuyqe tq nqsmz bdmkuzs
mdpqzfxk, tq xazsqp fa bagd agf tue ftmzwrgxzqee mzp xahq....

ngf itqz tq tmp nqsgz fa bdmk, tq bmeeqp egppqzxk fa eayqftuzs qxeq, mzp
emzw uzfa ftagstf, radsqffuzs naft ftq bdmkqd mzp itmf tmp uzfqddgbfqp uf.
