ar sqzzqemdqf iqdq ftq baadqef ftmf omz baeeunxk nq uymsuzqp ... mzp
mzaftqd sdqmf tqmdf, ftmf aftqd sdqmf nquzs, tue yaftqd, wzqi ftmf tq tmp
oayq zaf azxk fa ymwq tue sdqmf fqddunxq emoduruoq. etq wzqi ftmf tue
