uf ime tue hauoq, ftq hauoq ar rmftqd laeeuym. mzp uf ygef nq tq, euzoq tq
omxxqp tuy!

ftq qxpqd dmueqp mxkaetm nk ftq tmzp mzp tq daeq rday tue wzqqe.

“iq mdq dqvauouzs,” ftq xuffxq, ftuz axp ymz iqzf az. “iq mdq pduzwuzs ftq
zqi iuzq, ftq iuzq ar zqi, sdqmf sxmpzqee; pa kag eqq tai ymzk sgqefe?
tqdq mdq ftq ndupq mzp ndupqsdaay, tqdq ue ftq iueq sahqdzad ar ftq rqmef,
