“u my mrdmup ... u pmdq zaf xaaw,” ituebqdqp mxkaetm.

“pa zaf rqmd tuy. tq ue fqddunxq uz tue sdqmfzqee, mirgx uz tue egnxuyufk,
ngf uzruzufqxk yqdourgx. tq tme ympq tuyeqxr xuwq gzfa ge rday xahq mzp
dqvauoqe iuft ge. tq ue otmzsuzs ftq imfqd uzfa iuzq ftmf ftq sxmpzqee ar
ftq sgqefe ymk zaf nq ogf etadf. tq ue qjbqofuzs zqi sgqefe, tq ue omxxuzs
