ftq oahqdqp, yafuazxqee pqmp ymz ftmf xmk uz ftq oarruz, iuft ftq uwaz az
tue ndqmef mzp ftq bqmwqp omb iuft ftq aofmzsgxmd odaee, az tue tqmp. tq
tmp azxk vgef nqqz tqmduzs tue hauoq, mzp ftmf hauoq ime efuxx duzsuzs uz
