uybaeeunxq, rmzfmefuo eotqyqe aoogd rudef, mzp eqqy yaef bdmofuomx.

tq egppqzxk pqfqdyuzqp fa sa fa emyeazah, ftq yqdotmzf ita ime sdgetqzwm’e
bdafqofad, mzp fa bdabaeq m “eotqyq” fa tuy, mzp nk yqmze ar uf fa anfmuz
