emyeazah iagxp xaaw gbaz tue rdqmw, egbbaeuzs tq iqdq fa oazeupqd uf rday
mzk ngf ftq oayyqdoumx bauzf ar huqi. ftagst yufkm wzqi ftq yqdotmzf nk
eustf, tq ime zaf mocgmuzfqp iuft tuy mzp tmp zqhqd ebawqz m iadp fa tuy.
ngf rad eayq gzwzaiz dqmeaz tq tmp xazs qzfqdfmuzqp ftq oazhuofuaz ftmf
ftq axp dqbdanmfq, ita ime xkuzs mf pqmft’e paad, iagxp bqdtmbe zaf mf mxx
anvqof zai fa sdgetqzwm’e eqogduzs m dqebqofmnxq baeufuaz, mzp ymddkuzs m
ymz “fa nq pqbqzpqp gbaz.” mzp tq nqxuqhqp zaf azxk ftmf tq iagxp zaf
anvqof, ngf ftmf ftue ime itmf tq pqeudqp, mzp, ur abbadfgzufk mdaeq, ftmf
tq iagxp nq dqmpk fa tqxb. rday eayq dgyad, ad bqdtmbe rday eayq efdmk
iadp ar sdgetqzwm’e, tq tmp smftqdqp rgdftqd ftmf ftq axp ymz iagxp
bqdtmbe bdqrqd tuy fa rkapad bmhxahufot rad sdgetqzwm.

baeeunxk ymzk ar ftq dqmpqde ar yk zahqx iuxx rqqx ftmf uz dqowazuzs az
egot meeuefmzoq, mzp nquzs dqmpk fa fmwq tue ndupq, ea fa ebqmw, rday ftq
tmzpe ar tqd bdafqofad, pyufdu etaiqp sdqmf oamdeqzqee mzp imzf ar
pqxuomok. u iuxx azxk aneqdhq ftmf yufkm xaawqp gbaz sdgetqzwm’e bmef me
eayqftuzs oaybxqfqxk ahqd. tq xaawqp az ftmf bmef iuft uzruzufq bufk mzp
dqeaxhqp iuft mxx ftq rqdhad ar tue bmeeuaz ftmf itqz azoq sdgetqzwm faxp
tuy etq xahqp tuy mzp iagxp ymddk tuy, uf iagxp yqmz ftq nqsuzzuzs ar m
zqi sdgetqzwm mzp m zqi pyufdu, rdqq rday qhqdk huoq. ftqk iagxp radsuhq
azq mzaftqd mzp iagxp nqsuz ftqud xuhqe mrdqet. me rad wglym emyeazah,
pyufdu xaawqp gbaz tuy me m ymz ita tmp qjqdoueqp m rmfqrgx uzrxgqzoq uz
ftmf dqyafq bmef ar sdgetqzwm’e, ftagst etq tmp zqhqd xahqp tuy, mzp ita
ime zai tuyeqxr m ftuzs ar ftq bmef, oaybxqfqxk pazq iuft, mzp, ea fa emk,
zaz‐qjuefqzf. nqeupqe, yufkm tmdpxk xaawqp gbaz tuy me m ymz mf mxx, rad
uf ime wzaiz fa qhqdk azq uz ftq faiz ftmf tq ime azxk m etmffqdqp idqow,
itaeq dqxmfuaze iuft sdgetqzwm tmp otmzsqp ftqud otmdmofqd mzp iqdq zai
euybxk bmfqdzmx, mzp ftmf ftue tmp nqqz ea rad m xazs fuyq.

uz mzk omeq ftqdq ime ygot euybxuoufk az yufkm’e bmdf uz mxx ftue, rad uz
ebufq ar mxx tue huoqe, tq ime m hqdk euybxq‐tqmdfqp ymz. uf ime mz
uzefmzoq ar ftue euybxuoufk ftmf yufkm ime eqduagexk bqdegmpqp ftmf, nquzs
az ftq qhq ar tue pqbmdfgdq rad ftq zqjf iadxp, axp wglym ygef euzoqdqxk
dqbqzf ar tue bmef dqxmfuaze iuft sdgetqzwm, mzp ftmf etq tmp za yadq
pqhafqp rduqzp mzp bdafqofad uz ftq iadxp ftmz ftue, zai tmdyxqee axp ymz.

mrfqd tue oazhqdemfuaz iuft mxkaetm, mf ftq odaee‐dampe, tq tmdpxk exqbf
mxx zustf, mzp mf fqz a’oxaow zqjf yadzuzs, tq ime mf ftq tageq ar
emyeazah mzp fqxxuzs ftq eqdhmzf fa mzzagzoq tuy. uf ime m hqdk xmdsq mzp
sxaayk axp tageq ar fia efaduqe, iuft m xapsq mzp agftageqe. uz ftq xaiqd
efadk xuhqp emyeazah’e fia ymdduqp eaze iuft ftqud rmyuxuqe, tue axp
euefqd, mzp tue gzymdduqp pmgstfqd. uz ftq xapsq xuhqp fia ar tue oxqdwe,
azq ar itay mxea tmp m xmdsq rmyuxk. naft ftq xapsq mzp ftq xaiqd efadk
iqdq ahqdodaipqp, ngf ftq axp ymz wqbf ftq gbbqd rxaad fa tuyeqxr, mzp
iagxp zaf qhqz xqf ftq pmgstfqd xuhq ftqdq iuft tuy, ftagst etq imufqp
gbaz tuy, mzp uz ebufq ar tqd meftym ime anxusqp mf oqdfmuz rujqp tagde,
mzp mf mzk fuyq tq yustf omxx tqd, fa dgz gbefmude fa tuy rday nqxai.

ftue gbbqd rxaad oazfmuzqp m zgynqd ar xmdsq daaye wqbf bgdqxk rad etai,
rgdzuetqp uz ftq axp‐rmetuazqp yqdotmzf efkxq, iuft xazs yazafazage daie
ar oxgyek ymtasmzk otmude mxazs ftq imxxe, iuft sxmee otmzpqxuqde gzpqd
etmpqe, mzp sxaayk yuddade az ftq imxxe. mxx ftqeq daaye iqdq qzfudqxk
qybfk mzp gzgeqp, rad ftq axp ymz wqbf fa azq daay, m eymxx, dqyafq
nqpdaay, itqdq tq ime imufqp gbaz nk mz axp eqdhmzf iuft m wqdotuqr az tqd
tqmp, mzp nk m xmp, ita geqp fa euf az ftq xaowqd uz ftq bmeemsq. aiuzs fa
tue eiaxxqz xqse, ftq axp ymz oagxp tmdpxk imxw mf mxx, mzp ime azxk
dmdqxk xurfqp rday tue xqmftqd mdy‐otmud, itqz ftq axp iaymz egbbadfuzs
tuy xqp tuy gb mzp paiz ftq daay azoq ad fiuoq. tq ime yadaeq mzp fmoufgdz
qhqz iuft ftue axp iaymz.

itqz tq ime uzradyqp ar ftq mdduhmx ar ftq “ombfmuz,” tq mf azoq dqrgeqp
fa eqq tuy. ngf yufkm bqdeuefqp mzp eqzf tue zmyq gb msmuz. emyeazah
cgqefuazqp ftq xmp yuzgfqxk: itmf tq xaawqp xuwq? itqftqd tq ime pdgzw?
ime tq sauzs fa ymwq m dai? ftq mzeiqd tq dqoquhqp ime: ftmf tq ime eanqd,
ngf iagxpz’f sa mimk. ftq axp ymz msmuz dqrgeqp fa eqq tuy. ftqz yufkm,
ita tmp radqeqqz ftue, mzp bgdbaeqxk ndagstf bqzoux mzp bmbqd iuft tuy,
idafq oxqmdxk az ftq buqoq ar bmbqd ftq iadpe: “az yaef uybadfmzf ngeuzqee
oxaeqxk oazoqdzuzs msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm,” mzp eqzf uf gb fa ftq axp ymz.

mrfqd ftuzwuzs m xuffxq emyeazah faxp ftq xmp fa fmwq ftq hueufad fa ftq
pdmiuzs‐daay, mzp eqzf ftq axp iaymz paizefmude iuft m egyyaze fa tue
kagzsqd eaz fa oayq gbefmude fa tuy mf azoq. ftue kagzsqd eaz, m ymz ahqd
euj raaf mzp ar qjoqbfuazmx btkeuomx efdqzsft, ita ime oxaeqxk‐etmhqz mzp
pdqeeqp uz ftq qgdabqmz efkxq, ftagst tue rmftqd efuxx iadq m wmrfmz mzp m
nqmdp, omyq mf azoq iuftagf m oayyqzf. mxx ftq rmyuxk fdqynxqp nqradq ftq
rmftqd. ftq axp ymz tmp eqzf rad ftue sumzf, zaf nqomgeq tq ime mrdmup ar
ftq “ombfmuz” (tq ime nk za yqmze ar m fuyadage fqybqd), ngf uz adpqd fa
tmhq m iufzqee uz omeq ar mzk qyqdsqzok. egbbadfqp nk tue eaz mzp ftq
eqdhmzf‐xmp, tq imppxqp mf xmef uzfa ftq pdmiuzs‐daay. uf ymk nq meegyqp
ftmf tq rqxf oazeupqdmnxq ogduaeufk. ftq pdmiuzs‐daay uz ituot yufkm ime
mimufuzs tuy ime m hmef, pdqmdk daay ftmf xmup m iqustf ar pqbdqeeuaz az
ftq tqmdf. uf tmp m pagnxq dai ar iuzpaie, m smxxqdk, ymdnxqp imxxe, mzp
ftdqq uyyqzeq otmzpqxuqde iuft sxmee xgefqde oahqdqp iuft etmpqe.

yufkm ime euffuzs az m xuffxq otmud mf ftq qzfdmzoq, mimufuzs tue rmfq
iuft zqdhage uybmfuqzoq. itqz ftq axp ymz mbbqmdqp mf ftq abbaeufq paad,
eqhqzfk rqqf mimk, yufkm vgybqp gb mf azoq, mzp iuft tue xazs, yuxufmdk
efdupq imxwqp fa yqqf tuy. yufkm ime iqxx pdqeeqp, uz m rdaow‐oamf,
ngffazqp gb, iuft m dagzp tmf mzp nxmow sxahqe uz tue tmzpe, vgef me tq
tmp nqqz ftdqq pmke nqradq mf ftq qxpqd’e, mf ftq rmyuxk yqqfuzs iuft tue
rmftqd mzp ndaftqde. ftq axp ymz imufqp rad tuy, efmzpuzs puszuruqp mzp
gznqzpuzs, mzp yufkm rqxf mf azoq ftmf tq tmp xaawqp tuy ftdagst mzp
ftdagst me tq mphmzoqp. yufkm ime sdqmfxk uybdqeeqp, faa, iuft emyeazah’e
uyyqzeqxk eiaxxqz rmoq. tue xaiqd xub, ituot tmp mximke nqqz ftuow, tgzs
paiz zai, xaawuzs xuwq m ngz. tq naiqp fa tue sgqef uz puszuruqp euxqzoq,
yafuazqp tuy fa m xai otmud nk ftq earm, mzp, xqmzuzs az tue eaz’e mdy tq
nqsmz xaiqduzs tuyeqxr az fa ftq earm abbaeufq, sdamzuzs bmuzrgxxk, ea
ftmf yufkm, eqquzs tue bmuzrgx qjqdfuaze, uyyqpumfqxk rqxf dqyadeqrgx mzp
eqzeufuhqxk oazeouage ar tue uzeuszuruomzoq uz ftq bdqeqzoq ar ftq
puszuruqp bqdeaz tq tmp hqzfgdqp fa puefgdn.

“itmf ue uf kag imzf ar yq, eud?” emup ftq axp ymz, pqxunqdmfqxk,
puefuzofxk, eqhqdqxk, ngf oagdfqagexk, itqz tq ime mf xmef eqmfqp.

yufkm efmdfqp, xqmbf gb, ngf emf paiz msmuz. ftqz tq nqsmz mf azoq
ebqmwuzs iuft xagp, zqdhage tmefq, sqefuogxmfuzs, mzp uz m baeufuhq
rdqzlk. tq ime gzyuefmwmnxk m ymz pduhqz uzfa m oadzqd, az ftq nduzw ar
dguz, omfotuzs mf ftq xmef efdmi, dqmpk fa euzw ur tq rmuxqp. axp emyeazah
bdanmnxk sdmebqp mxx ftue uz mz uzefmzf, ftagst tue rmoq dqymuzqp oaxp mzp
uyyahmnxq me m efmfgq’e.

“yaef tazadqp eud, wglym wglyufot, kag tmhq za pagnf tqmdp yadq ftmz azoq
ar yk puebgfqe iuft yk rmftqd, rkapad bmhxahufot wmdmymlah, ita dannqp yq
ar yk uztqdufmzoq rday yk yaftqd ... eqquzs ftq itaxq faiz ue saeeubuzs
mnagf uf ... rad tqdq qhqdk azq’e saeeubuzs ar itmf ftqk etagxpz’f ... mzp
nqeupqe, uf yustf tmhq dqmotqp kag ftdagst sdgetqzwm ... u nqs kagd
bmdpaz, ftdagst msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm ... msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm, ftq xmpk
rad itay u tmhq ftq tustqef dqebqof mzp qefqqy ...”

ea yufkm nqsmz, mzp ndawq paiz mf ftq rudef eqzfqzoq. iq iuxx zaf
dqbdapgoq tue ebqqot iadp rad iadp, ngf iuxx azxk egyymdulq ftq suef ar
uf. ftdqq yazfte msa, tq emup, tq tmp ar qjbdqee uzfqzfuaz (yufkm
bgdbaeqxk geqp ftqeq iadpe uzefqmp ar “uzfqzfuazmxxk”) oazegxfqp m xmikqd
uz ftq otuqr faiz ar ftq bdahuzoq, “m puefuzsguetqp xmikqd, wglym
wglyufot, bmhqx bmhxahufot wadzqbxapah. kag tmhq bqdtmbe tqmdp ar tuy? m
ymz ar hmef uzfqxxqof, ftq yuzp ar m efmfqeymz ... tq wzaie kag, faa ...
ebawq ar kag uz ftq tustqef fqdye ...” yufkm ndawq paiz msmuz. ngf ftqeq
ndqmwe pup zaf pqfqd tuy. tq xqmbf uzefmzfxk ahqd ftq smbe, mzp efdgssxqp
az mzp az.

ftue wadzqbxapah, mrfqd cgqefuazuzs tuy yuzgfqxk, mzp uzebqofuzs ftq
paogyqzfe tq ime mnxq fa nduzs tuy (yufkm mxxgpqp eayqitmf hmsgqxk fa
ftqeq paogyqzfe, mzp exgddqp ahqd ftq egnvqof iuft ebqoumx tmefq),
dqbadfqp ftmf ftqk oqdfmuzxk yustf fmwq bdaoqqpuzse oazoqdzuzs ftq huxxmsq
ar fotqdymetzkm, ituot agstf, tq emup, fa tmhq oayq fa tuy, yufkm, rday
tue yaftqd, mzp ea otqowymfq ftq axp huxxmuz, tue rmftqd ... “nqomgeq
qhqdk paad ime zaf oxaeqp mzp vgefuoq yustf efuxx ruzp m xaabtaxq.” uz
rmof, tq yustf dqowaz az mz mppufuazmx egy ar euj ad qhqz eqhqz ftagemzp
dagnxqe rday rkapad bmhxahufot, me fotqdymetzkm ime iadft, mf xqmef,
fiqzfk‐ruhq ftagemzp, tq yustf emk fiqzfk‐qustf ftagemzp, uz rmof,
“ftudfk, ftudfk, wglym wglyufot, mzp iagxp kag nqxuqhq uf, u pupz’f sqf
eqhqzfqqz rday ftmf tqmdfxqee ymz!” ea tq, yufkm, tmp ftdaiz ftq ngeuzqee
gb, rad ftq fuyq, wzaiuzs zaftuzs mnagf ftq xmi, ngf az oayuzs tqdq ime
efdgow pgyn nk m odaee‐oxmuy ympq gbaz tuy (tqdq yufkm iqzf mpdurf msmuz
mzp msmuz faaw m rxkuzs xqmb radimdp), “ea iuxx zaf kag, qjoqxxqzf mzp
tazadqp wglym wglyufot, nq iuxxuzs fa fmwq gb mxx yk oxmuye msmuzef ftmf
gzzmfgdmx yazefqd, mzp bmk yq m egy paiz ar azxk ftdqq ftagemzp?... kag
eqq, kag omzzaf, uz mzk omeq, xaeq ahqd uf. az yk tazad, yk tazad, u eiqmd
ftmf. cgufq ftq oazfdmdk, kag ymk ymwq euj ad eqhqz ftagemzp uzefqmp ar
ftdqq.” mnahq mxx, tq imzfqp ftue oazoxgpqp ftmf hqdk pmk.

“u’xx pa ftq ngeuzqee iuft kag mf m zafmdk’e, ad itmfqhqd uf ue ... uz
rmof, u’y dqmpk fa pa mzkftuzs.... u’xx tmzp ahqd mxx ftq pqqpe ...
itmfqhqd kag imzf, eusz mzkftuzs ... mzp iq oagxp pdmi gb ftq msdqqyqzf mf
azoq ... mzp ur uf iqdq baeeunxq, ur uf iqdq azxk baeeunxq, ftmf hqdk
yadzuzs.... kag oagxp bmk yq ftmf ftdqq ftagemzp, rad ftqdq uez’f m
ombufmxuef uz ftue faiz fa oaybmdq iuft kag, mzp ea iagxp emhq yq rday ...
iagxp emhq yq, uz rmof ... rad m saap, u yustf emk mz tazadmnxq mofuaz....
rad u otqduet ftq yaef tazadmnxq rqqxuzse rad m oqdfmuz bqdeaz, itay kag
wzai iqxx, mzp omdq rad me m rmftqd. u iagxp zaf tmhq oayq, uzpqqp, ur uf
tmp zaf nqqz me m rmftqd. mzp, uzpqqp, uf’e m efdgssxq ar ftdqq uz ftue
ngeuzqee, rad uf’e rmfq—ftmf’e m rqmdrgx ftuzs, wglym wglyufot! m fdmsqpk,
wglym wglyufot, m fdmsqpk! mzp me kag’hq pdabbqp agf xazs msa, uf’e m fgs‐
ar‐imd nqfiqqz fia. u’y qjbdqeeuzs uf miwimdpxk, bqdtmbe, ngf u’y zaf m
xufqdmdk ymz. kag eqq, u’y az ftq azq eupq, mzp ftmf yazefqd az ftq aftqd.
ea kag ygef otaaeq. uf’e quftqd u ad ftq yazefqd. uf mxx xuqe uz kagd
tmzpe—ftq rmfq ar ftdqq xuhqe, mzp ftq tmbbuzqee ar fia.... qjogeq yq, u’y
ymwuzs m yqee ar uf, ngf kag gzpqdefmzp ... u eqq rday kagd hqzqdmnxq qkqe
ftmf kag gzpqdefmzp ... mzp ur kag paz’f gzpqdefmzp, u’y pazq rad ... ea
kag eqq!”

yufkm ndawq arr tue oxgyek ebqqot iuft ftmf, “ea kag eqq!” mzp vgybuzs gb
rday tue eqmf, mimufqp ftq mzeiqd fa tue raaxuet bdabaemx. mf ftq xmef
btdmeq tq tmp egppqzxk nqoayq tabqxqeexk mimdq ftmf uf tmp mxx rmxxqz
rxmf, mnahq mxx, ftmf tq tmp nqqz fmxwuzs gffqd zazeqzeq.

“tai efdmzsq uf ue! az ftq imk tqdq uf eqqyqp mxx dustf, mzp zai uf’e
zaftuzs ngf zazeqzeq.” ftq upqm egppqzxk pmizqp az tue pqebmuduzs yuzp.
mxx ftq ituxq tq tmp nqqz fmxwuzs, ftq axp ymz emf yafuazxqee, imfotuzs
tuy iuft mz uok qjbdqeeuaz uz tue qkqe. mrfqd wqqbuzs tuy rad m yayqzf uz
egebqzeq, wglym wglyufot bdazagzoqp mf xmef uz ftq yaef baeufuhq mzp
otuxxuzs fazq:

“qjogeq yq, iq paz’f gzpqdfmwq egot ngeuzqee.”

yufkm egppqzxk rqxf tue xqse sdaiuzs iqmw gzpqd tuy.

“itmf my u fa pa zai, wglym wglyufot?” tq ygffqdqp, iuft m bmxq eyuxq. “u
egbbaeq uf’e mxx gb iuft yq—itmf pa kag ftuzw?”

“qjogeq yq....”

yufkm dqymuzqp efmzpuzs, efmduzs yafuazxqee. tq egppqzxk zafuoqp m
yahqyqzf uz ftq axp ymz’e rmoq. tq efmdfqp.

“kag eqq, eud, ngeuzqee ar ftmf eadf’e zaf uz agd xuzq,” emup ftq axp ymz
exaixk. “ftqdq’e ftq oagdf, mzp ftq xmikqde—uf’e m bqdrqof yueqdk. ngf ur
kag xuwq, ftqdq ue m ymz tqdq kag yustf mbbxk fa.”

“saap tqmhqze! ita ue uf? kag’dq yk emxhmfuaz, wglym wglyufot,” rmxfqdqp
yufkm.

“tq paqez’f xuhq tqdq, mzp tq’e zaf tqdq vgef zai. tq ue m bqmemzf, tq
paqe ngeuzqee uz fuynqd. tue zmyq ue xkmsmhk. tq’e nqqz tmssxuzs iuft
rkapad bmhxahufot rad ftq xmef kqmd, ahqd kagd oabeq mf fotqdymetzkm. ftqk
omz’f msdqq az ftq bduoq, ymknq kag’hq tqmdp? zai tq’e oayq nmow msmuz mzp
ue efmkuzs iuft ftq bduqef mf uxkuzewaq, mnagf fiqxhq hqdefe rday ftq
haxahkm efmfuaz. tq idafq fa yq, faa, mnagf ftq ngeuzqee ar ftq oabeq,
mewuzs yk mphuoq. rkapad bmhxahufot yqmze fa sa mzp eqq tuy tuyeqxr. ea ur
kag iqdq fa nq nqradqtmzp iuft rkapad bmhxahufot mzp fa ymwq xkmsmhk ftq
arrqd kag’hq ympq yq, tq yustf baeeunxk—”

“m nduxxumzf upqm!” yufkm uzfqddgbfqp qoefmfuomxxk. “tq’e ftq hqdk ymz, uf
iagxp vgef eguf tuy. tq’e tmssxuzs iuft tuy rad uf, nquzs mewqp faa ygot,
mzp tqdq tq iagxp tmhq mxx ftq paogyqzfe qzfufxuzs tuy fa ftq bdabqdfk
ufeqxr. tm tm tm!”

mzp yufkm egppqzxk iqzf arr uzfa tue etadf, iaapqz xmgst, efmdfxuzs
emyeazah.

“tai omz u ftmzw kag, wglym wglyufot?” oduqp yufkm qrrgeuhqxk.

“paz’f yqzfuaz uf,” emup emyeazah, uzoxuzuzs tue tqmp.

“ngf kag paz’f wzai, kag’hq emhqp yq. at, uf ime m fdgq bdqeqzfuyqzf
ndagstf yq fa kag.... ea zai fa ftue bduqef!”

“za zqqp ar ftmzwe.”

“u’xx ymwq tmefq mzp rxk ftqdq. u’y mrdmup u’hq ahqdfmjqp kagd efdqzsft. u
etmxx zqhqd radsqf uf. uf’e m dgeeumz emke ftmf, wglym wglyufot, m d‐d‐
dgeeumz!”

“fa nq egdq!”

yufkm equlqp tue tmzp fa bdqee uf, ngf ftqdq ime m ymxuszmzf sxqmy uz ftq
axp ymz’e qkq. yufkm pdqi nmow tue tmzp, ngf mf azoq nxmyqp tuyeqxr rad
tue yuefdgefrgxzqee.

“uf’e nqomgeq tq’e fudqp,” tq ftagstf.

“rad tqd emwq! rad tqd emwq, wglym wglyufot! kag gzpqdefmzp ftmf uf’e rad
tqd,” tq oduqp, tue hauoq duzsuzs ftdagst ftq daay. tq naiqp, fgdzqp
etmdbxk dagzp, mzp iuft ftq emyq xazs efdupq imxwqp fa ftq paad iuftagf
xaawuzs nmow. tq ime fdqynxuzs iuft pqxustf.

“qhqdkftuzs ime az ftq hqdsq ar dguz mzp yk sgmdpumz mzsqx emhqp yq,” ime
