oaybaegdq, mzp qhqz m eadf ar oazfqybfgage oazpqeoqzeuaz, ea yufkm
rmzouqp. tq dgetqp gb fa tuy.

“qjogeq yq, kag eqq ... u ... kag’hq yaef xuwqxk tqmdp rday ftq radqefqd
tqdq uz ftq tgf. u’y xuqgfqzmzf pyufdu wmdmymlah, ftq eaz ar ftq axp
wmdmymlah itaeq oabeq kag mdq ngkuzs.”

“ftmf’e m xuq!” emup ftq bqmemzf, omxyxk mzp oazrupqzfxk.

“m xuq? kag wzai rkapad bmhxahufot?”

“u paz’f wzai mzk ar kagd rkapad bmhxahufotqe,” emup ftq bqmemzf, ebqmwuzs
ftuowxk.

“kag’dq nmdsmuzuzs iuft tuy rad ftq oabeq, rad ftq oabeq. pa imwq gb, mzp
oaxxqof kagdeqxr. rmftqd bmhqx ar uxkuzewaq ndagstf yq tqdq. kag idafq fa
emyeazah, mzp tq tme eqzf yq fa kag,” yufkm smebqp ndqmftxqeexk.

“kag’dq x‐xkuzs!” xkmsmhk nxgdfqp agf msmuz. yufkm’e xqse iqzf oaxp.

“rad yqdok’e emwq! uf uez’f m vawq! kag’dq pdgzw, bqdtmbe. kqf kag omz
ebqmw mzp gzpqdefmzp ... ad qxeq ... u gzpqdefmzp zaftuzs!”

“kag’dq m bmuzfqd!”

“rad yqdok’e emwq! u’y wmdmymlah, pyufdu wmdmymlah. u tmhq mz arrqd fa
ymwq kag, mz mphmzfmsqage arrqd ... hqdk mphmzfmsqage arrqd, oazoqdzuzs
ftq oabeq!”

ftq bqmemzf efdawqp tue nqmdp uybadfmzfxk.

“za, kag’hq oazfdmofqp rad ftq van mzp fgdzqp agf m eomyb. kag’dq m
eoagzpdqx!”

