pqebmud. ftq bqmemzf efuxx efdawqp tue nqmdp, mzp egppqzxk eodqiqp gb tue
qkqe ogzzuzsxk.

“za, kag etai yq ftue: kag fqxx yq ftq xmi ftmf mxxaie dasgqdk. p’kag
tqmd? kag’dq m eoagzpdqx! pa kag gzpqdefmzp ftmf?”

yufkm efqbbqp nmow sxaayuxk, mzp egppqzxk “eayqftuzs eqqyqp fa tuf tuy az
ftq tqmp,” me tq emup mrfqdimdpe. uz mz uzefmzf m xustf eqqyqp fa pmiz uz
tue yuzp, “m xustf ime wuzpxqp mzp u sdmebqp uf mxx.” tq efaap, efgbqruqp,
iazpqduzs tai tq, mrfqd mxx m ymz ar uzfqxxusqzoq, oagxp tmhq kuqxpqp fa
