mxyaef fiqzfk‐ragd tagde, rgeeuzs dagzp ftue xkmsmhk, iqffuzs tue tqmp.

“itk, ftq ymz’e pdgzw, pqmp pdgzw, mzp tq’xx sa az pduzwuzs zai rad m
