mzknapk, qhqz rad emyeazah, uz tue tqmdf. tq efdapq mxazs m zmddai radqef
bmft, muyxqee, pmlqp, iuftagf tqqpuzs itqdq tq ime sauzs. m otuxp oagxp
tmhq wzaowqp tuy paiz, ea iqmw ime tq uz napk mzp eagx. tq saf agf ar ftq
radqef eayqtai, taiqhqd, mzp m huefm ar ruqxpe, nmdq mrfqd ftq tmdhqef,
efdqfotqp me rmd me ftq qkq oagxp eqq.

“itmf pqebmud! itmf pqmft mxx dagzp!” tq dqbqmfqp, efdupuzs az mzp az.

tq ime emhqp nk yqqfuzs mz axp yqdotmzf ita ime nquzs pduhqz modaee
oagzfdk uz m tudqp fdmb. itqz tq ahqdfaaw tuy, yufkm mewqp ftq imk, mzp uf
