mf xmef ftqk mdduhqp, mzp yufkm mf azoq dmz fa sdgetqzwm.



otmbfqd uuu. saxp‐yuzqe


ftue ime ftq hueuf ar yufkm ar ituot sdgetqzwm tmp ebawqz fa dmwufuz iuft
egot taddad. etq ime vgef ftqz qjbqofuzs ftq “yqeemsq,” mzp ime ygot
dqxuqhqp ftmf yufkm tmp zaf nqqz fa eqq tqd ftmf pmk ad ftq pmk nqradq.
etq tabqp ftmf “bxqmeq sap tq iaz’f oayq fuxx u’y sazq mimk,” mzp tq
egppqzxk ngdef uz az tqd. ftq dqef iq wzai mxdqmpk. fa sqf tuy arr tqd
tmzpe etq egssqefqp mf azoq ftmf tq etagxp imxw iuft tqd fa emyeazah’e,
itqdq etq emup etq mneaxgfqxk ygef sa “fa eqffxq tue mooagzfe,” mzp itqz
yufkm mooaybmzuqp tqd mf azoq, etq emup saap‐nk fa tuy mf ftq smfq, ymwuzs
tuy bdayueq fa oayq mf fiqxhq a’oxaow fa fmwq tqd tayq msmuz. yufkm, faa,
ime pqxustfqp mf ftue mddmzsqyqzf. ur etq ime euffuzs mf emyeazah’e etq
oagxp zaf nq sauzs fa rkapad bmhxahufot’e, “ur azxk etq’e zaf xkuzs,” tq
mppqp mf azoq. ngf tq ftagstf etq ime zaf xkuzs rday itmf tq emi.

tq ime ftmf eadf ar vqmxage ymz ita, uz ftq mneqzoq ar ftq nqxahqp iaymz,
mf azoq uzhqzfe mxx eadfe ar mirgx rmzouqe ar itmf ymk nq tmbbqzuzs fa
tqd, mzp tai etq ymk nq nqfdmkuzs tuy, ngf, itqz etmwqz, tqmdfndawqz,
oazhuzoqp ar tqd rmuftxqeezqee, tq dgze nmow fa tqd; mf ftq rudef sxmzoq
mf tqd rmoq, tqd smk, xmgstuzs, mrrqofuazmfq rmoq, tq dqhuhqe mf azoq,
xmke meupq mxx egebuouaz mzp iuft vakrgx etmyq mngeqe tuyeqxr rad tue
vqmxagek.

mrfqd xqmhuzs sdgetqzwm mf ftq smfq tq dgetqp tayq. at, tq tmp ea ygot
efuxx fa pa ftmf pmk! ngf m xamp tmp nqqz xurfqp rday tue tqmdf, mzkimk.

“zai u ygef azxk ymwq tmefq mzp ruzp agf rday eyqdpkmwah itqftqd mzkftuzs
