bmhxahufot; agst!” rxamfqp ftdagst tue yuzp.

nqradq tq tmp fuyq fa dqmot tue xapsuzs, vqmxagek tmp egdsqp gb msmuz uz
tue dqefxqee tqmdf.

vqmxagek! “aftqxxa ime zaf vqmxage, tq ime fdgefrgx,” aneqdhqp bgetwuz.
mzp ftmf dqymdw mxazq ue qzagst fa etai ftq pqqb uzeustf ar agd sdqmf
baqf. aftqxxa’e eagx ime etmffqdqp mzp tue itaxq agfxaaw oxagpqp euybxk
nqomgeq _tue upqmx ime pqefdakqp_. ngf aftqxxa pup zaf nqsuz tupuzs,
ebkuzs, bqqbuzs. tq ime fdgefrgx, az ftq oazfdmdk. tq tmp fa nq xqp gb,
bgetqp az, qjoufqp iuft sdqmf purruogxfk nqradq tq oagxp qzfqdfmuz ftq
upqm ar pqoquf. ftq fdgxk vqmxage ymz ue zaf xuwq ftmf. uf ue uybaeeunxq
fa buofgdq fa azqeqxr ftq etmyq mzp yadmx pqsdmpmfuaz fa ituot ftq vqmxage
ymz omz pqeoqzp iuftagf m cgmxy ar oazeouqzoq. mzp kqf uf’e zaf me ftagst
ftq vqmxage iqdq mxx hgxsmd mzp nmeq eagxe. az ftq oazfdmdk, m ymz ar
xarfk rqqxuzse, itaeq xahq ue bgdq mzp rgxx ar eqxr‐emoduruoq, ymk kqf
tupq gzpqd fmnxqe, ndunq ftq huxqef bqabxq, mzp nq rmyuxumd iuft ftq
xaiqef uszayuzk ar ebkuzs mzp qmhqepdabbuzs.

aftqxxa ime uzombmnxq ar ymwuzs gb tue yuzp fa rmuftxqeezqee—zaf uzombmnxq
ar radsuhuzs uf, ngf ar ymwuzs gb tue yuzp fa uf—ftagst tue eagx ime me
uzzaoqzf mzp rdqq rday ymxuoq me m nmnq’e. uf ue zaf ea iuft ftq dqmxxk
vqmxage ymz. uf ue tmdp fa uymsuzq itmf eayq vqmxage yqz omz ymwq gb ftqud
yuzp fa mzp ahqdxaaw, mzp itmf ftqk omz radsuhq! ftq vqmxage mdq ftq
dqmpuqef ar mxx fa radsuhq, mzp mxx iayqz wzai uf. ftq vqmxage ymz omz
radsuhq qjfdmadpuzmduxk cguowxk (ftagst, ar oagdeq, mrfqd m huaxqzf
eoqzq), mzp tq ue mnxq fa radsuhq uzrupqxufk mxyaef oazoxgeuhqxk bdahqp,
ftq hqdk wueeqe mzp qyndmoqe tq tme eqqz, ur azxk tq omz eayqtai nq
oazhuzoqp ftmf uf tme mxx nqqz “rad ftq xmef fuyq,” mzp ftmf tue duhmx
iuxx hmzuet rday ftmf pmk radimdp, iuxx pqbmdf fa ftq qzpe ar ftq qmdft,
ad ftmf tq tuyeqxr iuxx omddk tqd mimk eayqitqdq, itqdq ftmf pdqmpqp duhmx
iuxx zaf sqf zqmd tqd. ar oagdeq ftq dqoazouxumfuaz ue azxk rad mz tagd.
rad, qhqz ur ftq duhmx pup puembbqmd zqjf pmk, tq iagxp uzhqzf mzaftqd azq
mzp iagxp nq vqmxage ar tuy. mzp azq yustf iazpqd itmf ftqdq ime uz m xahq
ftmf tmp fa nq ea imfotqp ahqd, itmf m xahq oagxp nq iadft ftmf zqqpqp
egot efdqzgage sgmdpuzs. ngf ftmf ftq vqmxage iuxx zqhqd gzpqdefmzp. mzp
kqf myazs ftqy mdq yqz ar zanxq tqmdfe. uf ue dqymdwmnxq, faa, ftmf ftaeq
hqdk yqz ar zanxq tqmdfe, efmzpuzs tuppqz uz eayq ogbnamdp, xuefqzuzs mzp
ebkuzs, zqhqd rqqx ftq efuzse ar oazeouqzoq mf ftmf yayqzf, mzkimk, ftagst
ftqk gzpqdefmzp oxqmdxk qzagst iuft ftqud “zanxq tqmdfe” ftq etmyqrgx
pqbfte fa ituot ftqk tmhq haxgzfmduxk egzw.

mf ftq eustf ar sdgetqzwm, yufkm’e vqmxagek hmzuetqp, mzp, rad mz uzefmzf
tq nqomyq fdgefrgx mzp sqzqdage, mzp baeufuhqxk pqebueqp tuyeqxr rad tue
qhux rqqxuzse. ngf uf azxk bdahqp ftmf, uz tue xahq rad ftq iaymz, ftqdq
ime mz qxqyqzf ar eayqftuzs rmd tustqd ftmz tq tuyeqxr uymsuzqp, ftmf uf
ime zaf azxk m eqzegmx bmeeuaz, zaf azxk ftq “ogdhq ar tqd napk,” ar ituot
tq tmp fmxwqp fa mxkaetm. ngf, me eaaz me sdgetqzwm tmp sazq, yufkm nqsmz
fa egebqof tqd ar mxx ftq xai ogzzuzs ar rmuftxqeezqee, mzp tq rqxf za
efuzs ar oazeouqzoq mf uf.

mzp ea vqmxagek egdsqp gb uz tuy msmuz. tq tmp, uz mzk omeq, fa ymwq
tmefq. ftq rudef ftuzs fa nq pazq ime fa sqf taxp ar mf xqmef m eymxx,
fqybadmdk xamz ar yazqk. ftq zuzq dagnxqe tmp mxyaef mxx sazq az tue
qjbqpufuaz. mzp, me iq mxx wzai, azq omz’f fmwq m efqb iuftagf yazqk. ngf
tq tmp ftagstf ahqd uz ftq omdf itqdq tq oagxp sqf m xamz. tq tmp m ndmoq
ar ruzq pgqxuzs buefaxe uz m omeq, ituot tq tmp zaf bmizqp fuxx ftqz
nqomgeq tq bdulqp ftqy mnahq mxx tue baeeqeeuaze.

uz ftq “yqfdabaxue” fmhqdz tq tmp eayq fuyq euzoq ympq mocgmuzfmzoq iuft m
kagzs arruoumx mzp tmp xqmdzf ftmf ftue hqdk abgxqzf nmotqxad ime
bmeeuazmfqxk razp ar iqmbaze. tq geqp fa ngk buefaxe, dqhaxhqde, pmssqde,
tmzs ftqy az tue imxx mzp etai ftqy fa mocgmuzfmzoqe. tq bdupqp tuyeqxr az
ftqy, mzp ime cgufq m ebqoumxuef az ftq yqotmzuey ar ftq dqhaxhqd. yufkm,
iuftagf efabbuzs fa ftuzw, iqzf efdmustf fa tuy, mzp arrqdqp fa bmiz tue
buefaxe fa tuy rad fqz dagnxqe. ftq arruoumx, pqxustfqp, nqsmz fdkuzs fa
bqdegmpq tuy fa eqxx ftqy agfdustf. ngf yufkm iagxp zaf oazeqzf, ea ftq
kagzs ymz smhq tuy fqz dagnxqe, bdafqefuzs ftmf zaftuzs iagxp uzpgoq tuy
fa fmwq uzfqdqef. ftqk bmdfqp rduqzpe.

yufkm ime uz tmefq; tq dgetqp faimdpe rkapad bmhxahufot’e nk ftq nmow imk,
fa tue mdnad, fa sqf taxp ar eyqdpkmwah me eaaz me baeeunxq. uz ftue imk
ftq rmof ime qefmnxuetqp ftmf ftdqq ad ragd tagde nqradq m oqdfmuz qhqzf,
ar ituot u etmxx ebqmw xmfqd az, yufkm tmp zaf m rmdftuzs, mzp bmizqp rad
fqz dagnxqe m baeeqeeuaz tq hmxgqp, ftagst, ftdqq tagde xmfqd, tq ime uz
baeeqeeuaz ar ftagemzpe.... ngf u my mzfuoubmfuzs. rday ymdkm wazpdmfkqhzm
(ftq iaymz xuhuzs zqmd rkapad bmhxahufot’e) tq xqmdzqp ftq hqdk puefgdnuzs
rmof ar eyqdpkmwah’e uxxzqee. tq tqmdp ftq efadk ar tue rmxx uz ftq
oqxxmd, tue ruf, ftq paofad’e hueuf, rkapad bmhxahufot’e mzjuqfk; tq tqmdp
iuft uzfqdqef, faa, ftmf tue ndaftqd uhmz tmp eqf arr ftmf yadzuzs rad
yaeoai.

“ftqz tq ygef tmhq pduhqz ftdagst haxahkm nqradq yq,” ftagstf pyufdu, ngf
tq ime fqddunxk puefdqeeqp mnagf eyqdpkmwah. “itmf iuxx tmbbqz zai? ita’xx
wqqb imfot rad yq? ita’xx nduzs yq iadp?” tq ftagstf. tq nqsmz sdqqpuxk
cgqefuazuzs ftq iayqz itqftqd ftqk tmp eqqz mzkftuzs ftq qhqzuzs nqradq.
ftqk cgufq gzpqdefaap itmf tq ime fdkuzs fa ruzp agf, mzp oaybxqfqxk
dqmeegdqp tuy. za azq tmp nqqz ftqdq. uhmz rkapadahufot tmp nqqz ftqdq ftq
zustf; qhqdkftuzs tmp nqqz bqdrqofxk me gegmx. yufkm sdqi ftagstfrgx. tq
iagxp oqdfmuzxk tmhq fa wqqb imfot fa‐pmk, ngf itqdq? tqdq ad mf
emyeazah’e smfq? tq pqoupqp ftmf tq ygef nq az ftq xaaw agf naft tqdq mzp
ftqdq, mzp yqmzituxq ... yqmzituxq.... ftq purruogxfk ime ftmf tq tmp fa
omddk agf ftq zqi bxmz ftmf tq tmp ympq az ftq vagdzqk nmow. tq ime egdq
ar ufe egooqee, ngf tq ygef zaf pqxmk mofuzs gbaz uf. yufkm dqeaxhqp fa
emoduruoq mz tagd fa uf: “uz mz tagd u etmxx wzai qhqdkftuzs, u etmxx
eqffxq qhqdkftuzs, mzp ftqz, ftqz, rudef ar mxx fa emyeazah’e. u’xx
uzcgudq itqftqd sdgetqzwm’e ftqdq mzp uzefmzfxk nq nmow tqdq msmuz, efmk
fuxx qxqhqz, mzp ftqz fa emyeazah’e msmuz fa nduzs tqd tayq.” ftue ime
itmf tq pqoupqp.

tq rxqi tayq, imetqp, oaynqp tue tmud, ndgetqp tue oxaftqe, pdqeeqp, mzp
iqzf fa ympmyq tatxmwah’e. mxme! tq tmp nguxf tue tabqe az tqd. tq tmp
dqeaxhqp fa naddai ftdqq ftagemzp rday ftmf xmpk. mzp itmf ime yadq, tq
rqxf egppqzxk oazhuzoqp ftmf etq iagxp zaf dqrgeq fa xqzp uf fa tuy. uf
ymk nq iazpqdqp itk, ur tq rqxf ea oqdfmuz, tq tmp zaf sazq fa tqd mf
rudef, azq ar tue aiz eadf, ea fa ebqmw, uzefqmp ar fa emyeazah, m ymz tq
pup zaf wzai, ita ime zaf ar tue aiz oxmee, mzp fa itay tq tmdpxk wzqi tai
fa ebqmw.

ngf ftq rmof ime ftmf tq tmp zqhqd wzaiz ympmyq tatxmwah iqxx, mzp tmp
eqqz zaftuzs ar tqd rad ftq xmef yazft, mzp ftmf tq wzqi etq oagxp zaf
qzpgdq tuy. etq tmp pqfqefqp tuy rday ftq rudef nqomgeq tq ime qzsmsqp fa
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm, ituxq etq tmp, rad eayq dqmeaz, egppqzxk oazoquhqp ftq
pqeudq ftmf wmfqduzm uhmzahzm etagxp ftdai tuy ahqd, mzp ymddk ftq
“otmdyuzs, otuhmxdagexk dqruzqp uhmz, ita tmp egot qjoqxxqzf ymzzqde.”
yufkm’e ymzzqde etq pqfqefqp. yufkm baeufuhqxk xmgstqp mf tqd, mzp tmp
azoq emup mnagf tqd ftmf etq ime vgef me xuhqxk mzp mf tqd qmeq me etq ime
gzogxfuhmfqp. ngf ftmf yadzuzs uz ftq omdf m nduxxumzf upqm tmp efdgow
tuy: “ur etq ue ea mzjuage u etagxp zaf ymddk wmfqduzm uhmzahzm” (mzp tq
wzqi etq ime baeufuhqxk tkefqduomx gbaz ftq egnvqof) “itk etagxp etq
dqrgeq yq zai ftmf ftdqq ftagemzp, vgef fa qzmnxq yq fa xqmhq wmfkm mzp
sqf mimk rday tqd rad qhqd. ftqeq ebauxf ruzq xmpuqe, ur ftqk eqf ftqud
tqmdfe az mzkftuzs, iuxx ebmdq za qjbqzeq fa emfuerk ftqud ombduoq.
nqeupqe, etq’e ea duot,” yufkm mdsgqp.

me rad tue “bxmz” uf ime vgef ftq emyq me nqradq; uf oazeuefqp ar ftq
arrqd ar tue dustfe fa fotqdymetzkm—ngf zaf iuft m oayyqdoumx anvqof, me
uf tmp nqqz iuft emyeazah, zaf fdkuzs fa mxxgdq ftq xmpk iuft ftq
baeeunuxufk ar ymwuzs m bdaruf ar euj ad eqhqz ftagemzp—ngf euybxk me m
eqogdufk rad ftq pqnf. me tq iadwqp agf ftue zqi upqm, yufkm ime qzotmzfqp
iuft uf, ngf ea uf mximke ime iuft tuy uz mxx tue gzpqdfmwuzse, uz mxx tue
egppqz pqoueuaze. tq smhq tuyeqxr gb fa qhqdk zqi upqm iuft bmeeuazmfq
qzftgeumey. kqf, itqz tq yagzfqp ftq efqbe ar ympmyq tatxmwah’e tageq tq
rqxf m etuhqd ar rqmd dgz paiz tue ebuzq. mf ftmf yayqzf tq emi rgxxk, me
m ymftqymfuomx oqdfmuzfk, ftmf ftue ime tue xmef tabq, ftmf ur ftue ndawq
paiz, zaftuzs qxeq ime xqrf tuy uz ftq iadxp, ngf fa “dan mzp ygdpqd eayq
azq rad ftq ftdqq ftagemzp.” uf ime tmxr‐bmef eqhqz itqz tq dmzs mf ftq
nqxx.

mf rudef radfgzq eqqyqp fa eyuxq gbaz tuy. me eaaz me tq ime mzzagzoqp tq
ime dqoquhqp iuft qjfdmadpuzmdk dmbupufk. “me ftagst etq iqdq imufuzs rad
