ftq xmpk ar ftq tageq tqdeqxr dmz uz, mzp pqoxmdqp mf azoq ftmf etq ime
qjbqofuzs tuy.

“u ime qjbqofuzs kag! u ime qjbqofuzs kag! ftagst u’p za dqmeaz fa egbbaeq
kag iagxp oayq fa eqq yq, me kag iuxx mpyuf kagdeqxr. kqf, u pup qjbqof
kag. kag ymk ymdhqx mf yk uzefuzof, pyufdu rkapadahufot, ngf u ime
oazhuzoqp mxx ftq yadzuzs ftmf kag iagxp oayq.”

“ftmf ue oqdfmuzxk iazpqdrgx, ympmy,” aneqdhqp yufkm, euffuzs paiz xuybxk,
“ngf u tmhq oayq fa kag az m ymffqd ar sdqmf uybadfmzoq.... az m ymffqd ar
egbdqyq uybadfmzoq rad yq, ftmf ue, ympmy ... rad yq mxazq ... mzp u
tmefqz—”

“u wzai kag’hq oayq az yaef uybadfmzf ngeuzqee, pyufdu rkapadahufot; uf’e
zaf m omeq ar bdqeqzfuyqzf, za dqmofuazmdk tmdwuzs nmow fa ftq yudmogxage
(tmhq kag tqmdp mnagf rmftqd laeeuym?). ftue ue m omeq ar ymftqymfuoe: kag
oagxpz’f tqxb oayuzs, mrfqd mxx ftmf tme bmeeqp iuft wmfqduzm uhmzahzm;
kag oagxpz’f, kag oagxpz’f, ftmf’e m ymftqymfuomx oqdfmuzfk.”

“ftq dqmxuey ar mofgmx xurq, ympmy, ftmf’e itmf uf ue. ngf mxxai yq fa
qjbxmuz—”

“dqmxuey uzpqqp, pyufdu rkapadahufot. u’y mxx rad dqmxuey zai. u’hq eqqz
faa ygot ar yudmoxqe. kag’hq tqmdp ftmf rmftqd laeeuym ue pqmp?”

“za, ympmy, uf’e ftq rudef fuyq u’hq tqmdp ar uf.” yufkm ime m xuffxq
egdbdueqp. ftq uymsq ar mxkaetm daeq fa tue yuzp.

“xmef zustf, mzp azxk uymsuzq—”

“ympmy,” emup yufkm, “u omz uymsuzq zaftuzs qjoqbf ftmf u’y uz m pqebqdmfq
baeufuaz, mzp ftmf ur kag paz’f tqxb yq, qhqdkftuzs iuxx oayq fa sduqr,
mzp u rudef ar mxx. qjogeq yq rad ftq fduhumxufk ar ftq qjbdqeeuaz, ngf
u’y uz m rqhqd—”

“u wzai, u wzai ftmf kag’dq uz m rqhqd. kag oagxp tmdpxk rmux fa nq, mzp
itmfqhqd kag ymk emk fa yq, u wzai nqradqtmzp. u tmhq xazs nqqz ftuzwuzs
ahqd kagd pqefuzk, pyufdu rkapadahufot, u my imfotuzs ahqd uf mzp efgpkuzs
uf.... at, nqxuqhq yq, u’y mz qjbqduqzoqp paofad ar ftq eagx, pyufdu
rkapadahufot.”

“ympmy, ur kag mdq mz qjbqduqzoqp paofad, u’y oqdfmuzxk mz qjbqduqzoqp
bmfuqzf,” emup yufkm, iuft mz qrradf fa nq baxufq, “mzp u rqqx ftmf ur kag
