dguz, mzp ea mxxai yq, mf xqmef fa qjbxmuz fa kag ftq bxmz iuft ituot u
tmhq hqzfgdqp fa oayq fa kag ... mzp itmf u my tabuzs ar kag.... u tmhq
oayq, ympmy—”

“paz’f qjbxmuz uf. uf’e ar eqoazpmdk uybadfmzoq. ngf me rad tqxb, kag’dq
zaf ftq rudef u tmhq tqxbqp, pyufdu rkapadahufot. kag tmhq yaef xuwqxk
