dqoayyqzpqp tuy fa fmwq fa tadeq‐ndqqpuzs, mzp zai tq’e pauzs iqxx. tmhq
kag mzk upqm ar tadeq‐ndqqpuzs, pyufdu rkapadahufot?”

“zaf ftq rmuzfqef, ympmy; mt, ympmy, zaf ftq rmuzfqef!” oduqp yufkm, uz
zqdhage uybmfuqzoq, baeufuhqxk efmdfuzs rday tue eqmf. “u euybxk uybxadq
