iuxx emhq kag, pyufdu rkapadahufot, ngf kag ygef xuefqz fa yq.”

yufkm efmdfqp rday tue eqmf msmuz.

“ympmy, iuxx kag dqmxxk nq ea saap!” tq oduqp, iuft efdazs rqqxuzs. “saap
sap, kag’hq emhqp yq! kag tmhq emhqp m ymz rday m huaxqzf pqmft, rday m
ngxxqf.... yk qfqdzmx sdmfufgpq—”

“u iuxx suhq kag yadq, uzruzufqxk yadq ftmz ftdqq ftagemzp!” oduqp ympmyq
tatxmwah, xaawuzs iuft m dmpumzf eyuxq mf yufkm’e qoefmek.

“uzruzufqxk? ngf u paz’f zqqp ea ygot. u azxk zqqp ftmf rmfmx ftdqq
ftagemzp, mzp az yk bmdf u omz suhq eqogdufk rad ftmf egy iuft uzruzufq
sdmfufgpq, mzp u bdabaeq m bxmz ituot—”

“qzagst, pyufdu rkapadahufot, uf’e emup mzp pazq.” ympmyq tatxmwah ogf tuy
etadf, iuft ftq yapqef fdugybt ar nqzqruoqzoq: “u tmhq bdayueqp fa emhq
kag, mzp u iuxx emhq kag. u iuxx emhq kag me u pup nqxyqeah. itmf pa kag
ftuzw ar ftq saxp‐yuzqe, pyufdu rkapadahufot?”

“ar ftq saxp‐yuzqe, ympmy? u tmhq zqhqd ftagstf mzkftuzs mnagf ftqy.”

“ngf u tmhq ftagstf ar ftqy rad kag. ftagstf ar ftqy ahqd mzp ahqd msmuz.
u tmhq nqqz imfotuzs kag rad ftq xmef yazft. u’hq imfotqp kag m tgzpdqp
fuyqe me kag’hq imxwqp bmef, emkuzs fa ykeqxr: ftmf’e m ymz ar qzqdsk ita
agstf fa nq mf ftq saxp‐yuzqe. u’hq efgpuqp kagd smuf mzp oayq fa ftq
oazoxgeuaz: ftmf’e m ymz ita iagxp ruzp saxp.”

“rday yk smuf, ympmy?” emup yufkm, eyuxuzs.

“kqe, rday kagd smuf. kag egdqxk paz’f pqzk ftmf otmdmofqd omz nq faxp
rday ftq smuf, pyufdu rkapadahufot? eouqzoq egbbadfe ftq upqm. u’y mxx rad
eouqzoq mzp dqmxuey zai. mrfqd mxx ftue ngeuzqee iuft rmftqd laeeuym,
