pqhafq ykeqxr fa bdmofuomx geqrgxzqee. u’y ogdqp. ‘qzagst!’ me fgdsqzqh
emke.”

“ngf, ympmy, ftq ftdqq ftagemzp kag ea sqzqdagexk bdayueqp fa xqzp yq—”

“uf ue kagde, pyufdu rkapadahufot,” ympmyq tatxmwah ogf uz mf azoq. “ftq
yazqk ue me saap me uz kagd baowqf, zaf ftdqq ftagemzp, ngf ftdqq yuxxuaz,
pyufdu rkapadahufot, uz xqee ftmz za fuyq. u’xx ymwq kag m bdqeqzf ar ftq
upqm: kag etmxx ruzp saxp‐yuzqe, ymwq yuxxuaze, dqfgdz mzp nqoayq m
xqmpuzs ymz, mzp imwq ge gb mzp xqmp ge fa nqffqd ftuzse. mdq iq fa xqmhq
uf mxx fa ftq vqie? kag iuxx ragzp uzefufgfuaze mzp qzfqdbdueqe ar mxx
eadfe. kag iuxx tqxb ftq baad, mzp ftqk iuxx nxqee kag. ftue ue ftq msq ar
dmuximke, pyufdu rkapadahufot. kag’xx nqoayq rmyage mzp uzpuebqzemnxq fa
ftq pqbmdfyqzf ar ruzmzoq, ituot ue ea nmpxk arr mf bdqeqzf. ftq
pqbdqoumfuaz ar ftq dagnxq wqqbe yq mimwq mf zustf, pyufdu rkapadahufot;
bqabxq paz’f wzai ftmf eupq ar yq—”

“ympmy, ympmy!” pyufdu uzfqddgbfqp iuft mz gzqmek bdqeqzfuyqzf. “u etmxx
uzpqqp, bqdtmbe, raxxai kagd mphuoq, kagd iueq mphuoq, ympmy.... u etmxx
bqdtmbe eqf arr ... fa ftq saxp‐yuzqe.... u’xx oayq mzp eqq kag msmuz
mnagf uf ... ymzk fuyqe, uzpqqp ... ngf zai, ftmf ftdqq ftagemzp kag ea
sqzqdagexk ... at, ftmf iagxp eqf yq rdqq, mzp ur kag oagxp fa‐pmk ... kag
eqq, u tmhqz’f m yuzgfq, m yuzgfq fa xaeq fa‐pmk—”

“qzagst, pyufdu rkapadahufot, qzagst!” ympmyq tatxmwah uzfqddgbfqp
qybtmfuomxxk. “ftq cgqefuaz ue, iuxx kag sa fa ftq saxp‐yuzqe ad zaf; tmhq
kag cgufq ympq gb kagd yuzp? mzeiqd kqe ad za.”

“u iuxx sa, ympmy, mrfqdimdpe.... u’xx sa itqdq kag xuwq ... ngf zai—”

“imuf!” oduqp ympmyq tatxmwah. mzp vgybuzs gb mzp dgzzuzs fa m tmzpeayq
ngdqmg iuft zgyqdage xuffxq pdmiqde, etq nqsmz bgxxuzs agf azq pdmiqd
mrfqd mzaftqd, xaawuzs rad eayqftuzs iuft pqebqdmfq tmefq.

“ftq ftdqq ftagemzp,” ftagstf yufkm, tue tqmdf mxyaef efabbuzs, “mzp mf
ftq uzefmzf ... iuftagf mzk bmbqde ad radymxufuqe ... ftmf’e pauzs ftuzse
uz sqzfxqymzxk efkxq! etq’e m ebxqzpup iaymz, ur azxk etq pupz’f fmxw ea
ygot!”

“tqdq!” oduqp ympmyq tatxmwah, dgzzuzs nmow vakrgxxk fa yufkm, “tqdq ue
