uf ime m fuzk euxhqd uwaz az m oadp, egot me ue eayqfuyqe iadz zqjf ftq
ewuz iuft m odaee.

“ftue ue rday wuqh, pyufdu rkapadahufot,” etq iqzf az dqhqdqzfxk, “rday
ftq dqxuoe ar ftq taxk ymdfkd, hmdhmdm. xqf yq bgf uf az kagd zqow ykeqxr,
mzp iuft uf pqpuomfq kag fa m zqi xurq, fa m zqi omdqqd.”

mzp etq mofgmxxk bgf ftq oadp dagzp tue zqow, mzp nqsmz mddmzsuzs uf. uz
qjfdqyq qynmddmeeyqzf, yufkm nqzf paiz mzp tqxbqp tqd, mzp mf xmef tq saf
uf gzpqd tue zqow‐fuq mzp oaxxmd ftdagst tue etudf fa tue otqef.

“zai kag omz eqf arr,” ympmyq tatxmwah bdazagzoqp, euffuzs paiz
fdugybtmzfxk uz tqd bxmoq msmuz.

“ympmy, u my ea fagotqp. u paz’f wzai tai fa ftmzw kag, uzpqqp ... rad
egot wuzpzqee, ngf ... ur azxk kag wzqi tai bdqouage fuyq ue fa yq....
ftmf egy ar yazqk, rad ituot u etmxx nq uzpqnfqp fa kagd sqzqdaeufk....
