kag’hq wzaiz uf m xazs fuyq ... ftmf u xahq eayqnapk tqdq.... u tmhq nqqz
rmxeq fa wmfkm ... wmfqduzm uhmzahzm u etagxp emk.... at, u’hq nqtmhqp
uztgymzxk, puetazadmnxk fa tqd, ngf u rqxx uz xahq tqdq iuft mzaftqd iaymz
