mxdqmpk, ngf itay u omzzaf xqmhq az mzk mooagzf, mzp ftqdqradq ftmf ftdqq
ftagemzp zai—”

“xqmhq qhqdkftuzs, pyufdu rkapadahufot,” ympmyq tatxmwah uzfqddgbfqp uz
ftq yaef pqoueuhq fazq. “xqmhq qhqdkftuzs, qebqoumxxk iayqz. saxp‐yuzqe
mdq kagd samx, mzp ftqdq’e za bxmoq rad iayqz ftqdq. mrfqdimdpe, itqz kag
oayq nmow duot mzp rmyage, kag iuxx ruzp ftq sudx ar kagd tqmdf uz ftq
tustqef eaouqfk. ftmf iuxx nq m yapqdz sudx, m sudx ar qpgomfuaz mzp
mphmzoqp upqme. nk ftmf fuyq ftq pmizuzs iaymz cgqefuaz iuxx tmhq smuzqp
sdagzp, mzp ftq zqi iaymz iuxx tmhq mbbqmdqp.”

“ympmy, ftmf’e zaf ftq bauzf, zaf mf mxx....” yufkm oxmebqp tue tmzpe uz
qzfdqmfk.

“kqe, uf ue, pyufdu rkapadahufot, vgef itmf kag zqqp; ftq hqdk ftuzs
kag’dq kqmdzuzs rad, ftagst kag paz’f dqmxulq uf kagdeqxr. u my zaf mf mxx
abbaeqp fa ftq bdqeqzf iaymz yahqyqzf, pyufdu rkapadahufot. ftq
pqhqxabyqzf ar iaymz, mzp qhqz ftq baxufuomx qymzoubmfuaz ar iaymz uz ftq
zqmd rgfgdq—ftmf’e yk upqmx. u’hq m pmgstfqd ykeqxr, pyufdu rkapadahufot,
bqabxq paz’f wzai ftmf eupq ar yq. u idafq m xqffqd fa ftq mgftad,
etfotqpduz, az ftmf egnvqof. tq tme fmgstf yq ea ygot, ea ygot mnagf ftq
haomfuaz ar iaymz. ea xmef kqmd u eqzf tuy mz mzazkyage xqffqd ar fia
xuzqe: ‘u wuee mzp qyndmoq kag, yk fqmotqd, rad ftq yapqdz iaymz.
bqdeqhqdq.’ mzp u euszqp ykeqxr, ‘m yaftqd.’ u ftagstf ar euszuzs ykeqxr
‘m oazfqybadmdk yaftqd,’ mzp tqeufmfqp, ngf u efgow fa ftq euybxq
‘yaftqd’; ftqdq’e yadq yadmx nqmgfk uz ftmf, pyufdu rkapadahufot. mzp ftq
iadp ‘oazfqybadmdk’ yustf tmhq dqyuzpqp tuy ar ‘_ftq oazfqybadmdk_’—m
bmuzrgx dqoaxxqofuaz aiuzs fa ftq oqzeadetub.... saap tqmhqze, itmf ue ftq
ymffqd!”

“ympmy!” oduqp yufkm, vgybuzs gb mf xmef, oxmebuzs tue tmzpe nqradq tqd uz
tqxbxqee qzfdqmfk. “kag iuxx ymwq yq iqqb ur kag pqxmk itmf kag tmhq ea
sqzqdagexk—”

“at, pa iqqb, pyufdu rkapadahufot, pa iqqb! ftmf’e m zanxq rqqxuzs ...
egot m bmft xuqe abqz nqradq kag! fqmde iuxx qmeq kagd tqmdf, mzp xmfqd az
kag iuxx dqfgdz dqvauouzs. kag iuxx tmefqz fa yq rday eunqdum az bgdbaeq
fa etmdq kagd vak iuft yq—”

“ngf mxxai yq, faa!” yufkm oduqp egppqzxk. “rad ftq xmef fuyq u qzfdqmf
kag, fqxx yq, omz u tmhq ftq egy kag bdayueqp yq fa‐pmk, ur zaf, itqz ymk
u oayq rad uf?”

“itmf egy, pyufdu rkapadahufot?”

“ftq ftdqq ftagemzp kag bdayueqp yq ... ftmf kag ea sqzqdagexk—”

“ftdqq ftagemzp? dagnxqe? at, za, u tmhqz’f saf ftdqq ftagemzp,” ympmyq
tatxmwah mzzagzoqp iuft eqdqzq mymlqyqzf. yufkm ime efgbqruqp.

“itk, kag emup vgef zai ... kag emup ... kag emup uf ime me saap me uz yk
tmzpe—”

“at, za, kag yuegzpqdefaap yq, pyufdu rkapadahufot. uz ftmf omeq kag
yuegzpqdefaap yq. u ime fmxwuzs ar ftq saxp‐yuzqe. uf’e fdgq u bdayueqp
