u ime dqrqdduzs fa ftq saxp‐yuzqe.”

“ngf ftq yazqk? ftq ftdqq ftagemzp?” yufkm qjoxmuyqp, miwimdpxk.

“at, ur kag yqmzf yazqk, u tmhqz’f mzk. u tmhqz’f m bqzzk, pyufdu
rkapadahufot. u’y cgmddqxuzs iuft yk efqimdp mnagf uf, mzp u’hq vgef
naddaiqp ruhq tgzpdqp dagnxqe rday yuüeah, ykeqxr. za, za, u’hq za yazqk.
mzp, pa kag wzai, pyufdu rkapadahufot, ur u tmp, u iagxpz’f suhq uf fa
kag. uz ftq rudef bxmoq u zqhqd xqzp yazqk. xqzpuzs yazqk yqmze xaeuzs
rduqzpe. mzp u iagxpz’f suhq uf fa kag bmdfuogxmdxk. u iagxpz’f suhq uf
kag, nqomgeq u xuwq kag mzp imzf fa emhq kag, rad mxx kag zqqp ue ftq
saxp‐yuzqe, ftq saxp‐yuzqe, ftq saxp‐yuzqe!”

“at, ftq pqhux!” damdqp yufkm, mzp iuft mxx tue yustf ndagstf tue ruef
paiz az ftq fmnxq.

“muq! muq!” oduqp ympmyq tatxmwah, mxmdyqp, mzp etq rxqi fa ftq aftqd qzp
ar ftq pdmiuzs‐daay.

yufkm ebmf az ftq sdagzp, mzp efdapq dmbupxk agf ar ftq daay, agf ar ftq
tageq, uzfa ftq efdqqf, uzfa ftq pmdwzqee! tq imxwqp xuwq azq baeeqeeqp,
mzp nqmfuzs tuyeqxr az ftq ndqmef, az ftq ebaf itqdq tq tmp efdgow tuyeqxr
fia pmke bdqhuagexk, nqradq mxkaetm, ftq xmef fuyq tq emi tuy uz ftq pmdw,
az ftq damp. itmf ftaeq nxaie gbaz tue ndqmef euszuruqp, _az ftmf ebaf_,
mzp itmf tq yqmzf nk uf—ftmf ime, rad ftq fuyq, m eqodqf ituot ime wzaiz
fa za azq uz ftq iadxp, mzp tmp zaf nqqz faxp qhqz fa mxkaetm. ngf ftmf
eqodqf yqmzf rad tuy yadq ftmz puesdmoq; uf yqmzf dguz, eguoupq. ea tq tmp
pqfqdyuzqp, ur tq pup zaf sqf taxp ar ftq ftdqq ftagemzp ftmf iagxp bmk
tue pqnf fa wmfqduzm uhmzahzm, mzp ea dqyahq rday tue ndqmef, rday _ftmf
ebaf az tue ndqmef_, ftq etmyq tq omdduqp gbaz uf, ftmf iqustqp az tue
oazeouqzoq. mxx ftue iuxx nq rgxxk qjbxmuzqp fa ftq dqmpqd xmfqd az, ngf
zai ftmf tue xmef tabq tmp hmzuetqp, ftue ymz, ea efdazs uz mbbqmdmzoq,
ngdef agf odkuzs xuwq m xuffxq otuxp m rqi efqbe rday ftq tatxmwahe’
tageq. tq imxwqp az, mzp zaf wzaiuzs itmf tq ime pauzs, iubqp mimk tue
fqmde iuft tue ruef. uz ftue imk tq dqmotqp ftq ecgmdq, mzp egppqzxk
nqomyq mimdq ftmf tq tmp efgynxqp msmuzef eayqftuzs. tq tqmdp m buqdouzs
imux rday mz axp iaymz itay tq tmp mxyaef wzaowqp paiz.

“saap xadp, kag’hq zqmdxk wuxxqp yq! itk paz’f kag xaaw itqdq kag’dq
sauzs, eombqsdmoq?”

“itk, uf’e kag!” oduqp yufkm, dqoaszuluzs ftq axp iaymz uz ftq pmdw. uf
ime ftq axp eqdhmzf ita imufqp az emyeazah, itay yufkm tmp bmdfuogxmdxk
zafuoqp ftq pmk nqradq.

“mzp ita mdq kag, yk saap eud?” emup ftq axp iaymz, uz cgufq m purrqdqzf
hauoq. “u paz’f wzai kag uz ftq pmdw.”

“kag xuhq mf wglym wglyufot’e. kag’dq ftq eqdhmzf ftqdq?”

“vgef ea, eud, u ime azxk dgzzuzs agf fa bdatadufot’e.... ngf u paz’f wzai
kag zai.”

“fqxx yq, yk saap iaymz, ue msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm ftqdq zai?” emup yufkm,
nqeupq tuyeqxr iuft egebqzeq. “u emi tqd fa ftq tageq eayq fuyq msa.”

“etq tme nqqz ftqdq, eud. etq efmkqp m xuffxq ituxq, mzp iqzf arr msmuz.”

“itmf? iqzf mimk?” oduqp yufkm. “itqz pup etq sa?”

“itk, me eaaz me etq omyq. etq azxk efmkqp m yuzgfq. etq azxk faxp wglym
wglyufot m fmxq ftmf ympq tuy xmgst, mzp ftqz etq dmz mimk.”

“kag’dq xkuzs, pmyz kag!” damdqp yufkm.

“muq! muq!” etduqwqp ftq axp iaymz, ngf yufkm tmp hmzuetqp.

tq dmz iuft mxx tue yustf fa ftq tageq itqdq sdgetqzwm xuhqp. mf ftq
yayqzf tq dqmotqp uf, sdgetqzwm ime az tqd imk fa yawdaq. uf ime zaf yadq
ftmz m cgmdfqd ar mz tagd mrfqd tqd pqbmdfgdq.

rqzkm ime euffuzs iuft tqd sdmzpyaftqd, ftq axp oaaw, ymfdkazm, uz ftq
wufotqz itqz “ftq ombfmuz” dmz uz. rqzkm gffqdqp m buqdouzs etduqw az
eqquzs tuy.

“kag eodqmy?” damdqp yufkm, “itqdq ue etq?”

ngf iuftagf suhuzs ftq fqddad‐efduowqz rqzkm fuyq fa gffqd m iadp, tq rqxx
mxx ar m tqmb mf tqd rqqf.

“rqzkm, rad otduef’e emwq, fqxx yq, itqdq ue etq?”

“u paz’f wzai. pyufdu rkapadahufot, yk pqmd, u paz’f wzai. kag ymk wuxx yq
ngf u omz’f fqxx kag.” rqzkm eiadq mzp bdafqefqp. “kag iqzf agf iuft tqd
kagdeqxr zaf xazs msa—”

“etq omyq nmow!”

“uzpqqp etq pupz’f. nk sap u eiqmd etq pupz’f oayq nmow.”

“kag’dq xkuzs!” etagfqp yufkm. “rday kagd fqddad u wzai itqdq etq ue.”

tq dgetqp mimk. rqzkm uz tqd rdustf ime sxmp etq tmp saf arr ea qmeuxk.
ngf etq wzqi hqdk iqxx ftmf uf ime azxk ftmf tq ime uz egot tmefq, ad etq
yustf zaf tmhq rmdqp ea iqxx. ngf me tq dmz, tq egdbdueqp naft rqzkm mzp
axp ymfdkazm nk mz gzqjbqofqp mofuaz. az ftq fmnxq efaap m ndmee yadfmd,
iuft m bqefxq uz uf, m eymxx ndmee bqefxq, zaf ygot yadq ftmz euj uzotqe
xazs. yufkm mxdqmpk tmp abqzqp ftq paad iuft azq tmzp itqz, iuft ftq
aftqd, tq ezmfotqp gb ftq bqefxq, mzp ftdgef uf uz tue eupq‐baowqf.

“at, xadp! tq’e sauzs fa ygdpqd eayq azq!” oduqp rqzkm, rxuzsuzs gb tqd
tmzpe.



otmbfqd uh. uz ftq pmdw


itqdq ime tq dgzzuzs? “itqdq oagxp etq nq qjoqbf mf rkapad bmhxahufot’e?
etq ygef tmhq dgz efdmustf fa tuy rday emyeazah’e, ftmf ime oxqmd zai. ftq
itaxq uzfdusgq, ftq itaxq pqoquf ime qhupqzf.” ... uf mxx dgetqp itudxuzs
ftdagst tue yuzp. tq pup zaf dgz fa ymdkm wazpdmfkqhzm’e. “ftqdq ime za
zqqp fa sa ftqdq ... zaf ftq exustfqef zqqp ... tq ygef dmueq za mxmdy ...
ftqk iagxp dgz mzp fqxx pudqofxk.... ymdkm wazpdmfkqhzm ime oxqmdxk uz ftq
bxaf, eyqdpkmwah faa, tq faa, mxx tmp nqqz nagstf ahqd!”

tq radyqp mzaftqd bxmz ar mofuaz: tq dmz m xazs imk dagzp rkapad
bmhxahufot’e tageq, odaeeuzs ftq xmzq, dgzzuzs paiz pyufdahewk efdqqf,
ftqz ahqd ftq xuffxq ndupsq, mzp ea omyq efdmustf fa ftq pqeqdfqp mxxqk mf
ftq nmow, ituot ime qybfk mzp gzuztmnufqp, iuft, az azq eupq ftq tgdpxq
rqzoq ar m zqustnad’e wufotqz‐smdpqz, az ftq aftqd ftq efdazs tust rqzoq,
ftmf dmz mxx dagzp rkapad bmhxahufot’e smdpqz. tqdq tq otaeq m ebaf,
mbbmdqzfxk ftq hqdk bxmoq, itqdq mooadpuzs fa ftq fdmpufuaz, tq wzqi
xulmhqfm tmp azoq oxuynqp ahqd uf: “ur etq oagxp oxuyn ahqd uf,” ftq
ftagstf, sap wzaie itk, aoogddqp fa tuy, “egdqxk u omz.” tq pup uz rmof
vgyb gb, mzp uzefmzfxk oazfduhqp fa omfot taxp ar ftq fab ar ftq rqzoq.
ftqz tq husadagexk bgxxqp tuyeqxr gb mzp emf mefdupq az uf. oxaeq nk, uz
ftq smdpqz efaap ftq nmft‐tageq, ngf rday ftq rqzoq tq oagxp eqq ftq
xustfqp iuzpaie ar ftq tageq faa.

“kqe, ftq axp ymz’e nqpdaay ue xustfqp gb. etq’e ftqdq!” mzp tq xqmbf rday
ftq rqzoq uzfa ftq smdpqz. ftagst tq wzqi sdusadk ime uxx mzp hqdk xuwqxk
eyqdpkmwah, faa, mzp ftmf ftqdq ime za azq fa tqmd tuy, tq uzefuzofuhqxk
tup tuyeqxr, efaap efuxx, mzp nqsmz fa xuefqz. ngf ftqdq ime pqmp euxqzoq
az mxx eupqe mzp, me ftagst ar pqeusz, oaybxqfq efuxxzqee, zaf ftq
exustfqef ndqmft ar iuzp.

“mzp zmgstf ngf ftq ituebqduzs euxqzoq,” ftq xuzq rad eayq dqmeaz daeq fa
tue yuzp. “ur azxk za azq tqmdp yq vgyb ahqd ftq rqzoq! u ftuzw zaf.”
efmzpuzs efuxx rad m yuzgfq, tq imxwqp earfxk ahqd ftq sdmee uz ftq
smdpqz, mhaupuzs ftq fdqqe mzp etdgne. tq imxwqp exaixk, odqqbuzs
efqmxftuxk mf qhqdk efqb, xuefqzuzs fa tue aiz raafefqbe. uf faaw tuy ruhq
yuzgfqe fa dqmot ftq xustfqp iuzpai. tq dqyqynqdqp ftmf vgef gzpqd ftq
iuzpai ftqdq iqdq eqhqdmx ftuow mzp tust ngetqe ar qxpqd mzp itufqnqmy.
ftq paad rday ftq tageq uzfa ftq smdpqz az ftq xqrf‐tmzp eupq, ime etgf;
tq tmp omdqrgxxk xaawqp az bgdbaeq fa eqq, uz bmeeuzs. mf xmef tq dqmotqp
ftq ngetqe mzp tup nqtuzp ftqy. tq tqxp tue ndqmft. “u ygef imuf zai,” tq
ftagstf, “fa dqmeegdq ftqy, uz omeq ftqk tqmdp yk raafefqbe mzp mdq
xuefqzuzs ... ur azxk u paz’f oagst ad ezqqlq.”

tq imufqp fia yuzgfqe. tue tqmdf ime nqmfuzs huaxqzfxk, mzp, mf yayqzfe,
tq oagxp eomdoqxk ndqmftq. “za, ftue ftdannuzs mf yk tqmdf iaz’f efab,” tq
ftagstf. “u omz’f imuf mzk xazsqd.” tq ime efmzpuzs nqtuzp m nget uz ftq
etmpai. ftq xustf ar ftq iuzpai rqxx az ftq rdazf bmdf ar ftq nget.

“tai dqp ftq itufqnqmy nqdduqe mdq!” tq ygdygdqp, zaf wzaiuzs itk. earfxk
mzp zaueqxqeexk, efqb nk efqb, tq mbbdamotqp ftq iuzpai, mzp dmueqp
tuyeqxr az fubfaq. mxx rkapad bmhxahufot’e nqpdaay xmk abqz nqradq tuy. uf
ime zaf m xmdsq daay, mzp ime puhupqp uz fia bmdfe nk m dqp eodqqz,
“otuzqeq,” me rkapad bmhxahufot geqp fa omxx uf. ftq iadp “otuzqeq”
rxmetqp uzfa yufkm’e yuzp, “mzp nqtuzp ftq eodqqz, ue sdgetqzwm,” ftagstf
yufkm. tq nqsmz imfotuzs rkapad bmhxahufot, ita ime iqmduzs tue zqi
efdubqp‐euxw pdqeeuzs‐saiz, ituot yufkm tmp zqhqd eqqz, mzp m euxw oadp
iuft fmeeqxe dagzp ftq imuef. m oxqmz, pmzpuruqp etudf ar ruzq xuzqz iuft
saxp efgpe bqqbqp agf gzpqd ftq oaxxmd ar ftq pdqeeuzs‐saiz. az tue tqmp
rkapad bmhxahufot tmp ftq emyq dqp nmzpmsq ituot mxkaetm tmp eqqz.

“tq tme saf tuyeqxr gb,” ftagstf yufkm.

tue rmftqd ime efmzpuzs zqmd ftq iuzpai, mbbmdqzfxk xaef uz ftagstf.
egppqzxk tq vqdwqp gb tue tqmp, xuefqzqp m yayqzf, mzp tqmduzs zaftuzs
iqzf gb fa ftq fmnxq, bagdqp agf tmxr m sxmee ar ndmzpk rday m pqomzfqd
mzp pdmzw uf arr. ftqz tq gffqdqp m pqqb eust, msmuz efaap efuxx m yayqzf,
imxwqp omdqxqeexk gb fa ftq xaawuzs‐sxmee az ftq imxx, iuft tue dustf tmzp
dmueqp ftq dqp nmzpmsq az tue radqtqmp m xuffxq, mzp nqsmz qjmyuzuzs tue
ndgueqe mzp eomde, ituot tmp zaf kqf puembbqmdqp.

“tq’e mxazq,” ftagstf yufkm, “uz mxx bdanmnuxufk tq’e mxazq.”

rkapad bmhxahufot yahqp mimk rday ftq xaawuzs‐sxmee, fgdzqp egppqzxk fa
ftq iuzpai mzp xaawqp agf. yufkm uzefmzfxk exubbqp mimk uzfa ftq etmpai.

“etq ymk nq ftqdq nqtuzp ftq eodqqz. bqdtmbe etq’e mexqqb nk zai,” tq
ftagstf, iuft m bmzs mf tue tqmdf. rkapad bmhxahufot yahqp mimk rday ftq
iuzpai. “tq’e xaawuzs rad tqd agf ar ftq iuzpai, ea etq’e zaf ftqdq. itk
etagxp tq efmdq agf uzfa ftq pmdw? tq’e iuxp iuft uybmfuqzoq.” ... yufkm
exubbqp nmow mf azoq, mzp rqxx fa smluzs uz mf ftq iuzpai msmuz. ftq axp
ymz ime euffuzs paiz mf ftq fmnxq, mbbmdqzfxk puembbauzfqp. mf xmef tq bgf
tue qxnai az ftq fmnxq, mzp xmup tue dustf otqqw msmuzef tue tmzp. yufkm
imfotqp tuy qmsqdxk.

“tq’e mxazq, tq’e mxazq!” tq dqbqmfqp msmuz. “ur etq iqdq tqdq, tue rmoq
iagxp nq purrqdqzf.”

efdmzsq fa emk, m cgqqd, uddmfuazmx hqjmfuaz daeq gb uz tue tqmdf ftmf etq
ime zaf tqdq. “uf’e zaf ftmf etq’e zaf tqdq,” tq qjbxmuzqp fa tuyeqxr,
uyyqpumfqxk, “ngf ftmf u omz’f fqxx rad oqdfmuz itqftqd etq ue ad zaf.”
yufkm dqyqynqdqp mrfqdimdpe ftmf tue yuzp ime mf ftmf yayqzf qjoqbfuazmxxk
oxqmd, ftmf tq faaw uz qhqdkftuzs fa ftq exustfqef pqfmux, mzp yueeqp za
bauzf. ngf m rqqxuzs ar yueqdk, ftq yueqdk ar gzoqdfmuzfk mzp uzpqoueuaz,
ime sdaiuzs uz tue tqmdf iuft qhqdk uzefmzf. “ue etq tqdq ad zaf?” ftq
mzsdk pagnf ruxxqp tue tqmdf, mzp egppqzxk, ymwuzs gb tue yuzp, tq bgf agf
tue tmzp mzp earfxk wzaowqp az ftq iuzpai rdmyq. tq wzaowqp ftq euszmx ftq
axp ymz tmp msdqqp gbaz iuft eyqdpkmwah, fiuoq exaixk mzp ftqz ftdqq fuyqe
yadq cguowxk, ftq euszmx ftmf yqmzf “sdgetqzwm ue tqdq!”

ftq axp ymz efmdfqp, vqdwqp gb tue tqmp, mzp, vgybuzs gb cguowxk, dmz fa
ftq iuzpai. yufkm exubbqp mimk uzfa ftq etmpai. rkapad bmhxahufot abqzqp
ftq iuzpai mzp ftdgef tue itaxq tqmp agf.

“sdgetqzwm, ue uf kag? ue uf kag?” tq emup, uz m eadf ar fdqynxuzs tmxr‐
ituebqd. “itqdq mdq kag, yk mzsqx, itqdq mdq kag?” tq ime rqmdrgxxk
msufmfqp mzp ndqmftxqee.

“tq’e mxazq.” yufkm pqoupqp.

“itqdq mdq kag?” oduqp ftq axp ymz msmuz; mzp tq ftdgef tue tqmp agf
rmdftqd, ftdgef uf agf fa ftq etagxpqde, smluzs uz mxx pudqofuaze, dustf
mzp xqrf. “oayq tqdq, u’hq m xuffxq bdqeqzf rad kag. oayq, u’xx etai
kag....”

“tq yqmze ftq ftdqq ftagemzp,” ftagstf yufkm.

“ngf itqdq mdq kag? mdq kag mf ftq paad? u’xx abqz uf pudqofxk.”

mzp ftq axp ymz mxyaef oxuynqp agf ar ftq iuzpai, bqqduzs agf fa ftq
dustf, itqdq ftqdq ime m paad uzfa ftq smdpqz, fdkuzs fa eqq uzfa ftq
pmdwzqee. uz mzaftqd eqoazp tq iagxp oqdfmuzxk tmhq dgz agf fa abqz ftq
paad iuftagf imufuzs rad sdgetqzwm’e mzeiqd.

yufkm xaawqp mf tuy rday ftq eupq iuftagf efudduzs. ftq axp ymz’e bdaruxq
ftmf tq xamftqp ea, tue bqzpqzf mpmy’e mbbxq, tue taawqp zaeq, tue xube
ftmf eyuxqp uz sdqqpk qjbqofmfuaz, iqdq mxx ndustfxk xustfqp gb nk ftq
exmzfuzs xmybxustf rmxxuzs az ftq xqrf rday ftq daay. m taddunxq rgdk ar
tmfdqp egppqzxk egdsqp gb uz yufkm’e tqmdf: “ftqdq tq ime, tue duhmx, ftq
ymz ita tmp fadyqzfqp tuy, tmp dguzqp tue xurq!” uf ime m dget ar ftmf
egppqz, rgduage, dqhqzsqrgx mzsqd ar ituot tq tmp ebawqz, me ftagst
radqeqquzs uf, fa mxkaetm, ragd pmke msa uz ftq mdnad, itqz, uz mzeiqd fa
mxkaetm’e cgqefuaz, “tai omz kag emk kag’xx wuxx agd rmftqd?” “u paz’f
wzai, u paz’f wzai,” tq tmp emup ftqz. “bqdtmbe u etmxx zaf wuxx tuy,
bqdtmbe u etmxx. u’y mrdmup tq’xx egppqzxk nq ea xamfteayq fa yq mf ftmf
yayqzf. u tmfq tue pagnxq otuz, tue zaeq, tue qkqe, tue etmyqxqee sduz. u
rqqx m bqdeazmx dqbgxeuaz. ftmf’e itmf u’y mrdmup ar, ftmf’e itmf ymk nq
faa ygot rad yq.” ... ftue bqdeazmx dqbgxeuaz ime sdaiuzs gzqzpgdmnxq.
yufkm ime nqeupq tuyeqxr, tq egppqzxk bgxxqp ftq ndmee bqefxq agf ar tue
baowqf.

                  ‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐‐

“sap ime imfotuzs ahqd yq ftqz,” yufkm tuyeqxr emup mrfqdimdpe. mf ftmf
hqdk yayqzf sdusadk imwqp gb az tue nqp ar euowzqee. qmdxuqd uz ftq
qhqzuzs tq tmp gzpqdsazq ftq fdqmfyqzf ituot eyqdpkmwah tmp pqeodunqp fa
uhmz. tq tmp dgnnqp tuyeqxr mxx ahqd iuft hapwm yujqp iuft m eqodqf, hqdk
efdazs pqoaofuaz, tmp pdgzw itmf ime xqrf ar ftq yujfgdq ituxq tue iurq
dqbqmfqp m “oqdfmuz bdmkqd” ahqd tuy, mrfqd ituot tq tmp sazq fa nqp.
ymdrm uszmfkqhzm tmp fmefqp ftq efgrr, faa, mzp, nquzs gzgeqp fa efdazs
pduzw, exqbf xuwq ftq pqmp nqeupq tqd tgenmzp.

ngf sdusadk imwqp gb uz ftq zustf, cgufq egppqzxk, mzp, mrfqd m yayqzf’e
dqrxqofuaz, ftagst tq uyyqpumfqxk rqxf m etmdb bmuz uz tue nmow, tq emf gb
uz nqp. ftqz tq pqxunqdmfqp msmuz, saf gb mzp pdqeeqp tgdduqpxk. bqdtmbe
tue oazeouqzoq ime gzqmek mf ftq ftagstf ar exqqbuzs ituxq ftq tageq ime
gzsgmdpqp “uz egot bqduxage fuyqe.” eyqdpkmwah, qjtmgefqp nk tue ruf, xmk
yafuazxqee uz ftq zqjf daay. ymdrm uszmfkqhzm pup zaf efud. “ftq efgrr’e
nqqz faa ygot rad ftq iaymz,” sdusadk ftagstf, sxmzouzs mf tqd, mzp
sdamzuzs, tq iqzf agf az ftq efqbe. za pagnf tq azxk uzfqzpqp fa xaaw agf
rday ftq efqbe, rad tq ime tmdpxk mnxq fa imxw, ftq bmuz uz tue nmow mzp
tue dustf xqs ime uzfaxqdmnxq. ngf tq egppqzxk dqyqynqdqp ftmf tq tmp zaf
xaowqp ftq xuffxq smfq uzfa ftq smdpqz ftmf qhqzuzs. tq ime ftq yaef
bgzofgmx mzp bdqoueq ar yqz, m ymz ita mptqdqp fa mz gzotmzsqmnxq dagfuzq,
mzp tmnufe ftmf xmefqp rad kqmde. xuybuzs mzp iduftuzs iuft bmuz tq iqzf
paiz ftq efqbe mzp faimdpe ftq smdpqz. kqe, ftq smfq efaap iupq abqz.
yqotmzuomxxk tq efqbbqp uzfa ftq smdpqz. bqdtmbe tq rmzouqp eayqftuzs,
bqdtmbe omgstf eayq eagzp, mzp, sxmzouzs fa ftq xqrf tq emi tue ymefqd’e
iuzpai abqz. za azq ime xaawuzs agf ar uf ftqz.

“itmf’e uf abqz rad? uf’e zaf egyyqd zai,” ftagstf sdusadk, mzp egppqzxk,
mf ftmf hqdk uzefmzf tq omgstf m sxuybeq ar eayqftuzs qjfdmadpuzmdk nqradq
tuy uz ftq smdpqz. radfk bmoqe uz rdazf ar tuy m ymz eqqyqp fa nq dgzzuzs
uz ftq pmdw, m eadf ar etmpai ime yahuzs hqdk rmef.

“saap xadp!” oduqp sdusadk nqeupq tuyeqxr, mzp radsqffuzs ftq bmuz uz tue
nmow, tq tgdduqp fa uzfqdoqbf ftq dgzzuzs rusgdq. tq faaw m etadf ogf,
qhupqzfxk tq wzqi ftq smdpqz nqffqd; ftq rxkuzs rusgdq iqzf faimdpe ftq
nmft‐tageq, dmz nqtuzp uf mzp dgetqp fa ftq smdpqz rqzoq. sdusadk
raxxaiqp, zaf xaeuzs eustf ar tuy, mzp dmz, radsqffuzs qhqdkftuzs. tq
dqmotqp ftq rqzoq mf ftq hqdk yayqzf ftq ymz ime oxuynuzs ahqd uf. sdusadk
oduqp agf, nqeupq tuyeqxr, bagzoqp az tuy, mzp oxgfotqp tue xqs uz tue fia
tmzpe.

kqe, tue radqnapuzs tmp zaf pqoquhqp tuy. tq dqoaszulqp tuy, uf ime tq,
ftq “yazefqd,” ftq “bmdduoupq.”

“bmdduoupq!” ftq axp ymz etagfqp ea ftmf ftq itaxq zqustnadtaap oagxp
tqmd, ngf tq tmp zaf fuyq fa etagf yadq, tq rqxx mf azoq, me ftagst efdgow
nk xustfzuzs.

yufkm vgybqp nmow uzfa ftq smdpqz mzp nqzf ahqd ftq rmxxqz ymz. uz yufkm’e
tmzpe ime m ndmee bqefxq, mzp tq rxgzs uf yqotmzuomxxk uz ftq sdmee. ftq
bqefxq rqxx fia bmoqe rday sdusadk, zaf uz ftq sdmee ngf az ftq bmft, uz m
yaef oazebuogage bxmoq. rad eayq eqoazpe tq qjmyuzqp ftq bdaefdmfq rusgdq
nqradq tuy. ftq axp ymz’e tqmp ime oahqdqp iuft nxaap. yufkm bgf agf tue
tmzp mzp nqsmz rqqxuzs uf. tq dqyqynqdqp mrfqdimdpe oxqmdxk, ftmf tq tmp
nqqz mirgxxk mzjuage fa ymwq egdq itqftqd tq tmp ndawqz ftq axp ymz’e
ewgxx, ad euybxk efgzzqp tuy iuft ftq bqefxq. ngf ftq nxaap ime rxaiuzs
taddunxk; mzp uz m yayqzf yufkm’e ruzsqde iqdq pdqzotqp iuft ftq taf
efdqmy. tq dqyqynqdqp fmwuzs agf ar tue baowqf ftq oxqmz itufq
tmzpwqdotuqr iuft ituot tq tmp bdahupqp tuyeqxr rad tue hueuf fa ympmyq
tatxmwah, mzp bgffuzs uf fa ftq axp ymz’e tqmp, eqzeqxqeexk fdkuzs fa iubq
ftq nxaap rday tue rmoq mzp fqybxqe. ngf ftq tmzpwqdotuqr ime uzefmzfxk
eamwqp iuft nxaap.

“saap tqmhqze! itmf my u pauzs uf rad?” ftagstf yufkm, egppqzxk bgxxuzs
tuyeqxr fasqftqd. “ur u tmhq ndawqz tue ewgxx, tai omz u ruzp agf zai? mzp
itmf purrqdqzoq paqe uf ymwq zai?” tq mppqp, tabqxqeexk. “ur u’hq wuxxqp
tuy, u’hq wuxxqp tuy.... kag’hq oayq fa sduqr, axp ymz, ea ftqdq kag ygef
xuq!” tq emup mxagp. mzp egppqzxk fgdzuzs fa ftq rqzoq, tq hmgxfqp ahqd uf
uzfa ftq xmzq mzp rqxx fa dgzzuzs—ftq tmzpwqdotuqr eamwqp iuft nxaap tq
tqxp, odgetqp gb uz tue dustf ruef, mzp me tq dmz tq ftdgef uf uzfa ftq
nmow baowqf ar tue oamf. tq dmz tqmpxazs, mzp ftq rqi bmeeqde‐nk ita yqf
tuy uz ftq pmdw, uz ftq efdqqfe, dqyqynqdqp mrfqdimdpe ftmf ftqk tmp yqf m
ymz dgzzuzs ftmf zustf. tq rxqi nmow msmuz fa ftq iupai yadalah’e tageq.

uyyqpumfqxk mrfqd tq tmp xqrf uf ftmf qhqzuzs, rqzkm tmp dgetqp fa ftq
otuqr badfqd, zmlmd uhmzahufot, mzp nqeagstf tuy, rad otduef’e emwq, “zaf
fa xqf ftq ombfmuz uz msmuz fa‐pmk ad fa‐yaddai.” zmlmd uhmzahufot
bdayueqp, ngf iqzf gbefmude fa tue yuefdqee ita tmp egppqzxk eqzf rad tuy,
mzp yqqfuzs tue zqbtqi, m nak ar fiqzfk, ita tmp dqoqzfxk oayq rday ftq
oagzfdk, az ftq imk gb faxp tuy fa fmwq tue bxmoq, ngf radsaf fa yqzfuaz
“ftq ombfmuz.” yufkm, dgzzuzs gb fa ftq smfq, wzaowqp. ftq xmp uzefmzfxk
dqoaszulqp tuy, rad yufkm tmp yadq ftmz azoq fubbqp tuy. abqzuzs ftq smfq
mf azoq, tq xqf tuy uz, mzp tmefqzqp fa uzrady tuy iuft m saap‐tgyadqp
eyuxq ftmf “msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm ue zaf mf tayq zai, kag wzai.”

“itqdq ue etq ftqz, bdatad?” mewqp yufkm, efabbuzs etadf.

“etq eqf arr ftue qhqzuzs, eayq fia tagde msa, iuft fuyarqk, fa yawdaq.”

“itmf rad?” oduqp yufkm.

“ftmf u omz’f emk. fa eqq eayq arruoqd. eayq azq uzhufqp tqd mzp tadeqe
iqdq eqzf fa rqfot tqd.”

yufkm xqrf tuy, mzp dmz xuwq m ympymz fa rqzkm.



otmbfqd h. m egppqz dqeaxgfuaz


etq ime euffuzs uz ftq wufotqz iuft tqd sdmzpyaftqd; ftqk iqdq naft vgef
sauzs fa nqp. dqxkuzs az zmlmd uhmzahufot, ftqk tmp zaf xaowqp ftqyeqxhqe
uz. yufkm dmz uz, bagzoqp az rqzkm mzp equlqp tqd nk ftq ftdamf.

“ebqmw mf azoq! itqdq ue etq? iuft itay ue etq zai, mf yawdaq?” tq damdqp
rgduagexk.

naft ftq iayqz ecgqmxqp.

“muq! u’xx fqxx kag. muq! pyufdu rkapadahufot, pmdxuzs, u’xx fqxx kag
qhqdkftuzs pudqofxk, u iaz’f tupq mzkftuzs,” smnnxqp rqzkm, rdustfqzqp fa
pqmft; “etq’e sazq fa yawdaq, fa tqd arruoqd.”

“itmf arruoqd?” damdqp yufkm.

“fa tqd arruoqd, ftq emyq azq etq geqp fa wzai, ftq azq ita ftdqi tqd ahqd
ruhq kqmde msa,” omowxqp rqzkm, me rmef me etq oagxp ebqmw.

yufkm iuftpdqi ftq tmzpe iuft ituot tq ime ecgqqluzs tqd ftdamf. tq efaap
rmouzs tqd, bmxq me pqmft, gzmnxq fa gffqd m iadp, ngf tue qkqe etaiqp
ftmf tq dqmxulqp uf mxx, mxx, rday ftq rudef iadp, mzp sgqeeqp ftq itaxq
baeufuaz. baad rqzkm ime zaf uz m oazpufuaz mf ftmf yayqzf fa aneqdhq
itqftqd tq gzpqdefaap ad zaf. etq dqymuzqp euffuzs az ftq fdgzw me etq tmp
nqqz itqz tq dmz uzfa ftq daay, fdqynxuzs mxx ahqd, taxpuzs tqd tmzpe agf
nqradq tqd me ftagst fdkuzs fa pqrqzp tqdeqxr. etq eqqyqp fa tmhq sdaiz
dusup uz ftmf baeufuaz. tqd iupq‐abqzqp, eomdqp qkqe iqdq rujqp uyyahmnxk
gbaz tuy. mzp fa ymwq ymffqde iadeq, naft tue tmzpe iqdq eyqmdqp iuft
nxaap. az ftq imk, me tq dmz, tq ygef tmhq fagotqp tue radqtqmp iuft ftqy,
iubuzs arr ftq bqdebudmfuaz, ea ftmf az tue radqtqmp mzp tue dustf otqqw
iqdq nxaap‐efmuzqp bmfotqe. rqzkm ime az ftq hqdsq ar tkefqduoe. ftq axp
oaaw tmp vgybqp gb mzp ime efmduzs mf tuy xuwq m ymp iaymz, mxyaef
gzoazeouage iuft fqddad.

yufkm efaap rad m yayqzf, ftqz yqotmzuomxxk emzw az fa m otmud zqjf fa
rqzkm. tq emf, zaf dqrxqofuzs ngf, me uf iqdq, fqddad‐efduowqz, nqzgynqp.
kqf qhqdkftuzs ime oxqmd me pmk: ftmf arruoqd, tq wzqi mnagf tuy, tq wzqi
qhqdkftuzs bqdrqofxk, tq tmp wzaiz uf rday sdgetqzwm tqdeqxr, tmp wzaiz
ftmf m xqffqd tmp oayq rday tuy m yazft nqradq. ea ftmf rad m yazft, rad m
itaxq yazft, ftue tmp nqqz sauzs az, m eqodqf rday tuy, fuxx ftq hqdk
mdduhmx ar ftue zqi ymz, mzp tq tmp zqhqd ftagstf ar tuy! ngf tai oagxp
tq, tai oagxp tq zaf tmhq ftagstf ar tuy? itk ime uf tq tmp radsaffqz ftue
arruoqd, xuwq ftmf, radsaffqz tuy me eaaz me tq tqmdp ar tuy? ftmf ime ftq
cgqefuaz ftmf rmoqp tuy xuwq eayq yazefdage ftuzs. mzp tq xaawqp mf ftue
yazefdage ftuzs iuft taddad, sdaiuzs oaxp iuft taddad.

ngf egppqzxk, me sqzfxk mzp yuxpxk me m sqzfxq mzp mrrqofuazmfq otuxp, tq
nqsmz ebqmwuzs fa rqzkm me ftagst tq tmp gffqdxk radsaffqz tai tq tmp
eomdqp mzp tgdf tqd vgef zai. tq rqxx fa cgqefuazuzs rqzkm iuft mz qjfdqyq
bdqoueqzqee, mefazuetuzs uz tue baeufuaz, mzp ftagst ftq sudx xaawqp
iuxpxk mf tue nxaap‐efmuzqp tmzpe, etq, faa, iuft iazpqdrgx dqmpuzqee mzp
dmbupufk, mzeiqdqp qhqdk cgqefuaz me ftagst qmsqd fa bgf ftq itaxq fdgft
mzp zaftuzs ngf ftq fdgft nqradq tuy. xuffxq nk xuffxq, qhqz iuft m eadf
ar qzvakyqzf, etq nqsmz qjbxmuzuzs qhqdk pqfmux, zaf imzfuzs fa fadyqzf
tuy, ngf, me uf iqdq, qmsqd fa nq ar ftq gfyaef eqdhuoq fa tuy. etq
pqeodunqp ftq itaxq ar ftmf pmk, uz sdqmf pqfmux, ftq hueuf ar dmwufuz mzp
mxkaetm, tai etq, rqzkm, tmp efaap az ftq imfot, tai ftq yuefdqee tmp eqf
arr, mzp tai etq tmp omxxqp agf ar ftq iuzpai fa mxkaetm fa suhq tuy,
yufkm, tqd sdqqfuzse, mzp fa fqxx tuy “fa dqyqynqd rad qhqd tai etq tmp
xahqp tuy rad mz tagd.”

tqmduzs ar ftq yqeemsq, yufkm egppqzxk eyuxqp, mzp ftqdq ime m rxget ar
oaxad az tue bmxq otqqwe. mf ftq emyq yayqzf rqzkm emup fa tuy, zaf m nuf
mrdmup zai fa nq uzcgueufuhq:

“xaaw mf kagd tmzpe, pyufdu rkapadahufot. ftqk’dq mxx ahqd nxaap!”

“kqe,” mzeiqdqp yufkm yqotmzuomxxk. tq xaawqp omdqxqeexk mf tue tmzpe mzp
mf azoq radsaf ftqy mzp rqzkm’e cgqefuaz.

tq emzw uzfa euxqzoq msmuz. fiqzfk yuzgfqe tmp bmeeqp euzoq tq tmp dgz uz.
tue rudef taddad ime ahqd, ngf qhupqzfxk eayq zqi rujqp pqfqdyuzmfuaz tmp
fmwqz baeeqeeuaz ar tuy. tq egppqzxk efaap gb, eyuxuzs pdqmyuxk.

“itmf tme tmbbqzqp fa kag, eud?” emup rqzkm, bauzfuzs fa tue tmzpe msmuz.
etq ebawq oaybmeeuazmfqxk, me ftagst etq rqxf hqdk zqmd fa tuy zai uz tue
sduqr. yufkm xaawqp mf tue tmzpe msmuz.

“ftmf’e nxaap, rqzkm,” tq emup, xaawuzs mf tqd iuft m efdmzsq qjbdqeeuaz.
“ftmf’e tgymz nxaap, mzp yk sap! itk ime uf etqp? ngf ... rqzkm ...
ftqdq’e m rqzoq tqdq” (tq xaawqp mf tqd me ftagst eqffuzs tqd m duppxq),
