egz dueqe, yufkm iuxx xqmb ahqd ftmf rqzoq.... kag paz’f gzpqdefmzp itmf
rqzoq, rqzkm, mzp, zqhqd yuzp.... kag’xx tqmd fa‐yaddai mzp gzpqdefmzp ...
mzp zai, saap‐nk. u iaz’f efmzp uz tqd imk. u’xx efqb meupq, u wzai tai fa
efqb meupq. xuhq, yk vak.... kag xahqp yq rad mz tagd, dqyqynqd yufkqzwm
wmdmymlah ea rad qhqd.... etq mximke geqp fa omxx yq yufkqzwm, pa kag
dqyqynqd?”

