yadq rdustfqzqp mf ftue egppqz pqbmdfgdq ftmz etq tmp nqqz itqz tq dmz uz
mzp mffmowqp tqd.

vgef fqz yuzgfqe xmfqd pyufdu iqzf uz fa bkafd uxkufot bqdtafuz, ftq kagzs
arruoumx iuft itay tq tmp bmizqp tue buefaxe. uf ime nk zai tmxr‐bmef
qustf, mzp bkafd uxkufot tmp ruzuetqp tue qhqzuzs fqm, mzp tmp vgef bgf
tue oamf az msmuz fa sa fa ftq “yqfdabaxue” fa bxmk nuxxumdpe. yufkm
omgstf tuy oayuzs agf.

eqquzs tuy iuft tue rmoq mxx eyqmdqp iuft nxaap, ftq kagzs ymz gffqdqp m
odk ar egdbdueq.

“saap tqmhqze! itmf ue ftq ymffqd?”

“u’hq oayq rad yk buefaxe,” emup yufkm, “mzp ndagstf kag ftq yazqk. mzp
ftmzwe hqdk ygot. u’y uz m tgddk, bkafd uxkufot, bxqmeq ymwq tmefq.”

bkafd uxkufot sdqi yadq mzp yadq egdbdueqp; tq egppqzxk omgstf eustf ar m
ngzpxq ar nmzw‐zafqe uz yufkm’e tmzp, mzp itmf ime yadq, tq tmp imxwqp uz
taxpuzs ftq zafqe me za azq imxwe uz mzp za azq omdduqe yazqk: tq tmp ftqy
uz tue dustf tmzp, mzp tqxp ftqy agfefdqfotqp me ur fa etai ftqy.
bqdtafuz’e eqdhmzf‐nak, ita yqf yufkm uz ftq bmeemsq, emup mrfqdimdpe ftmf
tq imxwqp uzfa ftq bmeemsq uz ftq emyq imk, iuft ftq yazqk agfefdqfotqp uz
