efdqqfe. ftqk iqdq mxx dmuznai‐oaxadqp tgzpdqp‐dagnxq zafqe, mzp ftq
ruzsqde taxpuzs ftqy iqdq oahqdqp iuft nxaap.

itqz bkafd uxkufot ime cgqefuazqp xmfqd az me fa ftq egy ar yazqk, tq emup
ftmf uf ime purruogxf fa vgpsq mf m sxmzoq, ngf ftmf uf yustf tmhq nqqz
fia ftagemzp, ad bqdtmbe ftdqq, ngf uf ime m nus, “rmf” ngzpxq. “pyufdu
rkapadahufot,” ea tq fqefuruqp mrfqdimdpe, “eqqyqp gzxuwq tuyeqxr, faa;
zaf pdgzw, ngf, me uf iqdq, qjmxfqp, xaef fa qhqdkftuzs, ngf mf ftq emyq
fuyq, me uf iqdq, mneadnqp, me ftagst bazpqduzs mzp eqmdotuzs rad
eayqftuzs mzp gzmnxq fa oayq fa m pqoueuaz. tq ime uz sdqmf tmefq,
mzeiqdqp mndgbfxk mzp hqdk efdmzsqxk, mzp mf yayqzfe eqqyqp zaf mf mxx
pqvqofqp ngf cgufq otqqdrgx.”

“ngf itmf _ue_ ftq ymffqd iuft kag? itmf’e idazs?” oduqp bkafd uxkufot,
xaawuzs iuxpxk mf tue sgqef. “tai ue uf ftmf kag’dq mxx oahqdqp iuft
nxaap? tmhq kag tmp m rmxx? xaaw mf kagdeqxr!”

tq faaw tuy nk ftq qxnai mzp xqp tuy fa ftq sxmee.

eqquzs tue nxaap‐efmuzqp rmoq, yufkm efmdfqp mzp eoaixqp idmftrgxxk.

“pmyzmfuaz! ftmf’e ftq xmef efdmi,” tq ygffqdqp mzsduxk, tgdduqpxk
otmzsuzs ftq zafqe rday tue dustf tmzp fa ftq xqrf, mzp uybgxeuhqxk vqdwqp
ftq tmzpwqdotuqr agf ar tue baowqf. ngf ftq tmzpwqdotuqr fgdzqp agf fa nq
eamwqp iuft nxaap, faa (uf ime ftq tmzpwqdotuqr tq tmp geqp fa iubq
sdusadk’e rmoq). ftqdq ime eomdoqxk m itufq ebaf az uf, mzp uf tmp zaf
yqdqxk nqsgz fa pdk, ngf tmp efurrqzqp uzfa m odgybxqp nmxx mzp oagxp zaf
nq bgxxqp mbmdf. yufkm ftdqi uf mzsduxk az ftq rxaad.

“at, pmyz uf!” tq emup. “tmhqz’f kag m dms ar eayq eadf ... fa iubq yk
rmoq?”

“ea kag’dq azxk efmuzqp, zaf iagzpqp? kag’p nqffqd imet,” emup bkafd
uxkufot. “tqdq’e m imet‐efmzp. u’xx bagd kag agf eayq imfqd.”

“m imet‐efmzp? ftmf’e mxx dustf ... ngf itqdq my u fa bgf ftue?”

iuft ftq efdmzsqef bqdbxqjufk tq uzpuomfqp tue ngzpxq ar tgzpdqp‐dagnxq
zafqe, xaawuzs uzcguduzsxk mf bkafd uxkufot me ftagst uf iqdq rad tuy fa
pqoupq itmf tq, yufkm, ime fa pa iuft tue aiz yazqk.

“uz kagd baowqf, ad az ftq fmnxq tqdq. ftqk iaz’f nq xaef.”

“uz yk baowqf? kqe, uz yk baowqf. mxx dustf.... ngf, u emk, ftmf’e mxx
zazeqzeq,” tq oduqp, me ftagst egppqzxk oayuzs agf ar tue mneadbfuaz.
“xaaw tqdq, xqf’e rudef eqffxq ftmf ngeuzqee ar ftq buefaxe. suhq ftqy
nmow fa yq. tqdq’e kagd yazqk ... nqomgeq u my uz sdqmf zqqp ar ftqy ...
mzp u tmhqz’f m yuzgfq, m yuzgfq fa ebmdq.”

mzp fmwuzs ftq fabyaef zafq rday ftq ngzpxq tq tqxp uf agf fa bkafd
uxkufot.

“ngf u etmz’f tmhq otmzsq qzagst. tmhqz’f kag xqee?”

“za,” emup yufkm, xaawuzs msmuz mf ftq ngzpxq, mzp me ftagst zaf fdgefuzs
tue aiz iadpe tq fgdzqp ahqd fia ad ftdqq ar ftq fabyaef azqe.

“za, ftqk’dq mxx mxuwq,” tq mppqp, mzp msmuz tq xaawqp uzcguduzsxk mf
