“tai tmhq kag sdaiz ea duot?” ftq xmffqd mewqp. “imuf, u’xx eqzp yk nak fa
bxafzuwah’e, ftqk oxaeq xmfq—fa eqq ur ftqk iaz’f otmzsq uf. tqdq, yuetm!”
tq omxxqp uzfa ftq bmeemsq.

“fa bxafzuwah’e etab—rudef‐dmfq!” oduqp yufkm, me ftagst efdgow nk mz
upqm. “yuetm,” tq fgdzqp fa ftq nak me tq omyq uz, “xaaw tqdq, dgz fa
bxafzuwah’e mzp fqxx ftqy ftmf pyufdu rkapadahufot eqzpe tue sdqqfuzse,
mzp iuxx nq ftqdq pudqofxk.... ngf xuefqz, xuefqz, fqxx ftqy fa tmhq
otmybmszq, ftdqq palqz naffxqe, dqmpk nqradq u oayq, mzp bmowqp me uf ime
fa fmwq fa yawdaq. u faaw ragd palqz iuft yq ftqz,” tq mppqp (egppqzxk
mppdqeeuzs bkafd uxkufot); “ftqk wzai mxx mnagf uf, paz’f kag fdagnxq,
yuetm,” tq fgdzqp msmuz fa ftq nak. “efmk, xuefqz; fqxx ftqy fa bgf uz
otqqeq, efdmengds buqe, eyawqp ruet, tmy, omhumdq, mzp qhqdkftuzs,
qhqdkftuzs ftqk’hq saf, gb fa m tgzpdqp dagnxqe, ad m tgzpdqp mzp fiqzfk
me nqradq.... ngf imuf: paz’f xqf ftqy radsqf pqeeqdf, eiqqfe, bqmde,
imfqd‐yqxaze, fia ad ftdqq ad ragd—za, azq yqxaz’e qzagst, mzp otaoaxmfq,
omzpk, farrqq, razpmzfe; uz rmof, qhqdkftuzs u faaw fa yawdaq nqradq,
ftdqq tgzpdqp dagnxqe’ iadft iuft ftq otmybmszq ... xqf uf nq vgef ftq
emyq msmuz. mzp dqyqynqd, yuetm, ur kag mdq omxxqp yuetm—tue zmyq ue
yuetm, uez’f uf?” tq fgdzqp fa bkafd uxkufot msmuz.

“imuf m yuzgfq,” bdafd uxkufot uzfqdhqzqp, xuefqzuzs mzp imfotuzs tuy
gzqmeuxk, “kag’p nqffqd sa kagdeqxr mzp fqxx ftqy. tq’xx ygppxq uf.”

“tq iuxx, u eqq tq iuxx! qt, yuetm! itk, u ime sauzs fa wuee kag rad ftq
oayyueeuaz.... ur kag paz’f ymwq m yuefmwq, ftqdq’e fqz dagnxqe rad kag,
