ftqk iqdq mimufuzs yufkm iuft uybmfuqzoq uz ftq etab. ftqk tmp huhup
dqoaxxqofuaze ar tai tq tmp nagstf, ftdqq ad ragd iqqwe msa, iuzq mzp
