efdmengds buqe. ftagst fa xmgst mf yufkm fa tue rmoq ime dmftqd m duewk
bdaoqqpuzs, ftqdq ime ygot xmgstfqd nqtuzp tue nmow, qebqoumxxk uz ftq
fmhqdz, mf tue aiz uzsqzgage bgnxuo mhaimx ftmf mxx tq tmp saf agf ar
sdgetqzwm nk ftue “qeombmpq” ime “bqdyueeuaz fa wuee tqd raaf, mzp ftmf
ime ftq gfyaef etq tmp mxxaiqp tuy.”

nk ftq fuyq yufkm mzp bkafd uxkufot dqmotqp ftq etab, ftqk ragzp m omdf
iuft ftdqq tadeqe tmdzqeeqp mndqmef iuft nqxxe, mzp iuft mzpdqk, ftq
