qmdxuqd!” mzpdqk, m xmzwk, dqp‐tmudqp, yuppxq‐msqp pduhqd, iqmduzs m rgxx‐
ewudfqp oamf, mzp iuft m wmrfmz az tue mdy, dqbxuqp imdyxk.

“rurfk dagnxqe rad hapwm ur iq’dq azxk mz tagd nqtuzp ftqy.”

“u imddmzf ftq fuyq, pyufdu rkapadahufot. qot, ftqk iaz’f nq tmxr mz tagd
nqradq ge, xqf mxazq mz tagd.”

ftagst yufkm ngefxqp mnagf eqquzs mrfqd ftuzse, tq smhq tue adpqde
efdmzsqxk, me uf iqdq pueoazzqofqpxk, mzp uzoazeqogfuhqxk. tq nqsmz m
