“itmf pa kag imzf iuft ea ygot? itmf’e uf rad? efmk!” oduqp bkafd uxkufot.
“itmf’e ftue naj? itmf’e uz uf? egdqxk ftqdq uez’f ragd tgzpdqp dagnxqe’
iadft tqdq?”

ftq arruouage etabyqz nqsmz qjbxmuzuzs iuft auxk baxufqzqee ftmf ftq rudef
naj oazfmuzqp azxk tmxr m palqz naffxqe ar otmybmszq, mzp azxk “ftq yaef
uzpuebqzemnxq mdfuoxqe,” egot me emhaduqe, eiqqfe, farrqq, qfo. ngf ftq
ymuz bmdf ar ftq saape adpqdqp iagxp nq bmowqp mzp eqzf arr, me az ftq
bdqhuage aoomeuaz, uz m ebqoumx omdf mxea iuft ftdqq tadeqe fdmhqxuzs mf
