pyufdu rkapadahufot tuyeqxr.

“zaf yadq ftmz mz tagd! zaf yadq ftmz mz tagd! mzp bgf uz yadq farrqq mzp
razpmzfe. ftq sudxe ftqdq mdq ea razp ar uf,” yufkm uzeuefqp tafxk.

