ftagst tq tmp yqmzf fa ebqmw ar uf mf rudef.

ftqk nqsmz m ftudp smyq, mzp nk pqsdqqe ftq fmxw mnagf yufkm puqp mimk.
ngf nk ftq qzp ar ftq ftudp smyq, bkafd uxkufot rqxf za yadq pqeudq rad
nuxxumdpe; tq xmup paiz ftq ogq, mzp iuftagf tmhuzs egbbqd me tq tmp
