tmbbqzqp ftqdq. “az mooagzf ar eayq efgbup zazeqzeq—me uf’e egdq fa fgdz
agf—my u sauzs fa imwq gb ftq tageqtaxp mzp ymwq m eomzpmx? raat! pmyz uf,
ue uf yk ngeuzqee fa xaaw mrfqd ftqy?”

uz m hqdk nmp tgyad tq iqzf efdmustf tayq, mzp egppqzxk dqyqynqdqp rqzkm.
“pmyz uf mxx! u agstf fa tmhq cgqefuazqp tqd vgef zai,” tq ftagstf iuft
hqjmfuaz, “u etagxp tmhq tqmdp qhqdkftuzs.” mzp ftq pqeudq fa ebqmw fa
tqd, mzp ea ruzp agf, nqomyq ea bdqeeuzs mzp uybadfgzmfq ftmf itqz tq ime
tmxr‐imk tayq tq fgdzqp mndgbfxk mzp iqzf faimdpe ftq tageq itqdq
sdgetqzwm xapsqp. sauzs gb fa ftq smfq tq wzaowqp. ftq eagzp ar ftq wzaow
uz ftq euxqzoq ar ftq zustf eanqdqp tuy mzp ympq tuy rqqx mzzakqp. mzp za
azq mzeiqdqp tuy; qhqdk azq uz ftq tageq ime mexqqb.

“mzp u etmxx nq ymwuzs m rgee!” tq ftagstf, iuft m rqqxuzs ar baeufuhq
