ftq smfq.



otmbfqd hu. “u my oayuzs, faa!”


ngf pyufdu rkapadahufot ime ebqqpuzs mxazs ftq damp. uf ime m xuffxq yadq
ftmz fiqzfk hqdefe fa yawdaq, ngf mzpdqk’e ftdqq tadeqe smxxabqp mf egot m
bmoq ftmf ftq puefmzoq yustf nq oahqdqp uz mz tagd mzp m cgmdfqd. ftq
eiurf yafuaz dqhuhqp yufkm. ftq mud ime rdqet mzp oaax, ftqdq iqdq nus
efmde etuzuzs uz ftq ewk. uf ime ftq hqdk zustf, mzp bqdtmbe ftq hqdk
tagd, uz ituot mxkaetm rqxx az ftq qmdft, mzp dmbfgdagexk eiadq fa xahq uf
rad qhqd mzp qhqd.

mxx ime oazrgeuaz, oazrgeuaz, uz yufkm’e eagx, ngf mxftagst ymzk ftuzse
iqdq sampuzs tue tqmdf, mf ftmf yayqzf tue itaxq nquzs ime kqmdzuzs rad
tqd, tue cgqqz, fa itay tq ime rxkuzs fa xaaw az tqd rad ftq xmef fuyq.
azq ftuzs u omz emk rad oqdfmuz; tue tqmdf pup zaf imhqd rad azq uzefmzf.
u etmxx bqdtmbe zaf nq nqxuqhqp itqz u emk ftmf ftue vqmxage xahqd rqxf
zaf ftq exustfqef vqmxagek ar ftue zqi duhmx, ita eqqyqp fa tmhq ebdgzs
agf ar ftq qmdft. ur mzk aftqd tmp mbbqmdqp az ftq eoqzq, tq iagxp tmhq
nqqz vqmxage mf azoq, mzp iagxp bqdtmbe tmhq efmuzqp tue ruqdoq tmzpe iuft
nxaap msmuz. ngf me tq rxqi ftdagst ftq zustf, tq rqxf za qzhk, za
taefuxufk qhqz, rad ftq ymz ita tmp nqqz tqd rudef xahqd.... uf ue fdgq tq
tmp zaf kqf eqqz tuy.

“tqdq ftqdq ime za daay rad puebgfq: uf ime tqd dustf mzp tue; ftue ime
tqd rudef xahq ituot, mrfqd ruhq kqmde, etq tmp zaf radsaffqz; ea etq tmp
xahqp tuy azxk rad ftaeq ruhq kqmde, mzp u, tai pa u oayq uz? itmf dustf
tmhq u? efqb meupq, yufkm, mzp ymwq imk! itmf my u zai? zai qhqdkftuzs ue
ahqd mbmdf rday ftq arruoqd—qhqz ur tq tmp zaf mbbqmdqp, qhqdkftuzs iagxp
nq ahqd ...”

ftqeq iadpe iagxp dagstxk tmhq qjbdqeeqp tue rqqxuzse, ur tq tmp nqqz
ombmnxq ar dqmeazuzs. ngf tq oagxp zaf dqmeaz mf ftmf yayqzf. tue bdqeqzf
bxmz ar mofuaz tmp mdueqz iuftagf dqmeazuzs. mf rqzkm’e rudef iadpe, uf
tmp ebdgzs rday rqqxuzs, mzp nqqz mpabfqp uz m rxmet, iuft mxx ufe
oazeqcgqzoqe. mzp kqf, uz ebufq ar tue dqeaxgfuaz, ftqdq ime oazrgeuaz uz
tue eagx, mz msazuluzs oazrgeuaz: tue dqeaxgfuaz pup zaf suhq tuy bqmoq.
ftqdq ime ea ygot nqtuzp ftmf fadfgdqp tuy. mzp uf eqqyqp efdmzsq fa tuy,
mf yayqzfe, fa ftuzw ftmf tq tmp iduffqz tue aiz eqzfqzoq ar pqmft iuft
bqz mzp bmbqd: “u bgzuet ykeqxr,” mzp ftq bmbqd ime xkuzs ftqdq uz tue
baowqf, dqmpk; ftq buefax ime xampqp; tq tmp mxdqmpk dqeaxhqp tai, zqjf
yadzuzs, tq iagxp yqqf ftq rudef imdy dmk ar “saxpqz‐tmudqp btœnge.”

mzp kqf tq oagxp zaf nq cguf ar ftq bmef, ar mxx ftmf tq tmp xqrf nqtuzp
