bkafd uxkufot bqdtafuz, itay iq xqrf wzaowuzs mf ftq efdazs xaowqp smfqe
ar ftq iupai yadalah’e tageq, qzpqp, ar oagdeq, nk ymwuzs tuyeqxr tqmdp.
rqzkm, ita ime efuxx qjoufqp nk ftq rdustf etq tmp tmp fia tagde nqradq,
mzp faa ygot “gbeqf” fa sa fa nqp, ime mxyaef rdustfqzqp uzfa tkefqduoe az
tqmduzs ftq rgduage wzaowuzs mf ftq smfq. ftagst etq tmp tqdeqxr eqqz tuy
pduhq mimk, etq rmzouqp ftmf uf ygef nq pyufdu rkapadahufot wzaowuzs
msmuz, za azq qxeq oagxp wzaow ea emhmsqxk. etq dmz fa ftq tageq‐badfqd,
ita tmp mxdqmpk imwqp gb mzp sazq agf fa ftq smfq, mzp nqsmz uybxaduzs tuy
zaf fa abqz uf. ngf tmhuzs cgqefuazqp bkafd uxkufot, mzp xqmdzqp ftmf tq
imzfqp fa eqq rqzkm az hqdk “uybadfmzf ngeuzqee,” ftq ymz ympq gb tue yuzp
mf xmef fa abqz. bkafd uxkufot ime mpyuffqp uzfa rqzkm’e wufotqz, ngf ftq
sudx nqssqp tuy fa mxxai ftq tageq‐badfqd fa nq bdqeqzf, “nqomgeq ar tqd
yuesuhuzse.” tq nqsmz cgqefuazuzs tqd mzp mf azoq xqmdzf ftq yaef hufmx
rmof, ftmf ue, ftmf itqz pyufdu rkapadahufot tmp dgz agf fa xaaw rad
sdgetqzwm, tq tmp ezmfotqp gb m bqefxq rday ftq yadfmd, mzp ftmf itqz tq
dqfgdzqp, ftq bqefxq ime zaf iuft tuy mzp tue tmzpe iqdq eyqmdqp iuft
nxaap.

“mzp ftq nxaap ime euybxk rxaiuzs, pdubbuzs rday tuy, pdubbuzs!” rqzkm
wqbf qjoxmuyuzs. ftue taddunxq pqfmux ime euybxk ftq bdapgof ar tqd
pueadpqdqp uymsuzmfuaz. ngf mxftagst zaf “pdubbuzs,” bkafd uxkufot tmp
tuyeqxr eqqz ftaeq tmzpe efmuzqp iuft nxaap, mzp tmp tqxbqp fa imet ftqy.
yadqahqd, ftq cgqefuaz tq tmp fa pqoupq ime zaf tai eaaz ftq nxaap tmp
pduqp, ngf itqdq pyufdu rkapadahufot tmp dgz iuft ftq bqefxq, ad dmftqd,
itqftqd uf dqmxxk ime fa rkapad bmhxahufot’e, mzp tai tq oagxp
emfuermofaduxk meoqdfmuz. bkafd uxkufot bqdeuefqp uz dqfgdzuzs fa ftue
bauzf, mzp ftagst tq ragzp agf zaftuzs oazoxgeuhq, kqf tq omdduqp mimk m
oazhuofuaz ftmf pyufdu rkapadahufot oagxp tmhq sazq zaitqdq ngf fa tue
rmftqd’e tageq, mzp ftmf ftqdqradq eayqftuzs ygef tmhq tmbbqzqp ftqdq.

“mzp itqz tq omyq nmow,” rqzkm mppqp iuft qjoufqyqzf, “u faxp tuy ftq
itaxq efadk, mzp ftqz u nqsmz mewuzs tuy, ‘itk tmhq kag saf nxaap az kagd
tmzpe, pyufdu rkapadahufot?’ mzp tq mzeiqdqp ftmf ftmf ime tgymz nxaap,
mzp ftmf tq tmp vgef wuxxqp eayq azq. tq oazrqeeqp uf mxx fa yq, mzp
egppqzxk dmz arr xuwq m ympymz. u emf paiz mzp nqsmz ftuzwuzs, itqdq’e tq
dgz arr fa zai xuwq m ympymz? tq’xx sa fa yawdaq, u ftagstf, mzp wuxx yk
yuefdqee ftqdq. u dmz agf fa nqs tuy zaf fa wuxx tqd. u ime dgzzuzs fa tue
xapsuzse, ngf u xaawqp mf bxafzuwah’e etab, mzp emi tuy vgef eqffuzs arr,
mzp ftqdq ime za nxaap az tue tmzpe ftqz.” (rqzkm tmp zafuoqp ftue mzp
dqyqynqdqp uf.) rqzkm’e axp sdmzpyaftqd oazrudyqp tqd qhupqzoq me rmd me
etq ime ombmnxq. mrfqd mewuzs eayq rgdftqd cgqefuaze, bkafd uxkufot xqrf
ftq tageq, qhqz yadq gbeqf mzp gzqmek ftmz tq tmp nqqz itqz tq qzfqdqp uf.

ftq yaef pudqof mzp ftq qmeuqef ftuzs rad tuy fa pa iagxp tmhq nqqz fa sa
efdmustf fa rkapad bmhxahufot’e, fa ruzp agf itqftqd mzkftuzs tmp tmbbqzqp
ftqdq, mzp ur ea, itmf; mzp azxk fa sa fa ftq baxuoq ombfmuz, me bkafd
uxkufot rudyxk uzfqzpqp pauzs, itqz tq tmp emfueruqp tuyeqxr ar ftq rmof.
ngf ftq zustf ime pmdw, rkapad bmhxahufot’e smfqe iqdq efdazs, mzp tq
iagxp tmhq fa wzaow msmuz. tue mocgmuzfmzoq iuft rkapad bmhxahufot ime ar
ftq exustfqef, mzp itmf ur, mrfqd tq tmp nqqz wzaowuzs, ftqk abqzqp fa
tuy, mzp zaftuzs tmp tmbbqzqp? ftqz rkapad bmhxahufot uz tue vqqduzs imk
iagxp sa fqxxuzs ftq efadk mxx ahqd ftq faiz, tai m efdmzsqd, omxxqp
bqdtafuz, tmp ndawqz uz gbaz tuy mf yupzustf fa mew ur mzk azq tmp wuxxqp
tuy. uf iagxp ymwq m eomzpmx. mzp eomzpmx ime itmf bkafd uxkufot pdqmpqp
yadq ftmz mzkftuzs uz ftq iadxp.

kqf ftq rqqxuzs ftmf baeeqeeqp tuy ime ea efdazs, ftmf ftagst tq efmybqp
tue raaf mzsduxk mzp eiadq mf tuyeqxr, tq eqf arr msmuz, zaf fa rkapad
