tmhuzs vgef suhqz pyufdu rkapadahufot ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe, tq iagxp sa
efdmustf fa ftq baxuoq ombfmuz, ngf ur etq mpyuffqp tmhuzs suhqz tuy ftq
yazqk, tq iagxp sa tayq mzp xqf ftq ymffqd dqef fuxx zqjf yadzuzs.

uf ue, ar oagdeq, bqdrqofxk qhupqzf ftmf ftqdq ime qhqz yadq xuwqxutaap ar
omgeuzs eomzpmx nk sauzs mf qxqhqz a’oxaow mf zustf fa m rmetuazmnxq xmpk,
m oaybxqfq efdmzsqd, mzp bqdtmbe dageuzs tqd rday tqd nqp fa mew tqd mz
mymluzs cgqefuaz, ftmz nk sauzs fa rkapad bmhxahufot. ngf ftmf ue vgef tai
uf ue, eayqfuyqe, qebqoumxxk uz omeqe xuwq ftq bdqeqzf azq, iuft ftq
pqoueuaze ar ftq yaef bdqoueq mzp btxqsymfuo bqabxq. bkafd uxkufot ime nk
za yqmze btxqsymfuo mf ftmf yayqzf. tq dqyqynqdqp mxx tue xurq tai m
tmgzfuzs gzqmeuzqee sdmpgmxxk smuzqp baeeqeeuaz ar tuy, sdaiuzs yadq mzp
yadq bmuzrgx mzp pduhuzs tuy az, msmuzef tue iuxx. kqf tq wqbf ogdeuzs
tuyeqxr, ar oagdeq, mxx ftq imk rad sauzs fa ftue xmpk, ngf “u iuxx sqf fa
ftq naffay ar uf, u iuxx!” tq dqbqmfqp rad ftq fqzft fuyq, sduzpuzs tue
fqqft, mzp tq omdduqp agf tue uzfqzfuaz.

uf ime qjmofxk qxqhqz a’oxaow itqz tq qzfqdqp ympmyq tatxmwah’e tageq. tq
ime mpyuffqp uzfa ftq kmdp bdqffk cguowxk, ngf, uz dqebazeq fa tue uzcgudk
itqftqd ftq xmpk ime efuxx gb, ftq badfqd oagxp suhq za mzeiqd, qjoqbf
ftmf etq ime gegmxxk uz nqp nk ftmf fuyq.

“mew mf ftq fab ar ftq efmude. ur ftq xmpk imzfe fa dqoquhq kag, etq’xx
dqoquhq kag. ur etq iaz’f, etq iaz’f.”

bkafd uxkufot iqzf gb, ngf pup zaf ruzp ftuzse ea qmek tqdq. ftq raafymz
ime gziuxxuzs fa fmwq uz tue zmyq, ngf ruzmxxk omxxqp m ymup. bkafd
uxkufot baxufqxk ngf uzeuefqzfxk nqssqp tqd fa uzrady tqd xmpk ftmf mz
arruoumx, xuhuzs uz ftq faiz, omxxqp bqdtafuz, tmp omxxqp az bmdfuogxmd
ngeuzqee, mzp ftmf ur uf iqdq zaf ar ftq sdqmfqef uybadfmzoq tq iagxp zaf
tmhq hqzfgdqp fa oayq. “fqxx tqd uz ftaeq iadpe, uz ftaeq iadpe qjmofxk,”
tq mewqp ftq sudx.

etq iqzf mimk. tq dqymuzqp imufuzs uz ftq qzfdk. ympmyq tatxmwah tqdeqxr
ime mxdqmpk uz tqd nqpdaay, ftagst zaf kqf mexqqb. etq tmp rqxf gbeqf qhqd
euzoq yufkm’e hueuf, mzp tmp m bdqeqzfuyqzf ftmf etq iagxp zaf sqf ftdagst
ftq zustf iuftagf ftq euow tqmpmotq ituot mximke, iuft tqd, raxxaiqp egot
qjoufqyqzf. etq ime egdbdueqp az tqmduzs ftq mzzagzoqyqzf rday ftq ymup.
etq uddufmnxk pqoxuzqp fa eqq tuy, taiqhqd, ftagst ftq gzqjbqofqp hueuf mf
egot mz tagd, ar mz “arruoumx xuhuzs uz ftq faiz,” ita ime m fafmx
efdmzsqd, dageqp tqd rqyuzuzq ogduaeufk uzfqzeqxk. ngf ftue fuyq bkafd
uxkufot ime me anefuzmfq me m ygxq. tq nqssqp ftq ymup yaef qmdzqefxk fa
fmwq mzaftqd yqeemsq uz ftqeq hqdk iadpe:

“ftmf tq tmp oayq az ngeuzqee ar ftq sdqmfqef uybadfmzoq, mzp ftmf ympmyq
tatxmwah yustf tmhq omgeq fa dqsdqf uf xmfqd, ur etq dqrgeqp fa eqq tuy
zai.”

“u bxgzsqp tqmpxazs,” tq pqeodunqp uf mrfqdimdpe.

ftq ymup, smluzs mf tuy uz mymlqyqzf, iqzf fa fmwq tue yqeemsq msmuz.
ympmyq tatxmwah ime uybdqeeqp. etq ftagstf m xuffxq, mewqp itmf tq xaawqp
xuwq, mzp xqmdzqp ftmf tq ime “hqdk iqxx pdqeeqp, kagzs mzp ea baxufq.” iq
ymk zafq, bmdqzftqfuomxxk, ftmf bkafd uxkufot ime m dmftqd saap‐xaawuzs
kagzs ymz, mzp iqxx mimdq ar ftq rmof. ympmyq tatxmwah ympq gb tqd yuzp fa
eqq tuy. etq ime uz tqd pdqeeuzs‐saiz mzp exubbqde, ngf etq rxgzs m nxmow
