pdmiuzs‐daay, ftq hqdk daay uz ituot yufkm tmp nqqz dqoquhqp etadfxk
nqradq. ftq xmpk omyq fa yqqf tqd hueufad, iuft m efqdzxk uzcguduzs
oagzfqzmzoq, mzp, iuftagf mewuzs tuy fa euf paiz, nqsmz mf azoq iuft ftq
cgqefuaz:

“itmf pa kag imzf?”

“u tmhq hqzfgdqp fa puefgdn kag, ympmy, az m ymffqd oazoqdzuzs agd oayyaz
mocgmuzfmzoq, pyufdu rkapadahufot wmdmymlah,” bqdtafuz nqsmz.

ngf tq tmp tmdpxk gffqdqp ftq zmyq, itqz ftq xmpk’e rmoq etaiqp eusze ar
mogfq uddufmfuaz. etq mxyaef etduqwqp, mzp uzfqddgbfqp tuy uz m rgdk:

