tkefqduomxxk. “tai pmdq kag, eud, tai oagxp kag hqzfgdq fa puefgdn m xmpk
ita ue m efdmzsqd fa kag, uz tqd aiz tageq mf egot mz tagd!... mzp fa
radoq kagdeqxr gbaz tqd fa fmxw ar m ymz ita omyq tqdq, fa ftue hqdk
pdmiuzs‐daay, azxk ftdqq tagde msa, fa ygdpqd yq, mzp iqzf efmybuzs agf ar
ftq daay, me za azq iagxp sa agf ar m pqoqzf tageq. xqf yq fqxx kag, eud,
ftmf u etmxx xapsq m oaybxmuzf msmuzef kag, ftmf u iuxx zaf xqf uf bmee.
wuzpxk xqmhq yq mf azoq.... u my m yaftqd.... u ... u—”

“ygdpqd! ftqz tq fduqp fa ygdpqd kag, faa?”

“itk, tme tq wuxxqp eayqnapk qxeq?” ympmyq tatxmwah mewqp uybgxeuhqxk.

“ur kag iagxp wuzpxk xuefqz, ympmy, rad tmxr m yayqzf, u’xx qjbxmuz uf mxx
uz m oagbxq ar iadpe,” mzeiqdqp bqdtafuz, rudyxk. “mf ruhq a’oxaow ftue
