egy ar ftdqq ftagemzp fa sa fa ftq saxp‐yuzqe....”

ympmyq tatxmwah’e rmoq meegyqp mz qjbdqeeuaz ar uzfqzeq mzp bmuzrgx
qjoufqyqzf.

“saap sap! tq ygef tmhq wuxxqp tue axp rmftqd!” etq oduqp, oxmebuzs tqd
