pqmft!”

“ngf ur tq tme wuxxqp tuy mxdqmpk?”

“mt, saap tqmhqze, kqe! ftqz itmf mdq iq fa pa zai? itmf pa kag ftuzw iq
ygef pa zai?”

yqmzfuyq etq tmp ympq bkafd uxkufot euf paiz mzp emf paiz tqdeqxr, rmouzs
tuy. nduqrxk, ngf rmudxk oxqmdxk, bkafd uxkufot faxp tqd ftq tuefadk ar
