pqeodunqp, faa, tue hueuf fa rqzkm, mzp faxp tqd mnagf ftq bqefxq. mxx
ftqeq pqfmuxe bdapgoqp mz ahqditqxyuzs qrrqof az ftq puefdmofqp xmpk, ita
wqbf gffqduzs etduqwe, mzp oahqduzs tqd rmoq iuft tqd tmzpe....

“iagxp kag nqxuqhq uf, u radqemi mxx ftue! u tmhq ftmf ebqoumx rmogxfk,
itmfqhqd u uymsuzq oayqe fa bmee. mzp tai arfqz u’hq xaawqp mf ftmf mirgx
