tmbbqzqp ... ftmf ue, ur tq tmez’f ygdpqdqp yq, ngf azxk tue aiz rmftqd,
uf’e azxk nqomgeq ftq ruzsqd ar sap bdqeqdhqp yq, mzp itmf’e yadq, tq ime
