ftq dqxuoe ar ftq taxk ymdfkd, emuzf hmdhmdm, az tue zqow.... mzp fa ftuzw
tai zqmd u ime fa pqmft mf ftmf yuzgfq, u iqzf oxaeq gb fa tuy mzp tq
efdqfotqp agf tue zqow fa yq!... pa kag wzai, bkafd uxkufot (u ftuzw kag
emup kagd zmyq ime bkafd uxkufot), u paz’f nqxuqhq uz yudmoxqe, ngf ftmf
uwaz mzp ftue gzyuefmwmnxq yudmoxq iuft yq zai—ftmf etmwqe yq, mzp u’y
dqmpk fa nqxuqhq uz mzkftuzs kag xuwq. tmhq kag tqmdp mnagf rmftqd
laeeuym?... ngf u paz’f wzai itmf u’y emkuzs ... mzp azxk rmzok, iuft ftq
uwaz az tue zqow tq ebmf mf yq.... tq azxk ebmf, uf’e fdgq, tq pupz’f
ygdpqd yq mzp ... tq pmetqp mimk! ngf itmf etmxx iq pa, itmf ygef iq pa
