tai iqxx kag’hq ftagstf ar qhqdkftuzs! u etagxp zqhqd tmhq ftagstf ar uf
uz kagd bxmoq!”

“qebqoumxxk me u wzai ftq baxuoq ombfmuz hqdk iqxx, faa,” aneqdhqp bkafd
