saap‐nk mzp sa mimk.

“mzp nq egdq, nq egdq,” etq bdmffxqp az, “fa oayq nmow mzp fqxx yq itmf
kag eqq ftqdq, mzp itmf kag ruzp agf ... itmf oayqe fa xustf ... tai
ftqk’xx fdk tuy ... mzp itmf tq’e oazpqyzqp fa.... fqxx yq, iq tmhq za
ombufmx bgzuetyqzf, tmhq iq? ngf nq egdq fa oayq, qhqz ur uf’e mf ftdqq
a’oxaow mf zustf, mf ragd, mf tmxr‐bmef ragd.... fqxx ftqy fa imwq yq, fa
