exqqb! ngf imuf, tmpz’f u nqffqd oayq iuft kag?”

“z—za. ngf ur kag iagxp idufq ftdqq xuzqe iuft kagd aiz tmzp, efmfuzs ftmf
kag pup zaf suhq pyufdu rkapadahufot yazqk, uf yustf, bqdtmbe, nq ar geq
... uz omeq uf’e zqqpqp....”

“fa nq egdq!” ympmyq tatxmwah ewubbqp, pqxustfqp, fa tqd ngdqmg. “mzp kag
wzai u’y euybxk efdgow, mymlqp mf kagd dqeagdoqrgxzqee, kagd saap eqzeq uz
egot mrrmude. mdq kag uz ftq eqdhuoq tqdq? u’y pqxustfqp fa ftuzw ftmf
kag’dq uz ftq eqdhuoq tqdq!”

mzp efuxx ebqmwuzs, etq eodunnxqp az tmxr m etqqf ar zafqbmbqd ftq
raxxaiuzs xuzqe:


    u’hq zqhqd uz yk xurq xqzf fa ftmf gztmbbk ymz, pyufdu
    rkapadahufot wmdmymlah (rad, uz ebufq ar mxx, tq ue gztmbbk),
    ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe fa‐pmk. u’hq zqhqd suhqz tuy yazqk, zqhqd:
    ftmf u eiqmd nk mxx ftmf’e taxk!

    w. tatxmwah.


“tqdq’e ftq zafq!” etq fgdzqp cguowxk fa bkafd uxkufot. “sa, emhq tuy.
uf’e m zanxq pqqp az kagd bmdf!”

mzp etq ympq ftq eusz ar ftq odaee ftdqq fuyqe ahqd tuy. etq dmz agf fa
mooaybmzk tuy fa ftq bmeemsq.

“tai sdmfqrgx u my fa kag! kag omz’f ftuzw tai sdmfqrgx u my fa kag rad
tmhuzs oayq fa yq, rudef. tai ue uf u tmhqz’f yqf kag nqradq? u etmxx rqqx
rxmffqdqp mf eqquzs kag mf yk tageq uz ftq rgfgdq. tai pqxustfrgx uf ue
ftmf kag mdq xuhuzs tqdq!... egot bdqoueuaz! egot bdmofuomx mnuxufk!...
ftqk ygef mbbdqoumfq kag, ftqk ygef gzpqdefmzp kag. ur ftqdq’e mzkftuzs u
