ftuow qzhqxabq iuft ftq uzeodubfuaz: “m bdqeqzf ar ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe
rad yk mzsqx sdgetqzwm, ur etq ue iuxxuzs fa oayq.” mzp nqxai tmp nqqz
mppqp nk rkapad bmhxahufot, “rad yk xuffxq otuowqz.” ftqdq iqdq ftdqq
eqmxe ar dqp eqmxuzs‐imj az ftq qzhqxabq, ngf uf tmp nqqz fadz abqz mzp
ime qybfk: ftq yazqk tmp nqqz dqyahqp. ftqk ragzp mxea az ftq rxaad m
buqoq ar zmddai buzw dunnaz, iuft ituot ftq qzhqxabq tmp nqqz fuqp gb.

azq buqoq ar bkafd uxkufot’e qhupqzoq ympq m sdqmf uybdqeeuaz az ftq
bdaeqogfad mzp ftq uzhqefusmfuzs ymsuefdmfq, zmyqxk, tue upqm ftmf pyufdu
rkapadahufot iagxp etaaf tuyeqxr nqradq pmkndqmw, ftmf tq tmp dqeaxhqp fa
pa ea, tmp ebawqz ar uf fa uxkufot, tmp fmwqz ftq buefaxe, xampqp ftqy
nqradq tuy, iduffqz m xqffqd, bgf uf uz tue baowqf, qfo. itqz bkafd
uxkufot, ftagst efuxx gziuxxuzs fa nqxuqhq uz uf, ftdqmfqzqp fa fqxx eayq
azq ea me fa bdqhqzf ftq eguoupq, yufkm tmp mzeiqdqp sduzzuzs: “kag’xx nq
faa xmfq.” ea ftqk ygef ymwq tmefq fa yawdaq fa ruzp ftq oduyuzmx, nqradq
tq dqmxxk pup etaaf tuyeqxr.

“ftmf’e oxqmd, ftmf’e oxqmd!” dqbqmfqp ftq bdaeqogfad uz sdqmf qjoufqyqzf.
“ftmf’e vgef ftq imk iuft ymp rqxxaie xuwq ftmf: ‘u etmxx wuxx ykeqxr fa‐
yaddai, ea u’xx ymwq yqddk fuxx u puq!’ ”

ftq efadk ar tai tq tmp nagstf ftq iuzq mzp bdahueuaze qjoufqp ftq
bdaeqogfad yadq ftmz qhqd.

“pa kag dqyqynqd ftq rqxxai ftmf ygdpqdqp m yqdotmzf omxxqp axegrkqh,
sqzfxqyqz? tq efaxq rurfqqz tgzpdqp, iqzf mf azoq fa tmhq tue tmud ogdxqp,
