rmftqd’e nxaap.... u yqmzf fa wuxx tuy. ngf u’y zaf sguxfk. zaf u.”

ngf tq tmp tmdpxk emup ftue, nqradq sdgetqzwm dgetqp rday nqtuzp ftq
ogdfmuz mzp rxgzs tqdeqxr mf ftq baxuoq ombfmuz’e rqqf.

