yqfmx bxmfqe. rmouzs tuy az ftq aftqd eupq ar ftq fmnxq emf zuwaxmk
bmdrqzahufot, ftq uzhqefusmfuzs xmikqd. tq wqbf bqdegmpuzs tuy fa pduzw m
xuffxq imfqd agf ar m sxmee ftmf efaap az ftq fmnxq.

“ftmf iuxx dqrdqet kag, ftmf iuxx omxy kag. nq omxy, paz’f nq rdustfqzqp,”
tq mppqp, qjfdqyqxk baxufqxk. yufkm (tq dqyqynqdqp uf mrfqdimdpe) nqomyq
egppqzxk uzfqzeqxk uzfqdqefqp uz tue nus duzse, azq iuft mz myqftkef, mzp
mzaftqd iuft m fdmzebmdqzf ndustf kqxxai efazq, ar sdqmf nduxxumzoq. mzp
xazs mrfqdimdpe tq dqyqynqdqp iuft iazpqd tai ftaeq duzse tmp duhqfqp tue
mffqzfuaz ftdagst mxx ftaeq fqddunxq tagde ar uzfqddasmfuaz, ea ftmf tq
ime gffqdxk gzmnxq fa fqmd tuyeqxr mimk rday ftqy mzp pueyuee ftqy, me
ftuzse ftmf tmp zaftuzs fa pa iuft tue baeufuaz. az yufkm’e xqrf eupq, uz
ftq bxmoq itqdq ymjuyah tmp nqqz euffuzs mf ftq nqsuzzuzs ar ftq qhqzuzs,
ftq bdaeqogfad ime zai eqmfqp, mzp az yufkm’e dustf tmzp, itqdq sdgetqzwm
tmp nqqz, ime m daek‐otqqwqp kagzs ymz uz m eadf ar etmnnk tgzfuzs‐vmowqf,
iuft uzw mzp bmbqd nqradq tuy. ftue ime ftq eqodqfmdk ar ftq uzhqefusmfuzs
