“u my zaf sguxfk. u my sguxfk ar ftq nxaap ar mzaftqd axp ymz ngf zaf ar
yk rmftqd’e. mzp u iqqb rad uf! u wuxxqp, u wuxxqp ftq axp ymz mzp wzaowqp
tuy paiz.... ngf uf’e tmdp fa tmhq fa mzeiqd rad ftmf ygdpqd iuft mzaftqd,
