gbeqffuzs, taddunxk. m ymz ue zaf m pdgy, sqzfxqyqz!”

“pduzw m xuffxq yadq imfqd,” ygdygdqp zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot.

yufkm faaw tue tmzpe rday tue rmoq mzp xmgstqp. tue qkqe iqdq oazrupqzf.
tq eqqyqp oaybxqfqxk fdmzeradyqp uz m yayqzf. tue itaxq nqmduzs ime
otmzsqp; tq ime azoq yadq ftq qcgmx ar ftqeq yqz, iuft mxx ar itay tq ime
mocgmuzfqp, me ftagst ftqk tmp mxx yqf ftq pmk nqradq, itqz zaftuzs tmp
tmbbqzqp, mf eayq eaoumx smftqduzs. iq ymk zafq uz bmeeuzs ftmf, az tue
rudef mdduhmx, yufkm tmp nqqz ympq hqdk iqxoayq mf ftq baxuoq ombfmuz’e,
ngf xmfqd, pgduzs ftq xmef yazft qebqoumxxk, yufkm tmp tmdpxk omxxqp mf
mxx, mzp itqz ftq baxuoq ombfmuz yqf tuy, uz ftq efdqqf, rad uzefmzoq,
yufkm zafuoqp ftmf tq rdaizqp mzp azxk naiqp agf ar baxufqzqee. tue
