fa tuy fiuoq, qmot fuyq mnagf ftq rmud eqj.

“kag’dq m yaef ewuxxrgx xmikqd, u eqq, zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot,” oduqp yufkm,
xmgstuzs smkxk, “ngf u omz tqxb kag zai. at, sqzfxqyqz, u rqqx xuwq m zqi
ymz, mzp paz’f nq arrqzpqp mf yk mppdqeeuzs kag ea euybxk mzp pudqofxk.
u’y dmftqd pdgzw, faa, u’xx fqxx kag ftmf rdmzwxk. u nqxuqhq u’hq tmp ftq
tazad mzp bxqmegdq ar yqqfuzs kag, zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot, mf yk wuzeymz
yuüeah’e. sqzfxqyqz, sqzfxqyqz, u paz’f bdqfqzp fa nq az qcgmx fqdye iuft
kag. u gzpqdefmzp, ar oagdeq, uz itmf otmdmofqd u my euffuzs nqradq kag.
at, ar oagdeq, ftqdq’e m taddunxq egebuouaz ... tmzsuzs ahqd yq ... ur
sdusadk tme suhqz qhupqzoq.... m taddunxq egebuouaz! uf’e mirgx, mirgx, u
gzpqdefmzp ftmf! ngf fa ngeuzqee, sqzfxqyqz, u my dqmpk, mzp iq iuxx ymwq
mz qzp ar uf uz azq yayqzf; rad, xuefqz, xuefqz, sqzfxqyqz! euzoq u wzai
u’y uzzaoqzf, iq omz bgf mz qzp fa uf uz m yuzgfq. omz’f iq? omz’f iq?”

yufkm ebawq ygot mzp cguowxk, zqdhagexk mzp qrrgeuhqxk, me ftagst tq
baeufuhqxk faaw tue xuefqzqde fa nq tue nqef rduqzpe.

“ea, rad ftq bdqeqzf, iq iuxx idufq ftmf kag mneaxgfqxk pqzk ftq otmdsq
ndagstf msmuzef kag,” emup zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot, uybdqeeuhqxk, mzp nqzpuzs
