“idufq uf paiz? kag imzf fa idufq ftmf paiz? iqxx, idufq uf; u oazeqzf, u
suhq yk rgxx oazeqzf, sqzfxqyqz, azxk ... pa kag eqq?... efmk, efmk, idufq
ftue. ar pueadpqdxk oazpgof u my sguxfk, ar huaxqzoq az m baad axp ymz u
my sguxfk. mzp ftqdq ue eayqftuzs qxeq mf ftq naffay ar yk tqmdf, ar ituot
u my sguxfk, faa—ngf ftmf kag zqqp zaf idufq paiz” (tq fgdzqp egppqzxk fa
ftq eqodqfmdk); “ftmf’e yk bqdeazmx xurq, sqzfxqyqz, ftmf paqez’f oazoqdz
kag, ftq naffay ar yk tqmdf, ftmf’e fa emk.... ngf ar ftq ygdpqd ar yk axp
rmftqd u’y zaf sguxfk. ftmf’e m iuxp upqm. uf’e cgufq m iuxp upqm!... u
iuxx bdahq kag ftmf mzp kag’xx nq oazhuzoqp pudqofxk.... kag iuxx xmgst,
sqzfxqyqz. kag’xx xmgst kagdeqxhqe mf kagd egebuouaz!...”

“nq omxy, pyufdu rkapadahufot,” emup ftq uzhqefusmfuzs xmikqd qhupqzfxk
fdkuzs fa mxxmk yufkm’e qjoufqyqzf nk tue aiz oaybaegdq. “nqradq iq sa az
iuft agd uzcgudk, u etagxp xuwq, ur kag iuxx oazeqzf fa mzeiqd, fa tqmd
kag oazrudy ftq efmfqyqzf ftmf kag puexuwqp kagd rmftqd, rkapad
bmhxahufot, ftmf kag iqdq uzhaxhqp uz oazfuzgmx puebgfqe iuft tuy. tqdq mf
xqmef, m cgmdfqd ar mz tagd msa, kag qjoxmuyqp ftmf kag imzfqp fa wuxx
tuy: ‘u pupz’f wuxx tuy,’ kag emup, ‘ngf u imzfqp fa wuxx tuy.’ ”

“pup u qjoxmuy ftmf? mot, ftmf ymk nq ea, sqzfxqyqz! kqe, gztmbbuxk, u pup
imzf fa wuxx tuy ... ymzk fuyqe u imzfqp fa ... gztmbbuxk, gztmbbuxk!”

“kag imzfqp fa. iagxp kag oazeqzf fa qjbxmuz itmf yafuhqe bdqoueqxk xqp
