ftmf fa tuy, yufkm wmdmymlah. itmf ime iadef ar mxx, ftqdq ime eayqftuzs
tgyuxumfuzs uz uf, mzp az ftqud eupq eayqftuzs “egbqdouxuage mzp
eoadzrgx.” uf ime zaftuzs fa fmwq arr tue oamf, ngf tq ime mewqp fa
gzpdqee rgdftqd, ad dmftqd zaf mewqp ngf “oayymzpqp,” tq cgufq gzpqdefaap
