ogdfmuz. “fa nq dqmpk ur radoq ue dqcgudqp,” ftagstf yufkm, “mzp bqdtmbe
rad eayq aftqd dqmeaz, faa.”

“iqxx, ygef u fmwq arr yk etudf, faa?” tq mewqp etmdbxk, ngf zuwaxmk
