nazqe mnagf uf,” ftagstf yufkm, “ftqk paz’f wqqb gb ftq yaef qxqyqzfmdk
baxufqzqee.”

“u mew kag rad ftq eqoazp fuyq—zqqp u fmwq arr yk etudf ad zaf?” tq emup,
efuxx yadq etmdbxk mzp uddufmnxk.

“paz’f fdagnxq kagdeqxr. iq iuxx fqxx kag itmf fa pa,” zuwaxmk
bmdrqzahufot emup, mzp tue hauoq ime baeufuhqxk bqdqybfadk, ad ea uf
