yqmzfuyq m oazegxfmfuaz ime sauzs az uz gzpqdfazqe nqfiqqz ftq xmikqde.
ftqdq fgdzqp agf fa nq az ftq oamf, qebqoumxxk az ftq xqrf eupq mf ftq
nmow, m tgsq bmfot ar nxaap, pdk, mzp efuxx efurr. ftqdq iqdq nxaapefmuze
az ftq fdageqde, faa. zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot, yadqahqd, uz ftq bdqeqzoq ar
ftq bqmemzf iufzqeeqe, bmeeqp tue ruzsqde mxazs ftq oaxxmd, ftq ogrre, mzp
