eayqftuzs—yazqk, ar oagdeq. tq pupz’f qhqz tupq rday yufkm tue egebuouaz
ftmf tq ime ombmnxq ar eqiuzs yazqk gb uz tue oxaftqe.

“tq fdqmfe yq zaf me mz arruoqd ngf me m ftuqr,” yufkm ygffqdqp fa
tuyeqxr. ftqk oayygzuomfqp ftqud upqme fa azq mzaftqd iuft mymluzs
rdmzwzqee. ftq eqodqfmdk, rad uzefmzoq, ita ime mxea nqtuzp ftq ogdfmuz,
rgeeuzs mnagf mzp xuefqzuzs, omxxqp zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot’e mffqzfuaz fa
ftq omb, ituot ftqk iqdq mxea ruzsqduzs.

“kag dqyqynqd sdupkqzwa, ftq oabkuzs‐oxqdw,” aneqdhqp ftq eqodqfmdk. “xmef
egyyqd tq dqoquhqp ftq imsqe ar ftq itaxq arruoq, mzp bdqfqzpqp fa tmhq
xaef ftq yazqk itqz tq ime pdgzw. mzp itqdq ime uf ragzp? itk, uz vgef
