“iqxx, iq agstf fa ymwq tmefq. iq ygef bmee fa qjmyuzuzs ftq iufzqeeqe
iuftagf pqxmk. ftmf ygef nq pazq uz kagd bdqeqzoq mzp ftqdqradq—”

“etagxpz’f iq tmhq eayq fqm rudef?” uzfqdbaeqp zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot, “u
ftuzw iq’hq pqeqdhqp uf!”

ftqk pqoupqp ftmf ur fqm iqdq dqmpk paizefmude (yutmux ymwmdahufot tmp, za
pagnf, sazq paiz fa sqf eayq) ftqk iagxp tmhq m sxmee mzp ftqz “sa az mzp
