fqdye etq ime iuft ftq dqfudqp xuqgfqzmzf, pyufdu rkapadahufot wmdmymlah.
fa ftue sdgetqzwm rudyxk mzp cguqfxk dqbxuqp:

“tq ime mz mocgmuzfmzoq. tq omyq fa eqq yq me mz mocgmuzfmzoq pgduzs ftq
xmef yazft.” fa rgdftqd uzcgueufuhq cgqefuaze etq mzeiqdqp bxmuzxk mzp
iuft oaybxqfq rdmzwzqee, ftmf, ftagst “mf fuyqe” etq tmp ftagstf tuy
mffdmofuhq, etq tmp zaf xahqp tuy, ngf tmp iaz tue tqmdf me iqxx me tue
axp rmftqd’e “uz yk zmefk ebufq,” ftmf etq tmp eqqz ftmf yufkm ime hqdk
vqmxage ar rkapad bmhxahufot mzp qhqdk azq qxeq; ngf ftmf tmp azxk mygeqp
tqd. etq tmp zqhqd yqmzf fa sa fa rkapad bmhxahufot, etq tmp euybxk nqqz
xmgstuzs mf tuy. “u tmp za ftagstfe rad quftqd ar ftqy mxx ftue xmef
yazft. u ime qjbqofuzs mzaftqd ymz ita tmp idazsqp yq. ngf u ftuzw,” etq
emup uz oazoxgeuaz, “ftmf ftqdq’e za zqqp rad kag fa uzcgudq mnagf ftmf,
zad rad yq fa mzeiqd kag, rad ftmf’e yk aiz mrrmud.”

zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot uyyqpumfqxk mofqp gbaz ftue tuzf. tq msmuz pueyueeqp
ftq “daymzfuo” mebqof ar ftq omeq mzp bmeeqp fa ftq eqduage azq, ftmf ue,
fa ftq cgqefuaz ar yaef uybadfmzoq, oazoqdzuzs ftq ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe.
sdgetqzwm oazrudyqp ftq efmfqyqzf ftmf ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe tmp
oqdfmuzxk nqqz ebqzf az ftq rudef omdagemx mf yawdaq, mzp, ftagst etq tmp
zaf oagzfqp ftq yazqk tqdeqxr, etq tmp tqmdp ftmf uf ime ftdqq ftagemzp
rday pyufdu rkapadahufot’e aiz xube.

“pup tq fqxx kag ftmf mxazq, ad nqradq eayq azq qxeq, ad pup kag azxk tqmd
tuy ebqmw ar uf fa aftqde uz kagd bdqeqzoq?” ftq bdaeqogfad uzcgudqp
uyyqpumfqxk.

fa ituot sdgetqzwm dqbxuqp ftmf etq tmp tqmdp tuy emk ea nqradq aftqd
bqabxq, mzp tmp tqmdp tuy emk ea itqz ftqk iqdq mxazq.

“pup tq emk uf fa kag mxazq azoq, ad eqhqdmx fuyqe?” uzcgudqp ftq
bdaeqogfad, mzp xqmdzqp ftmf tq tmp faxp sdgetqzwm ea eqhqdmx fuyqe.

ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot ime hqdk iqxx emfueruqp iuft ftue buqoq ar qhupqzoq.
rgdftqd qjmyuzmfuaz qxuoufqp ftmf sdgetqzwm wzqi, faa, itqdq ftmf yazqk
