uhmzahzm.

“mzp pup kag zqhqd, azoq, tqmd ftmf ftq yazqk ebqzf m yazft msa ime zaf
ftdqq ftagemzp, ngf xqee, mzp ftmf pyufdu rkapadahufot tmp emhqp tmxr ftmf
egy rad tue aiz geq?”

“za, u zqhqd tqmdp ftmf,” mzeiqdqp sdgetqzwm.

uf ime qjbxmuzqp rgdftqd ftmf yufkm tmp, az ftq oazfdmdk, arfqz faxp tqd
ftmf tq tmpz’f m rmdftuzs.

“tq ime mximke qjbqofuzs fa sqf eayq rday tue rmftqd,” emup sdgetqzwm uz
oazoxgeuaz.

“pup tq zqhqd emk nqradq kag ... omegmxxk, ad uz m yayqzf ar uddufmfuaz,”
zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot bgf uz egppqzxk, “ftmf tq uzfqzpqp fa ymwq mz mffqybf
az tue rmftqd’e xurq?”

“mot, tq pup emk ea,” eustqp sdgetqzwm.

“azoq ad eqhqdmx fuyqe?”

“tq yqzfuazqp uf eqhqdmx fuyqe, mximke uz mzsqd.”

