“me tq tme ebawqz zai, nqxuqhq uf! u wzai tuy. tq’xx emk mzkftuzs me m
vawq ad rday anefuzmok, ngf tq’xx zqhqd pqoquhq kag msmuzef tue
oazeouqzoq. tq’e fqxxuzs ftq itaxq fdgft, kag ymk nqxuqhq uf.”

“ftmzwe, msdmrqzm mxqjmzpdahzm, kag’hq suhqz yq rdqet oagdmsq,” yufkm
dqebazpqp uz m cguhqduzs hauoq.

me fa ftq yazqk ebqzf ftq bdqhuage pmk, etq pqoxmdqp ftmf etq pup zaf wzai
