ftagemzp iuft tuy. mzp fa ftq cgqefuaz itqdq tq saf ftq yazqk, etq emup
ftmf tq tmp faxp tqd ftmf tq tmp “efaxqz” uf rday wmfqduzm uhmzahzm, mzp
