mf xmef, ahqd. ftqk bdaoqqpqp fa m ruzmx dqhueuaz ar ftq bdafaoax. yufkm
saf gb, yahqp rday tue otmud fa ftq oadzqd nk ftq ogdfmuz, xmk paiz az m
xmdsq otqef oahqdqp iuft m dgs, mzp uzefmzfxk rqxx mexqqb.

tq tmp m efdmzsq pdqmy, gffqdxk agf ar wqqbuzs iuft ftq bxmoq mzp ftq
fuyq.

tq ime pduhuzs eayqitqdq uz ftq efqbbqe, itqdq tq tmp nqqz efmfuazqp xazs
msa, mzp m bqmemzf ime pduhuzs tuy uz m omdf iuft m bmud ar tadeqe,
ftdagst ezai mzp exqqf. tq ime oaxp, uf ime qmdxk uz zahqynqd, mzp ftq
ezai ime rmxxuzs uz nus iqf rxmwqe, yqxfuzs me eaaz me uf fagotqp ftq
qmdft. mzp ftq bqmemzf pdahq tuy eymdfxk, tq tmp m rmud, xazs nqmdp. tq
ime zaf mz axp ymz, eayqitqdq mnagf rurfk, mzp tq tmp az m sdmk bqmemzf’e
eyaow. zaf rmd arr ime m huxxmsq, tq oagxp eqq ftq nxmow tgfe, mzp tmxr
ftq tgfe iqdq ngdzf paiz, ftqdq iqdq azxk ftq otmddqp nqmye efuowuzs gb.
mzp me ftqk pdahq uz, ftqdq iqdq bqmemzf iayqz pdmiz gb mxazs ftq damp, m
xaf ar iayqz, m itaxq dai, mxx ftuz mzp imz, iuft ftqud rmoqe m eadf ar
ndaizuet oaxad, qebqoumxxk azq mf ftq qpsq, m fmxx, nazk iaymz, ita xaawqp
radfk, ngf yustf tmhq nqqz azxk fiqzfk, iuft m xazs ftuz rmoq. mzp uz tqd
