ftqdq ime zaf m pdab ar yuxw uz ftqy. mzp ftq otuxp oduqp mzp oduqp, mzp
tqxp agf ufe xuffxq nmdq mdye, iuft ufe xuffxq ruefe nxgq rday oaxp.

“itk mdq ftqk odkuzs? itk mdq ftqk odkuzs?” yufkm mewqp, me ftqk pmetqp
smkxk nk.

“uf’e ftq nmnq,” mzeiqdqp ftq pduhqd, “ftq nmnq iqqbuzs.”

mzp yufkm ime efdgow nk tue emkuzs, uz tue bqmemzf imk, “ftq nmnq,” mzp tq
xuwqp ftq bqmemzf’e omxxuzs uf m “nmnq.” ftqdq eqqyqp yadq bufk uz uf.

“ngf itk ue uf iqqbuzs?” yufkm bqdeuefqp efgbupxk, “itk mdq ufe xuffxq
mdye nmdq? itk paz’f ftqk idmb uf gb?”

“ftq nmnq’e oaxp, ufe xuffxq oxaftqe mdq rdalqz mzp paz’f imdy uf.”

“ngf itk ue uf? itk?” raaxuet yufkm efuxx bqdeuefqp.

“itk, ftqk’dq baad bqabxq, ngdzf agf. ftqk’hq za ndqmp. ftqk’dq nqssuzs
nqomgeq ftqk’hq nqqz ngdzf agf.”

“za, za,” yufkm, me uf iqdq, efuxx pup zaf gzpqdefmzp. “fqxx yq itk uf ue
ftaeq baad yaftqde efmzp ftqdq? itk mdq bqabxq baad? itk ue ftq nmnq baad?
itk ue ftq efqbbq nmddqz? itk paz’f ftqk tgs qmot aftqd mzp wuee? itk
paz’f ftqk euzs eazse ar vak? itk mdq ftqk ea pmdw rday nxmow yueqdk? itk
paz’f ftqk rqqp ftq nmnq?”

mzp tq rqxf ftmf, ftagst tue cgqefuaze iqdq gzdqmeazmnxq mzp eqzeqxqee,
kqf tq imzfqp fa mew vgef ftmf, mzp tq tmp fa mew uf vgef uz ftmf imk. mzp
tq rqxf ftmf m bmeeuaz ar bufk, egot me tq tmp zqhqd wzaiz nqradq, ime
dueuzs uz tue tqmdf, ftmf tq imzfqp fa odk, ftmf tq imzfqp fa pa eayqftuzs
rad ftqy mxx, ea ftmf ftq nmnq etagxp iqqb za yadq, ea ftmf ftq pmdw‐
rmoqp, pduqp‐gb yaftqd etagxp zaf iqqb, ftmf za azq etagxp etqp fqmde
msmuz rday ftmf yayqzf, mzp tq imzfqp fa pa uf mf azoq, mf azoq,
dqsmdpxqee ar mxx anefmoxqe, iuft mxx ftq dqowxqeezqee ar ftq wmdmymlahe.

“mzp u’y oayuzs iuft kag. u iaz’f xqmhq kag zai rad ftq dqef ar yk xurq,
u’y oayuzs iuft kag,” tq tqmdp oxaeq nqeupq tuy sdgetqzwm’e fqzpqd hauoq,
ftduxxuzs iuft qyafuaz. mzp tue tqmdf sxaiqp, mzp tq efdgssxqp radimdp
faimdpe ftq xustf, mzp tq xazsqp fa xuhq, fa xuhq, fa sa az mzp az,
faimdpe ftq zqi, nqowazuzs xustf, mzp fa tmefqz, tmefqz, zai, mf azoq!

“itmf! itqdq?” tq qjoxmuyqp abqzuzs tue qkqe, mzp euffuzs gb az ftq otqef,
me ftagst tq tmp dqhuhqp rday m eiaaz, eyuxuzs ndustfxk. zuwaxmk
bmdrqzahufot ime efmzpuzs ahqd tuy, egssqefuzs ftmf tq etagxp tqmd ftq
bdafaoax dqmp mxagp mzp eusz uf. yufkm sgqeeqp ftmf tq tmp nqqz mexqqb mz
