nqqz ftqdq itqz tq tmp xqmzf nmow, qjtmgefqp, az ftq otqef.

“ita bgf ftmf buxxai gzpqd yk tqmp? ita ime ea wuzp?” tq oduqp, iuft m
eadf ar qoefmfuo sdmfufgpq, mzp fqmde uz tue hauoq, me ftagst eayq sdqmf
wuzpzqee tmp nqqz etaiz tuy.

tq zqhqd ragzp agf ita ftue wuzp ymz ime; bqdtmbe azq ar ftq bqmemzf
iufzqeeqe, ad zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot’e xuffxq eqodqfmdk, tmp oaybmeeuazmfqxk
