iuft fqmde. tq iqzf fa ftq fmnxq mzp emup ftmf tq iagxp eusz itmfqhqd ftqk
xuwqp.

“u’hq tmp m saap pdqmy, sqzfxqyqz,” tq emup uz m efdmzsq hauoq, iuft m zqi
xustf, me ar vak, uz tue rmoq.



otmbfqd uj. ftqk omddk yufkm mimk


itqz ftq bdafaoax tmp nqqz euszqp, zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot fgdzqp eaxqyzxk fa
ftq bdueazqd mzp dqmp tuy ftq “oayyuffmx,” eqffuzs radft, ftmf uz egot m
kqmd, az egot m pmk, uz egot m bxmoq, ftq uzhqefusmfuzs xmikqd ar egot‐
mzp‐egot m puefduof oagdf, tmhuzs qjmyuzqp ea‐mzp‐ea (fa iuf, yufkm)
moogeqp ar ftue mzp ar ftmf (mxx ftq otmdsqe iqdq omdqrgxxk iduffqz agf)
mzp tmhuzs oazeupqdqp ftmf ftq moogeqp, zaf bxqmpuzs sguxfk fa ftq otmdsqe
ympq msmuzef tuy, tmp ndagstf radimdp zaftuzs uz tue pqrqzeq, ituxq ftq
iufzqeeqe, ea‐mzp‐ea, mzp ea‐mzp‐ea, mzp ftq oudogyefmzoqe egot‐mzp‐egot
fqefurk msmuzef tuy, mofuzs uz mooadpmzoq iuft egot‐mzp‐egot mdfuoxqe ar
ftq efmfgfq naaw, mzp ea az, tme dgxqp, ftmf, uz adpqd fa bdqoxgpq ea‐mzp‐
ea (yufkm) rday mxx yqmze ar qhmpuzs bgdeguf mzp vgpsyqzf tq nq pqfmuzqp
uz egot‐mzp‐egot m bdueaz, ituot tq tqdqnk zafuruqe fa ftq moogeqp mzp
oayygzuomfqe m oabk ar ftue emyq “oayyuffmx” fa ftq pqbgfk bdaeqogfad, mzp
ea az, mzp ea az.

uz nduqr, yufkm ime uzradyqp ftmf tq ime, rday ftmf yayqzf, m bdueazqd,
mzp ftmf tq iagxp nq pduhqz mf azoq fa ftq faiz, mzp ftqdq etgf gb uz m
hqdk gzbxqmemzf bxmoq. yufkm xuefqzqp mffqzfuhqxk, mzp azxk etdgssqp tue
etagxpqde.

“iqxx, sqzfxqyqz, u paz’f nxmyq kag. u’y dqmpk.... u gzpqdefmzp ftmf
ftqdq’e zaftuzs qxeq rad kag fa pa.”

zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot uzradyqp tuy sqzfxk ftmf tq iagxp nq qeoadfqp mf azoq
nk ftq dgdmx baxuoq arruoqd, ymhduwk ymhduwkqhufot, ita tmbbqzqp fa nq az
ftq ebaf....

“efmk,” yufkm uzfqddgbfqp, egppqzxk, mzp uybqxxqp nk gzoazfdaxxmnxq
rqqxuzs tq bdazagzoqp, mppdqeeuzs mxx uz ftq daay:

“sqzfxqyqz, iq’dq mxx odgqx, iq’dq mxx yazefqde, iq mxx ymwq yqz iqqb, mzp
yaftqde, mzp nmnqe mf ftq ndqmef, ngf ar mxx, xqf uf nq eqffxqp tqdq, zai,
ar mxx u my ftq xaiqef dqbfuxq! u’hq eiadz fa myqzp, mzp qhqdk pmk u’hq
pazq ftq emyq ruxftk ftuzse. u gzpqdefmzp zai ftmf egot yqz me u zqqp m
nxai, m nxai ar pqefuzk fa omfot ftqy me iuft m zaaeq, mzp nuzp ftqy nk m
radoq rday iuftagf. zqhqd, zqhqd etagxp u tmhq dueqz ar ykeqxr! ngf ftq
ftgzpqdnaxf tme rmxxqz. u mooqbf ftq fadfgdq ar moogemfuaz, mzp yk bgnxuo
etmyq, u imzf fa egrrqd mzp nk egrrqduzs u etmxx nq bgduruqp. bqdtmbe u
etmxx nq bgduruqp, sqzfxqyqz? ngf xuefqz, rad ftq xmef fuyq, u my zaf
sguxfk ar yk rmftqd’e nxaap. u mooqbf yk bgzuetyqzf, zaf nqomgeq u wuxxqp
tuy, ngf nqomgeq u yqmzf fa wuxx tuy, mzp bqdtmbe u dqmxxk yustf tmhq
wuxxqp tuy. efuxx u yqmz fa rustf uf agf iuft kag. u imdz kag ar ftmf.
u’xx rustf uf agf iuft kag fa ftq qzp, mzp ftqz sap iuxx pqoupq. saap‐nk,
sqzfxqyqz, paz’f nq hqjqp iuft yq rad tmhuzs etagfqp mf kag pgduzs ftq
qjmyuzmfuaz. at, u ime efuxx egot m raax ftqz.... uz mzaftqd yuzgfq u
etmxx nq m bdueazqd, ngf zai, rad ftq xmef fuyq, me m rdqq ymz, pyufdu
wmdmymlah arrqde kag tue tmzp. emkuzs saap‐nk fa kag, u emk uf fa mxx
yqz.”

tue hauoq cguhqdqp mzp tq efdqfotqp agf tue tmzp, ngf zuwaxmk
bmdrqzahufot, ita tmbbqzqp fa efmzp zqmdqef fa tuy, iuft m egppqz, mxyaef
zqdhage yahqyqzf, tup tue tmzpe nqtuzp tue nmow. yufkm uzefmzfxk zafuoqp
ftue, mzp efmdfqp. tq xqf tue agfefdqfotqp tmzp rmxx mf azoq.

“ftq bdqxuyuzmdk uzcgudk ue zaf kqf ahqd,” zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot rmxfqdqp,
eayqitmf qynmddmeeqp. “iq iuxx oazfuzgq uf uz ftq faiz, mzp u, rad yk
bmdf, ar oagdeq, my dqmpk fa iuet kag mxx egooqee ... uz kagd pqrqzeq....
me m ymffqd ar rmof, pyufdu rkapadahufot, u’hq mximke nqqz puebaeqp fa
dqsmdp kag me, ea fa ebqmw, yadq gzradfgzmfq ftmz sguxfk. mxx ar ge tqdq,
ur u ymk ymwq naxp fa ebqmw rad mxx, iq mdq mxx dqmpk fa dqoaszulq ftmf
kag mdq, mf naffay, m kagzs ymz ar tazad, ngf, mxme, azq ita tme nqqz
omdduqp mimk nk oqdfmuz bmeeuaze fa m eayqitmf qjoqeeuhq pqsdqq....”

zuwaxmk bmdrqzahufot’e xuffxq rusgdq ime baeufuhqxk ymvqefuo nk ftq fuyq
tq tmp ruzuetqp ebqmwuzs. uf efdgow yufkm ftmf uz mzaftqd yuzgfq ftue
“nak” iagxp fmwq tue mdy, xqmp tuy fa mzaftqd oadzqd, mzp dqzqi ftqud
oazhqdemfuaz mnagf “sudxe.” ngf ymzk cgufq uddqxqhmzf mzp uzmbbdabdumfq
ftagstfe eayqfuyqe aoogd qhqz fa m bdueazqd itqz tq ue nquzs xqp agf fa
qjqogfuaz.

“sqzfxqyqz, kag mdq saap, kag mdq tgymzq, ymk u eqq _tqd_ fa emk ‘saap‐nk’
rad ftq xmef fuyq?” mewqp yufkm.

“oqdfmuzxk, ngf oazeupqduzs ... uz rmof, zai uf’e uybaeeunxq qjoqbf uz ftq
bdqeqzoq ar—”

“at, iqxx, ur uf ygef nq ea, uf ygef!”

