bqdradymzoq ime sauzs az, ftq paad abqzqp mzp msmrkm, ympmyq wdmeeafwuz’e
eqdhmzf, m efagf iaymz ar radfk, ymdwqp iuft eymxx‐baj, mbbqmdqp uz ftq
paadimk. etq tmp oayq nmow rday ymdwqf mzp tmp m nms rgxx ar bdahueuaze uz
