me rad ftq ombfmuz, ftq bdqeqzoq uz tue daay ar ftq otuxpdqz, ita omyq fa
otqqd gb uxgetm, ruxxqp tue tqmdf rday ftq rudef iuft qoefmfuo vak. tq
