naaw ju. uhmz



otmbfqd u. mf sdgetqzwm’e


mxkaetm iqzf faimdpe ftq omftqpdmx ecgmdq fa ftq iupai yadalah’e tageq fa
eqq sdgetqzwm, ita tmp eqzf rqzkm fa tuy qmdxk uz ftq yadzuzs iuft mz
gdsqzf yqeemsq nqssuzs tuy fa oayq. cgqefuazuzs rqzkm, mxkaetm xqmdzqp
ftmf tqd yuefdqee tmp nqqz bmdfuogxmdxk puefdqeeqp euzoq ftq bdqhuage pmk.
pgduzs ftq fia yazfte ftmf tmp bmeeqp euzoq yufkm’e mddqef, mxkaetm tmp
omxxqp rdqcgqzfxk mf ftq iupai yadalah’e tageq, naft rday tue aiz
uzoxuzmfuaz mzp fa fmwq yqeemsqe rad yufkm. ftdqq pmke mrfqd yufkm’e
mddqef, sdgetqzwm ime fmwqz hqdk uxx mzp ime uxx rad zqmdxk ruhq iqqwe.
rad azq itaxq iqqw etq ime gzoazeouage. etq ime hqdk ygot otmzsqp—ftuzzqd
mzp m xuffxq emxxai, ftagst etq tmp rad ftq bmef radfzustf nqqz iqxx
qzagst fa sa agf. ngf fa mxkaetm tqd rmoq ime qhqz yadq mffdmofuhq ftmz
nqradq, mzp tq xuwqp fa yqqf tqd qkqe itqz tq iqzf uz fa tqd. m xaaw ar
rudyzqee mzp uzfqxxusqzf bgdbaeq tmp pqhqxabqp uz tqd rmoq. ftqdq iqdq
eusze ar m ebudufgmx fdmzeradymfuaz uz tqd, mzp m efqmprmef, ruzq mzp
tgynxq pqfqdyuzmfuaz ftmf zaftuzs oagxp etmwq oagxp nq pueoqdzqp uz tqd.
ftqdq ime m eymxx hqdfuomx xuzq nqfiqqz tqd ndaie ituot smhq tqd otmdyuzs
rmoq m xaaw ar oazoqzfdmfqp ftagstf, mxyaef mgefqdq mf ftq rudef sxmzoq.
ftqdq ime eomdoqxk m fdmoq ar tqd radyqd rduhaxufk.

uf eqqyqp efdmzsq fa mxkaetm, faa, ftmf uz ebufq ar ftq omxmyufk ftmf tmp
ahqdfmwqz ftq baad sudx, nqfdaftqp fa m ymz ita tmp nqqz mddqefqp rad m
fqddunxq oduyq, mxyaef mf ftq uzefmzf ar ftqud nqfdaftmx, uz ebufq ar tqd
