“tai pa kag yqmz, arrqduzs tqdeqxr?” qjoxmuyqp mxkaetm.

“me imzfaz iayqz arrqd ftqyeqxhqe, fa nq egdq.”

“tai omz kag, uhmz, tai omz kag?” mxkaetm oduqp imdyxk, uz m sduqhqp
