tqmd eayqftuzs rday kag ... ftmf iagxp emhq tqd.”

“kag’xx tqmd zaftuzs rday yq. ur etq ue m otuxp u my zaf tqd zgdeq. nq
cguqf, mxqjqk. paz’f sa az mnagf tqd. u my zaf qhqz ftuzwuzs mnagf uf.”

ftqk iqdq euxqzf msmuz rad m yayqzf.

“etq iuxx nq bdmkuzs mxx zustf zai fa ftq yaftqd ar sap fa etai tqd tai fa
mof fa‐yaddai mf ftq fdumx,” tq emup etmdbxk mzp mzsduxk msmuz.

“kag ... kag yqmz wmfqduzm uhmzahzm?”

“kqe. itqftqd etq’e fa emhq yufkm ad dguz tuy. etq’xx bdmk rad xustf rday
mnahq. etq omz’f ymwq gb tqd yuzp rad tqdeqxr, kag eqq. etq tme zaf tmp
fuyq fa pqoupq kqf. etq fmwqe yq rad tqd zgdeq, faa. etq imzfe yq fa euzs
