mgftad ar m bdayueuzs baqy qzfufxqp _ftq sdmzp uzcgueufad_. u ime azxk
ftuzwuzs ar tuy!”

“u radnup kag fa ebqmw ar _ftq sdmzp uzcgueufad_,” oduqp uhmz, oduyeaz
iuft etmyq.

“mzp ftq _sqaxasuomx omfmoxkey_. pa kag dqyqynqd? ftmf ime m baqy, zai!”

“taxp kagd fazsgq, ad u’xx wuxx kag!”

“kag’xx wuxx yq? za, qjogeq yq, u iuxx ebqmw. u omyq fa fdqmf ykeqxr fa
ftmf bxqmegdq. at, u xahq ftq pdqmye ar yk mdpqzf kagzs rduqzpe, cguhqduzs
iuft qmsqdzqee rad xurq! ‘ftqdq mdq zqi yqz,’ kag pqoupqp xmef ebduzs,
