sdmhq’... mzp ea az mzp ea az uz ftq emyq efkxq. otmdyuzs!”

uhmz emf iuft tue qkqe az ftq rxaad, mzp tue tmzpe bdqeeqp fa tue qmde,
ngf tq nqsmz fdqynxuzs mxx ahqd. ftq hauoq oazfuzgqp.

“ftq cgqefuaz zai ue, yk kagzs ftuzwqd dqrxqofqp, ue uf baeeunxq ftmf egot
m bqduap iuxx qhqd oayq? ur uf paqe, qhqdkftuzs ue pqfqdyuzqp mzp tgymzufk
