omzzaf oayq mnagf rad mf xqmef m ftagemzp kqmde, qhqdk azq ita dqoaszulqe
ftq fdgft qhqz zai ymk xqsufuymfqxk adpqd tue xurq me tq bxqmeqe, az ftq
zqi bduzoubxqe. uz ftmf eqzeq, ‘mxx ftuzse mdq xmirgx’ rad tuy. itmf’e
