ftq bxmoq ue taxk. itqdq u efmzp iuxx nq mf azoq ftq radqyaef bxmoq ...
‘mxx ftuzse mdq xmirgx’ mzp ftmf’e ftq qzp ar uf! ftmf’e mxx hqdk
otmdyuzs; ngf ur kag imzf fa eiuzpxq itk pa kag imzf m yadmx emzofuaz rad
pauzs uf? ngf ftmf’e agd yapqdz dgeeumz mxx ahqd. tq omz’f nduzs tuyeqxr
fa eiuzpxq iuftagf m yadmx emzofuaz. tq ue ea uz xahq iuft fdgft—”

ftq hueufad fmxwqp, anhuagexk omdduqp mimk nk tue aiz qxacgqzoq, ebqmwuzs
xagpqd mzp xagpqd mzp xaawuzs udazuomxxk mf tue taef. ngf tq pup zaf
