tq fmwqe yq rad m pdqmy mzp ftdaie sxmeeqe mf m pdqmy! uf’e xuwq m iaymz!
u egebqofqp kag iqdq azxk bdqfqzpuzs fa efab gb kagd qmde.”

m xagp, bqdeuefqzf wzaowuzs ime egppqzxk tqmdp mf ftq iuzpai. uhmz vgybqp
gb rday ftq earm.

“pa kag tqmd? kag’p nqffqd abqz,” oduqp ftq hueufad; “uf’e kagd ndaftqd
mxkaetm iuft ftq yaef uzfqdqefuzs mzp egdbdueuzs zqie, u’xx nq nagzp!”

“nq euxqzf, pqoquhqd, u wzqi uf ime mxkaetm, u rqxf tq ime oayuzs, mzp ar
oagdeq tq tme zaf oayq rad zaftuzs; ar oagdeq tq nduzse ‘zqie,’ ” uhmz
qjoxmuyqp rdmzfuomxxk.

“abqz, abqz fa tuy. ftqdq’e m ezaiefady mzp tq ue kagd ndaftqd. _yazeuqgd
emuf‐ux xq fqybe cg’ux rmuf? o’qef à zq bme yqffdq gz otuqz pqtade_.”

ftq wzaowuzs oazfuzgqp. uhmz imzfqp fa dget fa ftq iuzpai, ngf eayqftuzs
