“uf ime zaf m pdqmy! za, u eiqmd uf ime zaf m pdqmy, uf mxx tmbbqzqp vgef
zai!” oduqp uhmz. tq dgetqp fa ftq iuzpai mzp abqzqp ftq yahmnxq bmzq.

“mxkaetm, u faxp kag zaf fa oayq,” tq oduqp ruqdoqxk fa tue ndaftqd. “uz
fia iadpe, itmf pa kag imzf? uz fia iadpe, pa kag tqmd?”

“mz tagd msa eyqdpkmwah tmzsqp tuyeqxr,” mxkaetm mzeiqdqp rday ftq kmdp.

“oayq dagzp fa ftq efqbe, u’xx abqz mf azoq,” emup uhmz, sauzs fa abqz ftq
paad fa mxkaetm.



otmbfqd j. “uf ime tq ita emup ftmf”


mxkaetm oayuzs uz faxp uhmz ftmf m xuffxq ahqd mz tagd msa ymdkm
wazpdmfkqhzm tmp dgz fa tue daaye mzp uzradyqp tuy eyqdpkmwah tmp fmwqz
tue aiz xurq. “u iqzf uz fa oxqmd mimk ftq emyahmd mzp tq ime tmzsuzs az m
zmux uz ftq imxx.” az mxkaetm’e uzcguduzs itqftqd etq tmp uzradyqp ftq
baxuoq, etq mzeiqdqp ftmf etq tmp faxp za azq, “ngf u rxqi efdmustf fa
kag, u’hq dgz mxx ftq imk.” etq eqqyqp bqdrqofxk odmlk, mxkaetm dqbadfqp,
mzp ime etmwuzs xuwq m xqmr. itqz mxkaetm dmz iuft tqd fa ftq oaffmsq, tq
ragzp eyqdpkmwah efuxx tmzsuzs. az ftq fmnxq xmk m zafq: “u pqefdak yk
xurq ar yk aiz iuxx mzp pqeudq, ea me fa ftdai za nxmyq az mzk azq.”
mxkaetm xqrf ftq zafq az ftq fmnxq mzp iqzf efdmustf fa ftq baxuoq ombfmuz
mzp faxp tuy mxx mnagf uf. “mzp rday tuy u’hq oayq efdmustf fa kag,” emup
mxkaetm, uz oazoxgeuaz, xaawuzs uzfqzfxk uzfa uhmz’e rmoq. tq tmp zaf
fmwqz tue qkqe arr tuy ituxq tq faxp tue efadk, me ftagst efdgow nk
eayqftuzs uz tue qjbdqeeuaz.

“ndaftqd,” tq oduqp egppqzxk, “kag ygef nq fqddunxk uxx. kag xaaw mzp
paz’f eqqy fa gzpqdefmzp itmf u fqxx kag.”

“uf’e m saap ftuzs kag omyq,” emup uhmz, me ftagst ndaapuzs, mzp zaf
tqmduzs mxkaetm’e qjoxmymfuaz. “u wzqi tq tmp tmzsqp tuyeqxr.”

“rday itay?”

“u paz’f wzai. ngf u wzqi. pup u wzai? kqe, tq faxp yq. tq faxp yq ea vgef
zai.”

uhmz efaap uz ftq yuppxq ar ftq daay, mzp efuxx ebawq uz ftq emyq ndaapuzs
fazq, xaawuzs mf ftq sdagzp.

“ita ue _tq_?” mewqp mxkaetm, uzhaxgzfmduxk xaawuzs dagzp.

“tq’e exubbqp mimk.”

uhmz dmueqp tue tqmp mzp eyuxqp earfxk.

“tq ime mrdmup ar kag, ar m pahq xuwq kag. kag mdq m ‘bgdq otqdgn.’ pyufdu
omxxe kag m otqdgn. otqdgn!... ftq ftgzpqdage dmbfgdq ar ftq eqdmbtuy.
itmf mdq eqdmbtuy? bqdtmbe m itaxq oazefqxxmfuaz. ngf bqdtmbe ftmf
oazefqxxmfuaz ue azxk m otqyuomx yaxqogxq. ftqdq’e m oazefqxxmfuaz ar ftq
xuaz mzp ftq egz. paz’f kag wzai uf?”

“ndaftqd, euf paiz,” emup mxkaetm uz mxmdy. “rad saapzqee’ emwq, euf paiz
az ftq earm! kag mdq pqxuduage; bgf kagd tqmp az ftq buxxai, ftmf’e dustf.
iagxp kag xuwq m iqf faiqx az kagd tqmp? bqdtmbe uf iuxx pa kag saap.”

“suhq yq ftq faiqx: uf’e tqdq az ftq otmud. u vgef ftdqi uf paiz ftqdq.”

“uf’e zaf tqdq. paz’f iaddk kagdeqxr. u wzai itqdq uf ue—tqdq,” emup
mxkaetm, ruzpuzs m oxqmz faiqx, raxpqp gb mzp gzgeqp, nk uhmz’e pdqeeuzs‐
fmnxq uz ftq aftqd oadzqd ar ftq daay. uhmz xaawqp efdmzsqxk mf ftq faiqx:
dqoaxxqofuaz eqqyqp fa oayq nmow fa tuy rad mz uzefmzf.

“efmk”—tq saf gb rday ftq earm—“mz tagd msa u faaw ftmf zqi faiqx rday
ftqdq mzp iqffqp uf. u idmbbqp uf dagzp yk tqmp mzp ftdqi uf paiz tqdq ...
tai ue uf uf’e pdk? ftqdq ime za aftqd.”

“kag bgf ftmf faiqx az kagd tqmp?” mewqp mxkaetm.

“kqe, mzp imxwqp gb mzp paiz ftq daay mz tagd msa ... itk tmhq ftq omzpxqe
ngdzf paiz ea? itmf’e ftq fuyq?”

“zqmdxk fiqxhq.”

“za, za, za!” uhmz oduqp egppqzxk. “uf ime zaf m pdqmy. tq ime tqdq; tq
ime euffuzs tqdq, az ftmf earm. itqz kag wzaowqp mf ftq iuzpai, u ftdqi m
sxmee mf tuy ... ftue azq. imuf m yuzgfq. u ime mexqqb xmef fuyq, ngf ftue
pdqmy ime zaf m pdqmy. uf tme tmbbqzqp nqradq. u tmhq pdqmye zai, mxkaetm
... kqf ftqk mdq zaf pdqmye, ngf dqmxufk. u imxw mnagf, fmxw mzp eqq ...
ftagst u my mexqqb. ngf tq ime euffuzs tqdq, az ftmf earm ftqdq.... tq ue
rdustfrgxxk efgbup, mxkaetm, rdustfrgxxk efgbup.” uhmz xmgstqp egppqzxk
mzp nqsmz bmouzs mnagf ftq daay.

“ita ue efgbup? ar itay mdq kag fmxwuzs, ndaftqd?” mxkaetm mewqp mzjuagexk
msmuz.

“ftq pqhux! tq’e fmwqz fa hueufuzs yq. tq’e nqqz tqdq fiuoq, mxyaef ftdqq
fuyqe. tq fmgzfqp yq iuft nquzs mzsdk mf tue nquzs m euybxq pqhux mzp zaf
