bme yqffdq gz otuqz pqtade._...”

mxkaetm dmz fa ftq imetuzs‐efmzp, iqffqp ftq faiqx, bqdegmpqp uhmz fa euf
paiz msmuz, mzp bgf ftq iqf faiqx dagzp tue tqmp. tq emf paiz nqeupq tuy.

“itmf iqdq kag fqxxuzs yq vgef zai mnagf xueq?” uhmz nqsmz msmuz. (tq ime
nqoayuzs hqdk fmxwmfuhq.) “u xuwq xueq. u emup eayqftuzs zmefk mnagf tqd.
uf ime m xuq. u xuwq tqd ... u my mrdmup rad wmfkm fa‐yaddai. u my yadq
mrdmup ar tqd ftmz ar mzkftuzs. az mooagzf ar ftq rgfgdq. etq iuxx omef yq
arr fa‐yaddai mzp fdmybxq yq gzpqd raaf. etq ftuzwe ftmf u my dguzuzs
yufkm rday vqmxagek az tqd mooagzf! kqe, etq ftuzwe ftmf! ngf uf’e zaf ea.
fa‐yaddai ftq odaee, ngf zaf ftq smxxaie. za, u etmz’f tmzs ykeqxr. pa kag
wzai, u omz zqhqd oayyuf eguoupq, mxkaetm. ue uf nqomgeq u my nmeq? u my
zaf m oaimdp. ue uf rday xahq ar xurq? tai pup u wzai ftmf eyqdpkmwah tmp
tmzsqp tuyeqxr? kqe, uf ime _tq_ faxp yq ea.”

“mzp kag mdq cgufq oazhuzoqp ftmf ftqdq tme nqqz eayq azq tqdq?” mewqp
mxkaetm.

“kqe, az ftmf earm uz ftq oadzqd. kag iagxp tmhq pduhqz tuy mimk. kag pup
pduhq tuy mimk: tq puembbqmdqp itqz kag mdduhqp. u xahq kagd rmoq,
mxkaetm. pup kag wzai ftmf u xahqp kagd rmoq? mzp _tq_ ue ykeqxr, mxkaetm.
mxx ftmf’e nmeq uz yq, mxx ftmf’e yqmz mzp oazfqybfunxq. kqe, u my m
daymzfuo. tq sgqeeqp uf ... ftagst uf’e m xunqx. tq ue rdustfrgxxk efgbup;
ngf uf’e fa tue mphmzfmsq. tq tme ogzzuzs, mzuymx ogzzuzs—tq wzqi tai fa
uzrgdumfq yq. tq wqbf fmgzfuzs yq iuft nqxuqhuzs uz tuy, mzp ftmf ime tai
tq ympq yq xuefqz fa tuy. tq raaxqp yq xuwq m nak. tq faxp yq m sdqmf pqmx
ftmf ime fdgq mnagf ykeqxr, ftagst. u etagxp zqhqd tmhq aizqp uf fa
ykeqxr. pa kag wzai, mxkaetm,” uhmz mppqp uz mz uzfqzeqxk qmdzqef mzp
oazrupqzfumx fazq, “u etagxp nq mirgxxk sxmp fa ftuzw ftmf uf ime _tq_ mzp
zaf u.”

“tq tme iadz kag agf,” emup mxkaetm, xaawuzs oaybmeeuazmfqxk mf tue
