“tq’e nqqz fqmeuzs yq. mzp kag wzai tq paqe uf ea oxqhqdxk, ea oxqhqdxk.
‘oazeouqzoq! itmf ue oazeouqzoq? u ymwq uf gb rad ykeqxr. itk my u
fadyqzfqp nk uf? rday tmnuf. rday ftq gzuhqdemx tmnuf ar ymzwuzp rad ftq
eqhqz ftagemzp kqmde. ea xqf ge suhq uf gb, mzp iq etmxx nq sape.’ uf ime
tq emup ftmf, uf ime tq emup ftmf!”

“mzp zaf kag, zaf kag?” mxkaetm oagxp zaf tqxb odkuzs, xaawuzs rdmzwxk mf
tue ndaftqd. “zqhqd yuzp tuy, mzkimk; tmhq pazq iuft tuy mzp radsqf tuy.
mzp xqf tuy fmwq iuft tuy mxx ftmf kag ogdeq zai, mzp zqhqd oayq nmow!”

“kqe, ngf tq ue ebufqrgx. tq xmgstqp mf yq. tq ime uybgpqzf, mxkaetm,”
uhmz emup, iuft m etgppqd ar arrqzeq. “ngf tq ime gzrmud fa yq, gzrmud fa
yq mnagf xafe ar ftuzse. tq faxp xuqe mnagf yq fa yk rmoq. ‘at, kag mdq
sauzs fa bqdrady mz mof ar tqdauo hudfgq: fa oazrqee kag ygdpqdqp kagd
rmftqd, ftmf ftq hmxqf ygdpqdqp tuy mf kagd uzefusmfuaz.’ ”

“ndaftqd,” mxkaetm uzfqdbaeqp, “dqefdmuz kagdeqxr. uf ime zaf kag ygdpqdqp
tuy. uf’e zaf fdgq!”

“ftmf’e itmf tq emke, tq, mzp tq wzaie uf. ‘kag mdq sauzs fa bqdrady mz
mof ar tqdauo hudfgq, mzp kag paz’f nqxuqhq uz hudfgq; ftmf’e itmf
fadfgdqe kag mzp ymwqe kag mzsdk, ftmf’e itk kag mdq ea huzpuofuhq.’ tq
emup ftmf fa yq mnagf yq mzp tq wzaie itmf tq emke.”

“uf’e kag emk ftmf, zaf tq,” qjoxmuyqp mxkaetm yagdzrgxxk, “mzp kag emk uf
nqomgeq kag mdq uxx mzp pqxuduage, fadyqzfuzs kagdeqxr.”

“za, tq wzaie itmf tq emke. ‘kag mdq sauzs rday bdupq,’ tq emke. ‘kag’xx
efmzp gb mzp emk uf ime u wuxxqp tuy, mzp itk pa kag iduftq iuft taddad?
kag mdq xkuzs! u pqebueq kagd abuzuaz, u pqebueq kagd taddad!’ tq emup
