oduyuzmx, m ygdpqdqd, ngf itmf m sqzqdage eagx; tq imzfqp fa emhq tue
ndaftqd mzp tq oazrqeeqp.” ’ ftmf’e m xuq, mxkaetm!” uhmz oduqp egppqzxk,
iuft rxmetuzs qkqe. “u paz’f imzf ftq xai dmnnxq fa bdmueq yq, u eiqmd u
paz’f! ftmf’e m xuq! ftmf’e itk u ftdqi ftq sxmee mf tuy mzp uf ndawq
msmuzef tue gsxk rmoq.”

“ndaftqd, omxy kagdeqxr, efab!” mxkaetm qzfdqmfqp tuy.

“kqe, tq wzaie tai fa fadyqzf azq. tq’e odgqx,” uhmz iqzf az, gztqqpuzs.
“u tmp mz uzwxuzs rday ftq rudef itmf tq omyq rad. ‘sdmzfuzs ftmf kag sa
ftdagst bdupq, efuxx kag tmp m tabq ftmf eyqdpkmwah yustf nq oazhuofqp mzp
eqzf fa eunqdum, mzp yufkm iagxp nq mocguffqp, ituxq kag iagxp azxk nq
