“at, kqe, ftmf’e itmf u emk,” tq iqzf az efgnnadzxk. “azq tqmp ue saap,
ngf fia mdq ygot nqffqd, ngf tq pup zaf yqqf mzaftqd tqmp iuft iufe, mzp
