xuebqp, ‘_saff pqd eatz_.’ ‘_saff pqd tquxusq squef_.’ ftqz tq xmgstqp mzp
emup me nqef tq oagxp, ‘_saff pqd tquxusq squef_.’ u iqzf mimk, mzp fia
pmke mrfqd u tmbbqzqp fa nq bmeeuzs, mzp tq etagfqp fa yq ar tuyeqxr,
‘gzoxq, _saff pqd hmfqd, saff pqd eatz_,’ mzp tq tmp azxk radsaffqz ‘_saff
pqd tquxusq squef_.’ ngf u dqyuzpqp tuy ar uf mzp u rqxf hqdk eaddk rad
tuy msmuz. ngf tq ime fmwqz mimk, mzp u pup zaf eqq tuy msmuz. fiqzfk‐
ftdqq kqmde bmeeqp. u my euffuzs azq yadzuzs uz yk efgpk, m itufq‐tmudqp
axp ymz, itqz ftqdq imxwe uzfa ftq daay m nxaayuzs kagzs ymz, itay u
etagxp zqhqd tmhq dqoaszulqp, ngf tq tqxp gb tue ruzsqd mzp emup,
xmgstuzs, ‘_saff pqd hmfqd, saff pqd eatz_, mzp _saff pqd tquxusq squef_.
u tmhq vgef mdduhqp mzp tmhq oayq fa ftmzw kag rad ftmf bagzp ar zgfe, rad
za azq qxeq qhqd nagstf yq m bagzp ar zgfe; kag mdq ftq azxk azq ftmf qhqd
pup.’ mzp ftqz u dqyqynqdqp yk tmbbk kagft mzp ftq baad otuxp uz ftq kmdp,
iuftagf naafe az tue rqqf, mzp yk tqmdf ime fagotqp mzp u emup, ‘kag mdq m
sdmfqrgx kagzs ymz, rad kag tmhq dqyqynqdqp mxx kagd xurq ftq bagzp ar
zgfe u nagstf kag uz kagd otuxptaap.’ mzp u qyndmoqp tuy mzp nxqeeqp tuy.
mzp u etqp fqmde. tq xmgstqp, ngf tq etqp fqmde, faa ... rad ftq dgeeumz
arfqz xmgste itqz tq agstf fa nq iqqbuzs. ngf tq pup iqqb; u emi uf. mzp
