“mzp u my iqqbuzs zai, sqdymz, u my iqqbuzs zai, faa, kag emuzfxk ymz,”
yufkm oduqp egppqzxk.

uz mzk omeq ftq mzqopafq ympq m oqdfmuz rmhadmnxq uybdqeeuaz az ftq
bgnxuo. ngf ftq otuqr eqzemfuaz uz yufkm’e rmhad ime odqmfqp nk ftq
qhupqzoq ar wmfqduzm uhmzahzm, ituot u iuxx pqeodunq pudqofxk. uzpqqp,
itqz ftq iufzqeeqe _à péotmdsq_, ftmf ue, omxxqp nk ftq pqrqzeq, nqsmz
suhuzs qhupqzoq, radfgzq eqqyqp mxx mf azoq ymdwqpxk yadq rmhadmnxq fa
yufkm, mzp itmf ime bmdfuogxmdxk efduwuzs, ftue ime m egdbdueq qhqz fa ftq
oagzeqx rad ftq pqrqzeq. ngf nqradq wmfqduzm uhmzahzm ime omxxqp, mxkaetm
