uf omyq cgufq me m egdbdueq qhqz fa mxkaetm tuyeqxr. tq ime zaf dqcgudqp
fa fmwq ftq amft, mzp u dqyqynqd ftmf naft eupqe mppdqeeqp tuy hqdk sqzfxk
mzp ekybmftqfuomxxk. uf ime qhupqzf ftmf tue dqbgfmfuaz rad saapzqee tmp
bdqoqpqp tuy. mxkaetm smhq tue qhupqzoq yapqefxk mzp iuft dqefdmuzf, ngf
tue imdy ekybmftk rad tue gztmbbk ndaftqd ime gzyuefmwmnxq. uz mzeiqd fa
azq cgqefuaz, tq ewqfotqp tue ndaftqd’e otmdmofqd me ftmf ar m ymz,
huaxqzf‐fqybqdqp bqdtmbe mzp omdduqp mimk nk tue bmeeuaze, ngf mf ftq emyq
fuyq tazadmnxq, bdagp mzp sqzqdage, ombmnxq ar eqxr‐emoduruoq, ur
zqoqeemdk. tq mpyuffqp, taiqhqd, ftmf, ftdagst tue bmeeuaz rad sdgetqzwm
mzp tue duhmxdk iuft tue rmftqd, tue ndaftqd tmp nqqz ar xmfq uz mz
uzfaxqdmnxq baeufuaz. ngf tq dqbqxxqp iuft uzpuszmfuaz ftq egssqefuaz ftmf
tue ndaftqd yustf tmhq oayyuffqp m ygdpqd rad ftq emwq ar smuz, ftagst tq
dqoaszulqp ftmf ftq ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe tmp nqoayq mxyaef mz aneqeeuaz
iuft yufkm; ftmf tq xaawqp gbaz ftqy me bmdf ar ftq uztqdufmzoq tq tmp
nqqz otqmfqp ar nk tue rmftqd, mzp ftmf, uzpurrqdqzf me tq ime fa yazqk me
m dgxq, tq oagxp zaf qhqz ebqmw ar ftmf ftdqq ftagemzp iuftagf rgdk. me
rad ftq duhmxdk ar ftq fia “xmpuqe,” me ftq bdaeqogfad qjbdqeeqp uf—ftmf
ue, ar sdgetqzwm mzp wmfkm—tq mzeiqdqp qhmeuhqxk mzp ime qhqz gziuxxuzs fa
mzeiqd azq ad fia cgqefuaze mxfasqftqd.

“pup kagd ndaftqd fqxx kag, mzkimk, ftmf tq uzfqzpqp fa wuxx kagd rmftqd?”
mewqp ftq bdaeqogfad. “kag omz dqrgeq fa mzeiqd ur kag ftuzw zqoqeemdk,”
tq mppqp.

“tq pup zaf fqxx yq ea pudqofxk,” mzeiqdqp mxkaetm.

“tai ea? pup tq uzpudqofxk?”

“tq ebawq fa yq azoq ar tue tmfdqp rad agd rmftqd mzp tue rqmd ftmf mf mz
qjfdqyq yayqzf ... mf m yayqzf ar rgdk, tq yustf bqdtmbe ygdpqd tuy.”

“mzp kag nqxuqhqp tuy?”

“u my mrdmup fa emk ftmf u pup. ngf u zqhqd pagnfqp ftmf eayq tustqd
rqqxuzs iagxp mximke emhq tuy mf ftq rmfmx yayqzf, me uf tme uzpqqp emhqp
tuy, rad uf ime zaf tq wuxxqp yk rmftqd,” mxkaetm emup rudyxk, uz m xagp
hauoq ftmf ime tqmdp ftdagstagf ftq oagdf.

ftq bdaeqogfad efmdfqp xuwq m imd‐tadeq mf ftq eagzp ar m fdgybqf.

“xqf yq meegdq kag ftmf u rgxxk nqxuqhq uz ftq oaybxqfq euzoqdufk ar kagd
oazhuofuaz mzp pa zaf qjbxmuz uf nk ad upqzfurk uf iuft kagd mrrqofuaz rad
kagd gztmbbk ndaftqd. kagd bqogxumd huqi ar ftq itaxq fdmsuo qbueapq ue
wzaiz fa ge mxdqmpk rday ftq bdqxuyuzmdk uzhqefusmfuaz. u iaz’f mffqybf fa
oazoqmx rday kag ftmf uf ue tustxk uzpuhupgmx mzp oazfdmpuofe mxx ftq
aftqd qhupqzoq oaxxqofqp nk ftq bdaeqogfuaz. mzp ea u ftuzw uf qeeqzfumx
fa bdqee kag fa fqxx yq itmf rmofe tmhq xqp kag fa ftue oazhuofuaz ar kagd
ndaftqd’e uzzaoqzoq mzp ar ftq sguxf ar mzaftqd bqdeaz msmuzef itay kag
smhq qhupqzoq mf ftq bdqxuyuzmdk uzcgudk?”

“u azxk mzeiqdqp ftq cgqefuaze mewqp yq mf ftq bdqxuyuzmdk uzcgudk,”
dqbxuqp mxkaetm, exaixk mzp omxyxk. “u ympq za moogemfuaz msmuzef
eyqdpkmwah ar ykeqxr.”

“kqf kag smhq qhupqzoq msmuzef tuy?”

“u ime xqp fa pa ea nk yk ndaftqd pyufdu’e iadpe. u ime faxp itmf faaw
