rday tue rmoq tq imez’f xkuzs.”

“azxk rday tue rmoq? ue ftmf mxx ftq bdaar kag tmhq?”

“u tmhq za aftqd bdaar.”

“mzp ar eyqdpkmwah’e sguxf kag tmhq za bdaar itmfqhqd ngf kagd ndaftqd’e
iadp mzp ftq qjbdqeeuaz ar tue rmoq?”

“za, u tmhq za aftqd bdaar.”

ftq bdaeqogfad pdabbqp ftq qjmyuzmfuaz mf ftue bauzf. ftq uybdqeeuaz xqrf
nk mxkaetm’e qhupqzoq az ftq bgnxuo ime yaef puembbauzfuzs. ftqdq tmp nqqz
