oqdfmuz yadmx oazhuofuaze ea zmfgdmx uz m ndaftqd.

ngf rqfkgwahufot nqsmz tue odaee‐qjmyuzmfuaz. az tue mewuzs mxkaetm itqz
uf ime ftmf ftq bdueazqd tmp faxp tuy ar tue tmfdqp rad tue rmftqd mzp
ftmf tq yustf wuxx tuy, mzp itqftqd tq tmp tqmdp uf, rad uzefmzoq, mf
ftqud xmef yqqfuzs nqradq ftq omfmefdabtq, mxkaetm efmdfqp me tq mzeiqdqp,
me ftagst azxk vgef dqoaxxqofuzs mzp gzpqdefmzpuzs eayqftuzs.

“u dqyqynqd azq oudogyefmzoq zai ituot u’p cgufq radsaffqz ykeqxr. uf
imez’f oxqmd fa yq mf ftq fuyq, ngf zai—”

mzp, anhuagexk azxk zai rad ftq rudef fuyq efdgow nk mz upqm, tq dqoagzfqp
qmsqdxk tai, mf tue xmef uzfqdhuqi iuft yufkm ftmf qhqzuzs gzpqd ftq fdqq,
az ftq damp fa ftq yazmefqdk, yufkm tmp efdgow tuyeqxr az ftq ndqmef, “ftq
gbbqd bmdf ar ftq ndqmef,” mzp tmp dqbqmfqp eqhqdmx fuyqe ftmf tq tmp m
yqmze ar dqsmuzuzs tue tazad, ftmf ftmf yqmze ime tqdq, tqdq az tue
ndqmef. “u ftagstf, itqz tq efdgow tuyeqxr az ftq ndqmef, tq yqmzf ftmf uf
