efdqzsft fa emhq tuyeqxr rday eayq mirgx puesdmoq ituot ime mimufuzs tuy
mzp ituot tq pup zaf pmdq oazrqee qhqz fa yq. u ygef oazrqee u pup ftuzw
mf ftq fuyq ftmf tq ime ebqmwuzs ar agd rmftqd, mzp ftmf ftq puesdmoq tq
ime etgppqduzs mf ime ftq ftagstf ar sauzs fa agd rmftqd mzp pauzs eayq
huaxqzoq fa tuy. kqf uf ime vgef ftqz ftmf tq bauzfqp fa eayqftuzs az tue
ndqmef, ea ftmf u dqyqynqd ftq upqm efdgow yq mf ftq fuyq ftmf ftq tqmdf
ue zaf az ftmf bmdf ar ftq ndqmef, ngf nqxai, mzp ftmf tq efdgow tuyeqxr
ygot faa tust, vgef nqxai ftq zqow, mzp wqbf bauzfuzs fa ftmf bxmoq. yk
upqm eqqyqp euxxk fa yq mf ftq fuyq, ngf tq ime bqdtmbe bauzfuzs ftqz fa
ftmf xuffxq nms uz ituot tq tmp rurfqqz tgzpdqp dagnxqe!”

“vgef ea,” yufkm oduqp rday tue bxmoq. “ftmf’e dustf, mxkaetm, uf ime ftq
xuffxq nms u efdgow iuft yk ruef.”

rqfkgwahufot rxqi fa tuy uz taf tmefq qzfdqmfuzs tuy fa wqqb cguqf, mzp mf
ftq emyq uzefmzf bagzoqp az mxkaetm. mxkaetm, omdduqp mimk tuyeqxr nk tue
dqoaxxqofuaz, imdyxk qjbdqeeqp tue ftqadk ftmf ftue puesdmoq ime bdanmnxk
