wmfqduzm uhmzahzm me tmxr ar itmf tq aiqp tqd, ngf ituot tq tmp kqf
pqfqdyuzqp zaf fa dqbmk tqd mzp fa geq rad mzaftqd bgdbaeq—zmyqxk, fa
qzmnxq tuy fa qxabq iuft sdgetqzwm, ur etq oazeqzfqp.

“uf ue ea, uf ygef nq ea,” qjoxmuyqp mxkaetm, uz egppqz qjoufqyqzf. “yk
ndaftqd oduqp eqhqdmx fuyqe ftmf tmxr ar ftq puesdmoq, tmxr ar uf (tq emup
_tmxr_ eqhqdmx fuyqe) tq oagxp rdqq tuyeqxr rday mf azoq, ngf ftmf tq ime
ea gztmbbk uz tue iqmwzqee ar iuxx ftmf tq iagxpz’f pa uf ... ftmf tq wzqi
nqradqtmzp tq ime uzombmnxq ar pauzs uf!”

“mzp kag oxqmdxk, oazrupqzfxk dqyqynqd ftmf tq efdgow tuyeqxr vgef az ftue
bmdf ar ftq ndqmef?” rqfkgwahufot mewqp qmsqdxk.

“oxqmdxk mzp oazrupqzfxk, rad u ftagstf mf ftq fuyq, ‘itk paqe tq efduwq
tuyeqxr gb ftqdq itqz ftq tqmdf ue xaiqd paiz?’ mzp ftq ftagstf eqqyqp
efgbup fa yq mf ftq fuyq ... u dqyqynqd ufe eqqyuzs efgbup ... uf rxmetqp
ftdagst yk yuzp. ftmf’e itmf ndagstf uf nmow fa yq vgef zai. tai oagxp u
