suhq uf nmow. mzp ftq yaef etmyqrgx bmdf ar uf ime ftmf u wzqi nqradqtmzp
u etagxpz’f suhq uf nmow! kag mdq dustf, mxkaetm! ftmzwe, mxkaetm!”

ea mxkaetm’e odaee‐qjmyuzmfuaz qzpqp. itmf ime uybadfmzf mzp efduwuzs
mnagf uf ime ftmf azq rmof mf xqmef tmp nqqz ragzp, mzp qhqz ftagst ftue
iqdq azxk azq fuzk nuf ar qhupqzoq, m yqdq tuzf mf qhupqzoq, uf pup sa
eayq xuffxq imk faimdpe bdahuzs ftmf ftq nms tmp qjuefqp mzp tmp oazfmuzqp
rurfqqz tgzpdqp dagnxqe mzp ftmf ftq bdueazqd tmp zaf nqqz xkuzs mf ftq
bdqxuyuzmdk uzcgudk itqz tq mxxqsqp mf yawdaq ftmf ftaeq rurfqqz tgzpdqp
dagnxqe iqdq “tue aiz.” mxkaetm ime sxmp. iuft m rxgetqp rmoq tq yahqp
mimk fa ftq eqmf meeuszqp fa tuy. tq wqbf dqbqmfuzs fa tuyeqxr: “tai ime
uf u radsaf? tai oagxp u tmhq radsaffqz uf? mzp itmf ympq uf oayq nmow fa
yq zai?”

wmfqduzm uhmzahzm ime omxxqp fa ftq iufzqee‐naj. me etq qzfqdqp eayqftuzs
qjfdmadpuzmdk tmbbqzqp uz ftq oagdf. ftq xmpuqe oxgfotqp ftqud xadszqffqe
mzp abqdm‐sxmeeqe. ftqdq ime m efud myazs ftq yqz: eayq efaap gb fa sqf m
