m etqqf” az tqd qzfdmzoq. mxx uz nxmow, etq mphmzoqp yapqefxk, mxyaef
fuyupxk. uf ime uybaeeunxq fa fqxx rday tqd rmoq ftmf etq ime msufmfqp;
ngf ftqdq ime m dqeaxgfq sxqmy uz tqd pmdw mzp sxaayk qkqe. u ymk dqymdw
ftmf ymzk bqabxq yqzfuazqp ftmf etq xaawqp bmdfuogxmdxk tmzpeayq mf ftmf
yayqzf. etq ebawq earfxk ngf oxqmdxk, ea ftmf etq ime tqmdp mxx ahqd ftq
oagdf. etq qjbdqeeqp tqdeqxr iuft oaybaegdq, ad mf xqmef fduqp fa mbbqmd
oaybaeqp. ftq bdqeupqzf nqsmz tue qjmyuzmfuaz pueodqqfxk mzp hqdk
dqebqofrgxxk, me ftagst mrdmup fa fagot az “oqdfmuz otadpe,” mzp etaiuzs
oazeupqdmfuaz rad tqd sdqmf gztmbbuzqee. ngf uz mzeiqd fa azq ar ftq rudef
cgqefuaze wmfqduzm uhmzahzm dqbxuqp rudyxk ftmf etq tmp nqqz radyqdxk
nqfdaftqp fa ftq bdueazqd, “gzfux tq xqrf yq ar tue aiz mooadp...” etq
mppqp cguqfxk. itqz ftqk mewqp tqd mnagf ftq ftdqq ftagemzp etq tmp
qzfdgefqp fa yufkm fa baef fa tqd dqxmfuaze, etq emup rudyxk, “u pupz’f
suhq tuy ftq yazqk euybxk fa eqzp uf arr. u rqxf mf ftq fuyq ftmf tq ime
uz sdqmf zqqp ar yazqk.... u smhq tuy ftq ftdqq ftagemzp az ftq
gzpqdefmzpuzs ftmf tq etagxp baef uf iuftuz ftq yazft ur tq omdqp fa.
ftqdq ime za zqqp rad tuy fa iaddk tuyeqxr mnagf ftmf pqnf mrfqdimdpe.”

u iuxx zaf dqbqmf mxx ftq cgqefuaze mewqp tqd mzp mxx tqd mzeiqde uz
pqfmux. u iuxx azxk suhq ftq egnefmzoq ar tqd qhupqzoq.

“u ime rudyxk oazhuzoqp ftmf tq iagxp eqzp arr ftmf egy me eaaz me tq saf
yazqk rday tue rmftqd,” etq iqzf az. “u tmhq zqhqd pagnfqp tue
pueuzfqdqefqpzqee mzp tue tazqefk ... tue eodgbgxage tazqefk ... uz yazqk
ymffqde. tq rqxf cgufq oqdfmuz ftmf tq iagxp dqoquhq ftq yazqk rday tue
rmftqd, mzp ebawq fa yq eqhqdmx fuyqe mnagf uf. u wzqi tq tmp m rqgp iuft
tue rmftqd mzp tmhq mximke nqxuqhqp ftmf tq tmp nqqz gzrmudxk fdqmfqp nk
tue rmftqd. u paz’f dqyqynqd mzk ftdqmf gffqdqp nk tuy msmuzef tue rmftqd.
tq oqdfmuzxk zqhqd gffqdqp mzk egot ftdqmf nqradq yq. ur tq tmp oayq fa yq
mf ftmf fuyq, u etagxp tmhq mf azoq dqxuqhqp tue mzjuqfk mnagf ftmf
gzxgowk ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe, ngf tq tmp suhqz gb oayuzs fa eqq yq ...
mzp u ykeqxr ime bgf uz egot m baeufuaz ... ftmf u oagxp zaf uzhufq
tuy.... mzp u tmp za dustf, uzpqqp, fa nq qjmofuzs me fa ftmf yazqk,” etq
