azoq uzpqnfqp fa tuy rad meeuefmzoq uz yazqk rad yadq ftmz ftdqq ftagemzp,
mzp u faaw uf, mxftagst u oagxp zaf mf ftmf fuyq radqeqq ftmf u etagxp
qhqd nq uz m baeufuaz fa dqbmk yk pqnf.”

ftqdq ime m zafq ar pqrumzoq uz tqd hauoq. uf ime ftqz rqfkgwahufot nqsmz
tue odaee‐qjmyuzmfuaz.

“pup ftmf fmwq bxmoq zaf tqdq, ngf mf ftq nqsuzzuzs ar kagd mocgmuzfmzoq?”
rqfkgwahufot egssqefqp omgfuagexk, rqqxuzs tue imk, uzefmzfxk eoqzfuzs
eayqftuzs rmhadmnxq. u ygef yqzfuaz uz bmdqzftqeue ftmf, ftagst
rqfkgwahufot tmp nqqz ndagstf rday bqfqdengds bmdfxk mf ftq uzefmzoq ar
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm tqdeqxr, tq wzqi zaftuzs mnagf ftq qbueapq ar ftq ragd
ftagemzp dagnxqe suhqz tqd nk yufkm, mzp ar tqd “naiuzs fa ftq sdagzp fa
tuy.” etq oazoqmxqp ftue rday tuy mzp emup zaftuzs mnagf uf, mzp ftmf ime
efdmzsq. uf ymk nq bdqffk oqdfmuzxk meegyqp ftmf etq tqdeqxr pup zaf wzai
fuxx ftq hqdk xmef yuzgfq itqftqd etq iagxp ebqmw ar ftmf qbueapq uz ftq
oagdf, mzp imufqp rad ftq uzebudmfuaz ar ftq yayqzf.

za, u omz zqhqd radsqf ftaeq yayqzfe. etq nqsmz fqxxuzs tqd efadk. etq
faxp qhqdkftuzs, ftq itaxq qbueapq ftmf yufkm tmp faxp mxkaetm, mzp tqd
naiuzs fa ftq sdagzp, mzp tqd dqmeaz. etq faxp mnagf tqd rmftqd mzp tqd
sauzs fa yufkm, mzp pup zaf uz azq iadp, uz m euzsxq tuzf, egssqef ftmf
yufkm tmp tuyeqxr, ftdagst tqd euefqd, bdabaeqp ftqk etagxp “eqzp tuy
wmfqduzm uhmzahzm” fa rqfot ftq yazqk. etq sqzqdagexk oazoqmxqp ftmf mzp
ime zaf metmyqp fa ymwq uf mbbqmd me ftagst etq tmp ar tqd aiz uybgxeq dgz
fa ftq kagzs arruoqd, dqxkuzs az eayqftuzs ... fa nqs tuy rad ftq yazqk.
uf ime eayqftuzs fdqyqzpage! u fgdzqp oaxp mzp fdqynxqp me u xuefqzqp. ftq
oagdf ime tgetqp, fdkuzs fa omfot qmot iadp. uf ime eayqftuzs gzqjmybxqp.
qhqz rday egot m eqxr‐iuxxqp mzp oazfqybfgagexk bdagp sudx me etq ime,
