eyqdpkmwah ime pqmp! uf ime egot m etaow ftmf uf pdahq tuy agf ar tue yuzp
... mzp mxx ftdagst ftue yazefqd, mxx rad ftq emwq ar emhuzs ftq yazefqd!”

