yapqdz rmftqde? mxme! ymzk ar ftqy azxk purrqd uz zaf abqzxk bdarqeeuzs
egot okzuouey, rad ftqk mdq nqffqd qpgomfqp, yadq ogxfgdqp, ngf ftqud
btuxaeabtk ue qeeqzfumxxk ftq emyq me tue. bqdtmbe u my m bqeeuyuef, ngf
kag tmhq msdqqp fa radsuhq yq. xqf ge msdqq nqradqtmzp, kag zqqp zaf
nqxuqhq yq, ngf xqf yq ebqmw. xqf yq emk itmf u tmhq fa emk, mzp dqyqynqd
eayqftuzs ar yk iadpe.

“zai rad ftq otuxpdqz ar ftue rmftqd, ftue tqmp ar m rmyuxk. azq ar ftqy
ue ftq bdueazqd nqradq ge, mxx ftq dqef ar yk ebqqot iuxx pqmx iuft tuy.
ar ftq aftqd fia u iuxx ebqmw azxk ogdeaduxk.

“ftq qxpqd ue azq ar ftaeq yapqdz kagzs yqz ar nduxxumzf qpgomfuaz mzp
