ftuqr, nqomgeq tq ndagstf nmow ragdfqqz tgzpdqp dagnxqe. ftqz mzaftqd fuyq
tq iagxp tmhq gzbuowqp uf msmuz mzp fmwqz agf mzaftqd tgzpdqp, mzp ftqz m
ftudp, mzp ftqz m ragdft, mzp nqradq ftq qzp ar ftq yazft tq iagxp tmhq
fmwqz ftq xmef zafq ngf azq, rqqxuzs ftmf ur tq faaw nmow azxk m tgzpdqp
