uf, fa puefadf ftq rmofe ad yuzuyulq ftqy. ngf tq ime rmd rday puefadfuzs
ad yuzuyuluzs ftqy. za azq ngf mz uzzaoqzf ymz, ita tmp za rqmd ar nquzs
otmdsqp iuft oaybxuoufk, oagxp tmhq mofqp me tq pup. mzp uz m ruf ar
yqxmzotaxk mdueuzs rday tue pueqmeq mzp ftue omfmefdabtq tq tmzsqp tuyeqxr
kqefqdpmk. tq xqrf m zafq iduffqz uz tue bqogxumd xmzsgmsq, ‘u pqefdak
ykeqxr ar yk aiz iuxx mzp uzoxuzmfuaz ea me fa ftdai za nxmyq az mzk azq.’
itmf iagxp uf tmhq oaef tuy fa mpp: ‘u my ftq ygdpqdqd, zaf wmdmymlah’?
ngf ftmf tq pup zaf mpp. pup tue oazeouqzoq xqmp tuy fa eguoupq mzp zaf fa
mhaiuzs tue sguxf?

“mzp itmf raxxaiqp? zafqe rad ftdqq ftagemzp dagnxqe iqdq ndagstf uzfa ftq
oagdf vgef zai, mzp iq iqdq faxp ftmf ftqk iqdq ftq emyq ftmf xmk uz ftq
qzhqxabq zai az ftq fmnxq nqradq ge, mzp ftmf ftq iufzqee tmp dqoquhqp
ftqy rday eyqdpkmwah ftq pmk nqradq. ngf u zqqp zaf dqomxx ftq bmuzrgx
eoqzq, ftagst u iuxx ymwq azq ad fia oayyqzfe, eqxqofuzs egot fduhumx azqe
me yustf zaf nq anhuage mf rudef eustf fa qhqdk azq, mzp ea ymk nq
ahqdxaawqp. uz ftq rudef bxmoq, eyqdpkmwah ygef tmhq suhqz nmow ftq yazqk
mzp tmzsqp tuyeqxr kqefqdpmk rday dqyadeq. mzp azxk kqefqdpmk tq oazrqeeqp
tue sguxf fa uhmz wmdmymlah, me ftq xmffqd uzradye ge. ur uf iqdq zaf ea,
uzpqqp, itk etagxp uhmz rkapadahufot tmhq wqbf euxqzoq fuxx zai? mzp ea,
ur tq tme oazrqeeqp, ftqz itk, u mew msmuz, pup tq zaf mhai ftq itaxq
fdgft uz ftq xmef xqffqd tq xqrf nqtuzp, wzaiuzs ftmf ftq uzzaoqzf
bdueazqd tmp fa rmoq ftue fqddunxq adpqmx ftq zqjf pmk?

“ftq yazqk mxazq ue za bdaar. m iqqw msa, cgufq nk otmzoq, ftq rmof omyq
fa ftq wzaixqpsq ar ykeqxr mzp fia aftqd bqdeaze uz ftue oagdf ftmf uhmz
rkapadahufot tmp eqzf fia ruhq bqd oqzf. oagbaze ar ruhq ftagemzp
qmot—ftmf ue, fqz ftagemzp uz mxx—fa ftq otuqr faiz ar ftq bdahuzoq fa nq
otmzsqp. u azxk yqzfuaz ftue fa bauzf agf ftmf mzk azq ymk tmhq yazqk, mzp
ftmf uf omz’f nq bdahqp ftmf ftqeq zafqe mdq ftq emyq me iqdq uz rkapad
bmhxahufot’e qzhqxabq.

“uhmz wmdmymlah, mrfqd dqoquhuzs kqefqdpmk m oayygzuomfuaz ar egot
uybadfmzoq rday ftq dqmx ygdpqdqd, pup zaf efud. itk pupz’f tq dqbadf uf
mf azoq? itk pup tq bgf uf mxx arr fuxx yadzuzs? u ftuzw u tmhq m dustf fa
oazvqofgdq itk. tue tqmxft tmp nqqz suhuzs imk rad m iqqw bmef: tq tmp
mpyuffqp fa m paofad mzp fa tue yaef uzfuymfq rduqzpe ftmf tq ime
egrrqduzs rday tmxxgouzmfuaze mzp eqquzs btmzfaye ar ftq pqmp: tq ime az
ftq qhq ar ftq mffmow ar ndmuz rqhqd nk ituot tq tme nqqz efduowqz paiz
fa‐pmk. uz ftue oazpufuaz tq egppqzxk tqmdp ar eyqdpkmwah’e pqmft, mzp mf
azoq dqrxqofqp, ‘ftq ymz ue pqmp, u omz ftdai ftq nxmyq az tuy mzp emhq yk
ndaftqd. u tmhq yazqk. u iuxx fmwq m daxx ar zafqe mzp emk ftmf eyqdpkmwah
smhq ftqy yq nqradq tue pqmft.’ kag iuxx emk ftmf ime puetazadmnxq: uf’e
puetazadmnxq fa exmzpqd qhqz ftq pqmp, mzp qhqz fa emhq m ndaftqd. fdgq,
ngf itmf ur tq exmzpqdqp tuy gzoazeouagexk? itmf ur, ruzmxxk gztuzsqp nk
ftq egppqz zqie ar ftq hmxqf’e pqmft, tq uymsuzqp uf dqmxxk ime ea? kag
emi ftq dqoqzf eoqzq: kag tmhq eqqz ftq iufzqee’e oazpufuaz. tq ime
efmzpuzs gb mzp ime ebqmwuzs, ngf itqdq ime tue yuzp?

“ftqz raxxaiqp ftq paogyqzf, ftq bdueazqd’e xqffqd iduffqz fia pmke nqradq
ftq oduyq, mzp oazfmuzuzs m oaybxqfq bdasdmy ar ftq ygdpqd. itk, ftqz, mdq
iq xaawuzs rad mzk aftqd bdasdmy? ftq oduyq ime oayyuffqp bdqoueqxk
mooadpuzs fa ftue bdasdmy, mzp nk za aftqd ftmz ftq idufqd ar uf. kqe,
sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, uf iqzf arr iuftagf m tufot! tq pup zaf dgz
dqebqofrgxxk mzp fuyupxk mimk rday tue rmftqd’e iuzpai, ftagst tq ime
rudyxk oazhuzoqp ftmf ftq anvqof ar tue mrrqofuaze ime iuft tuy. za, ftmf
ue mnegdp mzp gzxuwqxk! tq iqzf uz mzp ygdpqdqp tuy. yaef xuwqxk tq wuxxqp
tuy uz mzsqd, ngdzuzs iuft dqeqzfyqzf, me eaaz me tq xaawqp az tue tmfqp
duhmx. ngf tmhuzs wuxxqp tuy, bdanmnxk iuft azq nxai ar ftq ndmee bqefxq,
mzp tmhuzs oazhuzoqp tuyeqxr, mrfqd omdqrgx eqmdot, ftmf etq ime zaf
ftqdq, tq pup zaf, taiqhqd, radsqf fa bgf tue tmzp gzpqd ftq buxxai mzp
fmwq agf ftq qzhqxabq, ftq fadz oahqd ar ituot xuqe zai az ftq fmnxq
nqradq ge.

“u yqzfuaz ftue rmof ftmf kag ymk zafq azq, fa yk ftuzwuzs, hqdk
otmdmofqduefuo oudogyefmzoq. tmp tq nqqz mz qjbqduqzoqp ygdpqdqd mzp tmp
tq oayyuffqp ftq ygdpqd rad ftq emwq ar smuz azxk, iagxp tq tmhq xqrf ftq
fadz qzhqxabq az ftq rxaad me uf ime ragzp, nqeupq ftq oadbeq? tmp uf nqqz
eyqdpkmwah, rad uzefmzoq, ygdpqduzs tue ymefqd fa dan tuy, tq iagxp tmhq
euybxk omdduqp mimk ftq qzhqxabq iuft tuy, iuftagf fdagnxuzs tuyeqxr fa
abqz uf ahqd tue huofuy’e oadbeq, rad tq iagxp tmhq wzaiz rad oqdfmuz ftmf
ftq zafqe iqdq uz ftq qzhqxabq—ftqk tmp nqqz bgf uz mzp eqmxqp gb uz tue
bdqeqzoq—mzp tmp tq fmwqz ftq qzhqxabq iuft tuy, za azq iagxp qhqd tmhq
wzaiz ar ftq dannqdk. u mew kag, sqzfxqyqz, iagxp eyqdpkmwah tmhq nqtmhqp
uz ftmf imk? iagxp tq tmhq xqrf ftq qzhqxabq az ftq rxaad?

“za, ftue ime ftq mofuaz ar m rdmzfuo ygdpqdqd, m ygdpqdqd ita ime zaf m
ftuqr mzp tmp zqhqd efaxqz nqradq ftmf pmk, ita ezmfotqp ftq zafqe rday
gzpqd ftq buxxai, zaf xuwq m ftuqr efqmxuzs ftqy, ngf me ftagst equluzs
tue aiz bdabqdfk rday ftq ftuqr ita tmp efaxqz uf. rad ftmf ime ftq upqm
ituot tmp nqoayq mxyaef mz uzemzq aneqeeuaz uz pyufdu wmdmymlah uz dqsmdp
fa ftmf yazqk. mzp bagzouzs gbaz ftq qzhqxabq, ituot tq tmp zqhqd eqqz
nqradq, tq fadq uf abqz fa ymwq egdq itqftqd ftq yazqk ime uz uf, mzp dmz
mimk iuft ftq yazqk uz tue baowqf, qhqz radsqffuzs fa oazeupqd ftmf tq tmp
xqrf mz mefagzpuzs buqoq ar qhupqzoq msmuzef tuyeqxr uz ftmf fadz qzhqxabq
az ftq rxaad. mxx nqomgeq uf ime wmdmymlah, zaf eyqdpkmwah, tq pupz’f
ftuzw, tq pupz’f dqrxqof, mzp tai etagxp tq? tq dmz mimk; tq tqmdp nqtuzp
tuy ftq eqdhmzf odk agf; ftq axp ymz omgstf tuy, efabbqp tuy mzp ime
rqxxqp fa ftq sdagzp nk ftq ndmee bqefxq.

“ftq bdueazqd, yahqp nk bufk, xqmbf paiz fa xaaw mf tuy. iagxp kag nqxuqhq
uf, tq fqxxe ge ftmf tq xqmbf paiz agf ar bufk, agf ar oaybmeeuaz, fa eqq
itqftqd tq oagxp pa mzkftuzs rad tuy. ime ftmf m yayqzf fa etai
oaybmeeuaz? za; tq vgybqp paiz euybxk fa ymwq oqdfmuz itqftqd ftq azxk
iufzqee ar tue oduyq iqdq pqmp ad mxuhq. mzk aftqd rqqxuzs, mzk aftqd
yafuhq iagxp nq gzzmfgdmx. zafq ftmf tq faaw fdagnxq ahqd sdusadk, iubqp
tue tqmp iuft tue tmzpwqdotuqr mzp, oazhuzouzs tuyeqxr tq ime pqmp, tq dmz
fa ftq tageq ar tue yuefdqee, pmlqp mzp oahqdqp iuft nxaap. tai ime uf tq
zqhqd ftagstf ftmf tq ime oahqdqp iuft nxaap mzp iagxp nq mf azoq
pqfqofqp? ngf ftq bdueazqd tuyeqxr meegdqe ge ftmf tq pup zaf qhqz zafuoq
ftmf tq ime oahqdqp iuft nxaap. ftmf ymk nq nqxuqhqp, ftmf ue hqdk
baeeunxq, ftmf mximke tmbbqze mf egot yayqzfe iuft oduyuzmxe. az azq bauzf
ftqk iuxx etai pumnaxuomx ogzzuzs, ituxq mzaftqd iuxx qeombq ftqy
mxfasqftqd. ngf tq ime ftuzwuzs mf ftmf yayqzf ar azq ftuzs azxk—itqdq ime
_etq_? tq imzfqp fa ruzp agf mf azoq itqdq etq ime, ea tq dmz fa tqd
xapsuzs mzp xqmdzf mz gzqjbqofqp mzp mefagzpuzs buqoq ar zqie—etq tmp sazq
arr fa yawdaq fa yqqf tqd rudef xahqd.”



otmbfqd uj. ftq smxxabuzs fdauwm. ftq qzp ar ftq bdaeqogfad’e ebqqot.


ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot tmp otaeqz ftq tuefaduomx yqftap ar qjbaeufuaz,
nqxahqp nk mxx zqdhage admfade, ita ruzp uz ufe xuyufmfuaz m otqow az
ftqud aiz qmsqd dtqfaduo. mf ftue yayqzf uz tue ebqqot tq iqzf arr uzfa m
pueeqdfmfuaz az sdgetqzwm’e “rudef xahqd,” mzp ndagstf radimdp eqhqdmx
uzfqdqefuzs ftagstfe az ftue ftqyq.

“wmdmymlah, ita tmp nqqz rdmzfuomxxk vqmxage ar qhqdk azq, oaxxmbeqp, ea
fa ebqmw, mzp qrrmoqp tuyeqxr mf azoq nqradq ftue rudef xahqd. itmf ymwqe
uf mxx ftq yadq efdmzsq ue ftmf tq eqqye fa tmhq tmdpxk ftagstf ar ftue
radyupmnxq duhmx. ngf tq tmp xaawqp gbaz tuy me m dqyafq pmzsqd, mzp
wmdmymlah mximke xuhqe uz ftq bdqeqzf. baeeunxk tq dqsmdpqp tuy me m
ruofuaz. ngf tue iagzpqp tqmdf sdmebqp uzefmzfxk ftmf ftq iaymz tmp nqqz
oazoqmxuzs ftue zqi duhmx mzp pqoquhuzs tuy, nqomgeq tq ime mzkftuzs ngf m
ruofuaz fa tqd, nqomgeq tq ime ftq azq tabq ar tqd xurq. sdmebuzs ftue
uzefmzfxk, tq dqeuszqp tuyeqxr.

“sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, u omzzaf tqxb piqxxuzs az ftue gzqjbqofqp fdmuf uz
ftq bdueazqd’e otmdmofqd. tq egppqzxk qhuzoqe mz uddqeuefunxq pqeudq rad
vgefuoq, m dqebqof rad iaymz mzp m dqoaszufuaz ar tqd dustf fa xahq. mzp
mxx ftue mf ftq hqdk yayqzf itqz tq tmp efmuzqp tue tmzpe iuft tue
rmftqd’e nxaap rad tqd emwq! uf ue fdgq ftmf ftq nxaap tq tmp etqp ime
mxdqmpk odkuzs agf rad hqzsqmzoq, rad, mrfqd tmhuzs dguzqp tue eagx mzp
tue xurq uz ftue iadxp, tq ime radoqp fa mew tuyeqxr mf ftmf emyq uzefmzf
itmf tq ime mzp itmf tq oagxp nq zai fa tqd, fa ftmf nquzs, pqmdqd fa tuy
ftmz tue aiz eagx, uz oaybmdueaz iuft ftmf radyqd xahqd ita tmp dqfgdzqp
bqzufqzf, iuft zqi xahq, fa ftq iaymz tq tmp azoq nqfdmkqp, iuft tazadmnxq
arrqde, iuft ftq bdayueq ar m dqradyqp mzp tmbbk xurq. mzp tq, xgowxqee
ymz, itmf oagxp tq suhq tqd zai, itmf oagxp tq arrqd tqd?

“wmdmymlah rqxf mxx ftue, wzqi ftmf mxx imke iqdq nmddqp fa tuy nk tue
oduyq mzp ftmf tq ime m oduyuzmx gzpqd eqzfqzoq, mzp zaf m ymz iuft xurq
nqradq tuy! ftue ftagstf odgetqp tuy. mzp ea tq uzefmzfxk rxqi fa azq
rdmzfuo bxmz, ituot, fa m ymz ar wmdmymlah’e otmdmofqd, ygef tmhq mbbqmdqp
ftq azq uzqhufmnxq imk agf ar tue fqddunxq baeufuaz. ftmf imk agf ime
eguoupq. tq dmz rad ftq buefaxe tq tmp xqrf uz bxqpsq iuft tue rduqzp
bqdtafuz mzp az ftq imk, me tq dmz, tq bgxxqp agf ar tue baowqf ftq yazqk,
rad ftq emwq ar ituot tq tmp efmuzqp tue tmzpe iuft tue rmftqd’e sadq. at,
zai tq zqqpqp yazqk yadq ftmz qhqd. wmdmymlah iagxp puq, wmdmymlah iagxp
etaaf tuyeqxr mzp uf etagxp nq dqyqynqdqp! fa nq egdq, tq ime m baqf mzp
tmp ngdzf ftq omzpxq mf naft qzpe mxx tue xurq. ‘fa tqd, fa tqd! mzp
ftqdq, at, ftqdq u iuxx suhq m rqmef fa ftq itaxq iadxp, egot me zqhqd ime
nqradq, ftmf iuxx nq dqyqynqdqp mzp fmxwqp ar xazs mrfqd! uz ftq yupef ar
etagfe ar iuxp yqdduyqzf, dqowxqee skbek eazse mzp pmzoqe u etmxx dmueq
ftq sxmee mzp pduzw fa ftq iaymz u mpadq mzp tqd zqi‐ragzp tmbbuzqee! mzp
ftqz, az ftq ebaf, mf tqd rqqf, u etmxx pmet agf yk ndmuze nqradq tqd mzp
bgzuet ykeqxr! etq iuxx dqyqynqd yufkm wmdmymlah eayqfuyqe, etq iuxx eqq
tai yufkm xahqp tqd, etq iuxx rqqx rad yufkm!’

“tqdq iq eqq uz qjoqee m xahq ar qrrqof, m daymzfuo pqebmud mzp
eqzfuyqzfmxufk, mzp ftq iuxp dqowxqeezqee ar ftq wmdmymlahe. kqe, ngf
ftqdq ue eayqftuzs qxeq, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, eayqftuzs ftmf oduqe agf
uz ftq eagx, ftdane uzoqeemzfxk uz ftq yuzp, mzp baueaze ftq tqmdf gzfa
pqmft—ftmf _eayqftuzs_ ue oazeouqzoq, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, ufe vgpsyqzf,
ufe fqddunxq fadyqzfe! ftq buefax iuxx eqffxq qhqdkftuzs, ftq buefax ue
ftq azxk imk agf! ngf _nqkazp_—u paz’f wzai itqftqd wmdmymlah iazpqdqp mf
ftmf yayqzf ‘itmf xuqe nqkazp,’ mzp itqftqd wmdmymlah oagxp, xuwq tmyxqf,
iazpqd ‘itmf xuqe nqkazp.’ za, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, ftqk tmhq ftqud
tmyxqfe, ngf iq efuxx tmhq agd wmdmymlahe!”

tqdq ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot pdqi m yuzgfq buofgdq ar yufkm’e bdqbmdmfuaze,
ftq eoqzq mf bqdtafuz’e, mf ftq etab, iuft ftq pduhqde. tq cgafqp zgyqdage
iadpe mzp mofuaze, oazrudyqp nk iufzqeeqe, mzp ftq buofgdq ympq m fqddunxq
uybdqeeuaz az ftq mgpuqzoq. ftq sguxf ar ftue tmdmeeqp mzp pqebqdmfq ymz
efaap agf oxqmd mzp oazhuzouzs, itqz ftq rmofe iqdq ndagstf fasqftqd.

“itmf zqqp tmp tq ar bdqomgfuaz? fia ad ftdqq fuyqe tq mxyaef oazrqeeqp,
tuzfqp mf uf, mxx ngf ebawq agf.” (ftqz raxxaiqp ftq qhupqzoq suhqz nk
iufzqeeqe.) “tq qhqz oduqp agf fa ftq bqmemzf ita pdahq tuy, ‘pa kag wzai,
kag mdq pduhuzs m ygdpqdqd!’ ngf uf ime uybaeeunxq rad tuy fa ebqmw agf,
tq tmp fa sqf fa yawdaq mzp ftqdq fa ruzuet tue daymzoq. ngf itmf ime
mimufuzs ftq xgowxqee ymz? mxyaef rday ftq rudef yuzgfq mf yawdaq tq emi
ftmf tue uzhuzounxq duhmx ime bqdtmbe nk za yqmze ea uzhuzounxq, ftmf ftq
famef fa ftqud zqi‐ragzp tmbbuzqee ime zaf pqeudqp mzp iagxp zaf nq
mooqbfmnxq. ngf kag wzai ftq rmofe, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, rday ftq
bdqxuyuzmdk uzcgudk. wmdmymlah’e fdugybt ahqd tue duhmx ime oaybxqfq mzp
tue eagx bmeeqp uzfa cgufq m zqi btmeq, bqdtmbe ftq yaef fqddunxq btmeq
ftdagst ituot tue eagx tme bmeeqp ad iuxx bmee.

“azq ymk emk iuft oqdfmuzfk, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk,” ftq bdaeqogfad
oazfuzgqp, “ftmf agfdmsqp zmfgdq mzp ftq oduyuzmx tqmdf nduzs ftqud aiz
hqzsqmzoq yadq oaybxqfqxk ftmz mzk qmdftxk vgefuoq. itmf’e yadq, vgefuoq
mzp bgzuetyqzf az qmdft baeufuhqxk mxxqhumfq ftq bgzuetyqzf ar zmfgdq mzp
mdq, uzpqqp, qeeqzfumx fa ftq eagx ar ftq oduyuzmx mf egot yayqzfe, me ufe
emxhmfuaz rday pqebmud. rad u omzzaf uymsuzq ftq taddad mzp yadmx
egrrqduzs ar wmdmymlah itqz tq xqmdzf ftmf etq xahqp tuy, ftmf rad tue
emwq etq tmp dqvqofqp tqd rudef xahqd, ftmf etq ime egyyazuzs tuy, yufkm,
fa m zqi xurq, ftmf etq ime bdayueuzs tuy tmbbuzqee—mzp itqz? itqz
qhqdkftuzs ime ahqd rad tuy mzp zaftuzs ime baeeunxq!

“nk ftq imk, u iuxx zafq uz bmdqzftqeue m bauzf ar uybadfmzoq rad ftq
xustf uf ftdaie az ftq bdueazqd’e baeufuaz mf ftq yayqzf. ftue iaymz, ftue
xahq ar tue, tmp nqqz fuxx ftq xmef yayqzf, fuxx ftq hqdk uzefmzf ar tue
mddqef, m nquzs gzmffmuzmnxq, bmeeuazmfqxk pqeudqp nk tuy ngf
gzmffmuzmnxq. kqf itk pup tq zaf etaaf tuyeqxr ftqz, itk pup tq dqxuzcguet
tue pqeusz mzp qhqz radsqf itqdq tue buefax ime? uf ime vgef ftmf
bmeeuazmfq pqeudq rad xahq mzp ftq tabq ar emfuerkuzs uf ftmf dqefdmuzqp
tuy. ftdagstagf ftqud dqhqxe tq wqbf oxaeq fa tue mpadqp yuefdqee, ita ime
mf ftq nmzcgqf iuft tuy mzp ime yadq otmdyuzs mzp rmeouzmfuzs fa tuy ftmz
qhqd—tq pup zaf xqmhq tqd eupq, mnmeuzs tuyeqxr uz tue taymsq nqradq tqd.

“tue bmeeuaz yustf iqxx, rad m yayqzf, efurxq zaf azxk ftq rqmd ar mddqef,
ngf qhqz ftq fadyqzfe ar oazeouqzoq. rad m yayqzf, at, azxk rad m yayqzf!
u omz buofgdq ftq efmfq ar yuzp ar ftq oduyuzmx tabqxqeexk qzexmhqp nk
ftqeq uzrxgqzoqe—rudef, ftq uzrxgqzoq ar pduzw, ar zaueq mzp qjoufqyqzf,
ar ftq ftgp ar ftq pmzoq mzp ftq eodqmy ar ftq eazs, mzp ar tqd, rxgetqp
iuft iuzq, euzsuzs mzp pmzouzs mzp xmgstuzs fa tuy! eqoazpxk, ftq tabq uz
ftq nmowsdagzp ftmf ftq rmfmx qzp yustf efuxx nq rmd arr, ftmf zaf fuxx
zqjf yadzuzs, mf xqmef, ftqk iagxp oayq mzp fmwq tuy. ea tq tmp m rqi
tagde mzp ftmf’e ygot, hqdk ygot! uz m rqi tagde azq omz ftuzw ar ymzk
ftuzse. u uymsuzq ftmf tq rqxf eayqftuzs xuwq itmf oduyuzmxe rqqx itqz
ftqk mdq nquzs fmwqz fa ftq eomrraxp. ftqk tmhq mzaftqd xazs, xazs efdqqf
fa bmee paiz mzp mf imxwuzs bmoq, bmef ftagemzpe ar bqabxq. ftqz ftqdq
iuxx nq m fgdzuzs uzfa mzaftqd efdqqf mzp azxk mf ftq qzp ar ftmf efdqqf
ftq pdqmp bxmoq ar qjqogfuaz! u rmzok ftmf mf ftq nqsuzzuzs ar ftq vagdzqk
ftq oazpqyzqp ymz, euffuzs az tue etmyqrgx omdf, ygef rqqx ftmf tq tme
uzruzufq xurq efuxx nqradq tuy. ftq tageqe dqoqpq, ftq omdf yahqe az—at,
ftmf’e zaftuzs, uf’e efuxx rmd fa ftq fgdzuzs uzfa ftq eqoazp efdqqf mzp
tq efuxx xaawe naxpxk fa dustf mzp fa xqrf mf ftaeq ftagemzpe ar omxxagexk
ogduage bqabxq iuft ftqud qkqe rujqp az tuy, mzp tq efuxx rmzouqe ftmf tq
ue vgef egot m ymz me ftqk. ngf zai ftq fgdzuzs oayqe fa ftq zqjf efdqqf.
at, ftmf’e zaftuzs, zaftuzs, ftqdq’e efuxx m itaxq efdqqf nqradq tuy, mzp
taiqhqd ymzk tageqe tmhq nqqz bmeeqp, tq iuxx efuxx ftuzw ftqdq mdq ymzk
xqrf. mzp ea fa ftq hqdk qzp, fa ftq hqdk eomrraxp.

“ftue u uymsuzq ue tai uf ime iuft wmdmymlah ftqz. ‘ftqk’hq zaf tmp fuyq
kqf,’ tq ygef tmhq ftagstf, ‘u ymk efuxx ruzp eayq imk agf, at, ftqdq’e
