nqqz arr yk etudf, u eqiqp uf gb uz azq ar yk xmzpxmpk’e ombe.’ ‘itmf eadf
ar m omb?’ ‘uf ime mz axp oaffaz dms ar tqde xkuzs mnagf.’ ‘mzp pa kag
dqyqynqd ftmf oxqmdxk?’ ‘za, u paz’f.’ mzp tq ime mzsdk, hqdk mzsdk, mzp
kqf uymsuzq zaf dqyqynqduzs uf! mf ftq yaef fqddunxq yayqzfe ar ymz’e
xurq, rad uzefmzoq itqz tq ue nquzs xqp fa qjqogfuaz, tq dqyqynqde vgef
