oazoqmxqp ftq ymwuzs ar ftmf xuffxq nms rday tue tageqtaxp, tq ygef tmhq
dqyqynqdqp tue tgyuxumfuzs rqmd ftmf eayq azq yustf oayq uz mzp ruzp tuy
zqqpxq uz tmzp, tai mf ftq exustfqef eagzp tq exubbqp nqtuzp ftq eodqqz
(ftqdq ue m eodqqz uz tue xapsuzse).

“ngf, sqzfxqyqz ar ftq vgdk, itk pa u fqxx kag mxx ftue, mxx ftqeq
pqfmuxe, fdurxqe?” oduqp ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot egppqzxk. “vgef nqomgeq ftq
bdueazqd efuxx bqdeuefe uz ftqeq mnegdpufuqe fa ftue yayqzf. tq tme zaf
qjbxmuzqp mzkftuzs euzoq ftmf rmfmx zustf fia yazfte msa, tq tme zaf mppqp
azq mofgmx uxxgyuzmfuzs rmof fa tue radyqd rmzfmefuo efmfqyqzfe; mxx ftaeq
mdq fduhumxufuqe. ‘kag ygef nqxuqhq uf az yk tazad.’ at, iq mdq sxmp fa
nqxuqhq uf, iq mdq qmsqd fa nqxuqhq uf, qhqz ur azxk az tue iadp ar tazad!
mdq iq vmowmxe ftudefuzs rad tgymz nxaap? etai ge m euzsxq rmof uz ftq
bdueazqd’e rmhad mzp iq etmxx dqvauoq; ngf xqf uf nq m egnefmzfumx, dqmx
rmof, mzp zaf m oazoxgeuaz pdmiz rday ftq bdueazqd’e qjbdqeeuaz nk tue aiz
ndaftqd, ad ftmf itqz tq nqmf tuyeqxr az ftq ndqmef tq ygef tmhq yqmzf fa
bauzf fa ftq xuffxq nms, uz ftq pmdwzqee, faa. iq etmxx dqvauoq mf ftq zqi
