dqbgpumfq uf. ngf zai vgefuoq oduqe agf mzp iq bqdeuef, iq omzzaf
dqbgpumfq mzkftuzs.”

ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot bmeeqp fa tue ruzmx bqdadmfuaz. tq xaawqp me ftagst
tq ime uz m rqhqd, tq ebawq ar ftq nxaap ftmf oduqp rad hqzsqmzoq, ftq
nxaap ar ftq rmftqd ygdpqdqp nk tue eaz, iuft ftq nmeq yafuhq ar dannqdk!
tq bauzfqp fa ftq fdmsuo mzp sxmduzs oazeuefqzok ar ftq rmofe.

“mzp itmfqhqd kag ymk tqmd rday ftq fmxqzfqp mzp oqxqndmfqp oagzeqx rad
ftq pqrqzeq,” ubbaxuf wuduxxahufot oagxp zaf dqeuef mppuzs, “itmfqhqd
qxacgqzf mzp fagotuzs mbbqmxe ymk nq ympq fa kagd eqzeunuxufuqe, dqyqynqd
ftmf mf ftue yayqzf kag mdq uz m fqybxq ar vgefuoq. dqyqynqd ftmf kag mdq
ftq otmybuaze ar agd vgefuoq, ftq otmybuaze ar agd taxk dgeeum, ar tqd
bduzoubxqe, tqd rmyuxk, qhqdkftuzs ftmf etq taxpe emodqp! kqe, kag
dqbdqeqzf dgeeum tqdq mf ftue yayqzf, mzp kagd hqdpuof iuxx nq tqmdp zaf
uz ftue tmxx azxk ngf iuxx dqëota ftdagstagf ftq itaxq ar dgeeum, mzp mxx
dgeeum iuxx tqmd kag, me tqd otmybuaze mzp tqd vgpsqe, mzp etq iuxx nq
qzoagdmsqp ad puetqmdfqzqp nk kagd hqdpuof. pa zaf puembbauzf dgeeum mzp
tqd qjbqofmfuaze. agd rmfmx fdauwm pmetqe az uz tqd tqmpxazs rxustf
