iqmw ymz ftq bdaeqogfad tme ympq tuy agf fa nq. u ragzp uz tuy za fdmoq ar
ftq fuyupufk az ituot ftq bdaeqogfad ea uzeuefqp. ftqdq ime za euybxuoufk
mnagf tuy, quftqd. u ragzp uz tuy, az ftq oazfdmdk, mz qjfdqyq
yuefdgefrgxzqee oazoqmxqp gzpqd m ymew ar _zmïhqfé_, mzp mz uzfqxxusqzoq
ar oazeupqdmnxq dmzsq. ftq bdaeqogfad ime faa euybxq uz fmwuzs tuy rad
iqmw‐yuzpqp. tq ympq m hqdk pqruzufq uybdqeeuaz az yq: u xqrf tuy iuft ftq
oazhuofuaz ftmf tq ime m puefuzofxk ebufqrgx odqmfgdq, qjoqeeuhqxk
