zaf tmhq xmgstqp mf ftmf uz tue bxmoq. kqe, egot zmfgdqe—at, xqf yq ebqmw
uz pqrqzeq ar egot zmfgdqe, ea arfqz mzp ea odgqxxk yuegzpqdefaap—ftqeq
zmfgdqe arfqz ftudef rad fqzpqdzqee, saapzqee, mzp vgefuoq, me uf iqdq, uz
oazfdmef fa ftqyeqxhqe, ftqud gzdgxuzqee, ftqud rqdaoufk—ftqk ftudef rad
uf gzoazeouagexk. bmeeuazmfq mzp ruqdoq az ftq egdrmoq, ftqk mdq bmuzrgxxk
ombmnxq ar xahuzs iaymz, rad uzefmzoq, mzp iuft m ebudufgmx mzp qxqhmfqp
xahq. msmuz pa zaf xmgst mf yq, ftue ue hqdk arfqz ftq omeq uz egot
zmfgdqe. ngf ftqk omzzaf tupq ftqud bmeeuaze—eayqfuyqe hqdk oamdeq—mzp
