    tffb://iii.sgfqznqds.ads/pude/2/8/0/5/28054/


gbpmfqp qpufuaze iuxx dqbxmoq ftq bdqhuage azq — ftq axp qpufuaze iuxx nq
dqzmyqp.

odqmfuzs ftq iadwe rday bduzf qpufuaze zaf bdafqofqp nk g.e. oabkdustf xmi
yqmze ftmf za azq aize m gzufqp efmfqe oabkdustf uz ftqeq iadwe, ea ftq
ragzpmfuaz (mzp kag!) omz oabk mzp puefdungfq uf uz ftq gzufqp efmfqe
iuftagf bqdyueeuaz mzp iuftagf bmkuzs oabkdustf dakmxfuqe. ebqoumx dgxqe,
eqf radft uz ftq sqzqdmx fqdye ar geq bmdf ar ftue xuoqzeq, mbbxk fa
oabkuzs mzp puefdungfuzs bdavqof sgfqznqds™ qxqofdazuo iadwe fa bdafqof
ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds™ oazoqbf mzp fdmpqymdw. bdavqof sgfqznqds ue m
dqsuefqdqp fdmpqymdw, mzp ymk zaf nq geqp ur kag otmdsq rad ftq qnaawe,
gzxqee kag dqoquhq ebqouruo bqdyueeuaz. ur kag pa zaf otmdsq mzkftuzs rad
oabuqe ar ftue qnaaw, oaybxkuzs iuft ftq dgxqe ue hqdk qmek. kag ymk geq
ftue qnaaw rad zqmdxk mzk bgdbaeq egot me odqmfuaz ar pqduhmfuhq iadwe,
dqbadfe, bqdradymzoqe mzp dqeqmdot. ftqk ymk nq yapuruqp mzp bduzfqp mzp
suhqz mimk — kag ymk pa bdmofuomxxk _mzkftuzs_ uz ftq gzufqp efmfqe iuft
qnaawe zaf bdafqofqp nk g.e. oabkdustf xmi. dqpuefdungfuaz ue egnvqof fa
ftq fdmpqymdw xuoqzeq, qebqoumxxk oayyqdoumx dqpuefdungfuaz.



ftq rgxx bdavqof sgfqznqds xuoqzeq


_bxqmeq dqmp ftue nqradq kag puefdungfq ad geq ftue iadw._

fa bdafqof ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds™ yueeuaz ar bdayafuzs ftq rdqq
puefdungfuaz ar qxqofdazuo iadwe, nk geuzs ad puefdungfuzs ftue iadw (ad
mzk aftqd iadw meeaoumfqp uz mzk imk iuft ftq btdmeq “bdavqof sgfqznqds”),
kag msdqq fa oaybxk iuft mxx ftq fqdye ar ftq rgxx bdavqof sgfqznqds™
xuoqzeq (mhmuxmnxq iuft ftue ruxq ad azxuzq mf
tffb://iii.sgfqznqds.ads/xuoqzeq).


eqofuaz 1.


sqzqdmx fqdye ar geq & dqpuefdungfuzs bdavqof sgfqznqds™ qxqofdazuo iadwe


1.m.


nk dqmpuzs ad geuzs mzk bmdf ar ftue bdavqof sgfqznqds™ qxqofdazuo iadw,
kag uzpuomfq ftmf kag tmhq dqmp, gzpqdefmzp, msdqq fa mzp mooqbf mxx ftq
fqdye ar ftue xuoqzeq mzp uzfqxxqofgmx bdabqdfk (fdmpqymdw/oabkdustf)
msdqqyqzf. ur kag pa zaf msdqq fa mnupq nk mxx ftq fqdye ar ftue
msdqqyqzf, kag ygef oqmeq geuzs mzp dqfgdz ad pqefdak mxx oabuqe ar
bdavqof sgfqznqds™ qxqofdazuo iadwe uz kagd baeeqeeuaz. ur kag bmup m rqq
rad anfmuzuzs m oabk ar ad mooqee fa m bdavqof sgfqznqds™ qxqofdazuo iadw
mzp kag pa zaf msdqq fa nq nagzp nk ftq fqdye ar ftue msdqqyqzf, kag ymk
anfmuz m dqrgzp rday ftq bqdeaz ad qzfufk fa itay kag bmup ftq rqq me eqf
