1.r.2.


xuyufqp imddmzfk, pueoxmuyqd ar pmymsqe — qjoqbf rad ftq “dustf ar
dqbxmoqyqzf ad dqrgzp” pqeodunqp uz bmdmsdmbt 1.r.3, ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds
