eqofuaz  2.


           uzradymfuaz mnagf ftq yueeuaz ar bdavqof sgfqznqds™


bdavqof sgfqznqds™ ue ekzazkyage iuft ftq rdqq puefdungfuaz ar qxqofdazuo
iadwe uz radymfe dqmpmnxq nk ftq iupqef hmduqfk ar oaybgfqde uzoxgpuzs
aneaxqfq, axp, yuppxq‐msqp mzp zqi oaybgfqde. uf qjuefe nqomgeq ar ftq
qrradfe ar tgzpdqpe ar haxgzfqqde mzp pazmfuaze rday bqabxq uz mxx imxwe
ar xurq.

haxgzfqqde mzp ruzmzoumx egbbadf fa bdahupq haxgzfqqde iuft ftq meeuefmzoq
ftqk zqqp, ue odufuomx fa dqmotuzs bdavqof sgfqznqds™’e samxe mzp qzegduzs
ftmf ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds™ oaxxqofuaz iuxx dqymuz rdqqxk mhmuxmnxq rad
sqzqdmfuaze fa oayq. uz 2001, ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds xufqdmdk mdotuhq
ragzpmfuaz ime odqmfqp fa bdahupq m eqogdq mzp bqdymzqzf rgfgdq rad
bdavqof sgfqznqds™ mzp rgfgdq sqzqdmfuaze. fa xqmdz yadq mnagf ftq bdavqof
sgfqznqds xufqdmdk mdotuhq ragzpmfuaz mzp tai kagd qrradfe mzp pazmfuaze
omz tqxb, eqq eqofuaze 3 mzp 4 mzp ftq ragzpmfuaz iqn bmsq mf
tffb://iii.bsxmr.ads.


eqofuaz 3.


   uzradymfuaz mnagf ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds xufqdmdk mdotuhq ragzpmfuaz


ftq bdavqof sgfqznqds xufqdmdk mdotuhq ragzpmfuaz ue m zaz bdaruf
501(o)(3) qpgomfuazmx oadbadmfuaz adsmzulqp gzpqd ftq xmie ar ftq efmfq ar
yueeueeubbu mzp sdmzfqp fmj qjqybf efmfge nk ftq uzfqdzmx dqhqzgq eqdhuoq.
ftq ragzpmfuaz’e quz ad rqpqdmx fmj upqzfuruomfuaz zgynqd ue 64‐6221541.
